NK064(ngu),002:1: // dpal gsang bdag dgongs rgyan gyi spyi don yan gyi
NK064(ngu),002:2: bshad pa'i zin bris bla ma'i man ngag rin chen
NK064(ngu),002:3: phreng ba zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK064(ngu),002:6: dpal gsang bdag dgongs rgyan gyi spyi don yan gyi
NK064(ngu),002:7: bshad pa'i zin bris bla ma'i man ngag rin chen
NK064(ngu),002:9: bla ma dang dpal kun tu bzang po dbyer ma mchis pa'i zhabs la gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK064(ngu),002:10: sems kyi chos nyid ye nas rang bzhin rnam dag gdod ma'i mgon po gzhi yi rgyud //
NK064(ngu),002:11: rtogs goms byed rtsol dang bcas rmad byung thabs dang grol ba shes thob lam gyi rgyud //
NK064(ngu),002:12: glo bur dri ma las grol bral thob yon tan bla na med gang 'bras bu'i rgyud //
NK064(ngu),002:13: rgyud gsum ngo bo srid zhi kun khyab rang byung ye shes kun tu bzang por 'dud //
NK064(ngu),002:14: dgongs pa brda dang snyan du brgyud pa yi //
NK064(ngu),002:15: bshes gnyen rim par byon pa'i tshogs kun la //
NK064(ngu),002:16: mos dang lhag bsam rnam par dag pa yi //
NK064(ngu),002:17: dad pa'i dbyangs kyis gus pas 'dir bstod do //
NK064(ngu),002:18: khyad par rgyal kun thugs rje'i mtsho las ngo mtshor rgyal ba'i nyi ma ni //
NK064(ngu),002:19: phan bde'i pad+mo kun dgar rgyas byed phrin las 'od stong 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:20: srid zhi'i mun sel gter chen bla ma 'gyur meda rdo rje nyin mor byed //
NK064(ngu),002:21: gdul bya'i mkha' la 'char nub bral khyod mi 'bral spyi bo'i gtsug tu mchod //
NK064(ngu),002:22: gang gi ye shes sgyu ma'i rnam rol ngaga tshig kun la dabnga 'byor ba //
NK064(ngu),002:23: ji lta ji snyed shes bya'i chosa rnams yongs gzigs legs bshad smra ba'i dapala //
NK064(ngu),002:24: dam pa rnam gnyis mthong thos dran reg 'gro ba'i 'dren pa bla na med //
NK064(ngu),002:25: spyi gtsug 'khor lo'i rgyan du mi 'bral brtse bas 'gro kun bu bzhin skyongs //
NK064(ngu),002:26: tshul bzhin bsnyen las dam chos gad+g+aa'i rgyun //
NK064(ngu),002:27: bla ma'i zhal gyi 'bab stegs las 'ongs pa //
NK064(ngu),002:28: rna ba'i bum par thig pa tsam 'khyil ba //
NK064(ngu),002:29: myong ba 'dis ni skal ba bzang por byas //
NK064(ngu),002:30: de phyir rgyud don ji bzhin rtogs min kyang //
NK064(ngu),002:31: 'di don 'chad dang rtsod dang rtsom sogs la //
NK064(ngu),002:32: dgyes pa'i 'dzum mdangs legs skyes dbugs dbyung sogs //
NK064(ngu),002:33: bka' drin dran pas mchod pa'i rdzas su spro //
NK064(ngu),002:34: 'on kyang bla ma'i gsung bshad gang //
NK064(ngu),002:35: ji bzhin zin thor 'god pa las //
NK064(ngu),002:36: blun pos don gzhan ji ltar spobs //
NK064(ngu),002:37: des na gus pas brjod par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:39: thog mar slob bu'i rgyud kyi sdig sgrib sbyong ba'i phyir du /
NK064(ngu),002:40: so so rang rang gi dbu gtsug tu pam las
NK064(ngu),002:41: pad+ma dang a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng
NK064(ngu),002:42: du ngo bo drin can rtsa ba'i bla ma la
NK064(ngu),002:43: rnam pa dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i rnam par gsal
NK064(ngu),002:44: ba'i thugs kar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du
NK064(ngu),002:45: yi ge brgya pa'i sngags phreng gsal btab ste /
NK064(ngu),002:46: yig brgya gsol 'debs kyi tshul du bzlas pas thugs
NK064(ngu),002:47: ka'i sngags phreng dang sku'i cha thams cad las bdud
NK064(ngu),002:48: rtsi dkar po'i rgyun skya chil chil babs pas nad
NK064(ngu),002:49: gdon sdig sgrub thams cad sangs kyis dag /
NK064(ngu),002:50: sku gsung thugs ye shes rdo rje'i dbang bzhi rdzogs
NK064(ngu),002:51: su thob pa'i thugs mos gnang bar zhu gsungs te
NK064(ngu),002:52: / lhan cig tu yig brgya tshar bdun re song ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:53: spyi bo'i bla ma rdo rje sems dpa' 'od du
NK064(ngu),002:54: zhu ste so so rang rang la thim par gyur
NK064(ngu),002:55: gsungs / de nas slob ma rin 'byung yab yum
NK064(ngu),002:56: gyi ngo bor bskyed bstim 'od zhus nyan dbang dang
NK064(ngu),002:57: gsungs / / slob dpon rang nyid snang ba mtha'
NK064(ngu),002:58: yas kyi ngo bo bskyed bstim 'od zhus 'chad pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:59: dbang bzhes te sangs rgyas thams cad kyi gsung rdo
NK064(ngu),002:61: gang dag rab 'byams phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten na //
NK064(ngu),002:62: bder gshegs slob mar gyur pa gang su dag /
NK064(ngu),002:63: deng 'dir ston pas chos kyi char 'bebs kyi //
NK064(ngu),002:64: mnyan par 'dod pa thams cad 'dir gshegs shig /
NK064(ngu),002:66: de nas las kyi slob dpon gyis man+dala phul nas /
NK064(ngu),002:67: de yang rna rgyud lung gi phreng ba las /
NK064(ngu),002:68: rgyal ba rnams ni 'jig rten 'byon pa'i tshe //
NK064(ngu),002:69: de yis gsungs pa'i lung chen rnams la ni //
NK064(ngu),002:70: phyi rol rgol ba ngan pa byung srid kyi //
NK064(ngu),002:71: dang por srid pa chos kyi lo rgyus smros //
NK064(ngu),002:73: rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po 'di nyid kyi lo rgyus cung zad brjod pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK064(ngu),002:74: dang po ston pas gsungs tshul dang /
NK064(ngu),002:75: de las ji ltar brgyud tshul gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:77: 'di las bzhed tshul mi 'dra ba 'ga' zhig snang ste /
NK064(ngu),002:78: slob dpon nyi 'od seng ges ni /
NK064(ngu),002:79: 'og min du longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skus gsang sngags kyi chos gsungs pa'i tshe /
NK064(ngu),002:80: de dang dus mtshungs par mi yul du mchog gi
NK064(ngu),002:81: sprul skus rdo rje gdan du 'tshang rgya tshul ma
NK064(ngu),002:82: bstan pa'i gong du gsungs pa yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:83: zhes gsungs te nyi 'od seng ge'i rgya cher 'grel du de ltar bshad /
NK064(ngu),002:84: yang slob dpon sgeg pa rdo rjes ni /
NK064(ngu),002:85: mchog gi sprul skus mi yul du thun mong gi
NK064(ngu),002:86: theg pa bshad pa dang dus mtshungs par ston pas
NK064(ngu),002:87: 'og min du gsungs par bzhed de /
NK064(ngu),002:88: des mdzad pa'i 'grel pa spar khab tu de ltar bshad pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:89: don la de gnyis kyang dgongs pa'i gnad gcig pas 'gal ba med kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:90: sngon gyi zur pa rnams kyis spar khab kyi lugs
NK064(ngu),002:91: ltar mdzad pas 'dir yang de ltar bzhed pa yin
NK064(ngu),002:92: / don la de gnyis 'gal med du 'chad thub ste /
NK064(ngu),002:93: gdul bya'i mthong snang gi dbang gis rgyud gzhung gcig
NK064(ngu),002:94: gleng gzhi bshad tshul tha dad pa gzhan las kyang
NK064(ngu),002:95: 'byung ste / 'jam dpal sgyu d+r+wa'i bshad rgyud las /
NK064(ngu),002:96: gleng gzhi rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK064(ngu),002:97: 'og min gnas dang ri rab rtse //
NK064(ngu),002:99: byang chub sems dang lha rnams dang //
NK064(ngu),002:100: mi rnams kyi ni don du gsungs //
NK064(ngu),002:101: ston pa yang ni rnam gsum ste //
NK064(ngu),002:102: sangs rgyas rdo rje 'chang chen dang //
NK064(ngu),002:103: sprul sku 'khor los sgyur ba dang //
NK064(ngu),002:104: sh+aakya thub pa nyid kyis gsungs //
NK064(ngu),002:105: dus ni gdul bya 'dul ba'i dus //
NK064(ngu),002:108: gnyis pa de las ji ltar brgyud tshul ni /
NK064(ngu),002:110: rgyal ba sems dpa' rnal 'byor pa //
NK064(ngu),002:111: dgongs pa rig pa rna bar brgyud //
NK064(ngu),002:115: gang zag snyan brgyud dang gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:117: rgyal ba kun tu bzang pos 'og min bde ba
NK064(ngu),002:118: chen po'i gnas su nyid las mi gzhan pa'i 'khor
NK064(ngu),002:119: rgyal ba rigs lnga la chos 'od gsal gyi dgongs
NK064(ngu),002:120: pa zang thal du gsungs pa ni rgyal ba dgongs
NK064(ngu),002:121: pas brgyud pa / rig 'dzin brdas brgyud pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:122: rgyal ba rigs lngas rgyal sras sems dpa' sogs la
NK064(ngu),002:123: brjod med rig pa'i gsung dbyangs kyi brdas go bar
NK064(ngu),002:124: mdzad pa ni rig 'dzin brda brgyud /
NK064(ngu),002:125: gang zag snyan khung du brgyud pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:126: rgyal sras sems dpa'i 'khor rnams kyi nang nas rigs
NK064(ngu),002:127: gsum gyis gdul bya rang rang gi skal ba dang
NK064(ngu),002:129: 'jam dpal gyis lha'i gnas su lha grags ldan phyogs
NK064(ngu),002:130: skyong la bshad de lha'i rig 'dzin rnams la dar
NK064(ngu),002:131: bar mdzad / spyan ras gzigs kyis klu'i gnas su
NK064(ngu),002:132: klu rgyal mgrin pa nag po la bshad de dar
NK064(ngu),002:133: bar mdzad / / phyag na rdo rjes gnod sbyin
NK064(ngu),002:134: gyi gnas su gnod sbyin kun tu bzang po la
NK064(ngu),002:135: bshad de dar bar byas pa ni gang zag snyan
NK064(ngu),002:137: de'i dus su ston pas las can gyi gdul bya
NK064(ngu),002:138: dag pa la gsang sngags kyi theg pa gsungs nas
NK064(ngu),002:139: / lha klu mi'i 'jig rten du gsang thabs kyis spyod pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:140: gsang sngags kyi sgra yongs su ma grags te 'di la dgongs nas /
NK064(ngu),002:142: nges pa'i theg pa yongs ma gsungs //
NK064(ngu),002:144: des na re zhig rdo rje'i theg pas 'dul ba'i dus la ma babs pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:145: rigs can lnga dang rgyal po zla bzang sogs la gsungs nas /
NK064(ngu),002:146: 'jig rten du gsang sngags kyi sgra yongs su ma grags pa phyis 'byung bar lung bstan te /
NK064(ngu),002:147: sdom 'byung gi rgyud phyi ma las /
NK064(ngu),002:148: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK064(ngu),002:149: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK064(ngu),002:150: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK064(ngu),002:151: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK064(ngu),002:152: 'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK064(ngu),002:153: rgyal po dzahzhesa bya ba la //
NK064(ngu),002:154: bsod nams chen po'i mthus snang ba'i //
NK064(ngu),002:155: gsang ba'i bdag pos gnang bar 'gyur //
NK064(ngu),002:156: zhes gsungs pa dang mthun par ston pa mya ngan
NK064(ngu),002:157: las 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad 'das pa
NK064(ngu),002:158: na / dam pa'i rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga nang
NK064(ngu),002:159: du yang dag 'jog la gnas pa rang rang gi
NK064(ngu),002:160: mngon par shes pas mkhyen nas /
NK064(ngu),002:161: ri ma la ya gnas lcags yod pa'i rtser rdzu
NK064(ngu),002:162: 'phrul gyi bya bas 'dus nas phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas
NK064(ngu),002:163: thams cad yid la byas te /
NK064(ngu),002:164: kye ma kyi hud kye ma blong //
NK064(ngu),002:165: ston pa sgron me'i 'od nub na //
NK064(ngu),002:166: 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel //
NK064(ngu),002:167: zhes sogs gdung tshig nyi shu rtsa gsum bton pas /
NK064(ngu),002:168: ston pa rigs drug pa kun tu bzang po nyid
NK064(ngu),002:169: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje'i rnam par
NK064(ngu),002:170: bstan nas / sngar 'og min du gsungs pa nyid slar yang bzlas te gsung bar dgongs te /
NK064(ngu),002:172: sems kyi dkyil 'khor me long bzhin //
NK064(ngu),002:173: bstan pa de ltar bdag gis kyang //
NK064(ngu),002:174: thog ma tha ma med pa ru //
NK064(ngu),002:175: bdag gi dam bca' mi 'dor bas //
NK064(ngu),002:176: bskul ba'i dus ni gang byung ba //
NK064(ngu),002:177: bdag kyang de bzhin cho 'phrul snang //
NK064(ngu),002:178: zhes rmad du byung ba'i cho 'phrul gyis ri ma la ya'i rtser gshegs te /
NK064(ngu),002:179: rigs can dra ma lnga dang rig 'dzin phal mo
NK064(ngu),002:180: che'i 'khor gyi dbus su gsang bdag lag na rdo
NK064(ngu),002:181: rje'i sku'i rnam par bstan nas /
NK064(ngu),002:184: sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lha gnas rnams su grags
NK064(ngu),002:185: pa'i gsang ba'i theg pa nyid ston par mdzad cing
NK064(ngu),002:186: / de rnams srin po blo gros thabs ldan gyis
NK064(ngu),002:187: gser gyi glegs bam la bee d+aur+ya'i zhun mas bris
NK064(ngu),002:188: nas dgongs pa'i rtsal bdun gyis nam mkha' la sbas
NK064(ngu),002:189: / so // de'i tshe de'i byin rlabs kyis sa
NK064(ngu),002:190: ho ra'i rgyal po dzahl rmi ltas ngo mtshar ba
NK064(ngu),002:191: / so // bdun rmis te / ji skad du /
NK064(ngu),002:192: sku gsung thugs rtags thim pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:193: rin chen glegs bam babs pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:194: chos kyi bgro ba byas pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:195: kun gyi dam par bsgrags pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:196: mchod pa chen po byas pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:197: rin chen char pa babs pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:198: sangs rgyas sa la lung bstan pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:199: zhes pa'i rmi ltas dang mthun par rgyud sde'i glegs bam rnams mi yul du dngos su babs te /
NK064(ngu),002:200: kri ya'i rgyud rnams w+aa ra n+aa s+ai dang /
NK064(ngu),002:201: u pa ya'i rgyud rnams ri bo bya rkang can dang bsil ba'i tshal du babs /
NK064(ngu),002:202: yo ga'i rgyud rnams dur khrod me ri 'bar ba'i rtse mor babs /
NK064(ngu),002:203: ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud rnams za hor gyi yul
NK064(ngu),002:204: rgyal po dzah'i khang steng du tan+t+ra chen po sde
NK064(ngu),002:206: a nu yo ga'i rgyud rnams sing+ga la'i gling du glegs bam dang bcas te babs /
NK064(ngu),002:207: a ti yo ga rnams ni nub phyogs oo d+ai
NK064(ngu),002:208: ya na'i yul du slob dpon chen po dga' rab
NK064(ngu),002:209: rdo rjes dpal rdo rje sems dpa' las dngos su
NK064(ngu),002:210: gsan nas glegs bam la bkod par mdzad do //
NK064(ngu),002:211: de ltar tan+t+ra chen po sde bco brgyad po rgyal po dzahs slob dpon ku ku r+aa dza la /
NK064(ngu),002:212: des seng ha r+aa dza la /
NK064(ngu),002:213: des u pa r+aa dza la /
NK064(ngu),002:214: des sras mo go ma de wi la /
NK064(ngu),002:215: des sgeg pa rdo rje dang sangs rgyas gsang ba gnyis la /
NK064(ngu),002:216: de gnyis kyis pan chen bi ma mi tra la /
NK064(ngu),002:217: des bod du lo ts+aa ba rma rin chen mchog dang /
NK064(ngu),002:218: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra gnyis la /
NK064(ngu),002:219: rma rin chen mchog gis gtsug ru rin chen gzhon nu dang gye re phyogs skyong gnyis la /
NK064(ngu),002:220: de gnyis kas dar rje dpal gyi grags pa dang zhang rgyal ba'i yon tan gnyis la bshad /
NK064(ngu),002:221: zhang gis gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes la bshad pa ste bka' srol gcig go //
NK064(ngu),002:222: yang slob dpon pad+ma dang bi ma la gnyis kas gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra la /
NK064(ngu),002:223: des sog po dpal gyi ye shes la /
NK064(ngu),002:224: des gnubs chen la bshad pa ste bka' srol gcig go //
NK064(ngu),002:225: yang rma gnyags thun mong gi slob ma khu byang chub 'od nas /
NK064(ngu),002:226: mkhas pa gtsug gyer rnam gnyis la brgyud de gnubs la bshad pas bka' srol gcig go //
NK064(ngu),002:227: de ltar na gnubs la brgyud pa'i bka' srol gyi chu bo thams cad 'dus shing /
NK064(ngu),002:228: de la thugs zin gyi sras bzhi /
NK064(ngu),002:229: sras kyi dam pa gcig dang lnga byung bar grags /
NK064(ngu),002:230: sras kyi dam pa gnubs yon tan rgya mtshos sras ye shes rgya mtsho la /
NK064(ngu),002:231: des so ye shes dbang phyug la /
NK064(ngu),002:232: des nyang shes rab mchog la /
NK064(ngu),002:233: des nyang ye shes 'byung gnas la /
NK064(ngu),002:234: des lha rje zur po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas la /
NK064(ngu),002:235: de la slob ma rtse mo bzhi dang /
NK064(ngu),002:237: sgom chen brgya rtsa brgyad la sogs pa byung /
NK064(ngu),002:238: zur sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyis zur chung shes rab grags pa la /
NK064(ngu),002:239: de la slob ma ka ba bzhi /
NK064(ngu),002:242: dral ma sum cu so gnyis /
NK064(ngu),002:243: yus po che mi gnyis la sogs pa mang du byung /
NK064(ngu),002:244: lha rje zur chung gis rang gi sras gsang bdag sgro phug pa chen po sh+aakya seng ge la /
NK064(ngu),002:245: de la gdugs thogs kyi slob ma grwa sa 'dzin pa stong dang /
NK064(ngu),002:246: de'i nang nas kyang thugs zin gyi slob ma bzhi gsum bcu gnyis la sogs pa byung bar grags /
NK064(ngu),002:247: de nas zur gyi rigs las rim par brgyud pa'i mthar /
NK064(ngu),002:248: zur chen bkra shis kun dgas gnyos ston gsang bdag phrin las lhun grub la stsal /
NK064(ngu),002:249: des gter chen chos kyi rgyal po gter bdag gling pa la /
NK064(ngu),002:250: des mkhan chen d+har+m+aa sh+ri la brgyud pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:251: de ltar gong 'og gi babs so de dag gi
NK064(ngu),002:252: nang nas ma h+aa yo ga'i theg pa la tan+t+ra
NK064(ngu),002:253: chen po sde bco brgyad du yod pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:254: de'i grangs la bzhed pa mi mthun pa mang yang /
NK064(ngu),002:255: gter chen bla ma'i dgongs pa la sku gsung thugs
NK064(ngu),002:256: yon tan phrin las lnga'i gzhi dang rtsa bar gyur
NK064(ngu),002:257: pa'i rgyud sde chen po lnga /
NK064(ngu),002:258: sgrub pa lag len du ston pa rol pa'i rgyud sde lnga /
NK064(ngu),002:259: spyod pa'i yan lag tu 'gro ba'i rgyud sde lnga /
NK064(ngu),002:260: ma tshang ba kha skong bar byed pa'i rgyud phyi ma lta bu gnyis /
NK064(ngu),002:261: de thams cad kyi bsdus don lta bu'i rgyud sde chen po gcig dang bco brgyad do //
NK064(ngu),002:262: thams cad kyi bsdus don lta bu'i rgyud ni /
NK064(ngu),002:263: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba dpal gsang
NK064(ngu),002:264: ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i rgyud
NK064(ngu),002:265: kyi rgyal po chen po 'di nyid yin la /
NK064(ngu),002:266: de ni bshad bya'i chos ngos bzung ba de yin /
NK064(ngu),002:267: de gang gis 'chad na zhes pa ni 'chad byed kyi chos te /
NK064(ngu),002:268: de ni bshad pa'i rgyud rnams dang /
NK064(ngu),002:269: bla ma dam pa rnams kyis don la rton pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:270: dgongs 'grel mdzad pa de dag la brten nas so
NK064(ngu),002:271: // zhes pas bshad pa'i rgyud rnams dang zhes pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:272: 'di dag la snga rabs pa dag gis dgongs pa mi mthun pa mang yang /
NK064(ngu),002:273: zur lugs la sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad /
NK064(ngu),002:274: bshad rgyud sde bzhi zhes bshad pas sde brgyad ni /
NK064(ngu),002:275: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang snang dbyer med
NK064(ngu),002:276: du ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK064(ngu),002:277: ba / las tshogs rgyas par ston pa rnam par snang mdzad sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba /
NK064(ngu),002:278: sde snod yongs la khyab par ston pa 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba /
NK064(ngu),002:279: dkyil 'khor rgyas par ston pa sgyu 'phrul brgyad pa /
NK064(ngu),002:280: phrin las rdzogs par ston pa bzhi bcu pa /
NK064(ngu),002:281: dbang gtso bor ston pa bla ma /
NK064(ngu),002:282: yon tan mthar phyin par ston pa brgyad cu pa /
NK064(ngu),002:283: dam tshig mchog tu ston pa le lag dang brgyad do //
NK064(ngu),002:284: skabs don 'chad byed kyi chos ni bshad rgyud sde bzhi ste /
NK064(ngu),002:285: rgyud 'di'i bshad bya'i gtso bo la /
NK064(ngu),002:287: grol lam rim cig car du ston pa sgyu 'phrul ye shes snying po dang /
NK064(ngu),002:289: thabs lam rim cig car du ston pa sgyu 'phrul rgya mtsho dang /
NK064(ngu),002:291: bshad rgyud sde bzhi'i lung tshad ma dang /
NK064(ngu),002:292: bla ma dam pa rnams kyis don la rton pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:293: dgongs 'grel zhes pas rgyud sde de dag gi dgongs
NK064(ngu),002:294: 'grel gyi man ngag ste rgya bod kyi mkhas grub
NK064(ngu),002:295: rnams kyis mdzad pa'i man ngag tshad ma dang /
NK064(ngu),002:296: de gnyis dang rjes su mthun pa'i rig pa tshad
NK064(ngu),002:297: ma gsum gyis gtan la phab pas rgyud don phyin
NK064(ngu),002:298: ci ma log par rtogs par 'gyur te /
NK064(ngu),002:300: lung dang rig pa man ngag gi //
NK064(ngu),002:301: tshad ma dag gis gang gzhal bas //
NK064(ngu),002:302: shes bya khong du chud par 'gyur //
NK064(ngu),002:304: bi ma la'i 'grel chung las kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:305: thugs kyi sgron ma gsang ba'i 'grel ba 'di //
NK064(ngu),002:306: lung dang man ngag rig pas gtan la dbab //
NK064(ngu),002:308: rgyud lung man ngag gi mtshan nyid de yang gang zhe na /
NK064(ngu),002:310: 'brel zhing rgyun chags la dngos grub sgrub pa'i yan
NK064(ngu),002:311: lag ma tshang ba med cing phun sum tshogs pa
NK064(ngu),002:314: 'brel dang ma tshang med phyir dang //
NK064(ngu),002:315: phun sum tshogs pas rgyud ces bya //
NK064(ngu),002:318: mdo rgyud nas tshig dum bur phyungs shing yid ches su byed pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:320: lung ni yid ches tshig yin te //
NK064(ngu),002:321: nyes pa zad pa rdzun gyi ngag /
NK064(ngu),002:322: smra bar mi 'gyur rgyu med phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:323: nyes zad lung du shes par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:325: man ngag gi mtshan nyid ni /
NK064(ngu),002:326: tshegs chung ngus dpag par dka' ba'i don dpag tu
NK064(ngu),002:327: med pa rtogs sla ba'i thabs su gyur pa ste
NK064(ngu),002:329: thabs che tshegs chung don dpag med //
NK064(ngu),002:330: bya sla dpag dka' man ngag go //
NK064(ngu),002:333: zhes pa la 'chad tshul mang du yod do //
NK064(ngu),002:334: ma h+aa yo ga spyi'i 'chad tshul /
NK064(ngu),002:336: zur lugs kyi 'chad tshul sogs yod pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:337: dang po ni he ru ka galpo'i rgyud las /
NK064(ngu),002:338: ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyan bdun yang //
NK064(ngu),002:339: gleng bslang ba dang sangs rgyas tshul //
NK064(ngu),002:340: rgyas bshad mtha' dang bshad pa'i tshul //
NK064(ngu),002:341: dbye ba'i rnam pa gang zag snod //
NK064(ngu),002:342: bden pa'i dgongs pa shes par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:343: zhes gsungs pa ltar rgyan bdun gyi sgo nas 'chad de /
NK064(ngu),002:345: dri ba dris lan gyi sgo nas 'chad pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:347: rgyud 'di'i ming ni ci zhig yin //
NK064(ngu),002:348: rgyud 'di su yi don du mdzad //
NK064(ngu),002:349: ces sogs gsungs pa ltar yin /
NK064(ngu),002:352: sangs rgyas pa yi tshul bzhi ste //
NK064(ngu),002:353: rgyud dang gleng gzhi nges tshig rgyu //
NK064(ngu),002:354: zhes gsungs pa ltar tshul bzhi'i sgo nas 'chad de /
NK064(ngu),002:355: bcom ldan 'das thub pa'i dbang pos ni tshul bzhi'i
NK064(ngu),002:356: sgo nas sangs rgyas par 'jig rten du grags te
NK064(ngu),002:357: / mi'i rigs rgyud du 'khrungs pas rgyud kyi tshul dang /
NK064(ngu),002:358: de las khyim nas khyim med par rab tu byung ba gleng gzhi'i tshul dang /
NK064(ngu),002:359: rab tu byung nas kyang 'dul sdom bsrung bar nges pas nges tshig gi tshul dang /
NK064(ngu),002:360: de ltar bsrung nas lam la bslab pas rnam grol
NK064(ngu),002:361: thob pa'i rgyu yin pa'i phyir rgyu yi tshul te
NK064(ngu),002:362: / tshul bzhi'i sgo nas 'chad par bzhed pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:365: rgyas bshad mtha' ni rnam pa drug /
NK064(ngu),002:366: drang don nges don dgongs pas bshad //
NK064(ngu),002:367: dgongs min sgra ni ji bzhin pa //
NK064(ngu),002:368: ji bzhin ma yin nyid du bshad //
NK064(ngu),002:369: ces gsungs pa ltar drang nges gnyis /
NK064(ngu),002:371: sgra ji bzhin pa dang ji bzhin ma yin pa
NK064(ngu),002:372: gnyis te tshig don 'di drug las mi 'da' bas
NK064(ngu),002:373: na mtha' drug ces bshad pa'i phyir gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:376: tshig spyi sbas dang mthar thug yin //
NK064(ngu),002:377: zhes gsungs pa ltar bzhi las /
NK064(ngu),002:379: yi ge'i 'bru bsnol mtshams la gzhol ba'i bshad pa sgra tshad kyi gzhung mthun par 'chad pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:381: sngags lam bde zhing myur ba la mi zhugs par /
NK064(ngu),002:382: mdo lam bul zhing dka' thub kyi lam la zhugs par 'gyod na /
NK064(ngu),002:383: de dag kyang 'di'i lam stegs yin tshul du 'chad pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:384: yang sngags lam gtsang dme med pa khyi phag lta
NK064(ngu),002:385: bu dang sbyor sgrol sogs 'tshe ba chos su smra
NK064(ngu),002:386: bas mu stegs kyi chos so snyam du 'gyod na
NK064(ngu),002:387: / mdo lam du'ang gtsang dmer zhen 'dzin ma spang na mnyam nyid kyi don mi mthong ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:388: dge sems kyi spyod par 'dzin pa ma zhugs na gang yang bsod nams kyi tshogs su gsungs te /
NK064(ngu),002:389: mi nag mdung thung can bsad pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:390: ded dpon gyi bu mor bsgrod pa sogs bsod nams 'phel ba'i rgyur song tshul du 'chad pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:392: bskyed rim las rgya sogs dang /
NK064(ngu),002:393: rdzogs rim rtsa rlung thig le byed bcings sogs sbas don du 'chad pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:395: don dam 'od gsal gyi dgongs pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:396: bden gnyis zung 'jug gi gnas lugs mthar thug yin tshul du 'chad pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:399: nyan bshad dbye ba rnam pa gnyis //
NK064(ngu),002:400: tshogs dang slob ma dag tu 'dod //
NK064(ngu),002:404: theg pa thun mong gi don 'chad pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:406: sgra ji bzhin ma yin pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:407: nges don mthar thug gi don 'chad par byed pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:410: snod kyi gang zag rnam pa lnga //
NK064(ngu),002:412: tsan+dana rin po che yi dpe //
NK064(ngu),002:414: ut+pala lta bu'i gang zag dang /
NK064(ngu),002:415: pad+ma dkar dmar lta bu dang /
NK064(ngu),002:417: rin po che lta bu'i gang zag lnga'i snod la brtags nas 'chad par byed pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:420: bden pa'i dgongs pa rnam pa gnyis //
NK064(ngu),002:421: kun rdzob don dam bshad par gyis //
NK064(ngu),002:422: zhes gsungs pa ltar snga ma drug la brten nas
NK064(ngu),002:423: rgyud don bden pa gnyis su bsdus te 'chad par
NK064(ngu),002:424: byed pa'o // de ltar rgyan bdun gyi 'chad tshul
NK064(ngu),002:425: 'di ni rgyud 'di'i 'chad thabs kyi bka' srol ma
NK064(ngu),002:426: yin kyang ma h+aa yo ga spyi'i 'chad thabs yin
NK064(ngu),002:427: byed pa'o // gsungs / gnyis pa snga rabs pa rnams kyis 'chad tshul ni /
NK064(ngu),002:428: mda' ltar rtse mo nas bzung ste 'chad pa zhes bya ba /
NK064(ngu),002:429: mtshan gyi nang du chos thams cad gzhi lam 'bras gsum du bsdus nas 'chad pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:430: mdung ltar sked pa nas bzung ste 'chad pa zhes bya ba /
NK064(ngu),002:431: le'u lnga pa'i nang du chos thams cad mtshan nyid gsum du dril nas 'chad pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:432: ral gri ltar yu ba nas bzung ste 'chad pa zhes bya ba /
NK064(ngu),002:433: le'u tha mar chos thams cad snang ba bzhir bsdus nas 'chad pa yin gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:434: gsum pa bka' sde zur pa'i bshad srol ni /
NK064(ngu),002:436: rang bzhin dngos po'i gnas tshul /
NK064(ngu),002:438: thams cad mkhyen pas gzigs tshul /
NK064(ngu),002:439: brtse ba'i thugs rje skye tshul /
NK064(ngu),002:440: 'gro don ji ltar mdzad tshul dang lnga'i sgo nas 'chad gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:441: 'dir ni slob dpon bi ma la'i rjes su 'brangs nas 'chad de /
NK064(ngu),002:442: bi ma'i khog gzhung gsal sgron du /
NK064(ngu),002:443: rab la mtshan bstan 'bring la dbye //
NK064(ngu),002:446: rab la mtshan bstan zhes pa dbang po yang rab
NK064(ngu),002:447: la rgyud kyi mtshan bstan te bshad pa'i don yin
NK064(ngu),002:448: / 'bring la dbye zhes pa dbang po 'bring la
NK064(ngu),002:449: rgyud kyi spyi don rnam par dbye nas bshad pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:450: / don yin / tha mar 'bru gnyer dgrol ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:451: zhes pa dbang po tha ma la tshig 'bru re
NK064(ngu),002:452: re'i sgo nas dgrol te bshad pa'i don yin gsungs
NK064(ngu),002:453: / dang po dbang po yang rab rnams la rgyud kyi mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:455: rab mtshan tha snyad gsum du grags //
NK064(ngu),002:456: sgyu 'phrul snying po lung gi spyi //
NK064(ngu),002:457: lag gi rtsa bzhin dbu zhabs rtogs //
NK064(ngu),002:458: skal ba can gyi ched phyir ro //
NK064(ngu),002:460: de la rab mtshan tha snyad gsum du grags //
NK064(ngu),002:461: zhes pa ni dbang po yang rab la bstan pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:462: mtshan de la rnam pa gsum du yod ces pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:463: don yin / gsum po gang zhe na /
NK064(ngu),002:464: sgyu 'phrul snying po lung gi spyi //
NK064(ngu),002:466: sgyu 'phrul zhes pas rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes pa rgyud dang mthun pa'i mtshan /
NK064(ngu),002:467: snying po zhes pas gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:468: zhes pa man ngag dang mthun pa'i mtshan /
NK064(ngu),002:469: lung gi spyi zhes pas mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams
NK064(ngu),002:470: cad kyi lung gi spyi zhes pa lung dang mthun
NK064(ngu),002:471: pa'i mtshan no // lag gi rtsa bzhin dbu zhabs rtogs //
NK064(ngu),002:472: zhes pas dbang rab kyis mtshan tha snyad gsum po
NK064(ngu),002:473: de la brten nas rgyud don rtogs tshul bstan te
NK064(ngu),002:474: / lag gi rtsa bzhin zhes pas dpe bstan /
NK064(ngu),002:475: dbu zhabs rtogs zhes pas dpe can bstan te /
NK064(ngu),002:476: dper na sman pa mkhas pas nad pa'i lag gi
NK064(ngu),002:477: rtsa la brten nas lus mgo mjug gi nad thams
NK064(ngu),002:478: cad ngos zin pa bzhin du /
NK064(ngu),002:479: dbang rab des kyang rgyud lung man ngag gi mtshan gsum la brten nas /
NK064(ngu),002:480: rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don thams cad bde blag tu
NK064(ngu),002:481: rtogs par 'gyur bas dbu zhabs rtogs zhes bshad pa
NK064(ngu),002:482: yin gsungs / skal pa can gyi ched phyir ro //
NK064(ngu),002:484: de ni skal ldan dbang rab kyi spyod yul yin
NK064(ngu),002:485: la skal med rnams kyi spyod yul ma yin zhes
NK064(ngu),002:486: pa'i don yin / de ltar rgyud dang dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu),002:487: gyi gtso bo dang 'chad pa'i skyes bu gsum gyi
NK064(ngu),002:488: mtshan thun mong du bstan pa la rdo rje sems
NK064(ngu),002:490: zhes pa la mtshan gyi zur gnyis te /
NK064(ngu),002:491: rdo rje sems dpa' bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:493: dang po rdo rje sems dpa' la'ang zur gnyis te /
NK064(ngu),002:496: dang po rdo rje zhes pa'i don ni /
NK064(ngu),002:498: tha dad med pa'i rang bzhin nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:499: rdo rje zhes ni bshad pa yin //
NK064(ngu),002:502: rdo rje ni rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pas shes rab stong pa nyid dang zhes pas /
NK064(ngu),002:503: rdo rje de rang bzhin gang dang dbyer mi phyed ce na /
NK064(ngu),002:504: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin stong pa nyid dang
NK064(ngu),002:505: dbyer mi phyed pa yin la stong pa nyid la
NK064(ngu),002:508: rdo rje stong pa nyid du bshad //
NK064(ngu),002:509: sems dpa' ye shes chen po ste //
NK064(ngu),002:511: de la tha dad med pa'i rang bzhin zhes bya ste /
NK064(ngu),002:512: stong nyid de gang dang tha dad med ce na /
NK064(ngu),002:513: 'khor 'das gnyis snang tshul la tha dad kyang rang
NK064(ngu),002:514: bzhin nam gnas lugs la stong nyid las nam yang
NK064(ngu),002:516: tha dad med pa'i rang bzhin nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:517: rdo rje zhes ni bshad pa yin //
NK064(ngu),002:519: rang bzhin gyi don yang gzhan gyis ma bcos pa'i don te /
NK064(ngu),002:521: rang bzhin dag ni bcos min dang //
NK064(ngu),002:522: gzhan la ltos pa med pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:525: chos thams cad sems su 'du la /
NK064(ngu),002:526: sems nyid stong pa nyid du gnas pa de la rdo rje zhes bshad de /
NK064(ngu),002:528: sems can kun gyi sems gang zhig /
NK064(ngu),002:529: rdo rje zhes ni bshad pa yin //
NK064(ngu),002:531: sems las ma gtogs chos med de //
NK064(ngu),002:532: sgyu ma rdo rje btsan po mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:535: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NK064(ngu),002:536: de ni lung gi tshad mar bshad //
NK064(ngu),002:539: rin chen sems las phyir gyur pa'i //
NK064(ngu),002:540: sangs rgyas med cing sems can med //
NK064(ngu),002:543: sems nyid gcig po kun gyi sa bon te //
NK064(ngu),002:544: gang la srid dang mya ngan 'das 'phro ba //
NK064(ngu),002:545: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs so //
NK064(ngu),002:546: des na sems nyid stong pa nyid la rdo rje zhes brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:547: 'jig rten na rdzas rdo rje pha lam zhes pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:548: dngos po zhig yod pa des phar mtshan ma'i chos
NK064(ngu),002:550: tshur de'i ngo bo la gang gis kyang mi tshugs pa bzhin te /
NK064(ngu),002:551: rdo rje'i yon tan 'chad pa'i tshe /
NK064(ngu),002:552: rdo rje ni mi chod pa /
NK064(ngu),002:557: thams cad du thogs pa med pa /
NK064(ngu),002:558: thams cad du ma pham pa zhes chos bdun ldan du gsungs so //
NK064(ngu),002:559: mtshan gyi zur gnyis pa sems dpa' zhes pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:560: chos rnams ma lus gnyis med pa'i //
NK064(ngu),002:561: rang rig byang chub sems nyid do //
NK064(ngu),002:563: de yang sems dpa' zhes pas sat+wa'i sgra las don drug tsam la 'jug ste /
NK064(ngu),002:569: rtogs pa rnams la 'jug pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:570: 'dir brtan bsdus rtogs gsum la 'jug pa'i skabs yin pas /
NK064(ngu),002:571: gong du bshad pa'i shes rab stong pa nyid de'i
NK064(ngu),002:572: snang ba thabs rig pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK064(ngu),002:573: yin la / thabs rig pa rang byung gi ye
NK064(ngu),002:574: shes de shes rab stong pa nyid dang ro gcig
NK064(ngu),002:575: pa'i zung 'jug rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa
NK064(ngu),002:576: de rdo rje ltar brtan pas so zhes bshad /
NK064(ngu),002:577: des na sems nyid snang stong gnyis su med pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:578: rang byung gi ye shes de sems can nas sangs
NK064(ngu),002:579: rgyas kyi bar du rang bzhin bzang ngan med par
NK064(ngu),002:581: sems nyid mi 'gyur ba'i ngos nas brtan pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bshad de /
NK064(ngu),002:583: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK064(ngu),002:584: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK064(ngu),002:586: de nyid kyi phyag rgyas 'khor 'das kyi chos thams
NK064(ngu),002:587: cad la btab pas mnyam pa nyid du bsdus pa
NK064(ngu),002:588: zhes pa ni / sems nyid snang stong gnyis su
NK064(ngu),002:589: med pa'i chos des 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK064(ngu),002:590: la til la mar bzhin du khyab nas gnas pa
NK064(ngu),002:591: zhes pa ni / ste / mdo las /
NK064(ngu),002:592: bde gshegs snying pos 'gro kun yongs la khyab //
NK064(ngu),002:595: 'di nyid ye shes chen po ste //
NK064(ngu),002:596: brtan dang g.yo bar khyab nas gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:598: de ltar na sems nyid de nyid kyi phyag rgyas
NK064(ngu),002:599: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la btab pa zhes
NK064(ngu),002:600: bya ste / dper na rgyal po'i bka' rtags kyi
NK064(ngu),002:601: phyag rgyas btab na 'bangs rnams kyis de las nam
NK064(ngu),002:602: yang 'da' mi nus pa bzhin du chos thams cad
NK064(ngu),002:603: kyi gnas lugs stong pa nyid yin la /
NK064(ngu),002:604: de nyid chos thams cad kyi srog tu song bas
NK064(ngu),002:605: dbus na gnas pa'am kun la khyab bcas su gnas
NK064(ngu),002:606: pa ste / rdo rje phreng ba las /
NK064(ngu),002:607: chos rnams dbus na gnas pa'i khams //
NK064(ngu),002:608: khyab cing spyod yul ma yin te //
NK064(ngu),002:610: mnyam pa nyid du bsdus pa zhes pa /
NK064(ngu),002:611: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes de'i ngos nas gzhal na /
NK064(ngu),002:612: 'khor ba zhes pa'i ngan pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:613: myang 'das zhes pa'i bzang po gnyis ka tha dad
NK064(ngu),002:614: du ma grub par 'khor 'das bzang ngan med par
NK064(ngu),002:615: sems nyid de'i klong du mnyam pa nyid du bsdus
NK064(ngu),002:619: 'khor ba spangs nas gzhan du ni //
NK064(ngu),002:620: mya ngan 'das pa yod ma yin //
NK064(ngu),002:623: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad //
NK064(ngu),002:624: gdos pa can gyi chos min te //
NK064(ngu),002:625: rtog med rang rig 'od gsal ba'i //
NK064(ngu),002:628: sgrib gnyis zad cing tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i skyes bus
NK064(ngu),002:629: mngon du byas pa ni 'bras bu'i rdo rje sems
NK064(ngu),002:631: de ltar brtan bsdus gnyis po de sems nyid gnas lugs kyi ngos nas bzhag pa yin la /
NK064(ngu),002:632: rtogs pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' 'am 'bras bu'i rdo
NK064(ngu),002:633: rje sems dpa' ni snang lugs kyi ngos nas 'byung
NK064(ngu),002:634: ba ste / gnas lugs la de ltar yin kyang
NK064(ngu),002:635: snang lugs la 'khor 'das gnyis bzang ngan ltar du
NK064(ngu),002:636: snang bas na rnam grol don gnyer gyi gang zag
NK064(ngu),002:637: gis sems nyid rnal ma'i don rtogs pa'i thabs su
NK064(ngu),002:638: lam thabs grol gnyis la 'bad pas ji zhig na
NK064(ngu),002:639: sems nyid sangs rgyas su rtogs pa de la rtogs
NK064(ngu),002:640: pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya ste /
NK064(ngu),002:642: sems rtogs na sangs rgyas yin pas sangs rgyas gzhan
NK064(ngu),002:643: nas mi btsal ba'i 'du shes rab tu bsgom par
NK064(ngu),002:645: gang rtogs pa'i ye shes de yang rdo rje ltar gnyis su med par gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu),002:647: de ltar rtogs pa'i skyes bu de la rdo rje
NK064(ngu),002:648: sems dpa' zhes btags pas de'i thugs rgyud na yod
NK064(ngu),002:649: pa'i ye shes de yang rdo rje ltar gnyis su
NK064(ngu),002:650: med par rtogs par gyur pa'i phyir de ltar du
NK064(ngu),002:651: brjod do // des rgyud la rdo rje sems dpa' zhes pa'i mtshan btags pa song nas /
NK064(ngu),002:652: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo la rdo rje sems dpa' zhes pa'i don ni /
NK064(ngu),002:653: de nyid mtshan ma'i phyag rgyar snang ba dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu),002:654: gyi gtso bo dang zhes bshad pa de yin te
NK064(ngu),002:655: / de'i don ni sems nyid rang byung gi ye
NK064(ngu),002:656: shes de nyid kyi ngo bo mtshan med stong pa
NK064(ngu),002:657: / nyid yin kyang / sems can gyi blo la
NK064(ngu),002:658: ltos nas rig pa nyid ye shes kyi 'khor lo'i
NK064(ngu),002:659: tshul du mtshan ma'i phyag rgyar rang snang ba yin
NK064(ngu),002:660: / nyid yin kyang / te / 'di nyid las /
NK064(ngu),002:661: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK064(ngu),002:664: lam pas nyams su blangs pa'i tshe tshogs lam du mos spyod kyi lha sku dang /
NK064(ngu),002:665: sbyor lam du rlung sems kyi lha sku /
NK064(ngu),002:666: mthong lam du 'od gsal gyi lha sku /
NK064(ngu),002:667: sa gnyis pa nas bcu pa'i bar slob pa'i zung 'jug gi lha sku /
NK064(ngu),002:668: sangs rgyas kyi sar mi slob pa'i zung 'jug gi
NK064(ngu),002:669: lha sku'i gtso 'khor gyi rnam par snang ba rnams
NK064(ngu),002:670: la'ang rdo rje sems dpa' zhes pa'i mtshan du btags
NK064(ngu),002:671: pa yin / spyir 'chad pa'i skyes bu rigs lnga ste /
NK064(ngu),002:672: zhes 'byung yang skabs 'dir 'chad pa'i skyes bu mi
NK064(ngu),002:673: bskyod pa la'ang rdo rje sems dpa' zhes grags so
NK064(ngu),002:676: mi bskyod skyes bu mdun na gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:677: zhes pas thugs kyi sgyu 'phrul 'chad pa'i skabs 'dir
NK064(ngu),002:678: ston pa kun tu bzang po'i mdun na bzhugs pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:679: rdo rje mi bskyod pa de la'ang de ltar brjod
NK064(ngu),002:681: gzhan du sku dang gsung dang yon tan dang phrin
NK064(ngu),002:682: las kyi sgyu 'phrul gang ston pa'i tshe de dang
NK064(ngu),002:683: de'i 'chad pa'i skyes bu de rigs so so'i dkyil
NK064(ngu),002:685: des mtshan gyi zur dang po rdo rje sems dpa' bshad pa de song nas /
NK064(ngu),002:686: zur gnyis pa sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes pa'i mtshan ni /
NK064(ngu),002:688: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i don //
NK064(ngu),002:689: sgyu 'phrul zhes ni bzhir bshad do //
NK064(ngu),002:690: zhes pas de la bzhi las /
NK064(ngu),002:691: dang po rtog tshogs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:692: 'byung ba lnga sgyu ma ltar snang ba ris su
NK064(ngu),002:693: ma chad pa'i rgyus cir yang 'phrul pa ni phung
NK064(ngu),002:694: po lnga ste / zhes pas 'byung ba lnga sgyu ma ltar snang ba ris su ma chad de /
NK064(ngu),002:695: ci'i phyir ris su ma chad ce na /
NK064(ngu),002:696: dper na chu lta bu gcig la'ang mthong snang mi 'dra ba du ma 'byung ste /
NK064(ngu),002:697: ka ba dpal brtsegs kyi lta rim las /
NK064(ngu),002:698: dmyal bas rang sems me sogs snang //
NK064(ngu),002:699: yi dwags sdig sems mi gtsang yul //
NK064(ngu),002:700: byol song gyen mthur ngam grog ste //
NK064(ngu),002:701: mi la mthong yul 'di ltar snang //
NK064(ngu),002:702: de bzhin lha min go mtshon sogs //
NK064(ngu),002:703: lha la dge sems rin chen snang //
NK064(ngu),002:704: zhes gsungs pa ltar dmyal ba pa rnams kyis zangs zhun dang khro chu khol mar mthong /
NK064(ngu),002:705: yi dwags rnams kyis rnag khrag dang ljan ljin du mthong /
NK064(ngu),002:706: dud 'gros gyen mthur dang ngam grog dang /
NK064(ngu),002:708: lha ma yin gyis go mtshon du mthong /
NK064(ngu),002:710: grub pa'i sa la bzhugs pa'i 'phags pa rnams kyis yum m+aa ma k+air mthong ste /
NK064(ngu),002:712: dngos gcig yid ni tha dad phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:713: don ma grub pa so sor mthong //
NK064(ngu),002:715: des mtshon te 'byung ba lnga yin lugs nas ye nas yum lnga'i rang bzhin du yin kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:716: snang lugs nas so sor snang bas 'byung ba lnga sgyu ma ltar zhes bshad /
NK064(ngu),002:717: sgyu ma de yang sgyu ma mkhan gyis shing bu rde'u sogs la sngags btab ste /
NK064(ngu),002:718: de nyid rta ltar ston pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:719: glang po ltar ston pa sogs du mar snang ba bzhin /
NK064(ngu),002:720: da res 'dir yang rgyu 'byung ba lnga las 'bras
NK064(ngu),002:721: bu 'byung 'gyur phung po lngar rnam par 'phrul pa
NK064(ngu),002:723: lnga phung sgyu ma'i ye shes las //
NK064(ngu),002:724: rang rig thabs kyi rigs lngar 'phrul //
NK064(ngu),002:726: rgyu 'bras 'brel ba can gyi phyir d+r+wa ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:727: zhes pas 'byung ba lnga dang phung po lnga ngo bo bdag gcig gis 'brel ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:729: 'jig rten na thig gu phan tshun sbrel ba'i phad
NK064(ngu),002:730: bu la d+r+wa phad ces 'dogs pa bzhin 'dir yang
NK064(ngu),002:731: de gnyis zung 'jug tu gnas pa la d+r+wa ba
NK064(ngu),002:732: zhes pa'i tha snyad du bzhag go //
NK064(ngu),002:733: gnyis pa nges don sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:735: rtog tshogs sgyu d+r+wa'i skabs su 'byung ba lnga la sgyu ma /
NK064(ngu),002:737: de gnyis 'brel ba la d+r+wa bar bshad pa bzhin du /
NK064(ngu),002:738: stong pa nyid la sgyu ma /
NK064(ngu),002:739: rig pa'i ye shes la 'phrul pa /
NK064(ngu),002:740: de gnyis 'brel ba la d+r+wa ba zhes 'jog pas /
NK064(ngu),002:741: shes rab dbyings stong pa nyid dang thabs rig pa
NK064(ngu),002:742: rang byung gi ye shes gnyis zung du 'jug pa
NK064(ngu),002:743: ni nges don sgyu d+r+wa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:744: de'i don ni ston pa nyid la sgyu ma zhes bya ste /
NK064(ngu),002:745: stong pa nyid ni gang du'ang ma grub la cir yang 'char du rung ba zhig ste /
NK064(ngu),002:747: gang la stong pa nyid rung ba //
NK064(ngu),002:748: de la thams cad rung ba yin //
NK064(ngu),002:751: chos 'ga' yod pa ma yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:752: de phyir stong nyid ma gtogs pa'i //
NK064(ngu),002:753: chos 'ga' yod pa ma yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:755: stong nyid de ni cir yang snang la gang gi
NK064(ngu),002:756: ngo bor yang ma grub cing rnam pa mtha' yas
NK064(ngu),002:759: cir yang med las cir yang snang //
NK064(ngu),002:761: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor sna tshogs kyang //
NK064(ngu),002:762: sems kyi sgyu 'phrul chen po yin //
NK064(ngu),002:766: des na chos thams cad kyi snang gazhi'am gnas lugs
NK064(ngu),002:767: smra bsam brjod med de'i ngo bo dmigs su med
NK064(ngu),002:769: med pa nyid na sna tshogs snang //
NK064(ngu),002:770: thams cad shes rab dbyings las byung //
NK064(ngu),002:771: zhes gsungs pa ltar shes rab dbyings stong pa nyid
NK064(ngu),002:772: sgyu ma lta bu de thabs rang rig pa'i ye
NK064(ngu),002:773: shes su rnam par 'phrul pas sgyu 'phrul dang /
NK064(ngu),002:774: rig pa'i ye shes nyid shes rab stong pa nyid du grol bas na d+r+wa ba zhes bya ste /
NK064(ngu),002:775: des na nges don gyi sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:776: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs sam rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i zhe phug nges don mthar thug pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:777: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK064(ngu),002:779: gsum pa drang don brda'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:780: nges don gyi sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba de nyid rtogs pa'i thabs su gyur pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:781: de'i rtags lha yab yum zung du 'brel ba ni drang don brda'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:783: nges don gyi sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba dngos su mi
NK064(ngu),002:784: rtogs pa'i gang zag de la re zhig brda dang
NK064(ngu),002:785: rtags kyi sgo nas thabs ston pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:786: stong pa nyid mtshon pa'i lha yum /
NK064(ngu),002:787: rig pa'i ye shes mtshon pa'i lha yab /
NK064(ngu),002:788: zung 'jug mtshon pa'i lha yab yum phan tshun 'khril sbyor gyi phyag rgya'i brda dang rtags bstan pa /
NK064(ngu),002:789: lha yum gyi phyag rgya ni stong pa nyid do //
NK064(ngu),002:790: lha yab kyi phyag rgya ni rig pa'i ye shes yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:791: yab yum 'khril sbyor gyi tshul du bzhugs pa stong
NK064(ngu),002:792: pa nyid dang rig pa'i ye shes zung du 'jug
NK064(ngu),002:793: pa yin no // zhes pa la sogs pa mtshan
NK064(ngu),002:794: ma bsgom pa'i don bstan nas de ltar bsgom du
NK064(ngu),002:795: pa yin no // bcug pas / ji zhig na
NK064(ngu),002:796: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes de'i don rtogs
NK064(ngu),002:798: de yang gang drangs na gang zag mtshan ma'i blo can de drangs /
NK064(ngu),002:799: gang du drangs na nges don gyi sgyu d+r+wa de la drangs /
NK064(ngu),002:800: tshul ji lta bus drangs na lha yab yum thabs
NK064(ngu),002:801: shes phan tshun 'khril sbyor gyi phyag rgya'i brda dang
NK064(ngu),002:802: rtags la brten nas drangs te /
NK064(ngu),002:804: thabs 'di rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK064(ngu),002:805: skas kyi gdang bu lta bur bstan //
NK064(ngu),002:807: bzhi pa lha rtog dbyer med kyi sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:808: lha dang rtog pa dbyer med sgyu ma byung yang /
NK064(ngu),002:809: rtog tshoogs kyi rang bzhin lha dag pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:810: lha'i ngo bo rtog tshogs kyi rang bzhin du rnam
NK064(ngu),002:811: par 'phrul pa'i phyir na lha rtog dbyer med ces
NK064(ngu),002:812: bshad / yang 'di nyid kyi le'u bzhi pa las ni /
NK064(ngu),002:814: yum la d+r+wa bar bshad cing zhes pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:816: tha ni sgyu 'phrul rdo rje nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:818: rdo rje g.yung drung 'khyil ba'i mdo las kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:819: d+r+wa ba cir yang 'gyur ba ste //
NK064(ngu),002:820: mdo mdun 'brel zhing zang thal ba //
NK064(ngu),002:821: thams cad sdud cing shong ba'i phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:822: yum la d+r+wa ba zhes bshad do //
NK064(ngu),002:823: zhes gsungs pa ltar rdo rje'i tshig yin pas gang ltar bshad kyang mi 'gal lo gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:824: des rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes
NK064(ngu),002:825: pa rgyud dang mthun pa'i mtshan bshad pa de song
NK064(ngu),002:826: nas / gnyis pa che ba las mtshan du btags pa lung gi mtshan ni /
NK064(ngu),002:828: so sor bstan pa rgya mtsho'i rgyud //
NK064(ngu),002:830: don kun 'di la yongs rdzogs pas //
NK064(ngu),002:831: lung gi spyi zhes bshad pa yin //
NK064(ngu),002:833: ston pas gdul bya so so'i blo dang 'tshams par bstan pa'i chos ni rgya mtsho'i rgyud de /
NK064(ngu),002:834: rgya mtsho ni zab cing gting dpag dka' bas 'di tsam zhes dpag par mi nus pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:835: ston pas gsungs pa'i chos rnams kyang don zab cing gting dpag dka' ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:836: tshig rgya che zhing mtha' yas pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:837: de thams cad kyang rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po
NK064(ngu),002:838: 'di'i nang du rdzogs par ston pas na 'dir ston
NK064(ngu),002:839: zhes bshad de / rgyas pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:840: mnyam nyid don rtogs rang rig rgyal po ni //
NK064(ngu),002:841: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'babs ltar //
NK064(ngu),002:842: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK064(ngu),002:843: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK064(ngu),002:846: bstan pa dang theg pa thams cad kyi don ma
NK064(ngu),002:847: lus pa rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po 'di nyid
NK064(ngu),002:848: las 'phros te ston pas na 'dis ston zhes bshad
NK064(ngu),002:850: phyogs bcu rnams su rab grags pa //
NK064(ngu),002:851: gsang ba'i snying po las 'phros te /
NK064(ngu),002:852: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po ni //
NK064(ngu),002:853: sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi //
NK064(ngu),002:857: theg pa'i sgo gang nas zhugs kyang mthar thug theg
NK064(ngu),002:858: pa 'di las mi 'da' bas na theg pa gzhan
NK064(ngu),002:859: thams cad nyid kyi lam stegs kyi tshul du gsungs
NK064(ngu),002:861: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK064(ngu),002:862: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK064(ngu),002:864: don de nyid kyi phyir na rgyud 'di la lung gi spyi zhes bshad de /
NK064(ngu),002:865: de yang gsang sngags spyi'i rgyud lta bu yin nam zhe na ma yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:867: mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi spyi /
NK064(ngu),002:871: mngon du phyungs pa'i lung zhes bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:872: yang drang ba mtshan nyid kyi lung dang /
NK064(ngu),002:873: nges pa sngags kyi lung zhes pa'i phyi ma la'ang gzhi gnas sbyor ba'i lung /
NK064(ngu),002:876: rnam grol rig pa'i lung zhes kyang bshad do //
NK064(ngu),002:878: dri ma med pa'i lung nyid de //
NK064(ngu),002:879: las dang ye shes spyi nyid kyi //
NK064(ngu),002:880: rdzogs pas rdzogs phyir lung nyid do //
NK064(ngu),002:882: rgya ma las kyi lung mtshan nyid sde gsum /
NK064(ngu),002:883: ye shes lha'i lung phyi rgyud sde gsum /
NK064(ngu),002:884: bya bral rdzogs pa'i lung nang rgyud sde gsum ste /
NK064(ngu),002:885: de dag gi lung gi spyir gyur pas lung gi spyi zhes bshad pa yin /
NK064(ngu),002:887: gsum pa don rang gi ngo bo la btags pa man ngag gi mtshan ni /
NK064(ngu),002:889: sngon du 'gro ba'i bdag nyid las //
NK064(ngu),002:890: ming nyid thog mar smos pa gces //
NK064(ngu),002:891: zhes gsungs pa ltar glegs bam gyi klad du mtshan
NK064(ngu),002:892: ma bkod na gang yin mi shes pas rmongs pa
NK064(ngu),002:893: sel ba'i phyir bkod pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:895: ming du gdags par ma mdzad na //
NK064(ngu),002:897: de bas rmongs pa sel ba'i phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:898: mgon pos ming du gdags par mdzad //
NK064(ngu),002:900: de la klad du bkod pa'i mtshan ni /
NK064(ngu),002:901: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:905: rang bzhin gsang ba zhes bya ste //
NK064(ngu),002:906: che ba zhes bya snying po'i don //
NK064(ngu),002:907: de kho na nyid mtshan nyid do //
NK064(ngu),002:908: nges pas nges don mdor bstan pa /
NK064(ngu),002:913: nges pa'i don bshad pa dang bzhi las /
NK064(ngu),002:914: dang po gsang ba'i don bshad pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:917: sbas pa'i gsang ba ste gsum las //
NK064(ngu),002:918: rang bzhin gyis gsang ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:919: mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud gnas lugs de bzhin
NK064(ngu),002:920: nyid de rang la rang chas su gnas kyang dbul
NK064(ngu),002:921: po'i khyim gyi sa 'og gi nor bu ltar ma
NK064(ngu),002:922: mthong ba rang la yod kyang rang gi mig rang
NK064(ngu),002:923: gis mi mthong ba ltar rang bzhin ma rtogs pas
NK064(ngu),002:924: gsang ba ste / rgyud bla ma las /
NK064(ngu),002:925: ji ltar mi dbul khyim nang sa 'og na //
NK064(ngu),002:926: mi zad pa yi gter ni yod gyur kyang //
NK064(ngu),002:927: mi des de ma shes shing gter des kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:928: de la nga 'dir yod ces mi smra ltar //
NK064(ngu),002:929: de bzhin sems kyi nang chud rin chen gter //
NK064(ngu),002:930: dri med bzhag dang bsal med ye shes te //
NK064(ngu),002:931: ma rtogs pas na dbul ba'i sdug bsngal ni //
NK064(ngu),002:932: rnam mang rgyun du skye rgu 'dis myong ngo //
NK064(ngu),002:935: sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin yin tshul mdo
NK064(ngu),002:936: rgyud du ma nas gsungs kyang rang sems sangs rgyas
NK064(ngu),002:937: yin pa bor nas sangs rgyas gzhan las 'tshol ba
NK064(ngu),002:938: rang gis rang la gab ste gnas pas gsang ba
NK064(ngu),002:939: ste / rnam snang mngon byang las /
NK064(ngu),002:940: byis pa mi shes pas bsgribs pa'i //
NK064(ngu),002:941: tshul 'di shes par ma gyur rnams //
NK064(ngu),002:942: sangs rgyas gzhan du 'tshol bar byed //
NK064(ngu),002:943: 'di na gnas pa yongs ma mthong //
NK064(ngu),002:946: gsang sngags kyi lta spyod zab mo blor mi shong
NK064(ngu),002:947: ba'i snod min gyi gang zag rnams kyis mi rtogs
NK064(ngu),002:948: par bya ba'i phyir sbas pas gsang ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:950: gsang sngags skyon yod ma yin te //
NK064(ngu),002:951: blo chung theg pa dman la gsang /
NK064(ngu),002:954: de'i steng du mi bstan pa'i gsang ba bsnan te bzhir bshad kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:956: rang bzhin gyis gsang ba ni gab pa'i khongs su gtogs shing /
NK064(ngu),002:957: mi bstan pa'i gsang ba'ang sbas pa'i nang du 'du bas na gab sbas gnyis su 'du ste /
NK064(ngu),002:959: gab pa'i gsang ba ma rtogs par sbas pa'i gsang ba la mngon par 'chel nas /
NK064(ngu),002:961: gnyis pa snying po'i don ni /
NK064(ngu),002:963: p+aa ra zhes pa gcig las du ma 'phro ba'i gzhi lta bu la 'jug ste /
NK064(ngu),002:964: sems nyid gnas lugs de bzhin nyid de 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kyi 'phro gzhi yin cing /
NK064(ngu),002:965: de gtan la 'bebs pa'i rgyud kyi rgyal po 'di
NK064(ngu),002:966: nyid kyang bstan pa dang theg pa thams cad kyi
NK064(ngu),002:967: 'byung khungs sam 'phro ba'i gzhi ma lta bu ste
NK064(ngu),002:969: phyogs bcu rnams su rab grags pa //
NK064(ngu),002:970: gsang ba'i snying po las 'phros te //
NK064(ngu),002:972: hri d+aa ya zhes pa khams che ba'am srog gam
NK064(ngu),002:973: snying ltar gces spras su bya ba'i don la 'jug
NK064(ngu),002:974: ste / sangs rgyas mi bsgrub na phar zhog /
NK064(ngu),002:975: bsgrub phyin theg pa'i sgo gang nas zhugs kyang mthar
NK064(ngu),002:976: thug bgrod pa gcig pa'i theg pa 'di la 'jug
NK064(ngu),002:977: dgos te / pan chen pad+ma dbang rgyal gyis /
NK064(ngu),002:978: bgrod gcig lam la ma brten 'bras thob ci //
NK064(ngu),002:981: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed du //
NK064(ngu),002:982: shin tu sbyangs la rab gnas shing //
NK064(ngu),002:983: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yi //
NK064(ngu),002:986: gar+b+ha ya zhes pa shun pa'i nang gi snying po lta bu la 'jug ste /
NK064(ngu),002:987: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kyi bcud 'dus pa'am /
NK064(ngu),002:988: de thams cad kyi srog tu song ba'i gnas lugs
NK064(ngu),002:989: kyi snying po yin lugs spros bral bsam brjod las
NK064(ngu),002:990: 'das pa ste / rdo rje phreng ba las /
NK064(ngu),002:991: chos rnams dbus na gnas pa'i khams //
NK064(ngu),002:992: khyab cing spyod yul ma yin te //
NK064(ngu),002:994: gsum pa de kho na nyid kyi don ni /
NK064(ngu),002:995: gzhi mi 'gyur ba dang lam gyi gzhi'i don nyams
NK064(ngu),002:996: su blangs pas 'bras bu 'byung ba la mi bslu
NK064(ngu),002:997: ba ste / don la de gnyis phyin ci ma
NK064(ngu),002:998: log pas gzhi 'bras lto sbyor te ma nor bas
NK064(ngu),002:999: de kho na nyid ces bya ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1001: gnyis po phyin ci ma log phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:1002: de nyid don 'dir rnam nges so //
NK064(ngu),002:1003: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu),002:1004: bzhi pa nges pa'i don ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1005: skal dman gyi gdul bya drang ba'i thabs tsam du bstan pa ma yin par /
NK064(ngu),002:1006: 'dir skal ldan dbang rnon rnams la rgyal ba'i dgongs
NK064(ngu),002:1007: pa'i zhe phug thun mong ma yin pa nyid bstan
NK064(ngu),002:1010: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus la //
NK064(ngu),002:1011: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK064(ngu),002:1013: gzhan yang mtshan nang ltar thabs lam steng sgo dang sbyar te bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1014: gsang ba ltar 'og sgo dang sbyar te bshad pa gnyis yod pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:1016: snying ga'i 'khor lo dang sbyar te bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1017: mtshan bzhi dang 'khor lo bzhi sbyar te bshad pa la gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:1019: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab brgyad kyi
NK064(ngu),002:1020: dbus na dwangs ma chen po lnga dang de'i dkyil
NK064(ngu),002:1021: na ye shes snying po'i thig le ye nas gnas
NK064(ngu),002:1022: kyang rang gsang thabs kyis chod nas ma mthong ba
NK064(ngu),002:1023: ni gsang ba / thig le de nyid la shes
NK064(ngu),002:1024: bya dang bsgrub bya'i don gyi bcud 'dus pas na
NK064(ngu),002:1025: ni gsang ba / snying po / thabs kyi man
NK064(ngu),002:1026: ngag dang ldan pa'i sgo nas nyams su blangs pas
NK064(ngu),002:1027: rang gi sems nyid bde chen lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:1028: ye shes su rang gsal bas na de kho na
NK064(ngu),002:1029: ni gsang ba / snying po / nyid / snying
NK064(ngu),002:1030: po'i thig le de gzhi lam 'bras gsum gyi dngos
NK064(ngu),002:1031: gzhir nges pas na nges pa zhes bshad pa'i phyir
NK064(ngu),002:1032: ni gsang ba / snying po / nyid / ro
NK064(ngu),002:1033: // gnyis pa mtshan bzhi dang 'khor lo bzhi sbyar
NK064(ngu),002:1035: lte ba'i 'khor lo rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa bzhi'i
NK064(ngu),002:1036: dbus na dbyings phyug lnga'i thig le yi ge a'i
NK064(ngu),002:1037: rnam par gnas pa de nyid yum gyi mkha' gsang
NK064(ngu),002:1038: gi sna rtse'i thig le dang 'brel te gnas pa
NK064(ngu),002:1039: ni gsang ba / snying ga'i 'khor lo rtsa 'dab
NK064(ngu),002:1040: brgyad kyi dwangs ma lnga'i dbus na ye shes snying
NK064(ngu),002:1041: po'i thig le bzhugs pa de chos thams cad kyi
NK064(ngu),002:1042: bcud 'dus pa'i snying po yin pas na snying po
NK064(ngu),002:1043: ni gsang ba / / mgrin pa'i 'khor lo rtsa
NK064(ngu),002:1044: 'dab bcu drug gi dbus na mkha' 'gro ma rngam
NK064(ngu),002:1045: ma'i thig le am yig gi dbyibs su gnas pa
NK064(ngu),002:1046: de 'od du 'bar tsa na bde ba skyes pas
NK064(ngu),002:1047: de kho na nyid las mi g.yo ba'i phyir de
NK064(ngu),002:1048: ni gsang ba / / kho na nyid / spyi
NK064(ngu),002:1049: bo'i 'khor lo'i rtsa 'dab so gnyis kyi dbus na
NK064(ngu),002:1050: kun tu bzang po'i thig le ham yig gi rnam
NK064(ngu),002:1051: par gnas pa de las skyes pa'i bde chen gyi
NK064(ngu),002:1052: ye shes de ni rgyal ba kun gyi dgongs pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:1053: dngos gzhir nges pa'i phyir na nges pa zhes bshad
NK064(ngu),002:1054: ni gsang ba / / kho na nyid / pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:1055: phyir ro // gnyis pa gsang ba ltar 'og sgo
NK064(ngu),002:1056: dang sbyar te bshad pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1057: lus can rnams kyi rtsa stong phrag bdun cu rtsa
NK064(ngu),002:1058: gnyis la sogs pa'i nang na thig le bde ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:1059: ye shes kyi ro dang bcas par rang chas su
NK064(ngu),002:1060: yod kyang ngo ma shes pas na gsang ba /
NK064(ngu),002:1061: thig le de la rgyu 'bras kyi bcud 'dus pas na snying po /
NK064(ngu),002:1062: byed pa sdom pa rlung dang bcas pa'i thabs kyis
NK064(ngu),002:1063: nyams su blangs pas bde chen lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:1064: ye shes dngos su rgyud la skyes pas na de
NK064(ngu),002:1065: kho na nyid / thig le de nyid gzhi lam
NK064(ngu),002:1066: 'bras gsum gyi dngos gzhir nges pas na de ltar
NK064(ngu),002:1067: nges pa zhes brjod pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu),002:1068: de rnams kyis dbang po rab la mtshan bstan pa song nas /
NK064(ngu),002:1069: gnyis pa dbang po 'bring po rnams la spyi'i don rnam par dbye bas bshad pa la gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:1070: dang po don gyi rnam grangs rnam par dbye ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1071: de la don gyi rnam grangs zhes pa /
NK064(ngu),002:1072: tshig la mi rton don la rton /
NK064(ngu),002:1073: don la'ang drang don la mi rton nges don la /
NK064(ngu),002:1074: de yang gang zag la mi rton chos la /
NK064(ngu),002:1075: chos la'ang rnam shes la mi rton ye shes la rton pas so //
NK064(ngu),002:1081: 'khor la gdams shing bstan pa gtad pa dang lnga las /
NK064(ngu),002:1084: ston pa la sogs rab dbye bas //
NK064(ngu),002:1085: phun sum tshogs pa lngar brjod do //
NK064(ngu),002:1087: gnas gang du ston pa gang zhig 'khor gang dang
NK064(ngu),002:1088: lhan cig tshogs pa de'i tshe rgyud don 'byung nges
NK064(ngu),002:1090: lnga po de la gleng gzhi zhes bya la /
NK064(ngu),002:1092: ci'i phyir gleng gzhi zhes bya zhe na /
NK064(ngu),002:1093: zhes pa'i dri ba bkod nas /
NK064(ngu),002:1095: d+aa na'i sgra las bka' yin min du rtog pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:1096: the tshom can dag la phun sum tshogs pa lnga'i
NK064(ngu),002:1097: lo rgyus brjod pas yid ches kyi nges pa sbyin
NK064(ngu),002:1100: gleng gzhi'i skad dod legs sbyar gyi sgra d+aa na zhes 'byung la /
NK064(ngu),002:1101: de bod skad du bsgyur na sbyin pa zhes 'byung la /
NK064(ngu),002:1102: de ltar du bsgyur na zang zing gi sbyin pa dang nor gyi dogs nas /
NK064(ngu),002:1103: gzhi mthun pa'i bsdu ba byas te phun sum tshogs
NK064(ngu),002:1104: pa lnga po de rgyud 'byung ba'i rgyu yang yin
NK064(ngu),002:1105: / rgyud gleng ba'i gzhi yang yin pas na gleng gzhi zhes bshad pa yin gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:1106: de yang gang sbyin na yid ches kyi nges pa sbyin /
NK064(ngu),002:1107: gang la sbyin na bka' yin min du rtog pa'i the tshom can de la sbyin /
NK064(ngu),002:1108: tshul ji lta bus sbyin na phun sum tshogs pa
NK064(ngu),002:1109: lnga'i lo rgyus brjod pa'i sgo nas sbyin pas so
NK064(ngu),002:1110: // de la dbye na thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1111: thun mong gi gleng gzhi gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:1113: thabs lam dang sbyar te nang gsang ltar 'chad pa dag yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:1115: nang thabs lam stong sgo dang sbyar te bshad rgyud rgya mtshos bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1116: gsang ba 'og sgo dang sbyar te bshad rgyud thal bas bshad pa gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:1119: 'od bzhi e sogs dbyibs su gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:1120: mi shigs thig le wam dbyibs can //
NK064(ngu),002:1121: rang la bde ba gsal byed dag /
NK064(ngu),002:1122: ma nu yid sogs rnam shes bzhi //
NK064(ngu),002:1123: ye shes myong bas bsdus par bshad //
NK064(ngu),002:1124: ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs skyes pa //
NK064(ngu),002:1125: pa ra m+aar+tha don zab mo //
NK064(ngu),002:1126: bde ba'i dus nyid snga phyir bral //
NK064(ngu),002:1127: dus gsum kun gyi ngo bor gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:1129: de yang phun sum tshogs pa lnga'i sgo nas 'chad de /
NK064(ngu),002:1130: rkang pa dang po gnyis kyis gnas phun sum tshogs pa ston pas /
NK064(ngu),002:1131: de yang snying ga chos kyi 'khor lor rtsa 'dab brgyad yod pa rigs bsdu na bzhir bsdu ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1132: mdun gyi rtsa gsum po de chos nyid skye ba
NK064(ngu),002:1133: med pa 'char ba'i las byed pas chos nyid kyi
NK064(ngu),002:1134: rtsa zhes bya la dbyibs mdog kyang dkar po zlum
NK064(ngu),002:1136: g.yas na gcig ste ye shes 'char ba'i las byed
NK064(ngu),002:1137: pas ye shes kyi rtsa zhes bya la dbyibs mdog
NK064(ngu),002:1138: kyang gru bzhi ser po'i rnam par gnas /
NK064(ngu),002:1139: g.yon na gcig ste yon tan dang mngon shes 'char
NK064(ngu),002:1140: ba'i las byed pas yon tan gyi rtsa zhes bya
NK064(ngu),002:1141: ba dbyibs mdog kyang zla gam dmar po'i rnam par
NK064(ngu),002:1142: gnas / rgyab na gsum yod pa gnyid rmug dang
NK064(ngu),002:1143: bcas pa'i las byed pas rang rgyud kyi rtsa zhes
NK064(ngu),002:1144: bya la dbyibs mdog kyang gru gsum dmar nag gi
NK064(ngu),002:1145: gnas / rnam par gnas / de yang phun sum
NK064(ngu),002:1146: tshogs pa lnga'i skad dod du e wam ma ya
NK064(ngu),002:1147: gnas / rnam par gnas / zhes 'byung la / de bod skad du bsgyur na /
NK064(ngu),002:1150: wam gyis mtshon pa'i ston pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1152: ya ni chos dang dus gnyis ka la 'jug ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1153: y+aa na'i sgra las theg pa chen po zhes bsnyad pas chos phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1154: ya yig gis mtshon pa'i dus te bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus rnams te /
NK064(ngu),002:1155: e sogs las bzhi'i dbyibs mdog can ni don dam
NK064(ngu),002:1156: 'od gsal gyi bzhugs gnas yin pas na gnas phun
NK064(ngu),002:1158: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1159: mi shigs thig le wam dbyibs can //
NK064(ngu),002:1160: rang la bde ba gsal byed dag /
NK064(ngu),002:1162: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo'i dbus na dwangs ma chen po lnga bzhugs te /
NK064(ngu),002:1163: sa'i dwangs ma rtsa dar dkar gyi skud pa lta bu sbom phra rta rnga bcu gshags tsam pa /
NK064(ngu),002:1164: de'i dbus na chu'i dwangs ma rgya mtshal lcog la'i khu ba lta bu /
NK064(ngu),002:1165: de'i dbus na me'i dwangs ma me long nyi ma la bzhag pa'i ngad tsam pa /
NK064(ngu),002:1166: de'i dbus na rlung gi dwangs ma gser sa 'og
NK064(ngu),002:1167: na yod pa'i rlangs pa nam mkha' la rgyu ba
NK064(ngu),002:1168: tsam pa / de'i dbus na nam mkha'i dwangs ma
NK064(ngu),002:1169: bar snang sang seng go 'byed pa'i rnam pa can
NK064(ngu),002:1171: de ltar dwangs ma lnga 'dus kyi dbus na ye
NK064(ngu),002:1172: shes snying po'i thig le stong gsal 'gags med yi
NK064(ngu),002:1173: ge wam dbyibs kyi rnam par gnas pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1174: rdo rje me long gi rgyud las /
NK064(ngu),002:1175: lus can snying la gang gnas pa //
NK064(ngu),002:1176: rang byung zag med ye shes gzugs //
NK064(ngu),002:1177: mi shigs thig le bde chen por //
NK064(ngu),002:1178: nam mkha' lta bur kun khyab pa //
NK064(ngu),002:1179: mi gnas chos sku'i rang bzhin yin //
NK064(ngu),002:1181: de nyid mar me gsal byed gzhan la ltos mi dgos pa ltar /
NK064(ngu),002:1182: rang gis rang la bde ba gsal bar ston pa'i phyir ston pa phun sum tshogs pa zhes bshad /
NK064(ngu),002:1184: ma nu yid sogs rnam shes bzhi //
NK064(ngu),002:1185: ye shes myong bas sdud par bshad //
NK064(ngu),002:1187: ma na shes pa la'o zhes yid la sogs pa'i rnam shes tshogs brgyad de /
NK064(ngu),002:1188: mdun chos nyid kyi rtsa la kun gzhi /
NK064(ngu),002:1189: g.yas ye shes kyi rtsa la yid /
NK064(ngu),002:1190: g.yon yon tan gyi rtsa la nyon yid /
NK064(ngu),002:1191: rgyab rang rgyud kyi rtsa la sgo lnga'i rna ma
NK064(ngu),002:1192: shes mig rna ba sna lce lus kyi rnam shes
NK064(ngu),002:1193: rnams te tshogs brgyad po des ye shes lnga nyams
NK064(ngu),002:1194: su myong bar byed pa'i cha nas 'khor phun sum
NK064(ngu),002:1195: tshogs pa'o // chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1196: ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs skyes pa //
NK064(ngu),002:1197: pa ra m+aar+tha don zab mo //
NK064(ngu),002:1199: de'i man ngag steng sgo'i lam nyams su blangs pa
NK064(ngu),002:1200: las bde gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes
NK064(ngu),002:1201: nam mkha'i gzugs can rgyud la skyes pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1202: pa ra m+aar+tha zhes pa'i sgra las /
NK064(ngu),002:1203: don dam pa'am don zab mo zhes gnas lugs kyi
NK064(ngu),002:1204: chos nyid zab mo yin pas chos phun sum tshogs
NK064(ngu),002:1205: pa'o // dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1206: bde ba'i dus nyid snga phyi bral //
NK064(ngu),002:1207: dus gsum kun gyi ngo bor gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:1209: ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs can rgyud la skyes pa
NK064(ngu),002:1210: de'i tshe snga phyir 'dzin pa'i rtog pa thams cad
NK064(ngu),002:1211: dang bral bas bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus te
NK064(ngu),002:1213: gnyis pa gsang ba 'og sgo dang sbyar te bshad rgyud thal bas bshad pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1214: 'di zhes nye bar mtshon pa ni //
NK064(ngu),002:1215: e sogs rnam bzhi'i dbyibs can gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:1216: skad ces gsal byed las ming can //
NK064(ngu),002:1217: wam dbyibs thig ler bcas ston pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:1218: ma d+aa ma nu sdom byed yid //
NK064(ngu),002:1219: las can rnam shes de dag la //
NK064(ngu),002:1220: gsal bar go bas bshad par 'dod //
NK064(ngu),002:1221: pa sgra don dam nges pa'i rgyud //
NK064(ngu),002:1222: y+aa na theg chen 'di yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:1223: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab dus //
NK064(ngu),002:1224: n+aa ma de ming zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:1226: de la gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1227: 'di zhes es mtshon pa'i chos 'byung gi rnam par gnas pa yum gyi b+ha ga sgo gru gsum /
NK064(ngu),002:1230: dbyings phyug gi sna rtse zlum por gnas pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1231: e sogs las bzhi'i dbyibs can ni gsang ba'i ston 'khor bzhugs pa'i gnas yin pas na gnas so //
NK064(ngu),002:1232: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1233: skad ces gsal byed las ming can //
NK064(ngu),002:1234: wam dbyibs thig ler bcas ston pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:1236: yab kyi rdo rje nor bu'i dbur rtsa sa ya
NK064(ngu),002:1237: phrag bcu gsum gyi bcud 'dus pa'i kun rdzob ye
NK064(ngu),002:1238: shes kyi thig le wam dbyibs kyi rnam pa can
NK064(ngu),002:1239: du gnas pa ni yab yum gnyis ka'i rgyud la
NK064(ngu),002:1240: bde ba gsal bar ston pa'i bdag nyid can yin
NK064(ngu),002:1243: ma d+aa ma nu sdom byed yid //
NK064(ngu),002:1244: las can rnam shes de dag la //
NK064(ngu),002:1245: gsal bar go bas bshad par 'dod //
NK064(ngu),002:1247: ma da na sdom byed dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1248: ma nu yid de byed pa sdom pa'i thabs /
NK064(ngu),002:1249: de ni 'du shes gsum ldan gyi mtshan rtog sdom
NK064(ngu),002:1250: par byed pa'i gsang ba'i rnam shes kyis reg bde
NK064(ngu),002:1251: nyams su myong bar byed pas na 'khor ro //
NK064(ngu),002:1252: chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1253: pa sgra don dam nges pa'i rgyud //
NK064(ngu),002:1254: y+aa na theg chen 'di yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:1256: thabs lam bde ba chen po'i ye shes nyams su
NK064(ngu),002:1257: myong bya sems lnga rdzogs pa'i dga' ba bcu drug
NK064(ngu),002:1258: gi ye shes ni rnam thar bzhi ldan te /
NK064(ngu),002:1259: ngo bo stong pa nyid dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1262: 'od gsal ba'i rnam par thar pa bzhi dang ldan
NK064(ngu),002:1263: pa rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes ni
NK064(ngu),002:1264: chos so // dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1265: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab dus //
NK064(ngu),002:1267: ye shes de nyams su myong ba'i tshe dus 'di
NK064(ngu),002:1268: zhes mtshon du med pas na bsam gyis mi khyab
NK064(ngu),002:1269: pa'i dus so // n+aa ma de ming zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:1271: phun sum tshogs pa lnga ka'i mjug sdud de ston pa phun sum tshogs pa zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:1272: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:1273: zhes pa la sogs pa'i don no //
NK064(ngu),002:1274: gnyis pa thun mong gi gleng gzhi ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1275: longs sku'i gleng gazhi'am rgyud 'byung ba khyad par can gyi gleng gzhi dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1276: zhar byung gdul bya dgos ched du bstan pa khro bo'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1277: sprul sku 'gro ba 'dul ba'i gleng gazhi'am bstan pa spyi'i gleng gzhir grags pa dang gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:1279: 'di nyid kyi le'u dang pos ston te /
NK064(ngu),002:1280: de la'ang phun sum tshogs pa lnga yod pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:1281: dang po chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1282: 'di skad bshad pa zhes pas bstan /
NK064(ngu),002:1283: de la 'di skad bshad rgyu ni rgyud don ma lus pa mtshon pa'i tshig 'phrad de /
NK064(ngu),002:1284: rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don thams cad mtshon pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:1285: de la bshad ces pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1286: ngas sngar 'og min du bshad pa nyid yang 'dir bshad par bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:1287: zhes ston 'khor dgongs pa tha mi dad pas bshad pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1289: nga ni che ba'i rgyal po ste //
NK064(ngu),002:1290: 'chad dang nyan pa'ang nga nyid yin //
NK064(ngu),002:1293: 'chad pa po nga chos kyang nga //
NK064(ngu),002:1294: rang gi tshogs ldan nyan pa'ang nga //
NK064(ngu),002:1296: nyi 'od seng ge'i rgya cher 'grel las kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:1297: bshad ces pas ni 'khor dang ston pa gnyis su med par bstan pa yin la /
NK064(ngu),002:1299: gnyis pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1301: de'i don ni longs sku'i gleng gzhi yin pas dus
NK064(ngu),002:1302: re 'ga' ba zhig gi nges pa las 'das pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:1303: phyir dus rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor chos gsungs
NK064(ngu),002:1304: pa'i dus yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu),002:1306: mdo rgyud gzhan rnams su 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na /
NK064(ngu),002:1308: 'dir de ltar ma smos pa'i phyir gleng gzhi log pas bka' yang dag pa ma yin no zer /
NK064(ngu),002:1309: de'i lan la gzhan lan la dpyad pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1310: rang lan gdab pa gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:1312: lha rje glan sh+aaka bzang na re /
NK064(ngu),002:1313: bshad thos gnyis tshig mi mthun kyang ston pas 'khor la bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1314: 'khor gyis ston pa las thos pa don mthun gsungs na'ang /
NK064(ngu),002:1315: thos pa la bshad pas ma khyab pa'i phyir legs par mi sems gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:1316: yang lha rje mda' tig na re /
NK064(ngu),002:1317: thos pa la ma rtogs log rtogs the tshom gyi skyon gsum srid pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:1318: 'dir bshad ces pa ston 'khor dgongs pa gnyis su
NK064(ngu),002:1319: med pas nyid la nyid kyis bshad pa'i phyir sngar
NK064(ngu),002:1320: gyi skyon gsum rnam par dpyad pa'o gsungs kyang mi
NK064(ngu),002:1321: 'thad de / bshad tsam la skyon gsum dang bral bas ma khyab cing /
NK064(ngu),002:1322: dgongs pa gnyis su med pa la nyid las nyid thos pa'ang 'gal ba'i phyir ro gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:1323: yang khyed bla ma dang rje sgro phug gi bzhed pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1324: sku gnyis kyis bstan pa'i khyad par yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:1325: longs skus tshig tu mi gsungs pas rna bas thos su med pa'i phyir bshad ces dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1326: sprul skus tshig tu gsungs pa'i phyir thos bya bar 'ong ba yin gsungs na'ang /
NK064(ngu),002:1327: longs skus gsungs pa'i rgyud thams cad la bshad ces 'ong bas khyab na /
NK064(ngu),002:1328: longs skus gsungs pa'i rgyud thams cad du de ltar
NK064(ngu),002:1329: 'byung rigs pa las ma byung ba'i phyir 'thad par
NK064(ngu),002:1330: ma go gsungs / yang lha rje dri ngas pa na re /
NK064(ngu),002:1331: ston pas dgongs pa brda'i bshad pa bsdus pa pos
NK064(ngu),002:1332: ma phri ma bsnan par bshad pa bzhed pa 'di
NK064(ngu),002:1333: la 'gal ba rang ma mthong ngo gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:1334: gnyis pa rang lan gdab pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1335: bshad ces pa gong du smos pa ltar ston 'khor
NK064(ngu),002:1336: dgongs pa dbyer med kyi phyogs bzung nas bshad pa
NK064(ngu),002:1337: yin la / dus na zhes pa'ang longs sku nges
NK064(ngu),002:1338: pa lnga ldan gyi dus yin pas skyon med do
NK064(ngu),002:1339: yin la / gsungs / gzhan du thun mong pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:1340: theg par gleng gzhi'i skabs su bdag gis thos pa
NK064(ngu),002:1342: bdag nyid kyis ston pa las mngon sum du thos
NK064(ngu),002:1343: kyi gzhan las brgyud de thos pa ni ma yin
NK064(ngu),002:1344: no // zhes chos khungs btsun par 'jog pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1345: yang tshig thos pa tsam du zad kyi don rtogs
NK064(ngu),002:1346: pa ni ma yin no zhes bka'i don rtogs dka'
NK064(ngu),002:1348: dus gcig na zhes 'byung ba yang /
NK064(ngu),002:1349: 'di ni ston pas dus lan gcig rang gsungs kyi
NK064(ngu),002:1350: gzhan du ma gsungs zhes bka'i don rnyed dka' ba
NK064(ngu),002:1352: yang dus gcig gi tshe 'di thos kyi gzhan du
NK064(ngu),002:1353: gzhan dag kyang thos so zhes sdud pa po rang
NK064(ngu),002:1354: nyid thos pa che ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1355: yang dus lan gcig gis khong du chud par shes
NK064(ngu),002:1356: rab phul du byung bar bstan pa yang yin no
NK064(ngu),002:1357: gsungs / gzhan yang 'di skad bdag gis thos pa
NK064(ngu),002:1358: ma smos pas bka' yang dag pa ma yin par
NK064(ngu),002:1359: gsungs / 'gyur na / bde mchog rtsa rgyud dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1360: 'jam dpal mtshan brjod sogs kyang der thal te /
NK064(ngu),002:1361: de ltar ma smos pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:1362: de nas gsang ba bshad par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:1364: de nas dpal ldan rdo rje 'chang //
NK064(ngu),002:1366: des na mngon rtogs rgyan gyi 'grel ba las /
NK064(ngu),002:1367: 'di ni rnam par bzhag pa gzhan kho na yin pas /
NK064(ngu),002:1368: theg pa gzhan gyi lugs la brten nas nam du'ang sun 'byin barjooda par mi bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:1369: zhes gsungs pa ltar yin gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:1370: gsum pa ston pa phun sum tshogs pa la'ang /
NK064(ngu),002:1372: ston pa'i ngo bo bshad pa gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:1374: de bzhin gshegs pa yang dag pa sogs nas /
NK064(ngu),002:1375: dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin te /
NK064(ngu),002:1377: de'i don ni de bzhin nyid du nar son pa'i rang bzhin /
NK064(ngu),002:1378: yon tan ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin /
NK064(ngu),002:1379: ye shes mtha' dbus dang bral ba'i rang bzhin /
NK064(ngu),002:1380: 'bras bu la mnga' mdzad kyang ngo bo bstan du med pa'i rang bzhin /
NK064(ngu),002:1381: mnyam pa nyid mngon du mdzad kyang spyod yul dang bral ba'i rang bzhin /
NK064(ngu),002:1382: gcig dang du ma las grol ba'i rang bzhin /
NK064(ngu),002:1383: dus gsum 'dul 'bral med pa'i rang bzhin dang bdun las /
NK064(ngu),002:1385: de bzhin gshegs pa zhes pas bstan te /
NK064(ngu),002:1386: de yang spyir ta th+aa ga ta'i sgra las /
NK064(ngu),002:1392: sngon gyi rgyal ba rnams kyis ji lta byang chub
NK064(ngu),002:1393: kyi spyod pa'i sgo nas gshegs pa de ltar lam
NK064(ngu),002:1394: mthun pas gshegs shing byon pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1395: de bzhin nyid ji lta ba bzhin mkhyen cing gsungs pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1396: 'dod yon gyi snang ba ji ltar snang ba de bzhin thabs kyi spyod pas gshegs pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1397: sems can skye ba rnam pa bzhi'i tshul gyis skye ba las /
NK064(ngu),002:1398: de dag gi bsam pa dang mthun par mngal nas
NK064(ngu),002:1399: skye ba de bzhin du gshegs pa sogs la bshad
NK064(ngu),002:1400: kyang / 'dir chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi don
NK064(ngu),002:1401: sgrib byed kyi zhen pa dang bral bas nar son
NK064(ngu),002:1402: kyang / zhing / de'i ngo bo mngon du gyur pas na gshegs pa zhes brjod pa yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:1404: de bzhin nyid du gshegs pa yang //
NK064(ngu),002:1405: sna tshogs zhen las grol bar bshad //
NK064(ngu),002:1408: gang phyir de bzhin nyid du gshegs //
NK064(ngu),002:1409: de bzhin gshegs pa mngon par brjod //
NK064(ngu),002:1411: gnyis pa yon tan ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1412: yang dag par rdzogs pa zhes pa 'dis bstan /
NK064(ngu),002:1413: rang byung gi ye shes la spang bya ma grub pas ma nor /
NK064(ngu),002:1414: mi 'gyur mi bslu bas yang dag pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1415: chos nyid de'i klong na 'bras bu sku dang ye
NK064(ngu),002:1416: shes kyi yon tan rdzogs par rang snang ba'i phyir
NK064(ngu),002:1417: spang thob med pa'i don yin pa'i phyir gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:1418: gsum pa ye shes mtha' dbus dang bral ba'i rang bzhin ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1421: sgrib bral gyi ye shes mtha' dbus med par brdal ba'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:1423: gnyid sad pa ltar sangs pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1424: pad+ma kha bye ba ltar rgyas pa'i don gnyis ka la 'jug pas /
NK064(ngu),002:1426: ma rig gnyid las sangs phyir dang //
NK064(ngu),002:1427: shes bya la yang blo rgyas phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:1429: 'dir mi mthun pa dang snying po dbyer med kyang
NK064(ngu),002:1430: don ji bzhin mngon du byas pa'i stobs kyis spang
NK064(ngu),002:1431: thob med pa'i yon tan mthar thug pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1433: ma rig pa nyid ye shes gsal //
NK064(ngu),002:1434: nyon mongs sdug bsngal byang chub mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:1436: bzhi pa 'bras bu la mnga' mdzad kyang ngo bo bstan du med pa'i rang bzhin ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1438: sgrib pa'i cha shas phra mo tsam yang mi gnas pas bdud bzhi bcom zhing /
NK064(ngu),002:1439: che ba'i yon tan gyi 'bras bu la mnga' mdzad
NK064(ngu),002:1440: kyang rang gi ngo bo 'di zhes bstan du med
NK064(ngu),002:1441: pa'i rang bzhin yin pas na de ltar du brjod
NK064(ngu),002:1442: pa'i phyir te / rdo rje las rim las /
NK064(ngu),002:1443: bdud bzhi la sogs rig pa'i gdengs kyi bcom //
NK064(ngu),002:1444: sku lnga la sogs yon tan brjod las 'das //
NK064(ngu),002:1445: rang gi ngo bo 'di zhes bstan du med //
NK064(ngu),002:1448: nyon mongs pa lnga nyid ma spangs par ye shes
NK064(ngu),002:1449: lnga'i ngo bor rnam par dag pas na nyon mongs
NK064(ngu),002:1451: de dag pas phung po lnga yang rigs lnga'i ngo bor sangs rgyas pas na phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK064(ngu),002:1452: de'i tshe dag pa lha dang ma dag pa rnam
NK064(ngu),002:1453: rtog gi 'ching ba las grol bas 'dod lha'i bar
NK064(ngu),002:1454: chad kyis mi tshugs te lha'i bu'i bdud bcom zhing
NK064(ngu),002:1455: / sems nyid skye 'chi las grol bas 'chi bdag gi bdud kyang bcom ste rgyas pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:1456: nyon mongs pa nyid rnam par dag /
NK064(ngu),002:1457: phung po lnga nyid mngon sangs rgyas //
NK064(ngu),002:1458: bdag nyid lha yi dkyil 'khor te //
NK064(ngu),002:1459: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:1461: lnga pa mnyam pa nyid mngon du mdzad kyang spyod yul dang bral ba'i rang bzhin ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1462: longs spyod chen po zhes pas bstan /
NK064(ngu),002:1463: 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid kyi don mngon du mdzad
NK064(ngu),002:1464: kyang 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la spyad bya
NK064(ngu),002:1465: spyod byed du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa dang bral ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:1466: sgo nas longs spyad pas spyod yul dang bral ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:1467: rang bzhin zhes bya ba yin /
NK064(ngu),002:1468: drug pa gcig dang du ma las grol ba'i rang bzhin ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1469: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK064(ngu),002:1470: kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje'i bdag nyid
NK064(ngu),002:1472: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i de bzhin gshegs
NK064(ngu),002:1473: pa thams cad kyi che ba'i yon tan gyi rten
NK064(ngu),002:1474: byed pa'i cha nas sku lnga dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1475: chos brda sprod pa'i cha nas gsung lnga /
NK064(ngu),002:1476: mi g.yo ba'i ngos nas thugs lnga /
NK064(ngu),002:1477: dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i ngos nas yon tan lnga /
NK064(ngu),002:1478: gzhan don mdzad pa'i ngos nas phrin las lnga ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1479: 'bras chos nyer lngar snang bas gcig gi rang bzhin dang bral zhing /
NK064(ngu),002:1480: 'bras chos nyer lnga po de rang byung gi ye shes su 'du zhing /
NK064(ngu),002:1481: rigs lnga yang drug par 'dus pas na du ma
NK064(ngu),002:1482: dang bral ba'i phyir bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gnas
NK064(ngu),002:1484: bdun pa dus gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i rang bzhin ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1485: ma lus mi lus lus pa med pa thams cad
NK064(ngu),002:1486: dang so so ma yin tha mi dad dbyer med
NK064(ngu),002:1489: rgyal ba rigs drug pa kun tu bzang po de
NK064(ngu),002:1490: khams gsum dang dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i 'khor ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:1491: chos thams cad dang so so ma yin tha mi
NK064(ngu),002:1493: kun rdzob tu rig pa sgyu ma'i snang brnyan yin pas so so ma yin /
NK064(ngu),002:1494: don dam par sems nyid du ma skyes pas tha mi dad /
NK064(ngu),002:1495: bden pa gnyis kyi tha snyad las kyang 'das pas na dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin can yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:1497: so so rang bzhin nges rnyed na //
NK064(ngu),002:1498: yang dag lam gyis bcos su med //
NK064(ngu),002:1499: ye nas ngo bo yod min na //
NK064(ngu),002:1500: nyon mongs spangs shing byang sgrub med //
