NK064(ngu),002:1501: ces pa la sogs pa rnams kyis gnod pa'i phyir ro gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:1502: de ltar bdun du bshad pa de ni spar khab
NK064(ngu),002:1503: kyi lugs ltar 'thad phyogs su bkod pa yin la
NK064(ngu),002:1504: / slob dpon bi ma las yang dag pa dang
NK064(ngu),002:1505: rdzogs pa gnyis so sor phye nas brgyad du bshad
NK064(ngu),002:1507: ston pa'i rang bzhin brgyad dang ldan //
NK064(ngu),002:1508: bdag nyid byed po kun tu bzang //
NK064(ngu),002:1511: byang chub mchog gi ngo bo dang //
NK064(ngu),002:1512: chos rnams rol par longs spyod dang //
NK064(ngu),002:1513: phyogs dus bde gshegs bdag po dang //
NK064(ngu),002:1514: chos so cog dang dbyer med pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:1515: zhes ston pa'i rang bzhin bzhir bshad kyang 'dir gong du smos pa ltar bzung ngo gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:1516: gnyis pa ston pa'i ngo bo bshad pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1517: sku mdun dang rgyab med pa thams cad du sogs nas /
NK064(ngu),002:1518: sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dbu gsum dang ldan pa /
NK064(ngu),002:1520: sngar smos pa'i rang bzhin de nyid gdul bya la
NK064(ngu),002:1521: sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan ma sna tshogs par snang
NK064(ngu),002:1522: ba'i rnam 'gyur gyi cha la ngo bo zhes bshad
NK064(ngu),002:1523: de / de la ston pa sku gsum gyi bdag nyid yin pa'i don rtags /
NK064(ngu),002:1524: thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i don rtags /
NK064(ngu),002:1525: ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i don rtags /
NK064(ngu),002:1526: rnam thar gsum dang ldan pa'i don rtags dang bzhi las /
NK064(ngu),002:1528: chos sku'i bdag nyid yin pa'i don rtags ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1529: sku mdun dang rgyab med pa'i thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal zhing zhes pas bstan /
NK064(ngu),002:1530: bde gshegs rang snang la sku mdun dang rgyab ma
NK064(ngu),002:1531: grub cing gdul bya'i snang ba la ris med pas
NK064(ngu),002:1532: thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal zhing gzugs
NK064(ngu),002:1533: sku'i yon tan mi 'gags pas de dang de ye
NK064(ngu),002:1534: shes kyi sku yin pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:1535: de ltar yang seng ge rtsa rdzogs las /
NK064(ngu),002:1536: kun tu bzang po'i zhal ni phyogs bcur gsal //
NK064(ngu),002:1537: kun gzigs kun bzang sku la mdun rgyab med //
NK064(ngu),002:1538: phyogs bcu gang bar spyan gyis rnam par gzigs //
NK064(ngu),002:1540: gnyis pa longs sku'i bdag nyid yin pa'i don rtags ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1541: mtshan dang dpe byad dang ldan pa zhes pas bstan /
NK064(ngu),002:1542: de la'ang thun mong dang khyad par gyi mtshan dpe gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:1544: phyag zhabs 'khor los mtshan dang rus sbal zhabs //
NK064(ngu),002:1546: thub pa'i sen mo zangs mdog dang //
NK064(ngu),002:1547: sogs dpe byad brgyad cu mnga' bas so //
NK064(ngu),002:1548: de ni 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po la'ang phyogs
NK064(ngu),002:1549: mthun tsam yod pas thun mong gi mtshan dpe zhes
NK064(ngu),002:1550: bshad / gnyis pa khyad par gyi mtshan dpe la'ang phyi nang gsang gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:1551: dang po phyi'i mtshan dpe ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1552: ston pa'i thugs me long lta bu la sogs pa
NK064(ngu),002:1553: ye shes bzhi po re re'ang bzhi bzhir phye ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:1554: ye shes bcu drug gi rtsal sems dpa' bcu drug
NK064(ngu),002:1555: / de'i yul chos nyid bcu drug gi rtsal sems ma bcu drug ste mtshan so gnyis dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1556: sems dpa' bcu drug por ye shes lnga'i rtags rigs
NK064(ngu),002:1557: lngas dbu brgyan pa'i lha brgyad cu ni dpe byad
NK064(ngu),002:1558: brgyad cu ste / spyi mdo las /
NK064(ngu),002:1559: mtshan gyi me tog la dpe byad kyi 'bras bus
NK064(ngu),002:1560: spras pa'i phyir sras kyi tshogs kyis kun nas brgyan
NK064(ngu),002:1562: gnyis pa nang gi mtshan dpe ni //
NK064(ngu),002:1563: spyi bo bde chen gyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab so gnyis ni mtshan so gnyis dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1564: lte ba'i re bzhi las stong pa'i rtsa bzhi phri bas drug cu /
NK064(ngu),002:1566: snying ga'i rtsa chen bzhi ste brgyad cu ni dpe byad brgyad cur bshad de /
NK064(ngu),002:1568: sgra dbyangs gsung gi gnas bzhi yis //
NK064(ngu),002:1569: dbye bas gsum gsum ngos gnyis dang //
NK064(ngu),002:1570: bzhi bcu gnyis su gyur pa yin //
NK064(ngu),002:1572: gsum pa gsang ba'i mtshan dpe ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1573: ston pa yab yum gnyis rol pa'i dus kyi dga' ba la brtsi ba yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:1574: yab yum gnyis kyi dga' ba bcu drug bcu drug ni mtshan so gnyis dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1575: yab kyi dga' ba re re la'ang ye shes lnga
NK064(ngu),002:1576: lnga'i ro dang ldan pa ni dpe byad brgyad cur
NK064(ngu),002:1579: +aa li k+aa li bde ba nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:1580: phan tshun ma 'dres gcig tu gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:1581: bcu drug ngos gnyis mtshan dang ldan //
NK064(ngu),002:1582: phyogs gcig ye shes lnga ldan pa //
NK064(ngu),002:1583: brgyad cu'o bzod sogs rgyu las 'phags //
NK064(ngu),002:1586: nang dang gsang ba'i mtshan dpe de rnams rtsa khams
NK064(ngu),002:1587: kyi rang bzhin du 'dug pa la rgyan du ji
NK064(ngu),002:1589: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la rtsa khams rnam par
NK064(ngu),002:1590: dag pa bde ba chen po'i rang bzhin du ro
NK064(ngu),002:1591: mnyam pa ni rgyan gyi nang nas mdzes byed mchog
NK064(ngu),002:1592: tu gyur pa yin pas de ltar du bshad pa
NK064(ngu),002:1593: yin gsungs / gsum pa sprul sku'i bdag nyid yin pa'i don rtags ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1594: bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad du sku gsung thugs sna tshogs par kun tu snang ba /
NK064(ngu),002:1596: 'di ni sprul pa thams cad kyi 'byung gnas yin
NK064(ngu),002:1597: pas mdzad pa'i snang tshul rnam par 'phrul pa bsam
NK064(ngu),002:1598: gyis mi khyab cing tshad med par rang snang ba
NK064(ngu),002:1599: ste / sdong po bkod pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:1600: skra yi rtse mo gcig la yang //
NK064(ngu),002:1601: zhing rnams bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK064(ngu),002:1602: sna tshogs dbyibs kyang tha dad de //
NK064(ngu),002:1603: de dag 'dres par gyur pa med //
NK064(ngu),002:1605: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdo las kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:1607: nam mkha' ji tsam khyab pa de srid du de bzhin gshegs pa'i skus khyab bo //
NK064(ngu),002:1608: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs so //
NK064(ngu),002:1609: gnyis pa thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i don rtags ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1610: thabs dang shes rab kyi zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs kyis skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa /
NK064(ngu),002:1612: thabs snying rje chen po dang shes rab stong pa
NK064(ngu),002:1613: nyid kyi ye shes kyi brdar zhabs gnyis yab yum
NK064(ngu),002:1614: gnyis ka bzhengs pa lta bu ma yin par yab
NK064(ngu),002:1615: rdo rje'i skyil krung dang yum brtul zhugs kyis skyil
NK064(ngu),002:1616: krung du mtshungs par bzhugs pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1618: thabs dang shes rab kyi zhabs gnyis mtshungs par skyil
NK064(ngu),002:1619: krung du bcings nas snyoms par 'jug cing bzhugs pa
NK064(ngu),002:1621: gsum pa ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i don rtags ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1622: ye shes drug gi phyag ye shes rin po che'i phyag rgya 'bar ba can /
NK064(ngu),002:1624: ye shes lnga rang byung gi ye shes dang drug ldan pa'i rtags su phyag drug dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1625: des 'gro don mdzad pa'i rtags su phyag mtshan drug 'dzin pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1626: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i mtshan mar gyur pa'i rdo rje sogs lnga dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1627: chos kyi dbyings kyi phyag rgyar dril bu ste drug 'dzin pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1628: sgyu 'phrul rol pa chen po las /
NK064(ngu),002:1629: ye shes drug gi bdag nyid kyis //
NK064(ngu),002:1630: phyag rgya rin chen 'bar bas mtshan //
NK064(ngu),002:1631: rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NK064(ngu),002:1634: bzhi pa rnam thar gsum chub pa'i don rtags ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1635: sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dbu gsum dang ldan pa zhes pas bstan /
NK064(ngu),002:1637: gsung mtshan ma med pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1638: thugs smon pa med pa gsum ni blo'i yul las 'das pas bsam gyis mi khyab la /
NK064(ngu),002:1639: de gsum gyi mtshan mar dbu g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing gar snang ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:1641: bzhi pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa la gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:1642: dang po gnas kyi rang bzhin ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1643: 'og min gyi gnas mtha' dang dbus med pa na /
NK064(ngu),002:1647: mtha' dbus med pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK064(ngu),002:1648: de ni gnas kyi bla mar 'dod //
NK064(ngu),002:1655: dbang phyug chen po'i 'og min dang lnga las /
NK064(ngu),002:1656: dang po ni chos kyi dbyings la grags te de ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rten gnas sam /
NK064(ngu),002:1657: rnam rtog dang mtshan ma gang gi yang 'og tu ma gyur pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1660: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:1662: gnyis pa rig pa'i 'og min ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1663: de ni chos kyi dbyings de rtogs pa'i rang rig pa'i ye shes la bya ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1664: gnyis 'dzin gyi 'og tu ma gyur pas so //
NK064(ngu),002:1665: gzhan du na longs sku'i zhing dang cha mthun par
NK064(ngu),002:1666: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa
NK064(ngu),002:1667: la'ang de ltar du grags pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:1669: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ji lta bar //
NK064(ngu),002:1672: gsum pa gsang ba'i 'og min ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1673: yum gyi mkha' la grags te ston pa'i gsang ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:1674: sku'i bzhugs gnas yin cing mtshan ma'i rtog pa rang
NK064(ngu),002:1675: rgyud pa'i 'og tu ma gyur pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1677: nub phyogs 'og min gnas mchog tu //
NK064(ngu),002:1678: ma chags pad+ma'i gdan steng na //
NK064(ngu),002:1679: dus gsum sangs rgyas bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:1682: rdo rje btsun mo'i b+ha ga la bzhugs so //
NK064(ngu),002:1683: zhes gsungs pa de yin gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:1684: bzhi pa 'jig rten gnas kyi 'og min ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1685: de ni gzugs khams gnas rigs bcu bdun gyi ya
NK064(ngu),002:1686: mtha' gtsang ma'i rigs kyi lha lnga'i dang po ste
NK064(ngu),002:1687: / gzugs can gyi gnas gzhan gyi 'og tu ma gyur pas so //
NK064(ngu),002:1689: lnga pa dbang phyug chen po'i 'og min ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1690: skabs 'dir bstan gyi longs sku'i bzhugs gnas su gyur pa'i 'og min chen po ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1692: gtsang ma'i rigs bdag rnam spangs pa'i //
NK064(ngu),002:1693: 'og min chen po'i gnas mchog na //
NK064(ngu),002:1694: rigs bdag phyag rgya lhun grub sku //
NK064(ngu),002:1695: gcig dang du ma rnam spangs pa //
NK064(ngu),002:1696: sangs rgyas kun gyi gzugs spyi ste //
NK064(ngu),002:1697: gdod nas theg chen mdzod yin phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:1698: sgrib pa mtha' spangs gdul bya la //
NK064(ngu),002:1699: skad cig gcig gis snang bar mdzad //
NK064(ngu),002:1700: ces gsungs pa'i phyir ro gsungs //
NK064(ngu),002:1701: de yang sangs rgyas kyi zhing ni rang nyid gang
NK064(ngu),002:1702: na gnas pa'i rang snang yin pas ma dag pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:1703: zhing spangs pa'i pha rol na dag pa'i zhing gzhan
NK064(ngu),002:1704: zhig blos btsal du med pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:1706: yang dag shes pa'i rang rig blo med na //
NK064(ngu),002:1707: bde gshegs zhing yang ngan song gnas su mthong //
NK064(ngu),002:1708: theg mchog mnyam pa'i don nyid rtogs pa na //
NK064(ngu),002:1709: ngan song gnas kyang 'og min dga' ldan gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:1712: spu yi rtse mo gcig la yang //
NK064(ngu),002:1713: zhing rnams bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK064(ngu),002:1714: sna tshogs dbyibs kyang tha dad de //
NK064(ngu),002:1717: phal po che'i mdo las kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:1718: rdul gcig steng na rdul snyed sangs rgyas rnams //
NK064(ngu),002:1719: zhes gsungs pa ltar don la nam mkhas gar khyab
NK064(ngu),002:1720: tu sangs rgyas kyi sku dang phri na las kyis
NK064(ngu),002:1721: khyab la / sh+aakya thub pa'i zhing 'di nyid kyang rang mtshan par ma grub ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1722: 'di ltar dri ma med par grags pa'i mdo las /
NK064(ngu),002:1723: btsun pa sh+aa ri'i bus smras pa /
NK064(ngu),002:1724: bdag gis ni sa chen po 'di mtho dman dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1726: ljan ljin gyis gang bar mthong ngo //
NK064(ngu),002:1728: sangs rgyas mya ngan med pa'i zhig nas 'ongs pa'i tshangs pa ral pa can gyis smras pa /
NK064(ngu),002:1729: bdag gis ni bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa'i zhing
NK064(ngu),002:1730: 'di nyid gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi lha'i gnas kyi
NK064(ngu),002:1731: bkod pa phun sum tshogs pa bzhin du yongs su
NK064(ngu),002:1732: dag par mthong ngo zhes zer /
NK064(ngu),002:1733: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu),002:1734: rnams la sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di'i rang bzhin bstan
NK064(ngu),002:1735: par mdzad pas / thams cad kyis shar phyogs kyi
NK064(ngu),002:1736: sangs rgyas rin po che'i rgyan bkod pa'i zhing khams
NK064(ngu),002:1737: bzhin yongs su dag par mthong bar gyur pa de'i
NK064(ngu),002:1738: tshe bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK064(ngu),002:1739: nga'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing ni rtag tu 'di 'dra ste khyed rnams kyis ma mthong ngo //
NK064(ngu),002:1741: gnyis pa gnas kyi ngo bo ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1742: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo gsal ba la zhes pa nas /
NK064(ngu),002:1743: gos pa med pa pad+ma rin po che'i gdan la /
NK064(ngu),002:1745: de'i don ni dbyings dang ye shes dbyer mi phyed
NK064(ngu),002:1746: pa'i rtags gzhal yas khang gi dbyibs dang kha dog
NK064(ngu),002:1749: gnas kyi rang bzhin de bzhin nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:1750: ngo bo 'og min gzhal yas khang //
NK064(ngu),002:1751: zhes gsungs pa ltar de bzhin nyid kyi ngang las yon tan gyi khyad par rang snang ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1752: de yang gnas kyi ngo bo'i chos rnams dbye bar bya ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1754: gzhal yas gzhi dang rgyu dang rgya //
NK064(ngu),002:1755: dbyibs dang glo 'bur rtse mo dang //
NK064(ngu),002:1756: rgyan dang sgo 'khyud rta bab dang //
NK064(ngu),002:1757: mtshan nyid gdan gyi rnam pa ste //
NK064(ngu),002:1759: dang po gzhal yas khang gi spyi'i 'og gzhi ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1760: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo gsal ba la /
NK064(ngu),002:1763: spyi'i 'og gzhi ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i rtags rgya
NK064(ngu),002:1764: khyon tshad med pa'i 'khor lo'i rnam pa can te
NK064(ngu),002:1765: / bshad rgyud rol pa chen po las /
NK064(ngu),002:1766: 'khor lo chen po'i sa gzhi la //
NK064(ngu),002:1767: khang pa gru bzhi rnam par brjid //
NK064(ngu),002:1770: spags pa zhes pas bstan te /
NK064(ngu),002:1771: gzhal yas khang gi sgo dang khyams sogs nas lte
NK064(ngu),002:1772: ba'i bar gyi nang gi 'og gzhi de rim pa
NK064(ngu),002:1773: ltar rdo rje 'greng bu res spags pa yin te
NK064(ngu),002:1774: theg pa 'og ma nas 'dir 'phar ba'i rtags yin
NK064(ngu),002:1775: pa'i phyir gsungs / gnyis pa rgyu ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1776: ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK064(ngu),002:1778: gdul bya'i re ba skong ba'i rtags su rgyu rin
NK064(ngu),002:1779: po che las grub pa'i ye shes nyid dbyibs dang
NK064(ngu),002:1780: kha dog tu rang snang bas so gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:1782: rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa /
NK064(ngu),002:1784: phyogs kun tu yongs su ma chad par chos dbyings
NK064(ngu),002:1785: mtha' klas par khyab par rang snang ba'i phyir gsungs
NK064(ngu),002:1787: yon tan dpag tu med pa rgyas pa'i phyir gru bzhir gyur pa /
NK064(ngu),002:1789: don ni gru bzhi pa yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:1790: de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon tan gyis 'dir khyab pa dang mnyam pa dang rgyas pa'i don te /
NK064(ngu),002:1791: de ltar yang rgya cher 'grel las /
NK064(ngu),002:1792: mnyam pa'i phyir dang khyab pa'i phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:1793: rgyas pa'i phyir ni gru bzhir 'gyur //
NK064(ngu),002:1796: lhag pa'i ye shes rin po che'i glo 'bur gyis mdzes pa /
NK064(ngu),002:1799: gru chad las phyir 'phyar ba'i phyir dbyibs mkhar thabs kyi 'bur thabs lta bu dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1800: kha dog rigs bzhi'i mdog can gyi rin po che'i glo 'bur gyis mdzes pa yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:1801: ye shes re re yang lhag pa'i ye shes bzhi bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags so gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:1802: drug pa rtse mo'i don ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1803: rtse mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil
NK064(ngu),002:1804: 'khor ma lus pa thams cad so so ma yin
NK064(ngu),002:1805: ngo bo nyid gcig pa'i ye shes kun tu 'khyil
NK064(ngu),002:1810: tshad dpag tu med pa dang dbyibs bum pa zlum po'i rnam par 'khyil ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1811: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes la mthar thug pa med cing spros pa dang bral bas so gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:1813: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes rin
NK064(ngu),002:1814: po che'i dbyibs dang kha dog la sogs pa rnam
NK064(ngu),002:1815: pa tha dad pa'i bye brag dang khyad par du
NK064(ngu),002:1817: ye shes rin po che'i phreng ba dang sogs nas /
NK064(ngu),002:1818: mi sgrib par gsal ba'i rgyan bsam gyis mi khyab pas klubs pa /
NK064(ngu),002:1821: spyir rgyan gyi rnam grangs la bdun du nges pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:1823: gzhal yas khang gi lte bar ye shes lnga mtshon
NK064(ngu),002:1824: pa'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i mthar chos nyid mtshon
NK064(ngu),002:1825: pa'i rdo rje'i ra ba zlum pos bskor ba dang
NK064(ngu),002:1826: / gnyis pa logs rgyan la gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:1828: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi rtsal snang ma
NK064(ngu),002:1829: 'gags par rang snang ba'i rtags su pany+tsa re kh+aa'i
NK064(ngu),002:1830: rtsig pa lnga'i steng na rin po che'i pha gu
NK064(ngu),002:1834: mda' yab la sogs pa'i rgyan khyad par du 'phags pa du mas spras pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1836: ye shes rtsig steng seng mgos gtams //
NK064(ngu),002:1837: mi 'jigs kha nas mu tig har //
NK064(ngu),002:1838: pha gu mdzes pa'i bad dang ldan //
NK064(ngu),002:1839: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed mgul 'khor ldan //
NK064(ngu),002:1842: gzugs rdo rje ma sogs 'dod yon lnga'i lha mos phyogs kun tu 'khrigs pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1843: don 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga ma spangs rnam dag
NK064(ngu),002:1844: rol pa'i rgyan du shar ba'i rtags su de ltar
NK064(ngu),002:1847: gzugs sogs lha maso 'khrigs pa ste //
NK064(ngu),002:1848: sna tshogs mchod byed rol mo yis //
NK064(ngu),002:1849: bar snang khams kun sprin phung bzhin //
NK064(ngu),002:1852: dbus bum pa zlum po'i steng du bre mtshon pa'i 'phyur bu'i rtser /
NK064(ngu),002:1853: pad+ma la gnas pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo rim pa
NK064(ngu),002:1854: bcu gsum gyi steng na rat+na'i gdugs kyis mdzes shing
NK064(ngu),002:1855: rdo rje rin po che'i tog gis mdzes par spras
NK064(ngu),002:1856: pa ste / rdo rje me long las /
NK064(ngu),002:1857: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor byas shing //
NK064(ngu),002:1858: nyon mongs tshad pa'i gdung ba sel //
NK064(ngu),002:1859: thugs rje'i gdugs kyi rtsa ba brtan //
NK064(ngu),002:1860: ma lus gcig tu 'dus pa ni //
NK064(ngu),002:1863: rta babs kyi rtser gdugs kyi rtsa bar 'khor lo ri dwags kyis bskyod pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1864: gzhan yang phyogs kun tu rnga yab dang ba dan
NK064(ngu),002:1865: la sogs pas mdzes par spras pa'i phyir ro gsungs
NK064(ngu),002:1866: / bzhi pa sgo dang rta babs kyi rgyan ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1867: sgo glang seng la sogs pa'i rgyan gyi bye brag sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1869: gzhal yas de yi sgo bzhi na //
NK064(ngu),002:1870: glang seng gnyis kyis mdzes par brgyan //
NK064(ngu),002:1871: rta babs rnams kyi 'khor lo la //
NK064(ngu),002:1872: gser gyi dril bu 'bar ba dag /
NK064(ngu),002:1873: dkon mchog gsum gyi sgra dbyangs sgrog /
NK064(ngu),002:1875: lnga pa phyi rol gyi rgyan ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1876: sgo'i g.yas g.yon gnyis na t+aa la'i ljon pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1877: dpag bsam gyi shing dang gser gyi thig gus sbrel
NK064(ngu),002:1878: ba las dril bu'i sgra sgrog pa la sogs pas
NK064(ngu),002:1880: sgo bzhi'i g.yas g.yon ljon shing dang //
NK064(ngu),002:1881: dpag bsam shing zung cong cong sbrel //
NK064(ngu),002:1882: dril bu g.yer kha theg chen sgrog /
NK064(ngu),002:1883: bkra shis bya snyan sgra sgrog ldan //
NK064(ngu),002:1884: yid bzhin rin chen brgyad bskor ba //
NK064(ngu),002:1885: rin chen phung po bzhi gnyis ldan //
NK064(ngu),002:1886: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:1887: drug pa ngo bo nyid kyi rgyan ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1888: bden bzhi mtshon pa'i gru chad dang /
NK064(ngu),002:1889: bden pa gnyis med mtshon pa'i bar khyams la sogs pas mdzes par brgyan pa'o gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:1890: bdun pa bdag po'i rgyan ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1891: dkyil 'khor sprul pa'i 'phro 'du rgyal ba bzhi bcu
NK064(ngu),002:1892: rtsa gnyis kyis gzhal yas khang mdzes par brgyan pa
NK064(ngu),002:1894: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis kyis brgyan //
NK064(ngu),002:1896: brgyad pa gzhal yas khang gi sgo'i don ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1897: rnam par thar pa bzhi'i sgo nas 'jug pa'i sgo 'khyud can /
NK064(ngu),002:1900: gzhal yas khang der 'jug pa'i sgo ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1901: rnam thar bzhi'i ting 'dzin gyi sgo nas byang chub
NK064(ngu),002:1902: chen por lhun gyis 'jug pa'i rtags su phyogs kyi
NK064(ngu),002:1903: dbye ba'i sgo bzhi dang ldan pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1906: de phyir ye shes sgo bzhir shar //
NK064(ngu),002:1908: de'ang thang sgo lta bu ma yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:1909: sgo 'khyud kyi zlas drangs pa'i 'gram logs dang ya
NK064(ngu),002:1910: phugs rdo rje'i d+r+wa mig can la sogs pas brgyan
NK064(ngu),002:1911: pa'o gsungs / dgu pa rta babs ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1912: rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi rta babs dang ldan pa //
NK064(ngu),002:1914: de la rgyu'i rta babs brgyad dang 'bras bu'i rta
NK064(ngu),002:1915: babs brgyad de bcu drug tu bstan pa yin te
NK064(ngu),002:1917: lam brgyad rim par bgrod pa yis //
NK064(ngu),002:1918: 'bras bu'i yon tan kun rdzogs pas //
NK064(ngu),002:1919: rta babs rgyu 'bras bcu drug bstan //
NK064(ngu),002:1921: de la rgyu'i rta babs ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1922: mtshon sgo rnam thar bzhi'i sgo nas mtshon bya byang chub chen por 'jug pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1923: de yang thun mong rnam thar gyi theg pa brgyad
NK064(ngu),002:1924: la sbyangs pas rtogs pa'i rtags su sgo phugs kyi
NK064(ngu),002:1925: phyi nang gnyis su them skas bzhi bzhi ste babs
NK064(ngu),002:1926: zhon gyi rta babs brgyad dang ldan pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1928: der 'gro lam stegs brgyad dang ldan //
NK064(ngu),002:1929: rta babs brgyad du 'gyur ba yin //
NK064(ngu),002:1932: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub dang //
NK064(ngu),002:1933: bya ba rgyud dang gnyis ka rgyud //
NK064(ngu),002:1934: rnal 'byor bskyed dang rdzogs pa yi //
NK064(ngu),002:1935: rnam thar brgyad phyir rta babs brgyad //
NK064(ngu),002:1938: theg pa brgyad kyi grub mtha'i yon tan brgyad rdzogs
NK064(ngu),002:1939: pa'i rtags su sgo logs kyi zur bzhi nas ka
NK064(ngu),002:1940: bas btegs pa'i steng du rgyan gyi rta babs brgyad
NK064(ngu),002:1942: sgyu 'phrul bye brag bstan pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:1943: de yi grub pa'i mtha' rdzogs pa'i //
NK064(ngu),002:1944: yon tan brgyad phyir rta rkang dang //
NK064(ngu),002:1945: chu skyes sgrom dang za ra tshags //
NK064(ngu),002:1947: khyung mgo mdzes pas rim par 'khrigs //
NK064(ngu),002:1949: de'ang rgyan dang ldan pa yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:1950: sgo khang dang sgo'i bsil khang gi mun pa sel
NK064(ngu),002:1951: byed glang rgyab mig gsum la sogs pa'i rgyan du
NK064(ngu),002:1953: bcu pa gnas kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1954: phyi dang nang med pa kun tu'ang nang du gyur pa na /
NK064(ngu),002:1957: gzhal yas khang de'i mtshan nyid ni chos kyi dbyings
NK064(ngu),002:1958: rdo rje kun tu bzang mo'i b+ha ga nyid du
NK064(ngu),002:1959: 'dus pas na tha snyad du'ang kun tu nang zhes
NK064(ngu),002:1961: rang byung ye shes la phyi gzung ba'i yul dang
NK064(ngu),002:1962: nang 'dzin pa'i sems gnyis su med pa'i shes bya'i
NK064(ngu),002:1963: dkyil 'khor kun kyang rang byung gi ye shes su
NK064(ngu),002:1964: gsal ba las gzhan ma dmigs pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:1966: gnas mchog mtshan nyid brjod pa ni //
NK064(ngu),002:1967: gzhal yas phyi nang chos dbyings nang //
NK064(ngu),002:1968: b+ha ga nyid du bsdus pas na //
NK064(ngu),002:1969: kun tu nang zhes brjod pa yin //
NK064(ngu),002:1971: de ltar na chos kyi dbyings de'i ngang las ye
NK064(ngu),002:1972: shes kyi 'phrul par snang ba'i gzhal yas khang rgyan
NK064(ngu),002:1973: dang bcas pa thams cad kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:1974: shel gyi sbu gur rin po che sna tshogs bcug
NK064(ngu),002:1975: pa ltar mi sgrib par gsal ba'i rang bzhin can
NK064(ngu),002:1977: phyi dang nang med pa kun tu yang nang du gyur pa na /
NK064(ngu),002:1979: bcu gcig pa gdan khri'i don ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1980: mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i khri dang sogs nas /
NK064(ngu),002:1981: gos pa med pa pad+ma rin po che'i gdan la /
NK064(ngu),002:1983: de'i don bshad na gsum ste /
NK064(ngu),002:1984: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i gdan /
NK064(ngu),002:1985: sa'i khyad par bgrod pa'i gdan /
NK064(ngu),002:1986: yon tan gyi che bas nyes tshogs bcom pa'i gdan dang gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:1988: sngar bshad pa'i 'og gzhi'i gdan te rigs lnga ye
NK064(ngu),002:1989: shes lnga'i phyag rgyas rtog tshogs gcod pa'i chos kyi
NK064(ngu),002:1990: 'khor lo rgyun mi chad par bskor ba'i rtags su
NK064(ngu),002:1991: rang snang ba de yin gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:1992: gnyis pa sa'i khyad par bgrod pa'i gdan ni /
NK064(ngu),002:1993: yon tan gyi rtags su seng ge la sogs pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:1994: sems can lnga po re re'ang brgyad brgyad kyis gdan
NK064(ngu),002:1995: khri dang ldan pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:1996: rang byung gi ye shes rtogs pa'i rig pa la
NK064(ngu),002:1997: 'bras bu'i chos mi 'jigs pa bzhi sogs lhun gyis
NK064(ngu),002:1998: grub pas yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas su
NK064(ngu),002:1999: bstan cing nges par byas pa'i rtags su de ltar
NK064(ngu),002:2001: dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK064(ngu),002:2002: thugs ni mi 'jigs bzhi yis bdud bzhi bcom //
NK064(ngu),002:2003: de grub rtags su seng ge'i khri la bzhugs //
NK064(ngu),002:2004: sku ni stobs bcus mi dge bcu rnams 'dul //
NK064(ngu),002:2005: de grub rtags su glang chen khri la bzhugs //
NK064(ngu),002:2006: yon tan rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhis chags med sgrol //
NK064(ngu),002:2007: de grub rtags su rta mchog khri la bzhugs //
NK064(ngu),002:2008: gsung ni dbang bcu mthar phyin rgyal po'i gsungs //
NK064(ngu),002:2009: de grub rtags su rma bya'i khri la bzhugs //
NK064(ngu),002:2010: las ni phrin las bzhi yis thogs med sgrol //
NK064(ngu),002:2011: de grub rtags su shang shang khri la bzhugs //
NK064(ngu),002:2013: de la mi 'jigs pa bzhi ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2014: ji lta ji snyed pa'i chos ma lus pa mngon
NK064(ngu),002:2015: sum du rtogs pa'i tshul gyis bdag nyid mngon par
NK064(ngu),002:2016: rdzogs par sangs rgyas so zhes zhal gyis bzhes pa
NK064(ngu),002:2018: thar pa thob pa la sgrib pa 'gog dgos so
NK064(ngu),002:2019: zhes bar du gcod pa'i chos ston pa la mi
NK064(ngu),002:2020: 'jigs pa dang / nges 'byung gi theg pa gsum gyi lam ston pa la mi 'jigs pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2021: spang bya spangs pa'i 'gog pa thob pa la mi 'jigs pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2023: chos kun rdzogs par byang chub dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2024: gegs ni 'gog par byed pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2025: lam ston pa dang 'gog ston la //
NK064(ngu),002:2026: mi 'jigs pa ni rnam pa bzhi //
NK064(ngu),002:2029: gnas dang gnas ma yin pa mkhyen pa'i stobs /
NK064(ngu),002:2030: las kyi rnam par smin pa mkhyen pa'i stobs /
NK064(ngu),002:2031: dbang po mchog dang mchog ma yin pa mkhyen pa'i stobs /
NK064(ngu),002:2032: 'jig rten gyi khams du ma mkhyen pa'i stobs /
NK064(ngu),002:2033: mos pa sna tshogs pa mkhyen pa'i stobs /
NK064(ngu),002:2034: thams cad du 'gro ba'i lam mkhyen pa'i stobs /
NK064(ngu),002:2035: nyon mongs pa dang rnam par byang ba mkhyen pa'i stobs /
NK064(ngu),002:2036: sngon gyi gnas mkhyen pa'i stobs /
NK064(ngu),002:2037: 'chi 'pho dang skye ba mkhyen pa'i stobs /
NK064(ngu),002:2038: zag pa zad pa mkhyen pa'i stobs rnams te /
NK064(ngu),002:2040: gnas dang gnas min las rnams kyis //
NK064(ngu),002:2041: rnam par smin dang dbang po dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2042: khams rnams dang ni mos pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2043: kun 'gro'i lam dang bsam gtan sogs //
NK064(ngu),002:2044: nyon mongs dri ma med pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2045: gnas ni rjes su dran pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2046: lha mi mig dang zhi ba dag /
NK064(ngu),002:2047: mkhyen pa'i stobs ni rnam pa bcu //
NK064(ngu),002:2049: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2051: dpyod pa'i ting 'dzin spong ba yis //
NK064(ngu),002:2052: 'du byed rnams ni rkang pa bzhi //
NK064(ngu),002:2055: yo byad skye ba tshe la dbang //
NK064(ngu),002:2056: ye shes chos dang sems dang las //
NK064(ngu),002:2057: rdzu 'phrul smon lam mos rnams kyis //
NK064(ngu),002:2058: khams sum kun gyi dbang phyug rgyal //
NK064(ngu),002:2061: zhi rgyas dbang drag las rnams kyis //
NK064(ngu),002:2062: thogs med las rnams lhun gyis grub //
NK064(ngu),002:2064: 'o na sems can gyi gdan de dag thugs rig
NK064(ngu),002:2065: pa rang snang bar 'dod pa ci yin zhe na
NK064(ngu),002:2066: / dper na rta bzang po gcig rang gi bsod
NK064(ngu),002:2067: nams kyis grub pa dang gzhan gyi dad pas phul
NK064(ngu),002:2068: pa gnyis rta gcig gi steng du mtshungs pa ltar
NK064(ngu),002:2069: / / sangs rgyas la mi 'jigs pa bzhi sogs lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags su snang ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2070: byang sems smon lam gyi rang dbang can rnams kyis
NK064(ngu),002:2071: seng+ge la sogs par sprul te gus pas lus gdan
NK064(ngu),002:2072: du phul te rna bas chos nyan pa'i phyir mi
NK064(ngu),002:2075: byang chub sems dpa' smon lam dbang //
NK064(ngu),002:2076: thos pa rgya mtsho bsags pa'i phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:2077: lus ni seng ge'i gdan du phul //
NK064(ngu),002:2079: gdan de rnams la sa'i khyad par bgrod pa'i gdan zhes brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2080: theg pa brgyad la bgrod nas 'bras bu'i yon tan
NK064(ngu),002:2081: thugs su chud pa'i rtags su seng ge la sogs
NK064(ngu),002:2082: pa re re'ang brgyad brgyad mjug ma nang du bsnol
NK064(ngu),002:2083: nas rin po che'i khri rkang 'degs pas so gsungs
NK064(ngu),002:2084: / gsum pa yon tan gyi che bas nyes tshogs bcom pa'i gdan ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2085: rgyal ba'i thugs rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal zhing thabs
NK064(ngu),002:2086: shes dbyer med pa'i rtags su nyi zla'i gdan dang
NK064(ngu),002:2087: / pad+ma 'dam las skyes kyang nyes skyon gyis ma
NK064(ngu),002:2088: gos pa ltar mtha'i skyon gyis gos pa med pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:2090: re ba yid bzhin du skong zhing dkor bdun ngo
NK064(ngu),002:2091: bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags su rin
NK064(ngu),002:2092: po che khri rkang mdzod mig bdun ldan rnams su
NK064(ngu),002:2094: gdan de rnams kyi brtsegs lugs kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:2095: skyes bu lnga la lnga brtsegs dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2096: sems dpa' la ni sum brtsegs so //
NK064(ngu),002:2097: nyi rkyang khro la pad rkyang thub //
NK064(ngu),002:2098: kun bzang yab yum bzhi brtsegs so //
NK064(ngu),002:2100: 'on kyang dkyil 'khor la 'god pa'i tshe de ltar yin gyi /
NK064(ngu),002:2101: 'dir chos 'chad pa'i tshe na kun bzang la gdan lnga brtsegs spyan 'grel las gsungs so //
NK064(ngu),002:2102: yang zla ba steng du 'ong ba'i rgyu mtshan yang /
NK064(ngu),002:2104: gtso bo ni shes rab la spyod pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:2105: nang gi chu skyes kyi lte ba'i nyi ma zla
NK064(ngu),002:2106: ba la brten pa'i phyir ri bong can steng na
NK064(ngu),002:2108: zla ba steng du 'ong ba gtso 'khor thabs snang ba 'gags pa med pa mtshon pa'i brda dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2109: lte ba'i a thung gi steng du spyi bo'i ham
NK064(ngu),002:2110: yig gam snying ga'i srog mi shigs pa'i thig le
NK064(ngu),002:2111: gnas pa'i phyir yang de ltar du bshad pa yin
NK064(ngu),002:2112: gsungs so // lnga pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa la /
NK064(ngu),002:2113: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i 'khor dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2114: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:2115: dang po la'ang rigs kyi yab lnga dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2117: dang po rigs kyi yab lnga ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2118: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang sogs nas /
NK064(ngu),002:2123: de lhar dag tshul bshad pa /
NK064(ngu),002:2124: de'i rigs kyii dbye ba bshad pa dang gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:2127: gzugs dang tshor ba 'du shes dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2128: 'du byed rnam par shes pa nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:2129: phung po lnga zhes rab tu brjod //
NK064(ngu),002:2130: ces gsungs pa ltar phung po lnga las /
NK064(ngu),002:2131: dang po rnam par shes pa'i phung po ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2132: spyir phung po zhes pa mngon pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:2133: du ma spungs pa phung po'i mtshan nyid /
NK064(ngu),002:2134: ces gsungs pa ltar dper na nas 'bru mang po
NK064(ngu),002:2135: spungs pa la nas phung zhes brjod pa dang gnad
NK064(ngu),002:2136: gcig gsungs / de la rnam par shes pa ni
NK064(ngu),002:2137: yul rnam par reg pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi tshogs
NK064(ngu),002:2138: gcig gsungs / brgyad de / kun gzhi /
NK064(ngu),002:2141: sgo lnga'i rnam par shes pa rnams te rnam shes kyi phung por bzhag /
NK064(ngu),002:2143: gzugs su rung ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi gzugs bco lnga yod de /
NK064(ngu),002:2146: gzugs ni dbang po lnga dang don //
NK064(ngu),002:2147: lnga dang rnam rig byed min nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:2148: ces pa ltar bcu gcig ste bco lnga ni gzugs kyi phung po'o //
NK064(ngu),002:2150: nyams su myong ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi tshor ba bde sdug bar ma gsum rnams so //
NK064(ngu),002:2152: yul la mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi
NK064(ngu),002:2153: 'du shes rgya che chung tshad med pa mtshan ma
NK064(ngu),002:2154: dang bcas pa mtshan ma med pa dang lnga'o //
NK064(ngu),002:2156: mngon par 'du byed pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi sems
NK064(ngu),002:2157: pa ste sems byung lnga bcu rtsa gcig yod de
NK064(ngu),002:2159: tshor 'du sems pa reg yid byed //
NK064(ngu),002:2161: 'dun mos dran ting shes rab ste //
NK064(ngu),002:2162: 'di dag yul nges lnga yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:2163: dad dang bag yod shin tu sbyangs /
NK064(ngu),002:2164: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug med //
NK064(ngu),002:2165: btang snyoms ngo tsha shes khrel yod //
NK064(ngu),002:2167: 'di dag dge ba bcu gcig go //
NK064(ngu),002:2168: 'dod chags khong khro nga rgyal dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2169: ma rig the tshom lta ba ste //
NK064(ngu),002:2170: drug po rtsa ba'i nyon mongs yin //
NK064(ngu),002:2172: phrag dog ser sna sgyu dang g.yo //
NK064(ngu),002:2173: rgyags dang rnam 'tshe ngo tsha med //
NK064(ngu),002:2174: khrel med dmu rgod ma dad dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2175: le lo bag med brjed nges dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2176: shes bzhin ma yin rnam g.yeng ste //
NK064(ngu),002:2179: zhes pa ste lnga bcu rtsa gcig las /
NK064(ngu),002:2180: tshor ba dang 'du shes gnyis phri ba'i lhag ma
NK064(ngu),002:2181: bzhi bcu rtsa dgu ni 'du byed kyi phung por
NK064(ngu),002:2182: 'jog pa'o gsungs / gzhung gzhan rnams su phung po'i go rim dang por gzugs phung smos la /
NK064(ngu),002:2183: 'dir rnam shes dang por smos pa ci yin zhe na /
NK064(ngu),002:2184: gzugs la sogs pa'i chos rnams kyang sems kyi rol rtsal tsam las gzhan ma yin pas so gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:2185: gnyis pa de dag lhar dag tshul bshad pa la /
NK064(ngu),002:2187: rang lugs bzhag pa gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:2188: dang po ni rje 'khon ston na re /
NK064(ngu),002:2189: 'di'i skabs kyi rnam shes ni tshogs brgyad ma yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:2191: gal te tsho gas brgyad du 'dod na //
NK064(ngu),002:2192: mi bskyod pa'i rgyud la kun gzhi yod pas dgra bcom pa ma yin par thal ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2193: nyon yid yod pas sgrib gnyis spangs pa'i gang zag
NK064(ngu),002:2194: ma yin par thal ba'i skyon yod do gsungs na'ang
NK064(ngu),002:2195: / thun mong gi gzhung dang bstun par zad kyi /
NK064(ngu),002:2196: 'dir ni shin tu mi rigs te /
NK064(ngu),002:2197: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK064(ngu),002:2198: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma yin //
NK064(ngu),002:2201: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2202: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' kun gzhi rnam par dag pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:2203: de yang yongs su ma dag pa'i dus na ni
NK064(ngu),002:2204: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba yin la
NK064(ngu),002:2205: / yongs su dag pa'i dus na ni mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:2207: de bas na theg pa 'di'i lugs kyi kun gzhi
NK064(ngu),002:2208: nyid chos dbyings ye shes su ye nas dag pas
NK064(ngu),002:2210: 'ching grol las 'das pa'i phyir ro gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:2211: gnyis pa rang lugs bzhag pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2212: rtog tshogs phung po lnga yi rang bzhin ye ji
NK064(ngu),002:2213: bzhin pa'i rigs lnga yin pa las khyad par du
NK064(ngu),002:2214: rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas lnga'i 'bras bu mngon du
NK064(ngu),002:2215: byas te mthar phyin par gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu),002:2216: de lta bu'i rtog pa la thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis rang dbang bsgyur zhing /
NK064(ngu),002:2217: zag med kyi chos la mnga' brnyes pas bde ba
NK064(ngu),002:2218: chen por longs spyod pas na rgyal po zhes bya'o
NK064(ngu),002:2219: // gzhung 'dir lha'i mtshan nas mi smos par rtog pa'i mtshan nas smos pa ci yin zhe na /
NK064(ngu),002:2220: ma dag pa 'khor ba'i gnas skabs su'ang rtog tshogs
NK064(ngu),002:2221: rnams rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa sku dang
NK064(ngu),002:2222: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rdzogs par gsang sngags
NK064(ngu),002:2223: kyi rgyud rnams su gsungs pa ma zad /
NK064(ngu),002:2224: nges don gyi mdo sde zab mo rnams las kyang 'byung ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2225: 'di ltar sdong po bkod pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:2226: gzugs dang tshor dang 'du shes dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2227: rnam par shes dang 'du byed ni //
NK064(ngu),002:2228: grangs med de bzhin gshegs pa rnams //
NK064(ngu),002:2229: de dag thub pa chen por 'gyur //
NK064(ngu),002:2231: des na rang bzhin shes bya'i gshis la rtog pa dang lha gnyis snang na snang mnyam /
NK064(ngu),002:2233: bzang ngan med par mnyam pa'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2234: thun min gyi theg pa 'dir lam pas lha rtog
NK064(ngu),002:2235: dbyer med du ngos zin par bya ba'i phyir dang
NK064(ngu),002:2236: / 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dus na rtog pa
NK064(ngu),002:2237: nyid ma spang ma bsgyur bar lha'i dkyil 'khor du
NK064(ngu),002:2238: rang snang ba'i phyir smos pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:2239: rtog tshogs lhar snang ba'i 'thad pa de gang yin zhe na /
NK064(ngu),002:2241: phyi rol gyi don yod pa'i dbang du byas pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2242: shes bya nang gi dbang du byas pa gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:2244: rtog pa'i rang bzhin lhar snang ba de ye nas
NK064(ngu),002:2245: yin pa nyid lam rkyen dang 'phrad pas lhar snang
NK064(ngu),002:2247: dper na dngul chus bsdus pa'i gser phye nyid dngul
NK064(ngu),002:2248: gyi gong bu ltar snang yang me'i rkyen dang 'phrad
NK064(ngu),002:2250: ma 'phrad na mi 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK064(ngu),002:2251: de ltar yang sgyu 'phrul rtog pa'i d+r+wa ba rnam par gsal ba'i rgyud phyi ma las /
NK064(ngu),002:2253: bcom ldan 'das rnal 'byor pa 'di dag rgyu ci lta bu zhig las bsgrub par bgyi ba lags /
NK064(ngu),002:2260: 'o na rgyu las kyang 'bras bu'i snang ba bskyed par 'gyur ba lags /
NK064(ngu),002:2263: rigs kyi bu de de bzhin te /
NK064(ngu),002:2264: rgyu las 'bras bu'i shes rab snang ngo //
NK064(ngu),002:2266: phung po la sogs pa gang dag sgyu ma'i phyag rgya bzhi bcur snang ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2267: don dam par ni don dam rtse gcig par snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu),002:2270: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa ltar na de nyid ni de ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:2271: sgrub par bya ba dang yang 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu),002:2274: dper na rkyen gyi 'brel ba dang ma 'phrad pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:2275: 'bras bu skye ba'i rgyu yod kyang mngon du 'byin
NK064(ngu),002:2276: pa'i nus pa med pa bzhin du /
NK064(ngu),002:2277: byang chub kyi rgyu yod kyang rkyen ting nge 'dzin
NK064(ngu),002:2278: dang ma 'phrad pa'i phyir 'bras bu 'byin pa'i nus
NK064(ngu),002:2279: pa med pas na de ltar shes par bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:2281: gnyis pa shes bya nang gi dbang du byas pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2282: rtog pa'i rang bzhin lhar snang ba yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:2283: de dang de chos mthun pas rnam shes ni thugs kyi bdag nyid /
NK064(ngu),002:2285: tshor ba ni yul la longs spyod du blta ba'i gzhi yin pa'i phyir yon tan gyi bdag nyid /
NK064(ngu),002:2286: 'du shes ni mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i bdag nyid phyi
NK064(ngu),002:2287: nang gi chos rnams tha snyad du 'dogs pa'i las
NK064(ngu),002:2288: kyi brda sprod pa'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2289: 'du byed ni bya ba byed pa las kyi bdag nyid yin pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:2290: de ltar yang rgyud gzhan las /
NK064(ngu),002:2291: gzugs ni rnam par snang mdzad nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:2292: tshor ba rin chen 'byung gnas la //
NK064(ngu),002:2293: 'du shes snang ba mtha' yas te //
NK064(ngu),002:2294: 'du byed don yod grub pa nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:2295: rnam par shes pa mi bskyod pa //
NK064(ngu),002:2299: tshul khrims la sogs phung po lnga //
NK064(ngu),002:2300: zag med rnams ni gzhan yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:2301: zhes nyer len gyi phung po lnga gnas gyur pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:2302: zag med kyi phung po lnga gsungs pa dang yang
NK064(ngu),002:2303: chos mthun brtsir yod dam zhe na /
NK064(ngu),002:2304: yod de rnam shes gnas gyur rnam par grol ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:2305: ye shes gzigs pa'i phung po ni thugs kyi bdag
NK064(ngu),002:2307: de bzhin du gzugs gnas gyur tshul khrims kyi phung po ni dri ma med pa'i sku dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2308: tshor ba gnas gyur ting nge 'dzin ni yon tan gyi gzhir gyur pa'i yon tan dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2309: 'du shes gnas gyur shes rab ni lung rtogs kyi chos kyi gzhir gyur pa'i phyir gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:2310: 'du byed gnas gyur rnam par grol ba'i phung po
NK064(ngu),002:2311: ni mdzad pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid dang
NK064(ngu),002:2312: gzhir gyur pa'i phyir phrin las te /
NK064(ngu),002:2314: gzugs kyi phung po gnas gyur tshul khrims sku //
NK064(ngu),002:2315: tshor ba gnas gyur ting 'dzin 'bum phrag brnyes //
NK064(ngu),002:2316: 'du shes gnas gyur shes rab phung po ste //
NK064(ngu),002:2317: 'du byed gnas gyur rnam par grol ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:2318: sems gyur ye shes de ni rnam grol mthong //
NK064(ngu),002:2321: rnam shes lhar dag pa'i tshe mig gi rnam shes kyang mi bskyod par dag gam ma dag /
NK064(ngu),002:2322: gnyis pa ltar na spyi bye brag dag mi gcig par 'gyur te /
NK064(ngu),002:2323: dag ma dag 'gal ba'i chos can yin pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:2325: mig gi rnam shes sa snying du dag par gsungs pa mi 'thad par thal /
NK064(ngu),002:2326: de las dag pa gzhan du brjod du med pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:2328: byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2329: zhes sogs gsungs pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK064(ngu),002:2331: ltos sa tha dad la ltos nas rnam shes kyi
NK064(ngu),002:2332: phung po spyi bye brag gnyis gtso 'khor du dag
NK064(ngu),002:2333: pa yin te / tha mal gyi rnam rtog ril
NK064(ngu),002:2334: por gcig tu zhen pa'i gnyen por bye brag sa
NK064(ngu),002:2335: snying sogs su dag tshul smos nas /
NK064(ngu),002:2336: lhar tha dad du zhen pa'i gnyen por spyir mi bskyod par dag tshul smos pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:2338: tha dad min las tha dad pa'i //
NK064(ngu),002:2339: nang dang nang gi phyi rol gyi //
NK064(ngu),002:2340: dkyil 'khor bsam yas ye shes rol //
NK064(ngu),002:2341: 'jigs med kun bzang phyag rgya'i mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:2343: gsum pa de'i rigs kyi dbye ba bshad pa la /
NK064(ngu),002:2346: zhar byung rigs kyi mtshan ma'i sku mdog bstan pa dang gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:2352: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po chos can /
NK064(ngu),002:2353: khyod lha'i dus na mi bskyod pa ma yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:2354: rnam shes thugs kyi bdag nyid rnam snang yin pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:2355: dbus su rigs rtags mtshon byed kyi gdan 'khor lo dang seng ge /
NK064(ngu),002:2357: chos dbyings ye shes rnams byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2358: khro bo'i skabs su'ang bud+d+ha he ru ka'i sku mdog dang sngags thog mar smos pa'i phyir zer /
NK064(ngu),002:2359: gnyis pa de dgag pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2360: de ltar rigs pa ma yin te thun mong ma
NK064(ngu),002:2361: yin pa'i lung rig man ngag gsum dang 'gal ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:2362: phyir / lung dang 'gal te sgyu 'phrul bla ma las /
NK064(ngu),002:2363: gzugs la rnam par snang mdzad de //
NK064(ngu),002:2365: rnam shes rdo rje sems dpa' ste //
NK064(ngu),002:2369: rnam shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:2370: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa //
NK064(ngu),002:2371: mi bskyod yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK064(ngu),002:2374: kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems rdo rje mi bskyod
NK064(ngu),002:2375: pa la rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po zhes gnas
NK064(ngu),002:2376: skabs 'dir bya'o zhes gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:2378: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po chos can /
NK064(ngu),002:2379: khyod rnam snang ma yin par thal /
NK064(ngu),002:2380: khyod mi bskyod pa yin pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:2381: rnam shes dag pa thugs kyi bdag nyid yin pa gang zhig /
NK064(ngu),002:2382: de rdo rje'i rigs mi bskyod par nges pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:2383: de ltar yang glang po che rab 'bogs kyi rgyud las /
NK064(ngu),002:2384: don dam par sems can gyi rnam par shes pa
NK064(ngu),002:2385: gnas su dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs kyi
NK064(ngu),002:2387: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje mi bskyod pa /
NK064(ngu),002:2389: yum nam mkha'i dbyings phyug ma chos can /
NK064(ngu),002:2390: khyod rnam snang gi yum ma yin par thal /
NK064(ngu),002:2391: khyed rnam shes kyi yul nam mkha'i khams dang sbyar
NK064(ngu),002:2392: ba'i mi bskyod pa'i yum du nges pa'i phyir te
NK064(ngu),002:2393: / rnam shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:2395: chos dbyings ye shes chos can /
NK064(ngu),002:2396: khyod gti mug dag pa sku'i rigs dang sbyor ba ma yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:2397: khyod zhe sdang dag pa thugs kyi rigs su bzhed pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:2399: zhe sdang rnam par dag pa'i rang bzhin rnam par
NK064(ngu),002:2400: shes pa'i phung po yongs su dag pa thugs rdo
NK064(ngu),002:2401: rje chos dbyings ye shes kyi bdag nyid mi bskyod
NK064(ngu),002:2403: ye shes thig le'i rgyud las kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:2404: gti mug me long ye shes te //
NK064(ngu),002:2405: nga rgyal mnyam pa nyid du dag /
NK064(ngu),002:2406: so sor rtog pa 'dod chags yin //
NK064(ngu),002:2407: bya ba grub pa phrag dog che //
NK064(ngu),002:2408: zhe sdang chos dbyings rnam par dag /
NK064(ngu),002:2410: khro bo'i skabs su bud+d+ha he ru ka gtso bor ma grub ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2411: pan grub kyi man ngag rnams su rgyud dkrug pa
NK064(ngu),002:2412: bsdebs nas gtso bor badz+ra he ru ka la bzhed
NK064(ngu),002:2413: pa'i phyir ro // de yang rgya cher 'grel las /
NK064(ngu),002:2414: zhi ba'i dus su mi bskyod pa dang por smos shing gtso bor byas la /
NK064(ngu),002:2415: khro bo'i skabs su ni gzugs kyi phung po rnam
NK064(ngu),002:2416: par dag pa bud+d+ha he ru ka dang por phyungs
NK064(ngu),002:2417: shing gtso bor smos pa ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK064(ngu),002:2418: de ni rgyud dkrug pa yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:2419: dbang phyug ma gtso bo la 'khril ba'i gnas skabs na de nyid mngon par 'gyur te /
NK064(ngu),002:2420: 'di ni rdo rje khrag 'thung nyid la ci nas kyang don gyis shes par bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:2422: 'dir yang rnam par shes pa'i rang bzhin zhe sdang
NK064(ngu),002:2423: rnam par dag pa'i ngo bo mi bskyod pa rdo
NK064(ngu),002:2424: rje khrag 'thung du mngon par 'du mdzad pa de
NK064(ngu),002:2427: gnyis pa rang lugs bzhag pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2428: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po la sogs pa de
NK064(ngu),002:2429: bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga po de dag gi rigs
NK064(ngu),002:2430: dang ye shes kyi dbye ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2431: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo mi bskyod pa ni thugs
NK064(ngu),002:2432: rdo rje'i rigs dang chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes
NK064(ngu),002:2433: / rnam snang sku de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK064(ngu),002:2434: rin 'byung ni yon tan rin po che'i rigs dang mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK064(ngu),002:2435: snang mtha' ni pad+ma'i rigs dang sor rtog ye shes /
NK064(ngu),002:2436: don grub ni phrin las kyi rigs dang bya ba grub pa'i ye shes su nges pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:2437: de ltar yang rdo rje bkod pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:2438: sku ni ma bcos de bzhin nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:2439: thugs ni mi 'gyur rdo rje'i rigs //
NK064(ngu),002:2440: yon tan kun 'byung rin chen rigs //
NK064(ngu),002:2441: gsung ni chags med pad+ma'i rigs //
NK064(ngu),002:2442: don grub spyod pa las kyi rigs //
NK064(ngu),002:2444: gsum pa rigs kyi mtshan mar gyur pa'i sku mdog bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2445: de dag kun kyang mthing ga dang sogs nas //
NK064(ngu),002:2448: rigs lnga po de dag kun gyi mtshan mas gyur pa'i sku mdog ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2449: chos dbyings ye shes dang rdo rje'i rigs mthing ga /
NK064(ngu),002:2450: me long ye shes dang bde gshegs rigs dkar po /
NK064(ngu),002:2451: mnyam nyid ye shes dang rin chen rigs ser po /
NK064(ngu),002:2452: sor rtog ye shes dang pad+ma'i rigs dmar po /
NK064(ngu),002:2453: bya grub ye shes dang las kyi rigs kyi mtshan ma ljang gur snang ba yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:2454: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'i rtags mthing ga /
NK064(ngu),002:2455: nyes skyon gyis ma gos pa'i rtags dkar po /
NK064(ngu),002:2456: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i rtags ser po /
NK064(ngu),002:2457: gdul bya la chags pa'i rtags dmar po /
NK064(ngu),002:2458: las sna tshogs lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags su ljang gur snang ba'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:2460: ma mthong rmongs pa thams cad la //
NK064(ngu),002:2461: ye shes mtshan nyid bstan pa'i phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:2462: dkar dang dmar dang ser ba dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2463: ljang gu la sogs nag por bstan //
NK064(ngu),002:2465: gnyis pa rigs kyi yum lnga ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2466: btsun mo dam pa snang ba'i dbyings dang sogs nas /
NK064(ngu),002:2467: bskyod pa'i dbyings la sogs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang gnyis su med pa /
NK064(ngu),002:2469: de'i don la yum lnga spyi'i mtshan bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2470: bye brag gi mtshan bshad pa gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:2472: btsun mo dam pa zhes pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2474: yum lnga la btsun mo zhes brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2475: skyed par byed pa'i rgyu dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2476: spyad par bya ba'i yul du gyur pas de ltar du brjod de /
NK064(ngu),002:2477: rtog pa'i dus su 'byung ba lngas phung po lnga bskyed pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2478: lha'i dus na rigs kyi yab lngas longs spyad par bya ba'i yul yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2479: yang na yum gyi ngo bo dbyings dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2480: yab kyi ngo bo ye shes yin pas /
NK064(ngu),002:2481: dbyings kyis ye shes bskyed pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2482: dbyings ye shes kyi yul du gyur pas so gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:2483: lnga po de la dam pa zhes brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2484: yon tan gyi khyad par gzhan las 'phags pas na dam pa zhes bshad /
NK064(ngu),002:2485: dbyings zhes pa la nyi 'od seng ges /
NK064(ngu),002:2486: dbyings kyi sgra ni mi zad pa la bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:2488: sras kyi 'byung khungs dang bde ba'i ye shes bskyed pa'i rgyur gyur pa'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2489: yum rnams dbyings kyi phyag rgyar gyur pas kyang de ltar du brjod do gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:2490: gnyis pa bye brag gi mtshan ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2491: yum nam mkha'i dbyings phyug ma la snang ba zhes brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2492: rtog pa dus na nam mkhas go ma phye na
NK064(ngu),002:2493: dngos po thams cad snang mi nus pas go 'byed
NK064(ngu),002:2495: lha'i dus na chos khams nam mkha' rnam shes kyi
NK064(ngu),002:2496: yul yin pa ltar thugs rdo rje mi bskyod pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:2497: yum dang / yum spyan ma la sra ba zhes brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2498: rtog pa'i dus na sra brtan mkhrang pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi sa'i khams dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2499: de lha'i dus na brtan cing rten du gyur pas sku'i rigs kyi yum dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2500: yum m+aa ma k+ai la mnyen pa zhes brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2501: rtog pa'i dus na gsher sdud brlan pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi chu'i khams dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2502: de lha'i dus na rgyud brlan cing yon tan sdud pa rin chen rigs kyi yum dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2503: yum gos dkar mo la dro ba zhes brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2504: rtog pa'i dus na tsha zhing bsregs pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi me'i khams dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2505: de lha'i dus na mtshan 'dzin gyi spu ris gsal
NK064(ngu),002:2506: bar shes rab kyi mes dag par byed pa'i bdag
NK064(ngu),002:2507: nyid pad+ma'i rigs kyi yum dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2508: yum dam tshig sgrol ma la bskyod pa zhes brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2509: rtog pa'i dus na yang zhing g.yo ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi rlung gi khams dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2510: de lha'i dus na rlung gis bskyod 'dod kyi bya
NK064(ngu),002:2511: ba byed pa ltar thogs pa med pa'i las can
NK064(ngu),002:2512: las kyi rigs kyi yum ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2514: sa chu spyan dang m+aa ma k+ai //
NK064(ngu),002:2515: me rlung gos dkar sgrol ma ste //
NK064(ngu),002:2516: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK064(ngu),002:2518: gnyis pa rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor la gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:2519: dang po rgyal sras sems dpa'i 'khor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2520: de nas byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2524: de'i don bshad na spyi dang bye brag gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:2526: sems dpa' yab rnams kyi mtshan la byang chub chen po rdo rje'i zhes brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2527: mig shes la sogs pa'i rtog tshogs rnams ye nas chos nyid byang chub kyi sems yin pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:2528: yin pa ltar mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu ni byang chub chen po /
NK064(ngu),002:2529: de ltar rgyu 'bras ltar snang yang don dam par
NK064(ngu),002:2530: lha rtog dbyer mi phyed pas na rdo rje zhes
NK064(ngu),002:2533: 'khor gyi bkod pa ji snyed pa //
NK064(ngu),002:2534: khams dang skye mched yin par grags //
NK064(ngu),002:2535: rnam shes yul dang dbang po dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2536: dus dang phyin ci ma log rnams //
NK064(ngu),002:2537: byang chub chen po'i rang bzhin du //
NK064(ngu),002:2538: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor yin //
NK064(ngu),002:2540: de dag gi yum sems ma rnams kyi mtshan la btsun mo zhes brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2541: skabs 'dir yul bzhis rnam shes bzhi bskyed pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2542: dus bzhis go phye nas dbang po bzhi bskyed pa'i cha nas de ltar du brjod pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu),002:2543: gnyis pa bye brag gi mtshan ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2544: nang sems yab bzhi po la mthong ba la sogs par smos pa ni rim pa ltar /
NK064(ngu),002:2545: mig rna ba sna lce'i rnam shes bzhi yin pas rtog pa'i mtshan te /
NK064(ngu),002:2546: mig dbang la brten nas mig shes kyis yul gzugs mthong ba la sogs pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:2547: mthong ba la sogs pa bzhi po lha'i dus na thugs kyi sems dpa' bzhi yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:2551: myong ba spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug rnams su nges pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:2552: de rnams la thugs kyi sems dpa' zhes brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2554: ka ni spyan gyi thugs kyi mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:2555: kha ni snyan gyi thugs kyi mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:2556: ga ni shangs kyi thugs kyi mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:2557: g+ha ni ljags kyi thugs kyi mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:2559: nang sems bzhi po'i yum yang /
NK064(ngu),002:2560: mthong bar bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2561: rim pa ltar yul gzugs sgra dri ro bzhi yin pas rtog pa'i mtshan te /
NK064(ngu),002:2562: mig shes la sogs pa'i mthong bya gzugs la sogs pa'i rten byed pa'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2563: de dag lha'i dus na mthong bar bya ba l+aa s+ye ma /
NK064(ngu),002:2564: nyan par bya ba g+airti ma /
NK064(ngu),002:2565: snom par bya ba m+aa le ma /
NK064(ngu),002:2566: myong bar bya ba n+airti ma rnams su nges pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:2567: de rnams la sku yi sems ma zhes brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2568: yul bzhis rnam par shes pa'i rten byed pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:2570: tsa ni spyan gyi sku yi mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:2571: tsha ni snyan gyi sku yi mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:2572: dza ni shangs kyi sku yi mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:2573: dz+ha ni ljags kyi sku yi mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:2576: rnam shes bzhi yi dmigs pa'i yul //
NK064(ngu),002:2577: mthong bar bya ba la sogs pa //
NK064(ngu),002:2578: dmigs par bya phyir sku yi mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:2581: 'dir rtog pa'i go rim ltar sbyar na yul yul can ma 'khrul na'ang /
NK064(ngu),002:2582: lha yab yum sbyor ba'i tshe rna ba'i yul ro dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2583: lce'i yul sgrar byung bas sbyor tshul nor te /
NK064(ngu),002:2584: spyan ras gzigs kyi yum g+airti ma dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2585: phyag rdor gyi yum n+airti mar byung ba'i phyir zer na /
NK064(ngu),002:2586: yul yul can gyi dbang du byas na de ltar yin mod kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:2587: 'dir rigs kyi dbang du byas pas 'gal ba med de /
NK064(ngu),002:2588: nyi 'od seng ge'i rgya cher 'grel las /
NK064(ngu),002:2589: rgyud 'dir ni rigs kho na gtso bor byas te /
NK064(ngu),002:2590: nyan par bya ba sgra'i lha mo rna ba'i yul yin kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:2591: rigs kyi dus su gsung gi rigs yin pas 'jig rten dbang phyug gi yum du shes par bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:2592: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu),002:2593: phyi sems bzhi po de dag la mthong byed la sogs pa smos pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2594: rim pa ltar mig rna ba sna lce'i dbang po bzhi yin pas rtog pa'i mtshan te /
NK064(ngu),002:2595: rnam shes bzhis yul bzhi mthong ba'i bdag rkyen dbang po bzhis byed pa'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2596: de dag lha'i dus na gsung gi sems dpa' bzhir grags te /
NK064(ngu),002:2600: myong byed 'jam dpal rnams su nges pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:2601: de rnams la gsung gi sems dpa' zhes brjod pa'i rgyu mtshan yang yod de /
NK064(ngu),002:2602: dbang pos yul dang shes pa gnyis phyi nang gi brda sbyor byed pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:2604: pa ni spyan gyi gsung gi mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:2605: pha ni snyan gyi gsung gi mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:2606: ba ni shangs kyi gsung gi mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:2607: b+ha ni ljags kyi gsung gi mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:2609: phyi sems bzhi'i yum de dag la 'das pa la sogs pa smos pa ni rtog pa'i mtshan te /
NK064(ngu),002:2610: dus bzhis go phye nas dbang po bzhi skyed par byed pa'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2611: de dag lha'i dus na dus bzhi'i lha mo ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2612: 'das pa'i dus bdug pa ma dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2613: da ltar ba me tog ma /
NK064(ngu),002:2614: 'byung ba ste ma 'ongs pa mar me ma //
NK064(ngu),002:2615: ma byon par 'byung bar ma nges pa'i dus te dri chab ma rnams su nges pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:2617: ya ni skye ba rnam par dag /
NK064(ngu),002:2618: wa ni gnas pa dag pa yin //
NK064(ngu),002:2619: ra ni 'jigs pa dag pa ste //
NK064(ngu),002:2620: la ni stong pa dag pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:2623: 'dir dus bzhir smos pas dus log ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2624: sde snod gzhan rnams su dus gsum las ma bshad pa'i phyir zer /
NK064(ngu),002:2625: de ltar na mngon pa mdzod nas chags gnas 'jig stong bzhi dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2626: rdzogs ldan la sogs pa'i dus bzhi bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2628: dus gsum dang bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus te
NK064(ngu),002:2629: bzhir gsungs pa sogs kyang dus log par thal lo
NK064(ngu),002:2630: // 'o na 'dir dus bzhi po gang zhe na /
NK064(ngu),002:2631: rgyu 'bras gnyis ka spyad zin pa'i dus ni 'das pa /
NK064(ngu),002:2632: rgyu spyad cing 'bras bu ma spyad pa ni da lta ba /
NK064(ngu),002:2633: rgyu 'bras tshogs la ma spyad pa ni ma 'ongs pa /
NK064(ngu),002:2634: rgyu 'bras yod la ma tshogs pa ni 'das ma 'ongs gang du'ang ma nges pa'i dus te /
NK064(ngu),002:2636: dbyar gyi dus lta bu zhig la gzhir bzhag nas brtsi na /
NK064(ngu),002:2640: dgun ni ma nges pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2641: dbyar gyi dus 'di las sngar 'das phyis 'byung gnyis ni 'das ma 'ongs par nges la /
NK064(ngu),002:2642: dgun ni 'das ma 'ongs gang rung gcig tu kha tshon ma chod pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:2643: dpyid kyi snga logs kyi dgun ni 'das pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2644: ston gyi phyi logs kyi dgun ni ma 'ongs pa ltar snang ba'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:2645: de ltar yang rngam glog las /
NK064(ngu),002:2646: rgyu 'bras nges pa ma tshogs pa /
NK064(ngu),002:2647: 'byung bar ma nges dus zhes grags //
NK064(ngu),002:2649: de'i phyir dus bzhir grangs kyang go rim nges pa yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:2650: gnyis pa 'joms byed khro bo'i 'khor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2651: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg pa dang nas /
NK064(ngu),002:2652: mtshan mar 'dzin pa ma yin pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2654: de la'ang spyi bye brag gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:2656: 'joms byed yab bzhi po la 'joms pa chen po rdo rje zhes brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2657: phyi lus kyi chos bzhi dang sbyar na rtog pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:2658: rang bzhin mngon du gyur pa'i khro bo bzhi'i sku
NK064(ngu),002:2659: gsung thugs kyi mdzad pas bdud dang log 'dren rnams
NK064(ngu),002:2660: 'joms pa dang / nang gsang ba'i khams bzhi dang sbyar na /
NK064(ngu),002:2661: 'og sgo gsang ba'i khams gsum 'dus pa'i bde ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:2662: rtog pa lha'am bde bar 'dzin pa'i zhen pa gnyis
NK064(ngu),002:2663: ka 'joms pa la thogs pa med pas na rdo
NK064(ngu),002:2664: rje zhes brjod pa yin cing /
NK064(ngu),002:2665: des 'joms pa'i phrin las gzhan las khyad par du
NK064(ngu),002:2666: gyur pas na chen po zhes brjod pa yin gsungs
NK064(ngu),002:2667: / de dag gi yum bzhi po la btsun mo zhes brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2668: de lta bu'i 'joms byed kyi snying po de yang
NK064(ngu),002:2669: rtag chad bdag mtshan bzhi ma yin pa'i chos nyid
NK064(ngu),002:2670: yum gyi ngo bo des bskyed pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:2671: dper na dkar po 'joms pa de dkar po ma yin pa zhig gis bskyed pa bzhin no //
NK064(ngu),002:2672: yang phyin ci log gi rtog pa bzhi ltar na /
NK064(ngu),002:2673: des lus kyi rtog pa bzhi po dngos su mi
NK064(ngu),002:2674: bskyed kyang brgyud nas bskyed par bzhed pa'i phyir ro
NK064(ngu),002:2675: // gnyis pa bye brag gi mtshan ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2676: sgo ba yab bzhi po de la reg pa la sogs par smos pa ni rtog pa'i mtshan te /
NK064(ngu),002:2677: phyi ltar lus kyi 'dus te reg pa'i rkyen gyis tshor ba bskyed pa la /
NK064(ngu),002:2678: reg byed yul dbang reg bya yul /
NK064(ngu),002:2679: de gnyis 'phrad pa'i reg shes so //
NK064(ngu),002:2680: nang ltar na gsang ba'i yul dbang rnam shes gsum 'dus kyi reg pa bskyed pa la /
NK064(ngu),002:2681: reg byed gsang dbang thabs kyi rdo rje /
NK064(ngu),002:2682: reg bya gsang yul shes rab kyi pad+ma /
NK064(ngu),002:2683: gsang ba'i reg shes dga' ba nyams su myong ba rnams so //
NK064(ngu),002:2684: de dag lha'i dus na mthar byed sgo ba bzhi ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2685: phyi nang gi rtog pa gnyis ka go rim bzhin du khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2688: gshin rje'i gshed rnams su nges pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:2689: de dag gi yum bzhi po de dag la rtag
NK064(ngu),002:2690: pa ma yin pa zhes sogs smos pa ni rtog
NK064(ngu),002:2691: pa'i mtshan te / rtag par ma yin pa ste phung po mi rtag par 'dzin pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2692: chad par ma yin pa ste sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin nga ru 'dzin pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2693: bdag tu ma yin pa ste bdag med du 'dzin pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2694: mtshan mar ma yin pa ste stong par 'dzin pa rnams /
NK064(ngu),002:2695: lha'i dus na go rim bzhan du khro mo lcags
NK064(ngu),002:2696: kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril bu ma dang bzhir
NK064(ngu),002:2697: nges pa'i phyir / yang rtag chad bdag mtshan du
NK064(ngu),002:2698: 'dzin pa phyin ci log gi shes pa bzhi ltar
NK064(ngu),002:2699: nges pa'i phyir / na / rtag par 'dzin pa
NK064(ngu),002:2700: sogs rtog pa bzhi po de rang ga mar snang
NK064(ngu),002:2702: de dag ma spangs par sgo ma bzhi'i rang bzhin du dag pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:2703: de ltar yang thal rgyud las /
NK064(ngu),002:2704: rtag sogs mtshan ma las skyes phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:2705: btsun mo zhes su bstan pa ste //
NK064(ngu),002:2707: glang po che rab 'bog gi rgyud las kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:2708: don dam par sems can gyi rtag par lta ba gnas su dag pa badz+ra ang+ku sha ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2710: de ltar rgyal sras sems dpa'i 'khor dang 'joms byed
NK064(ngu),002:2711: khro bo'i 'khor rnams la rig pa khyad par can
NK064(ngu),002:2713: ston pa'i thugs rig pa'i ye shes kyi khyad par las rang snang ba'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:2715: de bzhin thugs kyi khyad par las //
NK064(ngu),002:2716: rang snang rgyal ba sems sogs dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2718: der ma zad dad pas gtam nyan pa'i 'khor phyi'i
NK064(ngu),002:2719: khor yug la bzhugs pa'i 'jig rten gyi cha 'dzin
NK064(ngu),002:2720: pa lha chen po rnams kyang yod de /
NK064(ngu),002:2722: dad pas nyan pa'i lha chen rnams //
NK064(ngu),002:2725: thams cad la ni dbang bsgyur phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:2726: 'jig rten lha chen rnams kyis bskor //
NK064(ngu),002:2728: spyan 'grel las kyang 'khor ba'i chos rnams kyang bdag
NK064(ngu),002:2729: nyid du rang snang ba'i phyir phyi rol du ma
NK064(ngu),002:2730: h+aa de wa la sogs pa'i lha chen po rnams
NK064(ngu),002:2732: rang rang gi mchod yon dang rgyan dang ldan par 'khod pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:2734: de ltar bstan pa'i 'khor gyi tshad ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2735: chos kyi dbyings kun tu mtha' klas par khyab pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2736: dper na til gyi gong bu bzhin du gang nas khyab par bzhugs so //
NK064(ngu),002:2738: la sogs pa de lta bu'i tshogs brjod kyis mi lang ba dang gnyis su med par bzhugs so //
NK064(ngu),002:2742: kun tu khyab cing mtha' yas par khyab pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:2743: til gong der til 'bras kyis gang ba bzhin khyab pa yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:2744: gnyis pa mang ba'i tshad ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2745: sngar smos pa de lta bu'i 'khor tshogs kyi grangs
NK064(ngu),002:2746: tshad 'di tsam zhes brjod kyis mi lang ba'i phyir
NK064(ngu),002:2747: ro // 'o na khyab pa dang mang ba'i bdag
NK064(ngu),002:2748: nyid can gyi 'khor de dag dang gnyis su med
NK064(ngu),002:2749: par bzhugs tshul de ji lta bu zhe na /
NK064(ngu),002:2750: rang bzhin gnyis su med par bzhugs pa yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:2751: de bzhin gshegs pa dang byang chub sems dpa' ma
NK064(ngu),002:2752: lus pa thams cad dpal kun tu bzang po'i rang
NK064(ngu),002:2754: 'gro ba'i phung khams skye mched ji snyed pa thams
NK064(ngu),002:2755: cad kyang lha'i rang bzhin du gnas pa'i phyir te
NK064(ngu),002:2757: srid gsum 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK064(ngu),002:2758: phung po khams dang skye mched dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2759: brjod med brjod kyis mi lang ba //
NK064(ngu),002:2761: mngon rdzogs rgyal po de nyid nges //
NK064(ngu),002:2762: gnyis med lhun grub dkyil 'khor na //
NK064(ngu),002:2763: thams cad bdag nyid rtag par bzhugs //
NK064(ngu),002:2765: gnyis pa zhar byung gdul bya dgos ched du bstan
NK064(ngu),002:2766: pa khro bo'i gleng gzhi la'ang phun sum tshogs pa
NK064(ngu),002:2768: dang po ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2769: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag
NK064(ngu),002:2770: po sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid kyi
NK064(ngu),002:2771: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor mngon par 'du mdzad de /
NK064(ngu),002:2774: ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa rigs thams cad kyi
NK064(ngu),002:2775: bdag po drug pa kun tu bzang po nyid sangs
NK064(ngu),002:2776: rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bo
NK064(ngu),002:2777: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor las ma g.yos par
NK064(ngu),002:2778: / gdul bya ru tra'i ngor gdul byed khro bo'i
NK064(ngu),002:2779: dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs mngon par 'du mdzad de phrin
NK064(ngu),002:2780: las phyag rgya'i skur bzhengs pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2782: shin tu gdug cing gtum pa la //
NK064(ngu),002:2783: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
NK064(ngu),002:2784: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya yis //
NK064(ngu),002:2785: khro bor de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
NK064(ngu),002:2787: gnyis pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2788: dur khrod chen por dgyes nas khrag gi rgya mtsho'i
NK064(ngu),002:2789: dkyil na keng rus chen po'i ri rab kyi steng
NK064(ngu),002:2790: 'bar ba chen po'i klong gi 'khor lo'i dkyil na
NK064(ngu),002:2793: dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang chen por bzhugs par dgyes nas /
NK064(ngu),002:2794: mkha' rlung gi dkyil 'khor la brten pa'i khrag zhag gi rgya mtshor chags pa /
NK064(ngu),002:2795: zhing chen gyi sa gzhi'i dbus keng rus brtsegs pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:2796: ri rab kyi steng ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar
NK064(ngu),002:2797: ba chen po'i klong na bzhugs pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2798: he ru ka galpo'i rgyud las /
NK064(ngu),002:2799: chags pa rak+ta'i rgya mtsho rba klong 'khyil //
NK064(ngu),002:2800: zhing chen gtams pa'i sa gzhi mtha' dbus brdal //
NK064(ngu),002:2801: keng rus chen po brtsegs pa'i ri rab 'bar //
NK064(ngu),002:2802: ye shes 'bar ba'i me 'od kun tu 'phro //
NK064(ngu),002:2804: gsum pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa la /
NK064(ngu),002:2805: gdul bya gdug pa can gyi 'khor dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2808: bdag tu rmongs pa'i rtog pa dang btags pa la mngon par zhen nas /
NK064(ngu),002:2809: zhes pa la sogs pa rnams kyis bstan /
NK064(ngu),002:2810: de yang rgyu des spyir sems can thams cad 'khor ba ru gol zhing /
NK064(ngu),002:2811: bye brag tu ru tra nyid gab pa'i gsang ba
NK064(ngu),002:2812: lta ba gnas lugs de bzhin nyid ma rtogs par
NK064(ngu),002:2813: / sbas pa'i gsang ba spyod pa sbyor sgrol gnyis barlang por spyad pas /
NK064(ngu),002:2814: rnam smin gyi 'bras bu dmyal ba tsha grang gi sdug bsngal mi zad pa myong zhing /
NK064(ngu),002:2815: rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu lha rang rgyud par sgom
NK064(ngu),002:2816: nas ra la ra la sogs pa'i drag sngags rang
NK064(ngu),002:2817: gar bzlas shing las barlang por spyad pas yi dwags
NK064(ngu),002:2818: kyi 'gro bas bsdus pa'i srin po bya yi gshog
NK064(ngu),002:2819: pa can zhig tu skyes nas gzugs khams gnas ris
NK064(ngu),002:2820: bcu gnyis man chad dbang du byas pa na thugs
NK064(ngu),002:2823: thub dka' rdo rje snying po dang sngon dpon slob
NK064(ngu),002:2824: tu 'brel ba'i stobs kyis thug rjes 'dul bar gdul
NK064(ngu),002:2826: gnyis pa 'dul byed gnyen po'i 'khor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2827: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen por gyur te shar phyogs su bzhugs so //
NK064(ngu),002:2828: zhes sogs kyis de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga'i 'khor dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2829: dkar mo'i tshogs dang zhes sogs kyis gnas ma brgyad /
NK064(ngu),002:2830: seng gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang zhes sogs kyis yul ma brgyad /
NK064(ngu),002:2831: rdo rje sring 'gro ma'i tshogs dang zhes sogs kyis sgo ma bzhi /
NK064(ngu),002:2832: srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo dang zhes sogs
NK064(ngu),002:2833: kyis dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad rnams so
NK064(ngu),002:2834: // bzhi pa chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2835: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa che ba'i rdo rje bkod pa las zhes sogs kyis bstan /
NK064(ngu),002:2837: sbyor sgrol gyi phri na las rmad du byung ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2838: de la pho rnams sgrol bas 'dul ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2839: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nas gsang ba'i yum sprul
NK064(ngu),002:2840: te snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang chub kyi sems sprin
NK064(ngu),002:2841: las / khro bo 'chol ba'i tshogs mtha' yas par spros te /
NK064(ngu),002:2842: ltas chen po bco lnga bstan pas gdug pa can
NK064(ngu),002:2843: thams cad rab tu brgyal kun tu brgyal bar gyur
NK064(ngu),002:2844: pa na / khro tshogs rnams bsdus te slar yang
NK064(ngu),002:2845: rigs lnga'i he ru kar snang bar byas nas de
NK064(ngu),002:2846: dag zhabs 'og tu mnan pa na da dung dgra
NK064(ngu),002:2847: zlar mthong ste mi snyan pa'i barlang po'i gtum tshig
NK064(ngu),002:2848: pa na / smra ba na / dpal chen po
NK064(ngu),002:2849: nyid kyis dregs pa r+au tra'i ngor sgrol byed rdo
NK064(ngu),002:2850: rje srin po dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad pa'i rnam
NK064(ngu),002:2851: pa na / smra ba na / par bstan nas
NK064(ngu),002:2852: / gdug pa can de rnams kyi dug gsum dag
NK064(ngu),002:2856: gti mug sha yi rnam par phung po lhag ma
NK064(ngu),002:2857: ma lus par zhal du bstab pa dang bcas pa
NK064(ngu),002:2858: ni pho rnams sgrol bas 'dul ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:2859: mo rnams sbyor bas 'dul ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2860: gdug pa can de rnams kyi chung ma dbang mo
NK064(ngu),002:2861: nyer brgyad po dbang du bsdus nas rol par mdzad
NK064(ngu),002:2862: pa ste / de yang gtso bo la phyogs kyi
NK064(ngu),002:2863: gtso mo bzhi dang sgo ma bzhi ste brgyad 'khril
NK064(ngu),002:2864: pa ste / / rigs bzhi la phyogs kyi lhag
NK064(ngu),002:2865: ma lnga lnga 'khril te mnyam par sbyor ba'i sems
NK064(ngu),002:2866: pa ste / / sprin las / gnas ma brgyad /
NK064(ngu),002:2868: sgo ma bzhi rnams re re la yang nyer brgyad re 'thon cing /
NK064(ngu),002:2869: so so yang rigs bsdus te dkyil 'khor gyi gnas
NK064(ngu),002:2870: so sor bkod nas phata ces bsgrags te dbang mo
NK064(ngu),002:2871: rnams rang rang gi gnas ga la ba der yud
NK064(ngu),002:2873: de nas sngar zhal du bstab pa'i r+au tra pho
NK064(ngu),002:2874: rnams lto ba na gnas pa de 'og sgo nas
NK064(ngu),002:2875: bton te mi gtsang ba'i 'dam gyi rgya mtshor chud
NK064(ngu),002:2876: pa las / slar yang bsnams nas khro bo sme
NK064(ngu),002:2877: ba brtsegs pa phyungs nas 'dam kun 'thungs pas dregs
NK064(ngu),002:2878: pa can de dag dran pa slar rnyed nas snang
NK064(ngu),002:2879: ba rnam 'byed kyi ting nge 'dzin thob ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2880: bsam yas lhun grub khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi zhal mngon sum du mthong ngo //
NK064(ngu),002:2881: de nas shin tu 'dar zhing bred pas rab tu zhum pa'i nga ros /
NK064(ngu),002:2883: 'bangs su nan tan ma mchis na /
NK064(ngu),002:2884: zhes pa la sogs pas 'bangs su mchi bar dam bcas pa de nas yang smras pa /
NK064(ngu),002:2885: bdag cag rnams kyi mchis brang dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2886: zhes sogs kyis bro bor nas rang rang gi lus
NK064(ngu),002:2887: khrag 'thung rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor gyi gdan du phul
NK064(ngu),002:2888: bas / de nas dpal chen pos ma mo rnams
NK064(ngu),002:2889: kyi lag tu rdo rje re byin nas rdo rje
NK064(ngu),002:2890: mi'i srin mo zhes pa la sogs pa'i ming gi
NK064(ngu),002:2891: dbang bskur nas dkyil 'khor gyi khrag khyams la 'god
NK064(ngu),002:2892: bas / par mdzad do // lnga pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2893: thams cad 'dul ba'i thabs sna tshogs bsam gyis mi
NK064(ngu),002:2894: khyab pa so sor snang bas dus gcig tu btul
NK064(ngu),002:2897: de'i dus su 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i gdug
NK064(ngu),002:2898: pa can thams cad snga phyi med par dus gcig
NK064(ngu),002:2900: gleng gzhi 'di la zhar byung gdul bya dgos ched du bstan pa zhes pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2901: gsang ba'i 'og min du ston 'khor tshogs nas snying ga'i 'og min du sangs rgyas pa'i tshe /
NK064(ngu),002:2902: nang gi rtsa mdud grol bas nang gi bdud bzhi
NK064(ngu),002:2903: bcom pa'i rtags snang phyi rol tu de ltar byung
NK064(ngu),002:2904: ba'o gsungs / gsum pa sprul sku 'gro ba 'dul ba'i gleng gzhi la'ang lnga las /
NK064(ngu),002:2905: dang po ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2906: thub pa chen po bcom ldan re res /
NK064(ngu),002:2909: stong gsum gyi stong chen po re rer thub pa chen po re res don mdzad pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2910: sher phyin gyi sngags kyi dbang po bkram pa'i le'u las /
NK064(ngu),002:2911: bcom ldan 'das kyis stong gsum gyi stong chen po ljags kyi dbang pos khebs par mdzad pas /
NK064(ngu),002:2912: de na gnas pa'i sems can 'dul ba'i snod du
NK064(ngu),002:2913: gyur pa rnams ni bla na med pa'i byang chub
NK064(ngu),002:2914: tu lung bstan par gyur pas /
NK064(ngu),002:2915: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad ni 'od kyis khyab par mdzad do //
NK064(ngu),002:2917: de'ang gdul bya rigs drug so so'i las snang dang mthun par snang ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2919: lha yi gnas na brgya byin mgon //
NK064(ngu),002:2920: lha ma yin la thag bzang ris //
NK064(ngu),002:2922: yi dwags gnas na kha 'bar de //
NK064(ngu),002:2923: byol song seng ge nyid du smra //
NK064(ngu),002:2924: dmyal ba la ni gshin rje'i mgon //
NK064(ngu),002:2926: gnyis pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2927: 'gro ba lnga yi don mdzad de /
NK064(ngu),002:2930: lha min stod ris lha dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2935: bye brag 'khor rnam pa bzhi la sogs pa'o gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:2936: gsum pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2937: s+n+rel gzhi dang yas man gyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med ces dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2938: stong gsum gyi stong chen po re res /
NK064(ngu),002:2940: de la bla ma gong ma rnams mtha' yas mu med ces chos sku'i zhing dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2941: s+n+rel gzhi dang yas man gyi 'jig rten drug gi
NK064(ngu),002:2942: phyogs bcu zhes pas stong gsum gyi 'jig rten stong
NK064(ngu),002:2943: la stong rgyu bkod dang po dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2944: de stong la stong rgyu bkod gnyis pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:2945: de stong la stong mtshams sbyor yongs su dag pa
NK064(ngu),002:2946: zhes bya ba longs sku'i zhing gi tshad du 'dod
NK064(ngu),002:2947: cing / de'ang 'gal bar ma mthong zhing /
NK064(ngu),002:2948: kho bo ni phal chen las /
NK064(ngu),002:2949: las kyi bye brag bsam mi khyab //
NK064(ngu),002:2951: gshin rje'i 'jig rten s+n+rel gzhi ste //
NK064(ngu),002:2952: byol song lha min gyen mthur 'gro //
NK064(ngu),002:2954: yang na mgo gyen du bstan nas 'gro ba mtho ris /
NK064(ngu),002:2955: s+n+rel gzhi ste phred bstan gyis 'gro ba dud 'gro /
NK064(ngu),002:2956: mthur bstan gyis 'gro ba dmyal ba dang yi dwags te /
NK064(ngu),002:2957: de drug po stong gsum gyi 'jig rten gcig gi nang du tshang ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:2959: stong gsum gcig la chags tshul drug /
NK064(ngu),002:2960: sprul sku gcig gi zhing du grags //
NK064(ngu),002:2962: 'gro ba'i las snang gi zhing khams kyi bkod pa mtha' yas kyang 'dir mdzod las /
NK064(ngu),002:2963: gling bzhi pa dang nyi zla dang //
NK064(ngu),002:2964: ri rab dang ni 'dod lhar bcas //
NK064(ngu),002:2965: tshangs pa'i 'jig rten stong la ni //
NK064(ngu),002:2966: stong ni spyi phud yin par 'dod //
NK064(ngu),002:2967: de stong la ni stong gnyis pa //
NK064(ngu),002:2968: bar ma'i 'jig rten khams yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:2969: de stong la ni stong gsum mo //
NK064(ngu),002:2971: bzhi pa chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2974: de la dang po sku bsod nams chen pos 'dul ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2976: rab tu byung ba dang sogs nas /
NK064(ngu),002:2977: thub pas zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan gnyis pa thugs mngon sum pas 'dul ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2978: dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pa dang sogs nas /
NK064(ngu),002:2979: mngon par shes pa chen po drug dang zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan /
NK064(ngu),002:2980: gsum pa rdzu 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'dul ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2981: kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang sogs nas /
NK064(ngu),002:2982: bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad du grangs med pa phyogs bcu snang bar gyur te /
NK064(ngu),002:2984: bzhi pa gsung rig pas 'dul ba la bstan bshad bsdu gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:2986: lha dang mi'i theg pa dang sogs kyis rigs can
NK064(ngu),002:2987: lnga'i gdul bya la ltos nas theg pa lnga'i sgo
NK064(ngu),002:2988: nas mdor bstan / ma rig pa'i rnam par rtog pa zhes sogs kyis /
NK064(ngu),002:2989: nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong gi gnyen por
NK064(ngu),002:2990: chos phung brgya khri bzhi stong gsungs te rgyas par
NK064(ngu),002:2991: bshad / de dag thams cad kyang gzung ba dang
NK064(ngu),002:2992: 'dzin pa'i rnam par rtog pa zhes sogs kyis dbang
NK064(ngu),002:2993: po'i rim pas mjug bsdu ba dang bcas pa rnams
NK064(ngu),002:2994: bshad / so gsungs / lnga pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:2996: dus kyi ngo bo mnyam gnas kyang //
NK064(ngu),002:2997: skal pa can la dkon pa'i dus //
NK064(ngu),002:2999: de rnams kyis rgyud 'byung ba'i rgyu gleng bzhi bshad pa song nas /
NK064(ngu),002:3000: gnyis pa rkyen gleng bslang ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3002: ston pas gnang dang 'khor gyis zhus //
NK064(ngu),002:3003: skabs las gleng bslang ston dang 'khor //
NK064(ngu),002:3004: gnang 'dri'i rkyen du gang gyur pa //
NK064(ngu),002:3005: de des gsungs la ma rag pa //
NK064(ngu),002:3006: zhes gsungs pas ston 'khor dri lan gyi sbyor bas
NK064(ngu),002:3007: rgyud don gdul bya'i blo dang 'tshams par 'byung ma
NK064(ngu),002:3008: rag pa ste / de ltar gleng gzhi tshogs nas
NK064(ngu),002:3009: rkyen gleng ma bslang na rgyud don mi 'byung ste
NK064(ngu),002:3010: rag pa ste / / ston pas gnang dang zhes
NK064(ngu),002:3011: pas ston pas mdun bsus te gnang ba mdo sdud
NK064(ngu),002:3013: ngas sngar shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i don rgyas par bshad kyi /
NK064(ngu),002:3014: da de rnams kyi don mdor bsdus te ston par
NK064(ngu),002:3015: byed pas legs par nyon la yid la zungs shig
NK064(ngu),002:3017: 'khor gyis zhus zhes pas 'jam dpal mtshan brjod lta bu ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3018: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rjes /
NK064(ngu),002:3019: rab gsung gang lags bshad du gsol //
NK064(ngu),002:3021: nyid kyi zhal nas ljags bzang ba //
NK064(ngu),002:3022: ring zhing yangs pa brkyang mdzad de //
