NK064(ngu),002:3023: zhes 'khor gyis zhus pa ltar ston 'khor dri lan
NK064(ngu),002:3024: gyi sbyor ba de lta bu'i rkyen gyis rgyud don
NK064(ngu),002:3025: 'byung ma rag pa ni rkyen gleng bslang ba ste
NK064(ngu),002:3027: thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3028: thun mong gi gleng bslang gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:3030: ston pa yab yum gyis lhan cig pa'i 'khor la
NK064(ngu),002:3031: zab dbang bskur ba'i sbyor bas mdun bsus te thabs
NK064(ngu),002:3032: shes gnyis med kyi cha bzung nas gleng bslang ba
NK064(ngu),002:3034: yab kyis thabs kyi cha bzung nas gleng bslang ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3035: e ma hoh rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK064(ngu),002:3036: zhes sogs thabs kyi cha bzung nas gleng bslang bas
NK064(ngu),002:3037: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu),002:3038: gcig gi rang bzhin du sangs rgyas pa la ngo
NK064(ngu),002:3039: mtshar ba'i tshul gyis de ltar gleng bar mdzad pas
NK064(ngu),002:3040: / 'khor rnams kyis lhag pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa mthong /
NK064(ngu),002:3041: phung khams skye mched la sogs pa'i chos thams cad
NK064(ngu),002:3042: lha dang lha mo'i rang bzhin du rtogs pas sangs
NK064(ngu),002:3043: rgyas pa nyid las gzhan pa'i chos rdul tsam yang
NK064(ngu),002:3046: kye ma hoh phyogs bcu stong khams ye nas dben //
NK064(ngu),002:3047: zhes sogs shes rab kyi cha bzung nas gleng bslang
NK064(ngu),002:3048: bas kun rdzob kyi snang ba thams cad don dam
NK064(ngu),002:3049: stong nyid kyi klong du thim pa la ngo mtshar
NK064(ngu),002:3050: ba'i tshul gyis de ltar gleng bar mdzad pas /
NK064(ngu),002:3051: 'khor rnams kyis lhag pa don dam pa'i bden pa mthong nas /
NK064(ngu),002:3056: tha snyad bzhis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad ye nas
NK064(ngu),002:3057: chos kyi skur mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa
NK064(ngu),002:3058: las 'bras bu gzhan nas btsal du med par rtogs
NK064(ngu),002:3059: pa'i phyir ro // de nas thabs shes gnyis med
NK064(ngu),002:3060: kyi cha bzung nas dbang phyi ma gnyis bskur ba
NK064(ngu),002:3061: pa'i phyir ro // ni / mdo sde rgyan las /
NK064(ngu),002:3062: dgongs pa tha ma thob nas ni //
NK064(ngu),002:3063: 'od zer chen pos dbang bskur ro //
NK064(ngu),002:3064: zhes pas yab yum snyoms par zhugs pa'i nyi zla byang chub kyi sems kyis rgyu byas /
NK064(ngu),002:3065: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK064(ngu),002:3066: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK064(ngu),002:3067: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK064(ngu),002:3068: zhes sogs kyis rkyen gleng bslang bas /
NK064(ngu),002:3069: rtsa gnas thams cad nas bde ba 'go ldang ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:3070: tshul gyis skyes pa g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems
NK064(ngu),002:3071: / bde ba snga ma 'jig cing phyi ma'i bde
NK064(ngu),002:3072: ba la 'jug pa 'jig 'jug byang chub kyi sems
NK064(ngu),002:3073: / / snga ma'i bde bas mtshon nas phyi ma'i
NK064(ngu),002:3074: bde ba la smon pa smon pa byang chub kyi
NK064(ngu),002:3075: / / sems / rten can gyi bde ba rang
NK064(ngu),002:3076: sa na gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyis gnas pa
NK064(ngu),002:3077: gnas pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK064(ngu),002:3078: 'gro 'ong thams cad dang bral ba mthar phyin pa byang chub kyi sems dang lnga las /
NK064(ngu),002:3079: de ltar yas 'bab dga' bzhi'i bgrod kyi mthar byang
NK064(ngu),002:3080: sems yum gyi pad+ma'i ze'u 'brur zhal mjal ba'i mthar
NK064(ngu),002:3081: dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyams su
NK064(ngu),002:3082: myong ba ste / shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob pa ni 'gro dang zhes pa'i don yin /
NK064(ngu),002:3083: 'ong zhes pa slar yang mas brtan gyi dga' bzhi'i
NK064(ngu),002:3084: skabs su byang chub kyi sems dkar dmar gnyis gcig
NK064(ngu),002:3085: tu gyur pa gyen du ldog ste spyi bor son
NK064(ngu),002:3086: pas rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyams
NK064(ngu),002:3087: su myong ste / dbang bzhi pa bde ba chen po'i dbang thob pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3088: de'i tshe 'jig rten na chu mthur du 'gro ba
NK064(ngu),002:3089: gyen du song ste dkar cha chu'i rang bzhin spyi
NK064(ngu),002:3090: bor dag pas sku rdo rje thob /
NK064(ngu),002:3091: dmar cha me'i rang bzhin gyen du 'gro ba ste
NK064(ngu),002:3092: mthur du song nas rdo rje nor bu'i rtser 'gag
NK064(ngu),002:3093: pas dmar cha dag pa gsung rdo rje thob /
NK064(ngu),002:3094: dkar dmar bar gyi 'brel byed pa'i rlung dag pas thugs rdo rje thob /
NK064(ngu),002:3095: de gsum 'gyur ba myong ba'i shes rig dag pas
NK064(ngu),002:3096: ye shes rdo rje thob ste sku bzhi ye shees
NK064(ngu),002:3097: lnga'i ngo bor sangs rgyas pas na /
NK064(ngu),002:3098: ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med du gyur pa ni thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng bslang ngo gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:3099: gnyis pa thun mong gi gleng bslang ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3100: de ltar ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med du gyur nas rang don du rgyud zhu ma dgos kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:3101: e ma ho ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK064(ngu),002:3102: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK064(ngu),002:3103: ngo bo nyid kyis rab tu gsang //
NK064(ngu),002:3104: gzhan du min las shin tu gsang //
NK064(ngu),002:3105: zhes gsang ba bzhis chod pa'i thun mong gi gdul
NK064(ngu),002:3106: bya rnams thugs rjes bzung bar rigs so zhes zhus
NK064(ngu),002:3107: pas / sangs rgyas kyi ye shes chen po skyes nas zhes pas /
NK064(ngu),002:3108: bstan phyir spro ba sna tshogs mdzad //
NK064(ngu),002:3109: ces ston pa'i thugs rje skyes nas dngos dang brgyud
NK064(ngu),002:3110: pa'i sgo nas 'chad par dgyes pa'o zhes zhal gyis
NK064(ngu),002:3111: bzhes pa dang bcas pa ni thun mong gi gleng
NK064(ngu),002:3112: bslang ngo gsungs / de rnams kyis gleng bslang ba song nas /
NK064(ngu),002:3113: gsum pa 'bras bu yongs shes rgyud don bshad pa la /
NK064(ngu),002:3114: rgyud gsum gyi rnam bzhag spyir bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3115: lam gyi cha rkyen rgyud kyi dngos po bcu bye brag tu bshad pa gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:3118: rgyud ni rgyun chags la bshad de //
NK064(ngu),002:3121: spyir rgyun chags pa'i don gyis na rgyud ces bya ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3122: sems can nas sangs rgyas kyi bar du sems kyi
NK064(ngu),002:3123: chos nyid rang bzhin rnam dag de pi wang gi
NK064(ngu),002:3124: rgyud ltar breng chags su gnas pas rgyun chags pa
NK064(ngu),002:3125: zhes bshad / de nyid thabs kyi rkyen gyis zin
NK064(ngu),002:3126: pa la ltos nas gzhi lam 'bras gsum du snang
NK064(ngu),002:3127: zhes bshad / ste / thabs dang rgyu las 'bras bu'o //
NK064(ngu),002:3129: gang rtogs par bya ba gazhi'am rgyu'i rgyud /
NK064(ngu),002:3130: gang gis rtogs shing bgrod pa thabs sam lam gyi rgyud /
NK064(ngu),002:3131: gang du mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i rgyud dang gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:3133: bcing med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK064(ngu),002:3134: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK064(ngu),002:3135: zhes gsungs pa ltar gzhi 'ching grol med pa'i gnas
NK064(ngu),002:3136: lugs rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems bden pa
NK064(ngu),002:3137: dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba ye nas gnas
NK064(ngu),002:3140: sems kyi chos nyid 'di 'khor ba'i gnas skabs su
NK064(ngu),002:3141: bcings pa dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i gnas skabs
NK064(ngu),002:3142: su grol ba ltar snang yang /
NK064(ngu),002:3143: don la ltos gzhi bcings pa med pas /
NK064(ngu),002:3144: de ltos kyi grol ba'ang mi srid pas 'ching grol med pa zhes bya /
NK064(ngu),002:3145: 'ching grol med pa'i gnas lugs rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems zhes pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3146: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sems su 'dus shing
NK064(ngu),002:3147: sems kyi ngo bo la sgrib pas gos ma myong
NK064(ngu),002:3148: bas byang chub kyi sems zhes bya ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3150: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NK064(ngu),002:3151: de ni lung gi tshad mar bshad //
NK064(ngu),002:3153: byang chub kyi don ni spang thob med pa'i don yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:3154: spang bya sgrib gnyis spangs rgyu dang thob bya'i yon
NK064(ngu),002:3155: tan gsar du thob rgyu med par ye nas lhun
NK064(ngu),002:3156: grub tu yod pas byang chub kyi sems zhes bya
NK064(ngu),002:3157: / de la bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang
NK064(ngu),002:3158: bral bar ye nas gnas pa gang yin pa ste
NK064(ngu),002:3159: / / zhes pa ni sems de'i ngo bo don
NK064(ngu),002:3160: dam dkor bdun ngo bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub
NK064(ngu),002:3161: pa ni lhag pa don dam bden pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3163: de yang rnam gsum gnas tshul bzhag /
NK064(ngu),002:3167: 'bras bu don dam gsum gyi rang bzhin du gnas pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3168: de'i dpe ni sems nyid nam mkha' lta bu'am me
NK064(ngu),002:3169: long nag ling nge ba lta bu ni dbyings don
NK064(ngu),002:3170: dam / de la gsal dwangs sgrib g.yogs med pa'i cha ni ye shes don dam /
NK064(ngu),002:3171: me long la gzugs brnyan 'char rung gi nus pa yod pa ltar /
NK064(ngu),002:3172: sems nyid dwangs gsal sgrib g.yogs med pa'i klong na
NK064(ngu),002:3173: sku dang ye shes kyi yon tan 'char rung ma
NK064(ngu),002:3174: 'gags par gnas pa ni 'bras bu don dam ste
NK064(ngu),002:3176: bdun dang gsum phyir don dam pa //
NK064(ngu),002:3178: 'bras bu don dam la sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK064(ngu),002:3179: phrin las lngar phye bas sems nyid don dam dkor
NK064(ngu),002:3180: bdun ngo bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub pa lhag
NK064(ngu),002:3181: pa don dam bden pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3182: sems nyid don dam bden pa'i rtsal snang sku dang
NK064(ngu),002:3183: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang shar ba ni
NK064(ngu),002:3184: lhag pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3185: de gnyis kyang ngo bo dbyer mi phyed par /
NK064(ngu),002:3186: gser dang gser gyi ser po dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3187: g.yu dang g.yu yi sngon po dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3188: mar me dang mar me'i 'od lta bur zung 'jug
NK064(ngu),002:3189: ngo bo gcig pa'i bdag nyid du gnas pa ni
NK064(ngu),002:3190: lhag pa bden pa dbyer med pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3191: de yang spyod yul dang bral bar ye nas gnas
NK064(ngu),002:3192: pa zhes pas bden pa dbyer med de ni blos
NK064(ngu),002:3194: ngag gis brjod pa'i yul las 'das pas smra bsam brjod med kyi don te /
NK064(ngu),002:3195: smra bsam brjod med shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK064(ngu),002:3198: don de gang yin nam mkha' dag la brtag par gyis //
NK064(ngu),002:3200: de la ye nas gnas pa zhes pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3201: de ni bcos ma glo bur gyi chos ma yin
NK064(ngu),002:3202: par gdod ma khungs thub kyi chos sems nyid de
NK064(ngu),002:3203: ga'i gnas lugs sam yin lugs sam gshis lugs su
NK064(ngu),002:3204: gdod ma nas de ltar yod pas ye nas gnas
NK064(ngu),002:3205: pa zhes bshad pa yin gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:3206: de la mdo rgyud rnams su ming gi rnam grangs du ma zhig bshad pa yod de /
NK064(ngu),002:3207: khams bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3208: rang bzhin du gnas pa'i rigs dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3210: dri bcas de bzhin nyid la sogs pa tha snyad gang la'ang 'jug pa'i gazhi'o //
NK064(ngu),002:3212: de la bder gshegs snying po la /
NK064(ngu),002:3213: spyir mdo rgyud bstan bcos rnams su rigs zhes grags
NK064(ngu),002:3214: pa la grub mtha'i dbang gis 'dod tshul mi 'dra
NK064(ngu),002:3216: bye brag tu smra bas ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3217: srid pa dang srid pa'i yo byad la ma chags
NK064(ngu),002:3218: pa'i sems byung chog shes pa la 'phags pa'i rigs
NK064(ngu),002:3220: sems kyi sa bon zag med kyi ye shes 'byung rung gi nus pa la 'dod /
NK064(ngu),002:3222: thog ma med pa nas sems rgyud la gnas pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:3223: zag med kyi chos skyed par byed pa'i nus pa
NK064(ngu),002:3224: chos nyid kyis thob pa la 'dod /
NK064(ngu),002:3225: de rnams ni bde gshegs snying po 'dus byas su
NK064(ngu),002:3226: 'dod pa'i lugs te dngos por smra ba'i lugs so
NK064(ngu),002:3228: dri bcas de bzhin nyid la rigs su phal cher 'dod pa mthun kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:3229: ngos 'dzin lugs mi 'dra ba mang du snang mod /
NK064(ngu),002:3230: 'dir theg chen thun mong ma yin pa'i lugs ltar na /
NK064(ngu),002:3231: sems nyid ye nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag
NK064(ngu),002:3232: pa stong gsal 'gags med kun khyab kyi ngo bor
NK064(ngu),002:3233: 'pho 'gyur med par gnas pa ni khams bde bar
NK064(ngu),002:3234: gshegs pa'i snying po zhes nges don gyi mdo sde
NK064(ngu),002:3237: dag pa dwangs pa 'od gsal ba //
NK064(ngu),002:3239: bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ste //
NK064(ngu),002:3240: ye nas gnas pa'i chos nyid do //
NK064(ngu),002:3242: sangs rgyas phal po che las /
NK064(ngu),002:3243: stong gsum dar yug gi dpe bkod nas /
NK064(ngu),002:3244: kye rgyal ba'i sras de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa ye shes dang tshad med pa'i ye shes /
NK064(ngu),002:3245: sems can thams cad la nye bar 'tsho ba'i ye
NK064(ngu),002:3246: shes kyang sems can thams cad kyi sems kyi rgyud
NK064(ngu),002:3247: la ma tshang ba med par bzhugs te /
NK064(ngu),002:3248: sems can gyi sems kyi rgyud de dag kyang de
NK064(ngu),002:3249: bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes dang 'dra bar tshad med
NK064(ngu),002:3250: do // de lta mod kyi 'du shes kyi 'dzin
NK064(ngu),002:3251: pas bcings pa'i byis pa rnams kyis de bzhin gshegs
NK064(ngu),002:3252: pa'i ye shes mi shes rab tu mi shes shing
NK064(ngu),002:3253: nyams su mi myong mngon sum du mi byed do
NK064(ngu),002:3254: do // // des na de bzhin gshegs pa chags
NK064(ngu),002:3255: pa med pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes kyi
NK064(ngu),002:3256: chos kyi dbyings sems can gyi gnas thams cad rnam
NK064(ngu),002:3257: par gzigs nas 'du shes su 'gyur te /
NK064(ngu),002:3258: kye ma ma la sems can 'di dag ni de
NK064(ngu),002:3259: bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes yang dag pa ji lta
NK064(ngu),002:3260: ba bzhin mi shes pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3261: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes rjes su zhugs pa dag ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3262: gang yang ngas sems can 'di dag la 'phags pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:3263: lam nye bar bstan pas 'du shes kyis byas pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:3264: 'ching ba mtha' dag bsal bar bya ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3265: ji ltar rang nyid kyis 'phags pa'i ye shes kyi
NK064(ngu),002:3266: stobs bskyed pas 'du shes kyi mdud pa chen po
NK064(ngu),002:3267: bsal nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes so sor
NK064(ngu),002:3269: de bzhin gshegs pa dang mnyam pa nyid rjes su
NK064(ngu),002:3270: thob pa bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa'i lam bstan
NK064(ngu),002:3271: pas 'du shes kyis byas pa'i 'ching ba mtha' dag
NK064(ngu),002:3273: 'du shes kyis byas pa'i 'ching ba thams cad las
NK064(ngu),002:3274: log pa dag la ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye
NK064(ngu),002:3275: shes tshad med pa des 'gro ba thams cad kyi
NK064(ngu),002:3278: 'grib pa dang 'phel ba med pa'i mdo las kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:3279: sh+aa ri'i bu don dam pa zhes bya ba 'di
NK064(ngu),002:3280: ni sems can gyi khams kyi tshig bla dwags so
NK064(ngu),002:3281: // sh+aa ri'i bu sems can gyi khams zhes bya
NK064(ngu),002:3282: ba 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po'i tshig
NK064(ngu),002:3284: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po'i mdo las kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:3285: rigs kyi bu dag 'di ni chos rnams kyi chos nyid de bzhin nyid de /
NK064(ngu),002:3286: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams byung yang rung ma byung
NK064(ngu),002:3287: yang rung sems can 'di dag ni rtag tu de
NK064(ngu),002:3288: bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po can yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:3290: de dag gi dgongs 'grel gyi bstan bcos rgyud bla ma las /
NK064(ngu),002:3291: rdzogs sangs sku ni 'phro phyir dang //
NK064(ngu),002:3292: de bzhin nyid dbyer med phyir dang //
NK064(ngu),002:3293: rigs yod phyir na lus can kun //
NK064(ngu),002:3294: rtag tu bde gshegs snying po can //
NK064(ngu),002:3295: zhes rgyu mtshan gsum gyis sems can thams cad bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po can du bstan cing /
NK064(ngu),002:3296: nyon mongs sbubs nang gnas pa de //
NK064(ngu),002:3297: dpe dag gis ni shes par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:3298: zhes gsungs pas dpe dgu ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3300: sangs rgyas pad ngan sbrang ma sbrang rtsi dang //
NK064(ngu),002:3301: sbun la snying po mi gtsang nang na gser //
NK064(ngu),002:3302: sa la gter dang myug sogs 'bras chung dang //
NK064(ngu),002:3303: gos hrul na nga na rgyal ba'i sku dang ni //
NK064(ngu),002:3304: bud med ngan pa'i lto na mi bdag dang //
NK064(ngu),002:3305: sa nang rin chen gzugs yod ji ltar bar //
NK064(ngu),002:3306: glo bur nyon mongs dri mas bsgribs pa yi //
NK064(ngu),002:3307: sems can rnams la de bzhin khams 'di gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:3308: zhes dpe dgu'i sgo nas mdor bstan du bshad cing /
NK064(ngu),002:3309: rgyas bshad kyi skabs su rnam bzhag rnam pa bcu'i sgo nas gtan la phab pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3311: ngo bo rgyu 'bras las ldan 'jug pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:3312: gnas skabs de bzhin kun tu 'gro ba'i don //
NK064(ngu),002:3313: rtag tu mi 'gyur yon tan dbyer med pa //
NK064(ngu),002:3314: don dam dbyings kyi dgongs don yin zhes bya //
NK064(ngu),002:3315: zhes sogs rgyas par gsungs so //
NK064(ngu),002:3316: de yang mdor hril gyis dril na /
NK064(ngu),002:3317: de la bde gshegs snying po zhes brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3318: sems nyid bden pa dbyer med du gnas pa de
NK064(ngu),002:3319: nyid sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo yin pa'i cha nas
NK064(ngu),002:3321: sems nyid de la stong cha nas chos sku'i yon tan dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3322: snang cha nas gzugs sku'i yon tan 'char rung ma 'gags par gnas pas rang bzhin gnas rigs dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3323: 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i 'byung gzhi yin pas kun gzhi'i ye shes dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3324: de nyid sems can gyi dus su dri ma dang 'brel bas dri bcas de bzhin nyid dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3325: sogs khongs nas kri ya pa rnams kyis bdag gi de kho na nyid dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3326: u pa ya dang yo ga pa gnyis kyis don
NK064(ngu),002:3327: dam par mtshan ma med pa'i byin rlabs kun rdzob
NK064(ngu),002:3328: rdo rje dbyings kyi lhar blta ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3329: ma h+aa yo ga ba rnams kyis sems nyid ye
NK064(ngu),002:3330: nas bden pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen
NK064(ngu),002:3331: po zhes dang / a nu yo ga pa rnams
NK064(ngu),002:3332: kyis gnyis su med pa'i sras rtsa ba byang chub
NK064(ngu),002:3334: a ti yo ga ba rnams kyis ngo bo rang
NK064(ngu),002:3335: bzhin thugs rje gsum zhes pa la sogs pa ming
NK064(ngu),002:3336: gi tha snyad du ma la 'jug pa'i gzhi yin
NK064(ngu),002:3337: pas so gsungs / de nyid gzhi lam 'bras gsum
NK064(ngu),002:3338: gyi ldog cha gang rung dang ma bstun par spyir
NK064(ngu),002:3339: pas so gsungs / bzhag pa na / zhes pas /
NK064(ngu),002:3340: de la rang bzhin nam gnas lugs zhes pa las ming gi tha snyad gang yang mi 'jug pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:3341: de gsum gang rung dang bstun na /
NK064(ngu),002:3342: de nyid dri ma cung zad kyang ma spangs pa'i gnas skabs la gzhi /
NK064(ngu),002:3343: dri ma sbyong bzhin pa'i gnas skabs la ltos nas lam /
NK064(ngu),002:3344: dri ma mtha' dag dang bral ba'i gnas skabs la 'bras bur 'jog go //
NK064(ngu),002:3347: tha snyad gnyis kyi chos rnams kun //
NK064(ngu),002:3348: ma lus 'byung phyir gzhi zhes bya //
NK064(ngu),002:3349: zhes pas gnas lugs la ltos nas 'khor 'das gnyis kyi tha snyad las 'das kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:3350: snang lugs la de gnyis kyi tha snyad 'byung bas so gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:3351: gzhi de la dbye na rim gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:3352: ngo bo'i gzhi dang btags pa'i gzhi //
NK064(ngu),002:3353: zhes pas gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi ni
NK064(ngu),002:3354: dri ma sbyong ba'i gzhi nor bu rin po che
NK064(ngu),002:3355: lta bu'i zhes pas ngo bo'i gzhi ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3356: dper na 'dam rdzab kyi dbus kyi nor bu ltar ro //
NK064(ngu),002:3357: de ltar yang klu sgrub kyis /
NK064(ngu),002:3358: sa yi nang na gnas pa'i chu //
NK064(ngu),002:3359: dri ma med par yang dag gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:3360: nyon mongs nang na ye shes kyang //
NK064(ngu),002:3361: de bzhin dri ma med par gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:3363: nor bu'i 'dam rdzab lta bu ni btags pa'i gzhi ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3364: med snang 'khor ba'i chos thams cad sbyangs bya'i dri ma 'dam rdzab lta bu ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3365: de ni gnyis med la gnyis su bzung nas log shes 'khrul rtog ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3367: gang zhig log par rtog pas med mthong ba //
NK064(ngu),002:3368: byis pa 'di dag med pa'i chos la spyod //
NK064(ngu),002:3371: 'khor ba'i chos rnams thag khra yi //
NK064(ngu),002:3372: sbrul ltar med pa nyid du 'dod //
NK064(ngu),002:3374: de nyid la btags gzhi zhes pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3375: zhen snang nyid 'khor ba 'grub byed kyi rgyu dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3376: 'khor ba pa'i rnam shes kyi 'jug pa ma zad
NK064(ngu),002:3377: kyi bar du rgyun chags pa tsam yin pas de
NK064(ngu),002:3378: ltar du bshad pa yin gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:3379: 'bras bu'i nyer len du gyur pa'i rgyu rgyud ma yin zhes pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3380: 'bras bu'i nyer len du mi 'gro ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3381: 'bras bu thob pa'i dus zad nas rang zad nas rang sangs la 'gro ba'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3382: bcos ma glo bur gyi chos yin pas so gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:3383: rig pas dpyad don gyi stong nyid med dgag kyang rgyu rgyud mtshan nyid pa ma yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:3384: zhes pa mtshan nyid pa ma yin kyang btags pa tsam du khas len te /
NK064(ngu),002:3385: de la dmigs nas skyon yon skye ba tsam yin gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:3386: stong nyid med dgag de gang yin zhe na /
NK064(ngu),002:3387: ka ba ka ba'i ngo bor stong /
NK064(ngu),002:3388: bum pa bum pa'i ngo bor stong pa ste chos
NK064(ngu),002:3389: thams cad rang rang gi ngo bos stong pas dgag
NK064(ngu),002:3390: gzhi chos can stong pas skye med tsam du zad
NK064(ngu),002:3392: de rnams kyis gzhi'i don bshad pa song nas /
NK064(ngu),002:3393: gnyis pa lam gyi rgyud ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3394: rgyu'i rgyud de glo bur gyi dri ma dang bral bar byed pa'i zhes sogs kyis bstan /
NK064(ngu),002:3397: ngo bo shes rab rnam gsum gyis //
NK064(ngu),002:3398: sems lnga skye bar bstan pa yin //
NK064(ngu),002:3400: sems lnga'i sgo nas lam gyi ngo bo skye ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:3401: de yang sems skye tshul ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3402: gzhi'i sa nas sems skye ba zhes pa theg pa
NK064(ngu),002:3403: gang du yang ma zhugs pa'i gnas skabs nas skye
NK064(ngu),002:3404: ba dang / lam gyi sa nas sems skye ba
NK064(ngu),002:3405: zhes pa nyan rang sogs kyi theg par zhugs nas
NK064(ngu),002:3406: sked 'jus byas te lam de bor nas theg pa
NK064(ngu),002:3408: 'bras bu'i sa nas sems skye ba zhes pa theg pa 'og ma'i 'bras bu'i bar du bslabs nas /
NK064(ngu),002:3409: de nas sngags lam 'dir 'jug pa rnams so gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:3410: sems ji ltar skye tshul ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3411: theg pa 'og ma'i skyon mthong zhing gong ma'i yon
NK064(ngu),002:3412: tan mthong ste 'jug 'dod kyi sems dang po 'go
NK064(ngu),002:3413: ldang ba'i tshul gyis skyes pa g.yo ldang byang chub
NK064(ngu),002:3414: kyi sems / theg pa de'i yon tan thob na snyam pa smon pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK064(ngu),002:3415: de smon pa tsam du ma bzhag par de la 'jug pa 'jug pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK064(ngu),002:3416: de la gnas pa gnas pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK064(ngu),002:3417: de'i 'bras bu thob pa mthar phyin byang chub kyi sems te /
NK064(ngu),002:3418: de yang ngo bo shes rab rnam pa gsum gyis
NK064(ngu),002:3419: thun mong gi sems lnga theg pa 'og ma pa
NK064(ngu),002:3420: rnams dang / mchog gi sems lnga bla na med pa'i theg pa 'dir 'jug pa'i sems te /
NK064(ngu),002:3421: de yang skyes sam skyes so zhes pas /
NK064(ngu),002:3422: cig car du skye ba zhig yod de /
NK064(ngu),002:3423: skyes sam skyes so zhes pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3426: rtogs grol dus mnyam in+d+ra b+hu ti bzhin //
NK064(ngu),002:3428: skye ba ni rim gyis skye bas so gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:3429: nges tshig ni go sla zhing /
NK064(ngu),002:3431: rnal 'byor bla na med pa khyad par gyi lam
NK064(ngu),002:3432: 'di ni nye ba'i lam mam thabs rgyud yin la
NK064(ngu),002:3434: khyad par can gyi lam zhes pa theg chen dbu
NK064(ngu),002:3435: ma sogs su bden gnyis zung 'jug zer kyang zung
NK064(ngu),002:3436: 'jug rnal ma'i don ma myong ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3437: thabs bde ba chen po'i khyad par med pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu),002:3438: nye lam zhes pa'ang lam 'dir zhugs na theg pa
NK064(ngu),002:3439: gzhan bstan mi dgos par 'di kho nas 'bras bu
NK064(ngu),002:3442: theg pa gzhan rnams su ni dug gsum la spang byar byed la /
NK064(ngu),002:3443: 'dir ni dmigs med lta bas gzer btab nas /
NK064(ngu),002:3446: gti mug rig stong gi ngo bor bltas te dug
NK064(ngu),002:3447: gsum lam khyer gyi thabs la brten nas tshe gcig
NK064(ngu),002:3448: gis sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par byed pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:3449: thabs rmad du byung ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3450: sa pan gyi sdom gsum rab dbyer /
NK064(ngu),002:3451: sngags kyis btab pa'i sa bon ni //
NK064(ngu),002:3452: nyi ma gcig la lo thog smin //
NK064(ngu),002:3453: rdo rje theg pa'i thabs shes na //
NK064(ngu),002:3456: de las gzhan pa nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi zhes pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3457: lha mi'i theg pas ngan song las nges par 'byung /
NK064(ngu),002:3458: nyan rang gi theg pas 'khor ba las nges par 'byung /
NK064(ngu),002:3459: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pas mtha' gnyis las nges par 'byung bas so gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:3460: phyi rgyud sde gsum gyi lam skabs 'dir ring lam yin zhes pa /
NK064(ngu),002:3461: spyir sngags lam yin pas nye lam yin mod kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:3462: de dag bla med kyi lam 'di la 'jug dgos pas /
NK064(ngu),002:3463: theg pa 'di la ltos nas ring ba'i lam zhes bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:3464: de yang gzhi 'bras gnyis dang shes thob kyi bya
NK064(ngu),002:3465: byed 'brel pa can du gnas pa'i phyir zhes sogs
NK064(ngu),002:3466: kyi don lam rgyud de gzhi shes par bya ba
NK064(ngu),002:3467: dang mar 'brel / 'bras bu thob par byed pa
NK064(ngu),002:3468: dang yar 'brel te de gnyis kyi bar gyi bya
NK064(ngu),002:3469: byed 'brel ba can du gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu),002:3470: khyad par gyi lam la dbyer na thabs grol gnyis te //
NK064(ngu),002:3471: grol lam thabs su rnam par bstan //
NK064(ngu),002:3473: ngo mtshar ngan 'gro thar pa'i thabs //
NK064(ngu),002:3474: zhes pa 'ching byed kyi las la spyad kyang grol
NK064(ngu),002:3475: ba'i 'bras bu thob pa la ngo mtshar ba'i don
NK064(ngu),002:3476: no // de ni gtso bor thabs kyi khyad par
NK064(ngu),002:3477: brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa rmad du byung ba'i sgo
NK064(ngu),002:3478: nas 'bras bu myur du 'grub par byed pa ste
NK064(ngu),002:3479: no // / zhes pas gtso bor thabs kyi khyad par zhes pa /
NK064(ngu),002:3480: grol lam yang thabs shes gnyis ldan yin kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:3481: 'dir thabs gtso bor ston pa'i phyir gtso bo thabs kyi khyad par zhes smos /
NK064(ngu),002:3482: de la brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa zhes bshad pas /
NK064(ngu),002:3483: dug gsum mi spangs par thog bardzisa kyi spyod pa'i brtul bzhugs te /
NK064(ngu),002:3485: rna bar chu ni zhugs gyur na //
NK064(ngu),002:3486: chu nyid kyis ni gdon par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:3488: slar yang chu snon ma blugs nas bton pas thon 'gro ba bzhin du /
NK064(ngu),002:3489: dug gsum la lta ba'i brtul zhugs kyi gdengs dang
NK064(ngu),002:3490: ldan pas spyad na mi 'ching bar ma zad grol
NK064(ngu),002:3491: ba'i 'bras bu myur du ston pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3492: dper na mak+shi ka'i sbyor bas lcags khams yud tsam gyis gser du bsgyur ba bzhin no //
NK064(ngu),002:3494: mak+shi ka ni dngul chu'i sbyor ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3495: khe nyen gnyis ka'i dper mtshon pas //
NK064(ngu),002:3496: dngul chu'i sbyor ba legs par shes pa zhig gis
NK064(ngu),002:3497: gnas skabs lnga'i sgo nas lcags khams gser du 'gyur
NK064(ngu),002:3499: du ba dang ni tsag tsag dang //
NK064(ngu),002:3500: sbal pa 'phyong ba nyid dang ni //
NK064(ngu),002:3502: dngul chu yi ni gnas skabs lnga //
NK064(ngu),002:3504: de'i sbyor ba mi shes pa zhig gis byas na
NK064(ngu),002:3505: dngul chu'i dgra me yin pas lcags gser du mi
NK064(ngu),002:3506: 'gyur ba ma zad dngul chu'i rgyu khams chen po
NK064(ngu),002:3507: de yang chud zos su 'gro ba bzhin du /
NK064(ngu),002:3508: thabs dang mi ldan pa zhig gis sbyor sgrol gyi
NK064(ngu),002:3509: las la spyad na grol ba'i 'bras bu mi thob
NK064(ngu),002:3510: par ma zad / ngan song du ltung ba'i nyen chen po yod de /
NK064(ngu),002:3511: zhe sdang gis ni dmyal bar skye //
NK064(ngu),002:3515: thabs lam de la dbye na gnyis te /
NK064(ngu),002:3516: gdams ngag steng dang 'og gi sgo //
NK064(ngu),002:3518: 'khor lo drug la brten nas 'bar 'dzag gi sbyor bas sogs te /
NK064(ngu),002:3520: 'khor lo sum gnyis srog shing gsum //
NK064(ngu),002:3521: me rlung 'gro bas nam mkha'i ba //
NK064(ngu),002:3522: bzho bas steng du rnam par grags //
NK064(ngu),002:3524: 'khor lo gsum gnyis zhes pas gsum tshan gnyis te drug yin cing /
NK064(ngu),002:3525: srog shing gsum ni rtsa ro rkyang dbu gsum ste
NK064(ngu),002:3526: lus kyi dbus su srog shing bslang ba ltar yod
NK064(ngu),002:3527: pa de la brten pa'i rtsa 'khor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3528: spyi bo'i bde chen gyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab so gnyis //
NK064(ngu),002:3529: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab bcu drug /
NK064(ngu),002:3530: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab brgyad /
NK064(ngu),002:3531: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo rtsa 'dab drug cu re bzhi /
NK064(ngu),002:3532: de'i 'og tu sbar bya me'i 'khor lo gru gsum ram gyis mtshan pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3533: de'i 'og tu sbar byed rlung gi 'khor lo gzhu'i
NK064(ngu),002:3534: dbyibs can yam yig gis mtshan pa drug gnas shing
NK064(ngu),002:3535: / me rlung 'gro bas nam mkha'i ba //
NK064(ngu),002:3536: zhes pas de ltar steng sgo'i lam nyams su blangs
NK064(ngu),002:3537: pas steng rlung mnan pa ro rkyang gnyis kyi lam
NK064(ngu),002:3538: brgyud de lte 'og tu slebs pa dang 'og rlung
NK064(ngu),002:3539: bskum pa'i rkyen gyis sum mdo'i rlung dang bcas pas
NK064(ngu),002:3540: rlung gi dkyil 'khor g.yos pas me'i dkyil 'khor 'bar
NK064(ngu),002:3541: te me rlung gnyis po dbu ma'i lam brgyud spyi
NK064(ngu),002:3542: bo'i ham yig la nam mkha'i ba zhes pa'i tha
NK064(ngu),002:3543: snyad btags pas / ba las 'o ma bzho ba
NK064(ngu),002:3544: mtshon byed du byas pa ham yig las byang sems
NK064(ngu),002:3545: dngul chu'i rdog po ltar 'dzag pas spyi bo'i rtsa
NK064(ngu),002:3546: 'khor gang bas dga' ba'i ye shes skyes /
NK064(ngu),002:3547: de bzhin du mgrin pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3549: lte ba ste 'khor lo bzhir bde ba'i ye shes
NK064(ngu),002:3550: bskyed pa la bslab pa thabs lam steng sgo'i lam
NK064(ngu),002:3551: mo // de la spyi dang khyad par gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:3552: khyad par ba ni le'u bcu gsum pa'i dngos bstan sgra ji bzhin pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:3553: gnyis pa thabs lam 'og sgo ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3554: 'og sgo mkha' gsang gnyis la brten nas sogs te /
NK064(ngu),002:3556: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK064(ngu),002:3557: sgrub pa dang ni sgrub chen po //
NK064(ngu),002:3559: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi'i sgo nas ston pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3560: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i yum btsal ba /
NK064(ngu),002:3561: brtag pa sogs bsnyen pa'i yan lag /
NK064(ngu),002:3562: brda bzhis bskul te phyag rgya bzhis 'du shes gsum
NK064(ngu),002:3563: ldan gyi sgo nas snyoms par 'jug pa nye bsnyen
NK064(ngu),002:3564: / de ltar byang sems spyi bo mgrin pa snying
NK064(ngu),002:3565: ga lte ba rnams su rim gyis babs pas dga'
NK064(ngu),002:3566: bzhi'i rim pas dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye
NK064(ngu),002:3567: shes dbab bzung gi sbyor bas nyams su myong ba
NK064(ngu),002:3569: de nas byang sems ldog khyab kyi sbyor bas dkar
NK064(ngu),002:3570: dmar 'dres pa yum gyi rtsa kha kha mu kha'i
NK064(ngu),002:3571: rtse nas slar yang gyen du ldog ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3572: lte ba nas spyi bo'i rtsa 'khor gyi bar du khyab pas lus thams cad la rtsas khyab /
NK064(ngu),002:3573: rtsa thams cad la byang chub sems kyis khyab /
NK064(ngu),002:3574: de thams cad la bde ba'i ye shes kyis khyab
NK064(ngu),002:3575: pas rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyams
NK064(ngu),002:3576: su myong ba ni sgrub pa chen po'i yan lag
NK064(ngu),002:3577: ste / skad cig la bde stong gi ye shes
NK064(ngu),002:3578: btsan thabs su skye ba la sa lam chig chod
NK064(ngu),002:3579: du rdzogs pa'i thabs lam cig car ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3581: phun sum tshogs pa'i lhun grub rnams //
NK064(ngu),002:3582: gsang dbang mchog gis sbyin par byed //
NK064(ngu),002:3585: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK064(ngu),002:3586: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK064(ngu),002:3587: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK064(ngu),002:3588: ces pas gtso bor shes rab rnam pa gsum gyi sgo nas sogs te /
NK064(ngu),002:3589: lam 'di la thabs kyi khyad par yod mod kyang shes rab gtso bor gtan la 'bebs pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3590: dang po thos pa'i shes rab kyis gsung rab kyi
NK064(ngu),002:3591: mtha' rgya bcad de thos pa rgya mtsho bsags nas
NK064(ngu),002:3592: / bsam pa'i shes rab kyis thos don bsam pas brtags te /
NK064(ngu),002:3593: bsregs bcad brdar ba'i gser bzhin du //
NK064(ngu),002:3594: legs par brtags la nga yi bka' //
NK064(ngu),002:3595: blang bar bya yi gus phyir min //
NK064(ngu),002:3596: zhes gsungs pa bzhin du gtan la phab nas /
NK064(ngu),002:3597: sgom pa'i shes rab kyis sems nyid rnal ma'i don
NK064(ngu),002:3598: la ma bcos par bzhag pas rang rgyud kyi 'ching
NK064(ngu),002:3599: ba rang sangs su song nas chos nyid kyi klong
NK064(ngu),002:3600: du grol ba zhes bya gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:3601: dpe rin po che ko tu b+ha zhes bya ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:3602: rin po che'i rigs shig yod pa de khe nyen
NK064(ngu),002:3603: chung ba'i grol lam gyi dper mtshungs te /
NK064(ngu),002:3604: rin po che de rdo phal pa dang lhan cig tu bzhag pa na /
NK064(ngu),002:3605: de ma thag tu rin po che'i rigs su mi 'gyur la /
NK064(ngu),002:3606: ji zhig na de dang 'dra bar 'gyur bas na /
NK064(ngu),002:3607: grol lam de yang thabs lam lta bu'i myur khyad med kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:3608: ji zhig na 'bras bu la sbyor ba la khyad par med pas so gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:3611: ring ba'ang rim dang cig car ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:3612: zhes pas ring bas zhes pa /
NK064(ngu),002:3613: grol lam 'di ring ba'i lam yin zhing /
NK064(ngu),002:3614: de la'ang rim gyis pa dang cig car ba gnyis yod pa'i don yin gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:3615: dbang po yang rab rtogs goms thams cad dbyer med
NK064(ngu),002:3616: chig chod du byed pa zhig yod de cig car
NK064(ngu),002:3618: dbang dus su grol ba'i rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu ti lta bu'o gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:3619: rim gyis rtogs goms mthar phyin par byed pa ni rim gyis pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3623: 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen //
NK064(ngu),002:3624: nus mthu can du gang gyur pa //
NK064(ngu),002:3625: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NK064(ngu),002:3626: zhes pas mtshan nyid gsum ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3627: dang po rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3629: gzhi dang gtan tshigs grub pa'i don //
NK064(ngu),002:3631: gzhal bya zhen snang nyid sogs te /
NK064(ngu),002:3637: btags pa'i spyod yul gnyis la gzhal //
NK064(ngu),002:3638: zhes pas 'khor 'das gnyis su zhen pa'i zhen pa sgro btags dang bcas pa ni gzhal bya ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3639: 'o na 'khor 'das gnyis mi gzhal lam zhe na /
NK064(ngu),002:3641: 'khor ba ni med snang glo bur ba yin pas gzhal rgyu ma byung /
NK064(ngu),002:3642: mya ngan las 'das pa ni blo'i spyod yul las 'das pas gzhal byar ma grub pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3644: 'das pa spyod yul ma yin phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:3645: gzhal bya'i yul du ji ltar rigs //
NK064(ngu),002:3647: gnyis pa 'jal byed kyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3649: de nyid dngos lnga tshul dang tshig /
NK064(ngu),002:3653: tshig lnga'i gtan tshigs dang gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:3655: ston pa chos kyi skus 'khor ye shes rgya mtsho
NK064(ngu),002:3656: la skye med don gyi gsung gis brda sprod pa
NK064(ngu),002:3657: dang / longs skus 'khor smin pa rgya mtsho la
NK064(ngu),002:3658: dgongs pa brda yi gsung gis brda sprod pa dang
NK064(ngu),002:3659: dang / / sprul skus 'khor mos pa rgya mtsho
NK064(ngu),002:3660: la brjod pa tshig gi gsung gis brda sprod pa
NK064(ngu),002:3661: dang / / dang / rdo rje'i skus dbyer med
NK064(ngu),002:3662: rdo rje'i 'khor la rdo rje'i gsung gis brda sprod
NK064(ngu),002:3663: dang / / dang / pa dang / mngon byang
NK064(ngu),002:3664: gi skus 'khor rgyal ba rgya mtsho la rig pa
NK064(ngu),002:3665: byin rlabs kyi gsung gis brda sprod pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3667: ston pa sku lngas rang rang gi 'khor la gsung
NK064(ngu),002:3668: lnga'i sgo nas chos nyid kyi don dngos su gtan
NK064(ngu),002:3669: la phab pa ni dngos lnga'i gtan tshigs te /
NK064(ngu),002:3671: yang dag rdzogs sangs rgyas ston pa //
NK064(ngu),002:3673: gsung lnga bstan pa de kho na //
NK064(ngu),002:3676: gnyis pa rjes 'jug tshul lnga'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3677: sku lnga de dag gi gsung lnga dang tshul mthun pa'i brda don te /
NK064(ngu),002:3678: skye med mtshon pa nam mkha' lta bu dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3679: sgrib pa ngos 'dzin pa me long nang gi gzugs brnyan lta bu dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3680: rang rig mngon gsal rang gsal nyi ma'i 'od lta bu dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3681: dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung mtshon pa grags stong dbyer med brag cha lta bu dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3682: brjod pa tshig gi gsung mtshon pa kun yid 'jug pa tshangs pa dbyangs kyi sgra lta bu ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3684: brjod dang 'dra bar brda sprod pa //
NK064(ngu),002:3685: ngo bo nyid kyis bshad pa'i phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:3686: ma 'ongs don du gtan tshigs nges //
NK064(ngu),002:3688: gsum pa tshig lnga'i gtan tshigs ni sngar gyi tshul
NK064(ngu),002:3689: lnga po de tshig tu dngos su brjod pa ni
NK064(ngu),002:3692: chos sku'i tshig ni skye med rang du ston pa'i tshig dang yi ge rnams so //
NK064(ngu),002:3693: longs sku'i ldem dgongs brda ston pa'i tshig dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3694: sprul sku'i dkri drang brgyud pa'i tshig dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3695: rdo rje'i sku'i dbyer med rdo rje'i tshig dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3696: mngon byang gi dbyer med rang snang du ston pa'i tshig dang yi ge rnams so //
NK064(ngu),002:3697: zhes zhal lung las gsungs so //
NK064(ngu),002:3700: ngo bo snang tshig rang snang tshig /
NK064(ngu),002:3701: ldem dgongs tshig dang dkri drang tshig /
NK064(ngu),002:3702: 'dod rkyen tshig dang rdo rje'i tshig /
NK064(ngu),002:3703: rang rig mngon gsal tshig gis mtshon //
NK064(ngu),002:3705: de rnams bsdu na dpyad du med pas go ba sku bzhi'i gtan tshigs te /
NK064(ngu),002:3706: dbang rnon rnams brtag dpyad la ma ltos par don go ba'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3707: dpyad du yod pas go ba ni sprul sku'i gtan tshigs te /
NK064(ngu),002:3708: dbang rtul rnams brtag dpyad la brten nas don go dgos pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:3710: de lta mod kyang bsdu na gnyis //
NK064(ngu),002:3711: bzhi rjes mi spyod gcig rjes spyod //
NK064(ngu),002:3713: de ltar dpyad du yod pa sprul sku'i gtan tshigs la tshad ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshigs dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3714: sgra mthun don dpags kyi gtan tshigs gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:3719: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs dang bzhi las /
NK064(ngu),002:3722: rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul //
NK064(ngu),002:3723: byin gyis rlabs dang mngon sum pa //
NK064(ngu),002:3724: rab tu rtogs pa rnam bzhi yis //
NK064(ngu),002:3725: thams cad mngon rdzogs rgyal po che //
NK064(ngu),002:3727: rtogs pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyis chos thams cad bden
NK064(ngu),002:3728: pa dbyer med du gtan la 'bebs par byed pa
NK064(ngu),002:3729: ste / de la 'khor 'das gnyis su snang zhing
NK064(ngu),002:3730: zhen pa'i gnyis 'dzin gyi blo de gnyis med kyi
NK064(ngu),002:3731: ye shes su gtan la 'bebs pa'i ched du gnyis
NK064(ngu),002:3732: 'dzin gyi zhen pa de gzhal byar byas nas /
NK064(ngu),002:3733: 'jal byed rgyu gcig pa'i gtan tshigs kyis rang bzhin skye med du gtan la 'bebs pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:3735: snga ma snga mas gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha'i
NK064(ngu),002:3736: zhen cha de dang de gtan tshigs phyi ma phyi
NK064(ngu),002:3737: ma rnams kyi gzhal byar byas nas /
NK064(ngu),002:3740: mngon sum pa'i gtan tshigs rnams kyis bcal bas rim pa ji lta bar rang bzhin skye med /
NK064(ngu),002:3743: mtshan nyid blo bral du gtan la phebs pa ni grub mtha'o //
NK064(ngu),002:3745: 'khor 'das gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos so cog chos can /
NK064(ngu),002:3746: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes skye ba med pa'i dbyings su rgyu gcig pa yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:3747: de ltar rtogs pa dang ma rtogs pa las 'khor
NK064(ngu),002:3748: 'das so sor snang ba tsam las gnyis su ma
NK064(ngu),002:3749: grub pa'i phyir / zhes pas rgyu gcig pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK064(ngu),002:3750: sems nyid skye med kyi gdangs chos can /
NK064(ngu),002:3751: rol pa 'gag med sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:3752: mtshon du med pa'i yi ge a nyid mtshon byed
NK064(ngu),002:3753: yi ge du mar snang bas mtshon nas rtogs pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:3754: phyir zhes pa yig 'bru'i tshul gyi gtan tshigs so
NK064(ngu),002:3755: // rang bzhin skye med dang rol pa 'gags med gnyis chos can /
NK064(ngu),002:3756: tshig la snga phyi byung yang de dang de dbyer med du rtogs pa'i mthus /
NK064(ngu),002:3757: de nyid ngo bo dbyer med du rtogs pa'i byin rlabs shugs las 'byung ba yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:3758: lhag pa don dam dkor bdun ngo bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub pas /
NK064(ngu),002:3759: de'i snang ldog snod bcud sku dang ye shes kyi
NK064(ngu),002:3760: dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba'i phyir zhes pa byin
NK064(ngu),002:3761: gyis rlabs pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK064(ngu),002:3762: bden pa dbyer med chos can /
NK064(ngu),002:3763: blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:3764: rang rig mngon sum gyi yul med rang gsal du
NK064(ngu),002:3765: bsam brjod dang bral bar rtogs pa'i phyir zhes pa
NK064(ngu),002:3766: lta bu mngon sum pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK064(ngu),002:3767: rab tu rtogs pa rnam bzhi yis //
NK064(ngu),002:3768: zhes pa'i gtan tshigs bzhi po des bcal bas /
NK064(ngu),002:3769: thams cad mngon rdzogs rgyal po che //
NK064(ngu),002:3770: zhes pas chos thams cad rang rig mngon sum gyis
NK064(ngu),002:3771: rdzogs par gtan la phebs pas dag pa rab 'byams
NK064(ngu),002:3772: kyi snang ba la dbang bsgyur bas na rgyal po
NK064(ngu),002:3774: gnyis pa dag pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3775: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag rtogs shing //
NK064(ngu),002:3777: de yang 'di ltar snang ba phyi nang gi chos rnams chos can /
NK064(ngu),002:3778: ye nas sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:3779: dag pa gsum dang ldan pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:3780: snod 'byung ba lnga yum lngar rnam par dag /
NK064(ngu),002:3781: bcud phung po lnga yab lngar rnam par dag /
NK064(ngu),002:3782: rgyud rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar rnam par dag pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:3784: bdag dang gzhan dang rtog pa'i rgyun /
NK064(ngu),002:3785: rnam dag bla med theg pa'i mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:3787: gsum pa mnyam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3788: mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyis //
NK064(ngu),002:3789: dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK064(ngu),002:3791: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos rnams chos can /
NK064(ngu),002:3792: ye nas chos kyi skur sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:3793: mnyam pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:3795: mi la mir snang ba yang dag kun rdzob dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3796: tho yor la mir snang ba log pa'i kun rdzob gnyis ka snang ba sgyu mar mnyam pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3797: spros pa phyogs re tsam chod pa myu gu bdag
NK064(ngu),002:3798: las skye ba med par rtogs pa lta bu rnam
NK064(ngu),002:3799: grangs pa'i don dam bden pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3800: spros pa mtha' dag chod pa myu gu bdag las kyang mi skye /
NK064(ngu),002:3801: gzhan las kyang mi skye bar mtha' bzhi'i spros pa
NK064(ngu),002:3802: chod pa lta bu rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don
NK064(ngu),002:3803: dam gnyis ka skye med du mnyam pa gnyis ni
NK064(ngu),002:3804: / thun mong gi mnyam pa gnyis so //
NK064(ngu),002:3805: lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3807: snang du 'dra yang don byed dag /
NK064(ngu),002:3808: nus pa'i phyir dang mi nus pa'i //
NK064(ngu),002:3809: yang dag yang dag ma yin pa'i //
NK064(ngu),002:3810: kun rdzob kyi ni dbye ba byas //
NK064(ngu),002:3812: snang la don byed nus pa yang dag kun rdzob dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3813: snang la don byed mi nus pa log pa'i kun
NK064(ngu),002:3814: rdzob gnyis ka ma dag pa las snang log pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:3815: kun rdzob yin pas gnyis ka sku dang ye shes
NK064(ngu),002:3816: kyi dkyil 'khor du mnyam pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3817: chos thams cad rang rang gi ngo bos stong pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:3818: med dgag gi stong nyid de rnam grangs pa'i don
NK064(ngu),002:3819: dam pa dang / sems nyid ci yang ma yin
NK064(ngu),002:3820: pa'i dbyings ye zung du 'jug pa ma yin dgag
NK064(ngu),002:3821: gi stong nyid de rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don
NK064(ngu),002:3822: dam bden pa gnyis ka don dam dkor bdun ngo
NK064(ngu),002:3823: bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub pa mnyam pa lhag
NK064(ngu),002:3825: mnyam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs so //
NK064(ngu),002:3826: bzhi pa bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3827: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK064(ngu),002:3829: de yang 'khor 'das gnyis kyi chos thams cad chos can /
NK064(ngu),002:3830: snang lugs nas du mar snang yang yin lugs nas gzhal na de ltar ma yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:3831: sems nyid skye med rang byung gi ye shes chen
NK064(ngu),002:3832: po gcig gi bdag nyid du ye nas gnas pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:3834: snang ba 'di kun rang rang gi //
NK064(ngu),002:3835: rang bzhin med pa'i rnam shes nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:3836: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK064(ngu),002:3838: gnyis pa sgra mthun don dpag gi gtan tshigs ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3839: thun mong gi theg par dug lnga spong sbyong byed
NK064(ngu),002:3840: pa de theg pa 'dir rang bzhin ma grub pas
NK064(ngu),002:3841: lta bas don spags pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3842: de gtan tshigs kyis bsgrub na /
NK064(ngu),002:3844: yang dag par ma grub ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3845: rang rang gi ngo bos stong pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:3847: de ltar 'jal byed gtan tshigs rnams kyis gtan la
NK064(ngu),002:3848: phab pas rang bzhin rgyu rgyud gnas lugs kyi don
NK064(ngu),002:3849: mngon sum skye ba ni grub mtha' ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3851: rgya mtsho dwangs pa'i gzugs brnyan ltar //
NK064(ngu),002:3852: sgra brten yid la byed min par //
NK064(ngu),002:3853: rang rig mngon sum dmigs bral ba //
NK064(ngu),002:3854: rang sar gsum bral mi bsgul bar //
NK064(ngu),002:3855: nges par gdengs su gang byas pa //
NK064(ngu),002:3856: thos bsam brten pa'i lta mthar phyin //
NK064(ngu),002:3859: mngon sum rig pas thag chod na //
NK064(ngu),002:3860: rnal 'byor sa la slebs pa yin //
NK064(ngu),002:3862: gang dag sngags kyi grub mtha' ni sogs go sla'o //
NK064(ngu),002:3863: gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3864: de la mos sgom dang nges rdzogs gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:3866: don spyi'i rnam pa mos pa lam du byed pa yin cing /
NK064(ngu),002:3868: lam so so'i ting nge 'dzin nyams lnga mthar phyin par bslab pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3870: bi ma la yi phyag rgya bsam gtan gyi 'grel bar /
NK064(ngu),002:3871: g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin lnga //
NK064(ngu),002:3872: bsam gtan nyams kyi skye tshul yin //
NK064(ngu),002:3874: de la dang po g.yo ba'i nyams ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3875: gnas pa dang po ri gzar gyi 'bab chu ltar
NK064(ngu),002:3876: sems skad cig kyang mi gnas par rnam rtog sngar
NK064(ngu),002:3877: bas mang du song ba lta bu ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3878: de yang mang du song ba ma yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:3879: sngar rnam rtog la rtsis gdab ma byas pas ma tshor ba yin /
NK064(ngu),002:3880: da de ngos zin pas cung zad sems zin pa'i 'bras bu'o gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:3881: gnyis pa thob pa'i nyams ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3882: de la skyon yon du ma bltas par rgyun mthud de bsgoms pas /
NK064(ngu),002:3883: dpe rong khung dog po'i 'bab chu lta bu ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3884: rnam rtog 'phro mu nas yud tsam re rtog med du zhi me re gnas pa zhig 'byung ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3885: thob pa'i nyams sam rnam rtog ngal gsos pa'i nyams zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:3886: gsum pa goms pa'i nyams ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3887: de'i rgyun mthud de bsgoms pas /
NK064(ngu),002:3888: dpe g.yo 'gul mang po byed mi nus pa rgan po'i spyod pa lta bu'am /
NK064(ngu),002:3889: 'dab chags rnyis bzung ba ltar phal cher rtog med
NK064(ngu),002:3890: du gnas pa las res 'ga' rtog pa ban bun
NK064(ngu),002:3892: goms pa'i nyams sam rnam rtog thang chad pa'i nyams zhes bya gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:3893: bzhi pa brtan pa'i nyams ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3894: de nas kyang yun bsrings te bsgoms pas /
NK064(ngu),002:3895: dpe mtsho chung ser bus bskyod pa ltar /
NK064(ngu),002:3896: phal cher rtog med rgyal 'byams su nyal le gsal
NK064(ngu),002:3897: sing nger gnas pa las rkyen drag pos cung zad
NK064(ngu),002:3898: g.yo ba ste / brtan pa'i nyams sam rnam rtog
NK064(ngu),002:3899: gis cung zad bskyod du yod pa'i nyams zhes bya'o
NK064(ngu),002:3900: g.yo ba ste / gsungs / lnga pa mthar phyin pa'i nyams ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3902: dpe rgya mtsho rlabs dang bral ba'am ri bo chen
NK064(ngu),002:3903: po ltar gnas pa la rkyen gang gis kyang gnod
NK064(ngu),002:3904: mi nus pa ma zad slar la bogs 'byin zhing
NK064(ngu),002:3905: / btang 'gro bzhag sdod rang dbang du 'byor bas
NK064(ngu),002:3906: mthar phyin pa'i nyams sam rang dbang 'byor ba'i nyams
NK064(ngu),002:3907: / zhes bya'o gsungs / nges rdzogs kyi lam 'di cung zad bshad na /
NK064(ngu),002:3909: srid pa rim par smin tshul gyi //
NK064(ngu),002:3910: 'jug pa'i yan lag lnga ru bzhag /
NK064(ngu),002:3911: gang dag dngos kun rang rig phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:3912: shi ba don dam bden pa ste //
NK064(ngu),002:3913: skye ba bar ma kun rdzob yin //
NK064(ngu),002:3914: skyes pa'i rim gsum gnyis med don //
NK064(ngu),002:3915: zhes pas skye 'chi bar do gsum phrug gcig sbyong ba'i lam rdzogs par ston pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3916: 'chi ba 'od gsal dang rjes su mthun pa'i lam stong pa chen po /
NK064(ngu),002:3917: de bzhin du bar do dang snying rje sgyu ma /
NK064(ngu),002:3918: skyes pa'i rim pa gsum po dang phyag rgya gcig pa /
NK064(ngu),002:3920: tshom bu tshogs sgrub ste lnga las /
NK064(ngu),002:3921: de nyid rag pa bskyed rim gyis sbyong ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3922: phra ba rdzogs rim gyis sbyong tshul gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:3923: dang po bskyed rim gyis sbyong tshul ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3924: 'chi ba'i 'od gsal dang rjes su mthun pa'i lam stong pa chen po ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3925: de yang lus can rnams 'chi ba'i tshe /
NK064(ngu),002:3926: phyi nang gi thim rim rnams rdzogs pa'i mthar 'chi srid chos sku'i 'od gsal 'char te /
NK064(ngu),002:3928: snang ba thim dang rtog pa thim //
NK064(ngu),002:3929: phra ba thim dang rags pa thim //
NK064(ngu),002:3930: thim pa'i rjes la goms pa yis //
NK064(ngu),002:3933: 'di ltar phra rags kyi thim lugs rgyas pa'i phyogs nas 'chad pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK064(ngu),002:3934: thog mar rags pa'i rim pa rang bzhin nyi shu thim par 'gyur te /
NK064(ngu),002:3935: rnam snang gi rigs gzugs kyi phung po 'od gsal du 'jug pa'i rtags su /
NK064(ngu),002:3936: yan lag thams cad phra ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3937: lus kyi nyams zhan cing nus pa med par 'gyur /
NK064(ngu),002:3938: me long lta bu'i ye shes thim pas sems mi gsal zhing rab rib tu 'gyur /
NK064(ngu),002:3939: sa'i khams thim pas las thams cad skam par 'gyur /
NK064(ngu),002:3940: mig gi dbang po thim pas mig mi 'gyur zhing zlum par 'gyur /
NK064(ngu),002:3941: yul gyi gzugs thim pas lus kyi mdangs med cing nyams par 'gyur te /
NK064(ngu),002:3942: de ltar rnam snang gi rigs rnams don dam par 'jug pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:3943: de nas rin 'byung gi rigs tshor ba'i phung po thim pas tshor ba nyams su mi myong /
NK064(ngu),002:3944: mnyam nyid ye shes thim pas tshor ba gsum dran par mi 'gyur /
NK064(ngu),002:3945: chu'i khams thim pas rang lus kyi kha chu dang rdul gcin dang khu khrag sogs skam par 'gyur /
NK064(ngu),002:3946: rna ba'i dbang po thim pas phyi nang gi sgra mi thos /
NK064(ngu),002:3947: yul gyi sgra thim pas rang lus kyi sgra mi thos so //
NK064(ngu),002:3948: de nas pad+ma'i rigs 'du shes kyi phung po thim
NK064(ngu),002:3949: pas rkang gnyis la sogs pa'i sems can rnams mi
NK064(ngu),002:3950: dran / so sor rtog pa'i ye shes thim pas
NK064(ngu),002:3951: pha ma bu sring la sogs pa'i ming mi dran
NK064(ngu),002:3952: dran / / me'i khams thim pas zas mi 'ju /
NK064(ngu),002:3953: sna'i dbang po thim pas steng rlung dal gyi 'gro /
NK064(ngu),002:3954: yul gyi dri thim pas rang gi lus la dri mi bro ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:3955: de nas las kyi rigs 'du byed kyi phung po
NK064(ngu),002:3956: thim pas lus kyi bya ba thams cad la 'jug
NK064(ngu),002:3957: par mi 'gyur / bya ba 'grub pa'i ye shes
NK064(ngu),002:3958: thim pas 'jig rten gyi bya ba dang dgos pa
NK064(ngu),002:3959: par mi 'gyur / mi dran / rlung gi khams thim pas rlung bcu rang gi gnas nas 'pho /
NK064(ngu),002:3960: lce'i dbang po thim pas lce sbom zhing thung la rtsa ba sngon por 'gro /
NK064(ngu),002:3961: yul gyi ro thim pas ro drug nyams su mi
NK064(ngu),002:3962: myong ste de ltar rags pa'i rang bzhin nyi shu
NK064(ngu),002:3963: thim nas / phra ba nang gi 'byung bzhi'i thim lugs ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3964: ye shes rol pa chen po las /
NK064(ngu),002:3965: dang po sa ni chu la thim //
NK064(ngu),002:3966: chu yang me la thim gyur nas //
NK064(ngu),002:3967: me ni rlung la thim par 'gyur //
NK064(ngu),002:3968: rlung ni rnam par shes la thim //
NK064(ngu),002:3972: sa chu la thim pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:3973: lus kyi sa'i gnas su sa med par gyur pa'am /
NK064(ngu),002:3974: gnas 'phos nas chu'i nang du sa 'jug pa'i don yang ma yin gyi /
NK064(ngu),002:3975: dbu ma'i ye shes kyi rlung stobs su gyur pas sa'i las rlung bcom ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3976: rten thim pa na brten pa nges par thim pas
NK064(ngu),002:3977: sra bar snang ba'i rnam shes kyang rang gi bag
NK064(ngu),002:3978: chags dbu ma la bzhag nas 'gags te /
NK064(ngu),002:3979: rus pa la sogs pa srab shas che ba'i khams
NK064(ngu),002:3980: rten rlung dang rnam shes bral bar byas te sa'i
NK064(ngu),002:3981: dwangs ma de nyid chu'i dwangs ma la thim par
NK064(ngu),002:3982: gyur pas lus bsgul bskyod mi nus shing zungs mi
NK064(ngu),002:3983: thub / lus sa la bying snyam byed /
NK064(ngu),002:3984: nang rtags su rmig sgyu lta bu sngo mer mer ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:3986: char zim dang chu g.yo ba'i rnam pa lta bu 'byung /
NK064(ngu),002:3987: de bzhin du dbu ma'i ye shes kyi rlung stobs su gyur pas chu'i las rlung bcom ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3988: gsher ba snang ba'i rnam shes kyang rang gi bag chags dbu ma la bzhag nas 'gags te /
NK064(ngu),002:3989: khrag dang chu ser sogs gsher ba shas che ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:3990: khams rnams rten rlung dang rnam shes bral bas chu'i
NK064(ngu),002:3991: dwangs ma de nyid me'i dwangs ma la thim pas
NK064(ngu),002:3992: kha sna skams shing lce rkan phugs su 'gro /
NK064(ngu),002:3993: nang rtags su du ba 'phyur ba dang du thang chags pa lta bu 'byung /
NK064(ngu),002:3994: dbu ma'i ye shes kyi rlung gis me'i las rlung bcom ste /
NK064(ngu),002:3995: tsha bar snang ba'i rnam shes kyang rang gi bag chags dbu ma la bzhag nas 'gags te /
NK064(ngu),002:3996: drod sogs tsha ba shas che ba'i khams rnams rten rlung dang rnam shes bral bas /
NK064(ngu),002:3997: me'i dwangs ma de nyid rlung gi dwangs ma la
NK064(ngu),002:3998: thim pas lus kyi drod mtha' nas sdud cing pho
NK064(ngu),002:4000: nang rtags su srin bu me khyer lta bur dmar tsig tsig dang dmar phrom phrom 'byung /
NK064(ngu),002:4001: rlung rnam shes la thim pa'i don yang lus kyi rlung gi gnas su rlung med par gyur pa'am /
NK064(ngu),002:4002: sdod sa 'phos nas rlung nyid rnam shes kyi nang du 'jug pa'i don yang ma yin /
NK064(ngu),002:4003: rnam shes la rlung dwangs ma'i bag chags bzhag ste rlung 'gags pa'i don yang ma yin gyi /
NK064(ngu),002:4004: rlung gi dwangs mas srog rtsa rags pa'i bar gyi
NK064(ngu),002:4005: lus thams cad dor nas srog rtsa'i nang gi 'od
NK064(ngu),002:4006: lnga'i sbu gu can gyi rtsa lnga la zhugs nas
NK064(ngu),002:4007: yid kyi snang ba dang ro gcig tu gyur pas
NK064(ngu),002:4008: / dbugs phyir ring du rgyu zhing nang du sdud mi shes pas rags pa'i rgyu ba chad /
NK064(ngu),002:4009: nang rtags su dbu mar me 'bar ba'i rnam pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4010: sgron me'i phreng ba sgrigs pa lta bu 'byung /
NK064(ngu),002:4011: rnam shes nam mkha' la thim pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4012: rnam shes dngos med du gyur pa ma yin gyi /
NK064(ngu),002:4013: nam mkha' ltar dwangs shing thogs pa med pa la
NK064(ngu),002:4014: mtshon par dka' ba'i dbu ma la thim pa ste
NK064(ngu),002:4015: / de yang gsang 'dus 'phags skor gyi gzhung rnams su /
NK064(ngu),002:4016: nam mkha'i khams thim tshul gyi tha snyad gsal bar ma gsungs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4017: khams phra ba de rlung gi nang du sbas nas
NK064(ngu),002:4018: bshad pa yin pas na nam mkha'i khams thim pa
NK064(ngu),002:4019: logs su mi byed par rnam shes thim rim gyi
NK064(ngu),002:4020: skabs su nam mkha' sprin med kyi rtags snang 'char
NK064(ngu),002:4021: gzhir bzhag pa la dkar dmar nag gsum snang ba
NK064(ngu),002:4023: rtog pa thim pa ni rlung nam mkha' la thim pa yan chad du /
NK064(ngu),002:4024: rang bzhin brgyad cu'i snang ba 'du byed kyi bya
NK064(ngu),002:4025: ba byed nus pa rnam shes rlung dang bcas pa
NK064(ngu),002:4027: las mi byed pa'i rtog pa phra mo rnams ni snang gsum nyid la 'dres te gnas pas /
NK064(ngu),002:4028: skabs de dang der thim par 'gyur ba yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:4029: des na snang ba thim pa zhes pa nam mkha' 'od gsal la thim pa'i skabs 'dir /
NK064(ngu),002:4030: sems nyid stong pa'i cha las chos sku'i 'od gsal rnam pa bzhi 'char te /
NK064(ngu),002:4032: don dam de kho na nyid kyi snang ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4033: kun rdzob rten 'brel gyi snang ba gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:4034: don dam de kho na nyid kyi snang ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4035: rtsa ba chos kyi dbyings rang sems bde chen rtags
NK064(ngu),002:4036: pa 'gyur med don dam rang rig chen po de
NK064(ngu),002:4037: yin la / ngo bo bde chen de nyid rang
NK064(ngu),002:4038: gi snang cha'am rang gzugs 'char tshul rdo rje gsum
NK064(ngu),002:4039: gyi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4041: gsung gi gsang ba mched pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4042: thugs kyi gsang ba thob pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4043: sngar bshad kyi kun khyab bde ba chen po de
NK064(ngu),002:4044: nyid ni thams cad stong pa 'od gsal ba yin
NK064(ngu),002:4045: no // kun rdzob rten 'brel gyi snang ba la /
NK064(ngu),002:4046: rang bzhin dang bcas pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4047: rang bzhin dang bral ba'i snang ba gnyis kyi /
NK064(ngu),002:4048: 'dir rang bzhin dang bcas pa la'ang /
NK064(ngu),002:4049: gzhi dus dang lam dus gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:4051: de la'ang rgyun chags pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4052: khyad par gyi dus su 'byung ba gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:4053: phyi ma la'ang ches rags shing gsal bar 'byung ba 'chi ba'i dus dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4054: 'bring gi 'byung ba gnyid dang 'khrig pa'i dus dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4055: phra zhing mi gsal bar 'byung ba tshor drug gi snang ba rags pa shar ba'i dus te /
NK064(ngu),002:4056: de las 'dir 'chi ba'i dus kyi snga rol du
NK064(ngu),002:4057: phra rags nyer lnga yongs su rdzogs par thim rjes
NK064(ngu),002:4059: lus can rnams ni 'chi ba na //
NK064(ngu),002:4060: zla ba bdud rtsi mthur du 'gro //
NK064(ngu),002:4061: steng du nyi rdul sgra gcan de //
NK064(ngu),002:4062: rnam shes srid pa'i mtshan nyid sbyor //
NK064(ngu),002:4064: nam mkha' 'od gsal la mjug dus ro rkyang gi
NK064(ngu),002:4065: dwangs ma thams cad dbu ma'i yas mar gyi a
NK064(ngu),002:4066: ham la 'dus / de nyid snying ga'i ye shes
NK064(ngu),002:4067: 'od gsal gyi dwangs ma chen po'i nang du thim
NK064(ngu),002:4068: pas phra rags kyi rtog pa thams cad 'gags nas
NK064(ngu),002:4069: 'od gsal rnam pa bzhi'i ye shes 'char te /
NK064(ngu),002:4070: de yang dbu ma'i yas sna'i khams dkar cha'i dwangs
NK064(ngu),002:4071: ma mthur du babs nas snying gar son pa na
NK064(ngu),002:4072: / sems snang dang po'i dus su shes rab kyi rang bzhin sum cu rtsa gsum 'gags te /
NK064(ngu),002:4073: 'phags pa lhas mdzad pa'i spyod bsdus las /
NK064(ngu),002:4075: 'dod chags dang bral ba bar ma dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4076: shin tu 'dod chags dang bral ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4077: gang yid kyi 'gro ba dang 'ong ba dang //
NK064(ngu),002:4080: shin tu mya ngan du gyur pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4081: zhi ba dang rnam par rtog pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4104: dogs pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4106: phrag dog ste mtshan nyid sum cu rtsa gsum mo //
NK064(ngu),002:4108: de'i tshe na nang gi khams dkar po dang 'brel ba'i dbang gis /
NK064(ngu),002:4109: phyi rtags su snang ba thams cad sprin bral gyi
NK064(ngu),002:4110: nam mkha' g.ya' dag pa la zla 'od kyis khyab
NK064(ngu),002:4112: gzung ba'i rnam par rtog pa rags pa stong pas stong pa'i 'od gsal dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4113: shes pa'i rang gdangs gsal bar snang bas snang ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:4114: 'od gsal zhes bya ba skad cig ma dang po
NK064(ngu),002:4115: ste / gnyis med rnam rgyal las /
NK064(ngu),002:4116: snang ba zhes bya rnam par mi rtog la //
NK064(ngu),002:4117: gsal ba'i cha de gzung rtog spangs pa las //
NK064(ngu),002:4118: 'byung ba mi mngon rlung dang bcas pa gang //
NK064(ngu),002:4119: lhang nger gnas pa skad cig dang po yin //
NK064(ngu),002:4121: dbu ma'i mas sna'i khams dmar cha'i dwangs ma gyen du song ba'i tshe /
NK064(ngu),002:4122: snang ba'i ye shes mched pa la thim pas thabs
NK064(ngu),002:4123: kyi ye shes kyi rang bzhin bzhi bcu 'gags te
NK064(ngu),002:4145: dga' ba la sbyor ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4146: dga' ba la sbyor ba bar ma dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4147: shin tu dga' ba la sbyor ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4156: nye bar mi len pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4164: gya gyu che ba ste mtshan nyid bzhi bcu tham pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4166: de'i tshe nang gi khams dmar po dang 'brel ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:4167: dbang gis phyi rtags su sprin med kyi nam mkha'
NK064(ngu),002:4168: g.ya' dag pa la nyi 'od kyis khyab pa ltar
NK064(ngu),002:4169: dmar mthing nge ba'am dmar lam pa 'byung /
NK064(ngu),002:4170: 'dzin pa'i rnam par rtog pa rags pa ches stong pas na shin tu stong pa'i 'od gsal dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4171: sems shin tu gsal bar snang bas mched pa'i ye
NK064(ngu),002:4172: shes zhes bya ba skad cig ma gnyis pa ste
NK064(ngu),002:4174: mched pa snang ba rab tu mi rtog ste //
NK064(ngu),002:4175: ches gsal ba la 'dzin rtog ma zhugs te //
NK064(ngu),002:4176: ye shes phra ba rdul bral mi rtog pa //
NK064(ngu),002:4177: lhan ner gnas pa skad cig gnyis pa yin //
NK064(ngu),002:4179: dwangs ma dkar dmar snying gar 'phrad pa'i dus su
NK064(ngu),002:4180: mched pa'i ye shes thob pa la thim pas snang
NK064(ngu),002:4181: ba thob pa'i ye shes kyi rang bzhin bdun 'gags
NK064(ngu),002:4189: the tshom dang bcas pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4190: 'di'i rang bzhin gyi mtshan nyid ni bdun po dag go //
NK064(ngu),002:4192: de'i tshe dkar dmar gyi nus pa'ang dbyings su yal
NK064(ngu),002:4193: te srog rlung gi cha shas 'ga' zhig lus pa
NK064(ngu),002:4194: des dbang byas nas phyi rtags su nam mkha' la
NK064(ngu),002:4195: mun nag gis khyab pa ltar nag thibs kyis 'gro
NK064(ngu),002:4197: shin tu phra ba'i gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa ches
NK064(ngu),002:4198: cher stong pas na stong pa chen po'i 'od gsal
NK064(ngu),002:4199: dang / snang cha'i steng du tha dad pa'i mtshan
NK064(ngu),002:4200: ma thams cad nub pa'i sems 'gags pa la phyogs
NK064(ngu),002:4201: pas snang ba thob pa'i ye shes zhes bya ba
NK064(ngu),002:4204: thob pa'i ye shes shin tu mi rtog pa //
NK064(ngu),002:4205: gsal ba tsam du'ang mi gnas shin tu phra //
NK064(ngu),002:4206: rlung sems mi phyed gsal bar 'char ba ste //
NK064(ngu),002:4207: lham mer gnas pa skad cig gsum pa yin //
NK064(ngu),002:4209: de nas snying ga'i rtsa dar dkar gyi skud pa
NK064(ngu),002:4210: 'dra ba'i nang gi khrag dbugs kyi dwangs ma thig
NK064(ngu),002:4211: le a ham rdzogs par thim pa na thob pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:4212: ye shes kyang 'chi ba 'od gsal la thim pas
NK064(ngu),002:4213: srid pa'i chos thams cad bag chags kyi tshul du
NK064(ngu),002:4214: yod pa'i rgyun de dag la gnas pa yin kyang
NK064(ngu),002:4215: / bag chags de rnams ni 'dir mi mngon la /
NK064(ngu),002:4216: tshe 'dis bsdus pa'i rnam rtog dang kun rdzob kyi snang ba thams cad 'od gsal du thim /
NK064(ngu),002:4217: tshe rabs gzhan gyis bsdus pa rnams ma shar bas /
NK064(ngu),002:4218: re zhig gzung 'dzin gyi snang ba thams cad dang snang ba gsum yang 'gags pas /
NK064(ngu),002:4219: phyi rtags su sprin dang bral ba'i nam mkha' g.ya'
NK064(ngu),002:4220: dag pa lta bu dwangs gsal mtha' dbus med pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:4221: snang ba dang / nang rtags su rnam par mi
NK064(ngu),002:4222: rtog pa lhan cig skyes pa shin tu spros pa
NK064(ngu),002:4223: dang bral ba'i ye shes kho na la yud cig
NK064(ngu),002:4224: gnas pa thams cad stong pa 'od gsal gyi nyams
NK064(ngu),002:4225: 'char bas sems dri ma dang bral ba nye bar
NK064(ngu),002:4226: thob pa'i ye shes zhes bya ba skad cig ma
NK064(ngu),002:4227: snang ba dang / bzhi pa ste / gnyis med rnam rgyal las /
NK064(ngu),002:4228: nye bar thob pa dri ma med pa ste //
NK064(ngu),002:4229: rang byung rang gsal bde ba dmigs su med //
NK064(ngu),002:4230: phra rags rab zhi ting 'dzin mchog tu 'gyur //
NK064(ngu),002:4231: skad cig bzhi par mi 'gyur khyab byed yin //
NK064(ngu),002:4233: de rnams ngos zin pa la /
NK064(ngu),002:4234: snang ba ni goms pa'i 'od gsal /
NK064(ngu),002:4235: mched pa ni bsam gtan gyi 'od gsal /
NK064(ngu),002:4236: thob pa ni rdul bral zag pa med pa'i 'od gsal /
NK064(ngu),002:4237: nye bar thob pa ni lhan cig skyes pa chos sku rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal te /
NK064(ngu),002:4239: 'od gsal ba ni bsam gtan zag pa med //
NK064(ngu),002:4240: rdul bral sa bon med pa mi g.yo ba //
NK064(ngu),002:4241: lhan cig skyes pa chos sku'i snying po ni //
NK064(ngu),002:4242: lhun grub byang chub sems kyi ngo bo nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:4244: de yang 'od gsal bzhi rim gyis shar bas snang
NK064(ngu),002:4245: mched thob pa'i snang ba gsum gyi skabs su sgrib
NK064(ngu),002:4246: pa dang bral ba'i ye shes ka dag ye thog
NK064(ngu),002:4248: sangs rgyas mngon du byed dus bzhin no //
NK064(ngu),002:4249: 'on kyang sangs rgyas kyi spangs pa ni mi ldog la /
NK064(ngu),002:4250: 'di ngo ma shes na ldog pa ni sangs rgyas kyis sa lam du spangs pa yin la /
NK064(ngu),002:4251: 'dir spangs pa med pas ldog par 'gyur zhing /
NK064(ngu),002:4252: ngo shes na mi ldog pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4253: ngo shes pa'i skad cig la grol nas mngon par
NK064(ngu),002:4254: shes pa la sogs pa zag med kyi yon tan
NK064(ngu),002:4255: brnyes pa'i phyir ldog pa'i gnas med pa yin no
NK064(ngu),002:4256: // de ltar 'chi srid chos sku'i 'od gsal de
NK064(ngu),002:4257: nyid lam du khyer nas 'chi srid dag pa chos
NK064(ngu),002:4258: sku'o snyam pa'i gzhi 'bras sbrel ba'i nga rgyal dang
NK064(ngu),002:4259: ldan pas snang grags 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK064(ngu),002:4260: thams cad chos sku spros bral de bzhin nyid kyi
NK064(ngu),002:4261: ting nge 'dzin gyi ngang du bltas te bsgom pa
NK064(ngu),002:4262: ni lam stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor te /
NK064(ngu),002:4263: 'di la dag rdzogs smin gsum tshang dgos pas /
NK064(ngu),002:4264: stong pa chen po'i lam de bsgoms pas mar 'chi ba'i bag chags de dag par byed /
NK064(ngu),002:4265: yar chos sku spros bral gyi rigs kyi nus pa gsos 'debs pas 'bras bu rdzogs par byed /
NK064(ngu),002:4266: bar du lam de bsgoms pas don gyi 'od gsal
NK064(ngu),002:4267: rgyud la skye ba'i gzhi 'ding bas lam gong ma'i
NK064(ngu),002:4268: smin byed du 'gro ba yin gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:4269: gnyis pa bar do dang rjes su mthun pa'i lam snying rje sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4270: chos nyid 'od gsal gyi snang cha de nyid ngos ma zin par nub pa'i skad cig la /
NK064(ngu),002:4271: phyi ma'i bag chags sad byed kyi rkyen ci rigs
NK064(ngu),002:4272: pa dag gis bskul nas rlung sems phra ba'i 'byung
NK064(ngu),002:4273: bzhi dang bcas pa de rnams kyi rgyu rkyen byas
NK064(ngu),002:4274: pa las bar do'i gzugs dwangs shing thogs pa med
NK064(ngu),002:4275: pa de nyid 'grub par byed la /
NK064(ngu),002:4276: de sbyong bar byed pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4278: gnyis pa kun snang nam mkha'i ngang //
NK064(ngu),002:4279: snying rje gsum gyis khyab pa'i phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:4280: khyab brdal chen po'i ting 'dzin bsgom //
NK064(ngu),002:4282: de bzhin nyid ma rtogs pa'i 'gro ba la 'dzin
NK064(ngu),002:4283: med sgyu ma lta bu'i snying rje mkha' khyab tu
NK064(ngu),002:4284: bsgom pa ste / de yang nam mkha'i dbyings dag
NK064(ngu),002:4285: pa las glo bur du 'ja' tshon gyi rnam par
NK064(ngu),002:4286: shar ba yang nam mkha'i cho 'phrul tsam las bden
NK064(ngu),002:4287: par ma grub pa bzhin du stong nyid de bzhin
NK064(ngu),002:4288: nyid kyi gnas lugs de'i ngo na 'khor 'das gnyis
NK064(ngu),002:4289: su med pa de'i ngang las ma g.yos bzhin du
NK064(ngu),002:4290: sgyu ma'i mtshang ma shes pa ltar rtsal snang la
NK064(ngu),002:4291: bden par bzung bas 'khrul te 'khor ba'i gnas su
NK064(ngu),002:4292: rang dbang med par 'khyams pa'i 'gro ba 'di dag
NK064(ngu),002:4293: sdug bsngal las bsgral bar bya'o snyam du rigs drug
NK064(ngu),002:4294: gis bsdus pa'i sems can gyi khams thams cad la
NK064(ngu),002:4295: kun tu khyab pa'i snying rje 'dzin med sgyu ma
NK064(ngu),002:4296: lta bur bltas te bsgoms pa ni snying rje sgyu
NK064(ngu),002:4299: mar bar do'i yid lus sgyu ma lta bu'i bag chags dag par byed /
NK064(ngu),002:4300: yar chos sku spros bral las longs sku mtshan dpes
NK064(ngu),002:4301: brgyan pa'i rigs kyi nus pa gsos 'debs pas 'bras
NK064(ngu),002:4303: bar du snying rje sgyu ma'i lam de bsgoms pas /
NK064(ngu),002:4304: don gyi 'od gsal las zung 'jug gi lha skur
NK064(ngu),002:4305: ldang ba'i mtshams sbyor snying rje chen po rgyud la
NK064(ngu),002:4306: skye ba'i gzhi 'ding bas lam gong ma'i smin byed
NK064(ngu),002:4307: du 'gro gsungs / gsum pa skyes pa'i rim pa gsum po sbyong bar byed pa'i lam de la /
NK064(ngu),002:4310: tshom bu tshogs sgrub dang gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:4311: dang po ma'i mngal du skye ba'i rim pa dang po sbyong ba'i lam phyag rgya gcig pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4312: de la phra rags gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:4313: dang po phra ba yig 'bru la bslab pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4314: sbyangs bya bar do'i sems can de phyi ma'i skye
NK064(ngu),002:4315: ba len pa la phyogs pa na skye gnas la
NK064(ngu),002:4317: bardzusa te skye na gnas la /
NK064(ngu),002:4318: drod gsher las skye na dro grang la /
NK064(ngu),002:4319: sgo nga las skye na ro la /
NK064(ngu),002:4320: mngal las skye na pha ma'i 'du 'phrod la sred pa skye ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4321: gang du skye 'gyur gyi gnas la sred pa skyes
NK064(ngu),002:4322: pa'i rkyen gyis der 'jug ma rag pa skad cig
NK064(ngu),002:4323: ma'i bar do'i rlung sems de yin la /
NK064(ngu),002:4325: ahraba tu brtan gyur a dkar las //
NK064(ngu),002:4326: shin tu phra ba'i a rnams spro //
NK064(ngu),002:4327: phyogs bcur gang bar gsal gyur nas //
NK064(ngu),002:4330: stong nyid snying rje zung du 'jug pa'i rang rig a dkar po /
NK064(ngu),002:4331: gsal brtan gyi tshad brgyad dang ldan pa'i sgo nas bslab pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4332: gnyis pa rags pa lha sku la bslab pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4335: thig le zla ba khu ba sku //
NK064(ngu),002:4336: rnam par bcad bya rdul nyi gsung //
NK064(ngu),002:4337: a yig mun can thugs rab brjod //
NK064(ngu),002:4339: de ltar bar do'i rnam shes de pha ma'i khu
NK064(ngu),002:4340: khrag gi dbus su zhugs pa la lus ngag yid
NK064(ngu),002:4341: gsum gyi rten khu rdul rlung gsum bskyed de /
NK064(ngu),002:4342: de la pha ma gnyis kyi reg pa sra ba de nyams su myong bas sa'i khams grub /
NK064(ngu),002:4343: de bzhin du byang sems khu ba gsher ba'i rang bzhin las chu /
NK064(ngu),002:4344: bskyod pa las drod skyes pa me //
NK064(ngu),002:4345: rtsa gnas thams cad nas byang sems g.yo ba rlung /
NK064(ngu),002:4346: bde ba nam mkha'i khams te rnam par shes pa
NK064(ngu),002:4347: 'byung lnga ye shes kyi khams dang drug 'dus pa
NK064(ngu),002:4348: las grub ste / dgyes rdor las /
NK064(ngu),002:4349: sems ni chen po gcig nyid la //
NK064(ngu),002:4350: lnga yi gzugs kyis rnam par bskor //
NK064(ngu),002:4352: de yang zhag bdun tshan re re la chags pa
NK064(ngu),002:4353: dang bshigs pa sogs 'byung lngas bya ba byed pas
NK064(ngu),002:4354: / zhag bdun phrag bzhi la rim par mer nur ltar gor gyi gnas skabs bzhis zhag nyer brgyad /
NK064(ngu),002:4355: de nas bdun phrag lnga pa mkhrang 'gyur gyi zhag
NK064(ngu),002:4356: dang po la ma dang 'brel ba'i lte ba nas
NK064(ngu),002:4357: rang sor phyed dang bcu gsum gyis tshad dang ldan
NK064(ngu),002:4359: nang du srog rlung dang steng 'og gi sna gnyis
NK064(ngu),002:4360: su dkar dmar gyi thig le dang bcas pa grub
NK064(ngu),002:4361: / zhag gnyis pa la rlung bcu'i rten snying ga'i rtsa 'khor chags shing /
NK064(ngu),002:4362: de nas zhag re la rtsa nyis brgya re chags pas mngal gyi zla ba brgyad dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4363: phyi rol gyi zla ba bzhi ste zla ba bcu
NK064(ngu),002:4364: gnyis kyi bar du rtsa 'phel bas ro rkyang dbu
NK064(ngu),002:4365: gsum gyi rigs 'dzin pa'i rtsa stong phrag nyi shu
NK064(ngu),002:4366: rtsa bzhi re bsdoms pas stong phrag bdun cu rtsa
NK064(ngu),002:4369: lus kyi rjes su 'gro ba'i rtsa //
NK064(ngu),002:4370: stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis brjod //
NK064(ngu),002:4372: de yang lte 'khor chags nas nya'i rnam par 'gyur la /
NK064(ngu),002:4373: de nas rim par yan lag dod pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4374: rkang lag rdzogs pa'i gnas skabs su gcig por rus sbal lta bu zhes gnyis su phye la /
NK064(ngu),002:4375: de nas brtsam ste ji srid btsa' ba'i nyin zhag
NK064(ngu),002:4376: la thug gi bar du phag pa'i gnas skabs zhes
NK064(ngu),002:4377: bya zhing / de yang rim par tshigs rnams kyi
NK064(ngu),002:4378: bar rtsa'i 'khor lo dang sha khrag rus tshigs dang
NK064(ngu),002:4380: de yan chad brgyal ba ltar snang med du gnas pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4381: zla ba drug pa nas yid kyi rnam shes skye
NK064(ngu),002:4382: zhing sngon gyi skye ba dran pa sogs tshor ba
NK064(ngu),002:4383: myong / bdun pa nas skra dang ba spu sogs skyes shing dbang rten rnams kyang 'grub /
NK064(ngu),002:4384: brgyad pa la dbang po rdzogs pas bkres skom dang gshang gci 'byung /
NK064(ngu),002:4385: dgu pa'i mthar sdug bsngal zhing skyo ba skye ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4386: de ltar zla dgu zhag bcu nas btsa' ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4387: de ltar yang nyi zla kha sbyor gyi rgyud las /
NK064(ngu),002:4388: de nas mngal gyi sgor tshud nas //
NK064(ngu),002:4389: pha dang ma yi rgyu rkyen las //
NK064(ngu),002:4390: mer mer po dang nur nur po //
NK064(ngu),002:4391: tar tar po dang gor gor po //
NK064(ngu),002:4392: mkhrang 'gyur nya yi rnam pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:4393: rus sbal bzhin dang phag pa bzhin //
NK064(ngu),002:4394: de ltar zhag ni bdun phrag brgyad //
NK064(ngu),002:4395: lte ba las ni lus rnams bskyed //
NK064(ngu),002:4396: zla dgu de bzhin ngo bcu nas //
NK064(ngu),002:4397: lus rdzogs ma yi mngal nas 'thon //
NK064(ngu),002:4399: zhar la sems can rnams gang du skye ba'i snod
NK064(ngu),002:4400: kyi 'jig rten chags pa'i gzhi nam mkha'i khams dang
NK064(ngu),002:4401: / chags par 'gyur ba'i rgyu'i gtso bor dbu ma 'jug par /
NK064(ngu),002:4402: sems nyid kyis ni sems can 'jig rten dang //
NK064(ngu),002:4403: snod kyi 'jig rten sna tshogs shin tu 'god //
NK064(ngu),002:4404: 'gro ba ma lus las las skye bar gsungs //
NK064(ngu),002:4405: zhes pas spyir sems can dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4406: bye brag tu las mthun par bsags pa'i sems can
NK064(ngu),002:4407: spyi mthun gyi las kyi bag chags sems la 'gos
NK064(ngu),002:4408: pa yul snang 'dzin gyur thun mong du smin pas
NK064(ngu),002:4409: 'byung bzhi'i dkyil 'khor ri rab dang bcas pa grub
NK064(ngu),002:4410: pa / sems can rnams gang du rgyu zhing longs
NK064(ngu),002:4411: spyod pa'i gnas su gyur pa yul dang khang khyim
NK064(ngu),002:4412: la sogs pa'i zhen rtog sbyong ba'ang rten gzhal yas
NK064(ngu),002:4413: khang sngar longs sku'i gleng gzhir bshad pa bzhin goms
NK064(ngu),002:4415: de'i dag rdzogs smin gsum kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:4416: mar gong du bshad ma thag pa de rnams kyi bag chags dag par byed /
NK064(ngu),002:4417: yar sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rnam par dag pa
NK064(ngu),002:4418: de'i rigs kyi nus pa gsos 'debs pas 'bras bur
NK064(ngu),002:4419: rdzogs par byed / bar du ni 'byung ba rim
NK064(ngu),002:4420: brtsegs gzhal yas khang dang bcas pa'i ting 'dzin gyi
NK064(ngu),002:4422: 'byung ba rim brtsegs ri rab dang bcas pa ni rtsa 'khor lnga dang dbu ma /
NK064(ngu),002:4423: dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi pad nyi rgya gram ni rtsa 'khor gyi lte ba'i rlung thig /
NK064(ngu),002:4424: de rnams dang ro gcig tu 'dres pa'i sems gsal stong bde ba'i cha ni gzhal yas khang ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4425: de nyid legs par sgom pas rtsa rlung thig le
NK064(ngu),002:4426: rnams mnyen cing dul nas rdzogs rim gyi ye shes
NK064(ngu),002:4427: rgyud la skye ba'i gzhi 'ding bas de'i smin byed
NK064(ngu),002:4429: gong du bshad pa'i sbyang bya'i chos de rnams kyis
NK064(ngu),002:4430: sbyong byed kyi lam dang po phyag rgya gcig pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:4431: lam rags pa lha sku la bslab pa'i rnal 'byor
NK064(ngu),002:4432: ni / de yang gzhal yas khang gi dbus su gdan nyi ma'i rdul /
NK064(ngu),002:4434: sa bon a yig gdan steng du babs pa ni bar do'i rnam shes te /
NK064(ngu),002:4435: mngal du khu rdul sems gsum 'dres pas /
NK064(ngu),002:4436: pha ma'i 'du 'phrod kyi 'gyur bas khams lnga nyams
NK064(ngu),002:4437: su myong ba ni rigs so so'i sa bon phyag
NK064(ngu),002:4438: mtshan du gyur pa mtshon pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4440: mngal du lus chags pa'i tshe lus de nyid rlung gis 'phel bar byed /
NK064(ngu),002:4443: bsdus pa de yang sas sra bar byed /
NK064(ngu),002:4444: nam mkhas de thams cad kyi go phye bas phung khams skye mched grub pa de sbyong ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4445: khu rdul sems gsum 'dres pa'i dkar dmar 'od kyi
NK064(ngu),002:4446: gong bu de 'od zer spro bsdu'i lha so so'i
NK064(ngu),002:4447: rigs kyi phyag mtshan so sor sa bon gyis mtshan
NK064(ngu),002:4448: pa las sku yongs su rdzogs par bskyed pa ste
NK064(ngu),002:4449: / de yang 'dir mngal skyes gtso che ba tsam du byas nas bshad kyi /
NK064(ngu),002:4450: gzhan du sgong skyes la sogs pa'i bag chags kyang sbyong bar nus te /
NK064(ngu),002:4451: sgong skyes la sa bon ni dri za'i sems /
NK064(ngu),002:4452: phyag mtshan ni mngal du khu khrag gis dbus su zhugs pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4453: spro bsdus yongs su gyur pa'i gong bu ni sgo ngar gyur pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4454: de bzhin du drod gsher la gdan gyi nyi ma drod /
NK064(ngu),002:4456: sa bon phyag mtshan ni bar do'i rlung sems /
NK064(ngu),002:4457: spro bsdu dang sku yongs su rdzogs pa ni de
NK064(ngu),002:4458: gsum 'dus pa las drod gsher gyi dbus nas lus
NK064(ngu),002:4460: bardzusa skyes la gdan ni skye gnas /
NK064(ngu),002:4461: sa bon phyag mtshan ni bar do'i rlung sems /
NK064(ngu),002:4462: spro bsdu ni gnas lus la sred pa dang len pa'i mthu gsos btab pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4463: sku yongs su rdzogs pa ni lus skad cig gis grub pa mtshon zhing sbyong bar byed do //
NK064(ngu),002:4464: mngon byang lnga'i sgo nas bskyed tshul ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4465: khu ba mtshon byed zla gzugs ni me long ye shes /
NK064(ngu),002:4466: rdul mtshon byed nyi ma ni mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK064(ngu),002:4467: bar srid dkar dmar gyi dbus su zhugs pa mtshon
NK064(ngu),002:4468: byed sa bon phyag mtshan ni sor rtog ye shes
NK064(ngu),002:4469: / khu rdul sems gsum 'dres pa mtshon byed 'od
NK064(ngu),002:4470: zer spro bsdu yongs su gyur pa ni bya grub
NK064(ngu),002:4471: / ye shes / mngal du lus grub pa mtshon
NK064(ngu),002:4472: byed sku yongs su rdzogs pa ni chos dbyings ye
NK064(ngu),002:4473: / ye shes / shes yin te / de ltar
NK064(ngu),002:4474: sangs rgyas kyi nye rgyu'i lam ting nge 'dzin mngon
NK064(ngu),002:4475: par byang chub pa lnga thugs su chud pa las
NK064(ngu),002:4476: ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin 'bras bu'i ngo bor
NK064(ngu),002:4479: zla ba me long ye shes te //
NK064(ngu),002:4480: bdun gyi bdun pa mnyam pa nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:4481: rang lha'i sa bon phyag mtshan ni //
NK064(ngu),002:4482: so sor rtog pa brjod par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:4483: thams cad gcig gyur nan tan nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:4484: rdzogs par chos dbyings dag pa ste //
NK064(ngu),002:4485: rnam pa lnga po bsgom bya zhing //
NK064(ngu),002:4486: mkhas pas cho gar shes par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:4488: de la kha cig na re /
