NK064(ngu),002:4489: de ni lha sku phyag rgya gcig pa ma yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:4490: gnas gsum du sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4492: ye shes sems dpa' dang dgu byung bas so zer na /
NK064(ngu),002:4494: shing gi rtsa ba gcig la yal ga mang du
NK064(ngu),002:4495: yod kyang shing sdong gcig zer ba dang gnad gcig
NK064(ngu),002:4496: pa yin gsungs / de yang dag rdzogs smin gsum dang sbyar na /
NK064(ngu),002:4497: de ltar phyag rgya gcig pa'i lam de bsgoms pas /
NK064(ngu),002:4498: mar ma'i mngal du skyes nas btsa' ba'i bar gyi bag chags de dag par byed /
NK064(ngu),002:4499: yar longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku des gang 'dul gyi
NK064(ngu),002:4500: sprul skur snang nas lhums su zhugs nas bltams pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:4501: bar gyi rigs kyi nus pa gsos 'debs pas 'bras
NK064(ngu),002:4503: bar du lam de bsgoms pas snying rje chen po'i 'phen pas zung 'jug gi lha skur /
NK064(ngu),002:4504: ldang ba'i gzhi 'ding bas lam gong ma'i smin byed du 'gro gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:4505: skyes pa'i rim pa bar pa sbyong ba'i lam phyag rgya spros bcas kyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4507: 'khor lo tshom bu grangs zhal phyag /
NK064(ngu),002:4512: zhal phyag spro ba dang bzhi las /
NK064(ngu),002:4514: zhi ba la dkyil 'khor rgyas pa rigs lnga rigs
NK064(ngu),002:4515: chung gi sems dpa' dang bcas pa yab yum lnga
NK064(ngu),002:4516: bcu'i steng du sems dpa' sems ma bcu drug /
NK064(ngu),002:4519: thub drug dang bcas brgyad cu rtsa gnyis /
NK064(ngu),002:4525: thub drug dang bcas zhe gnyis /
NK064(ngu),002:4526: bsdus pa rigs lnga yab yum bcu dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4527: sgo ba yab yum brgyad de bco brgyad do //
NK064(ngu),002:4528: khro bo la dkyil 'khor rgyas pa khrag 'thung rigs
NK064(ngu),002:4529: lnga yab yum rigs chung dang bcas pa lnga bcu'i
NK064(ngu),002:4530: steng / gnas yul sgo ma dbang phyug ma nyer
NK064(ngu),002:4531: brgyad khro bcu yab yum ya nyi shu bcas bsnan
NK064(ngu),002:4532: pas brgya dang bco brgyad do //
NK064(ngu),002:4533: 'bring po khrag 'thung rigs lnga yab yum de steng gnas yul sogs sngar ltar bgrangs pas don brgyad /
NK064(ngu),002:4534: bsdus pa de dag las khro bcu yab yum ya nyi shu phri bas lnga bcu rtsa brgyad do //
NK064(ngu),002:4535: gnyis pa tshom bu spro ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4536: zhi ba la tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa dang gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:4538: mi bskyod pa yab yum rdo rje'i rigs kyi rigs chung zung bzhi dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4539: sgo ba yab yum brgyad de bco brgyad kyi bdag nyid can ni tshom bu gcig pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4540: dbus su mi bskyod pa dang shar nub tu rnam
NK064(ngu),002:4541: snang dang mtha' yas te rang rang gi rigs chung
NK064(ngu),002:4542: gis bskor ba / khro bcu las steng 'og gi
NK064(ngu),002:4543: khro bo spangs pa'i yab yum zung brgyad pa bsnan
NK064(ngu),002:4544: pa'i zhe drug ni tshom bu gsum pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4545: rigs lnga yab yum rigs chung dang bcas pa la
NK064(ngu),002:4546: khro bcu yab yum ya nyi shu bsnan pa'i bdun
NK064(ngu),002:4547: cu ni tshom bu lnga pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4548: khro bo la rtsa rgyud du tshogs sgrub tsam las ma gsungs na'ang /
NK064(ngu),002:4550: de nas 'khor lo gcig pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:4551: gsum dang lnga ru bsgom par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:4553: zhi ba dang mtshungs par tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4554: gsum ka mtshungs par gnas yul sgo skyong dbang mo dang bcas pa gzhir bzhag nas /
NK064(ngu),002:4555: tshom bu gcig pa'i skabs su dbus su rdo rje
NK064(ngu),002:4556: khrag 'thung yab yum la rdo rje rigs kyi rigs
NK064(ngu),002:4557: chung gi khro bo yab yum bzhis bskor ba dang
NK064(ngu),002:4558: / mtha' bskor du khro bcu yab yum ya nyi shu ste don brgyad ni tshom bu gcig pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4559: tshom bu gsum pa'i skabs su de rnams kyi steng du /
NK064(ngu),002:4560: shar nub tu bud+d+ha dang pad+ma khrag 'thung yab yum
NK064(ngu),002:4561: rigs chung dang bcas bsnan pa'i lha go brgyad ni
NK064(ngu),002:4563: tshom bu lnga pa'i skabs su de'i steng du lho
NK064(ngu),002:4564: byang gnyis su rat+na dang karma khrag 'thung rigs chung
NK064(ngu),002:4565: dang bcas bsnan pa'i brgya dang bco brgyad do //
NK064(ngu),002:4566: gsum pa grangs spro ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4567: snang ba rnam 'byed la bslab pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4568: de la zhi khro gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:4569: zhi ba la'ang tshom bu stong dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4571: bsam las lhun grub la bslab pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4574: yan lag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ldan //
NK064(ngu),002:4575: de nyid yan lag spros dag ste //
NK064(ngu),002:4577: zhes pas yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu tham pa
NK064(ngu),002:4578: rtsa lha yab yum gnyis la ldan par bsgoms pa
NK064(ngu),002:4579: ste / de yang mi bskyod pa la mtshon na
NK064(ngu),002:4580: bdag nyid mi bskyod pa yab yum du gsal ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:4581: yab kyi yan lag lnga la byed pa po dang
NK064(ngu),002:4583: mig rna ba sna lce bzhi'i g.yas kyi cha la nang sems dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4584: g.yon gyi cha la phyi sems bzhi /
NK064(ngu),002:4585: rkang lag gi mthil bzhir sgo ba bzhi rnams dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4586: yum gyi gnas de rnams su sngar gyi yum rnams bsgom /
NK064(ngu),002:4587: yab la lhag por mtshog ma la sogs pa'i gnas drug tu thub pa drug ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4588: de ltar sdom pa'i yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu
NK064(ngu),002:4589: ni rags pa dang phyir gnas pa'i cha nas thabs
NK064(ngu),002:4590: lha zhes bya / de rnams la shes rab kyi
NK064(ngu),002:4591: lha ye shes sems dpa' bzhi bcu thabs lha bzhi
NK064(ngu),002:4592: bcu po re re la sku gsung thugs kyi lha
NK064(ngu),002:4593: gsum gsum ste brgya nyi shu /
NK064(ngu),002:4594: thabs lha dang byin rlabs kyi lha bsdoms pas brgya
NK064(ngu),002:4595: drug cu po re re la yang dbang lha lnga
NK064(ngu),002:4597: kun dril bas chig stong bsgom pas ni tshom bu stong la bslab pa zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4598: gnyis pa nyi khri chig stong la bslab pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4600: de ltar ldan pa'i gtso mchog gis //
NK064(ngu),002:4601: rgyal ba rgyal mchog de bzhin nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:4604: mi bskyod pa la ji ltar bsgom pa bzhin du rgyal ba rigs bzhi /
NK064(ngu),002:4605: rgyal mchog kun tu bzang po dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4607: sgo ba bzhi ste yab yum zung bcu bdun /
NK064(ngu),002:4608: thub drug ste re re la'ang de ltar bsgom pa ni nyi khri bzhi stong la bslab zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4609: gsum pa bsam yas lhun grub la bslab pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4611: de la sogs te bsam mi khyab //
NK064(ngu),002:4613: de ltar mi bskyod pas gtso byas pa'i dbus kyi
NK064(ngu),002:4614: dkyil 'khor la yan lag gi lha ji ltar bsgoms
NK064(ngu),002:4616: shar gyi glo 'bur la rnam snang gis gtso byas
NK064(ngu),002:4617: pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bsgoms pa sogs rigs
NK064(ngu),002:4618: 'dres pas bsam gyis mi khyab par spro ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4620: stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu la bslab pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4621: bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya lnga bcu la bslab pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4622: bsam yas lhun grub la bslab pa dang gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:4625: yan lag bkod pa lnga bcu brgyad //
NK064(ngu),002:4626: cha lnga'i grangs ni nyis brgya dang //
NK064(ngu),002:4627: dgu bcu'i lha rnams yan lag ldan //
NK064(ngu),002:4628: zhes pas gtso bo badz+ra he ru ka'i yan lag lnga la khrag 'thung yab lnga dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4630: yab kyi dbang rten gyi nang rtsar goo r+ai ma brgyad dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4631: phyi rtsar seng ha ma brgyad /
NK064(ngu),002:4632: mthil bzhi la sgo ma bzhi /
NK064(ngu),002:4633: mjing 'jug gi tshig bsnan pa'i sgal tshig nyer brgyad
NK064(ngu),002:4634: la dbang mo nyer brgyad de thabs lha nga brgyad
NK064(ngu),002:4635: / de rnams la ye shes sems dpa' dang sku
NK064(ngu),002:4636: gsung thugs kyi lha rnams re re bsgoms pas nga
NK064(ngu),002:4637: brgyad pa cha lnga la nyis brgya dgu bcu /
NK064(ngu),002:4638: de las shes rab kyi lha nga brgyad phri ba'i byin rlabs dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4639: thabs lha gnyis po re re la dbu rgyan gyi
NK064(ngu),002:4640: lha lnga lnga ste stong gcig brgya drug cu 'byung
NK064(ngu),002:4641: ba nyis brgya dgu bcu la bsnan pas /
NK064(ngu),002:4642: stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu sgom pa ni de'i dkyil 'khor la bslab pa zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4643: gnyis pa bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya lnga bcu la bslab pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4644: khrag 'thung rigs lnga yab yum zung lnga sngar ltar dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4645: gnas yul sgo skyong dbang mo rnams la /
NK064(ngu),002:4646: mgo yi g.yas dang rkang lag gi g.yas kyi mdun rgyab la yab lnga /
NK064(ngu),002:4647: mgo yi g.yon dang rkang lag gi g.yon gyi mdun rgyab la yum lnga bkod de /
NK064(ngu),002:4648: lha re re la stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu bsgom
NK064(ngu),002:4649: pa'i nges pas bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya lnga
NK064(ngu),002:4650: bcu la bslab pa zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4651: gsum pa bsam yas lhun grub la bslab pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4652: sngar zhi ba'i skabs su bshad pas mtshon no //
NK064(ngu),002:4653: bzhi pa zhal phyag spro ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4654: zhi khro gnyis ka la rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4655: zhi ba la rgyas par bshad rgyud rdo rje nas
NK064(ngu),002:4656: thub drug dang yum rnams ma gtogs thams cad zhal
NK064(ngu),002:4658: 'bring po rigs lnga tsam mam gtso bo zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4659: bsdus pa thams cad zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4660: khro bo la gtso bo dbu phyag grangs med pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4661: dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4662: cha mthun gyi rgyud lha mo sgyu d+r+wa nas gnas
NK064(ngu),002:4663: yul gyi ma mo sogs kyang zhal gsum phyag drug
NK064(ngu),002:4665: da lta phyag bzhes su rgyas pa la rigs lnga zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4666: 'bring po gtso bo tsam zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4667: bsdus pa thams cad zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4668: de ltar phyag rgya spros bcas kyi lam de bsgom pas /
NK064(ngu),002:4669: mar 'khor ba'i bag chags gang dag na /
NK064(ngu),002:4670: byis pa btsas pa de nar son nas 'dod pa'i tshor bas gdung ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4671: don du gnyer ba chung ma len pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4672: sgo gsum gyi nus pa rim gyis 'phel ba rang
NK064(ngu),002:4673: rigs kyi bya ba la dbang bsgyur ba rnams kyi
NK064(ngu),002:4675: yar sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku des gdul bya rnams
NK064(ngu),002:4676: byang chub la 'god pa'i rigs kyi nus pa gsol
NK064(ngu),002:4678: bar phyag rgya spros bcas kyi lam de bsgom pas /
NK064(ngu),002:4679: zung 'jug gi lha sku'i rtsal snang gong nas gong
NK064(ngu),002:4680: du 'phel ba'i gzhi 'ding bas lam gong ma'i smin
NK064(ngu),002:4681: byed du 'gro ba yin no gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:4682: lnga pa tshom bu tshogs sgrub kyi lam gyi rnal 'byor la /
NK064(ngu),002:4683: phun sum tshogs pa lngas bsgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba /
NK064(ngu),002:4684: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi'i gzhung bsrang ba /
NK064(ngu),002:4685: 'bras bu rig 'dzin thob pa'i dus bstan pa dang gsum /
NK064(ngu),002:4687: gang du bsgrub pa'i gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4689: bskor khang phyi nang bar ldan pa //
NK064(ngu),002:4690: zhes pas bdag dbang bar chad med pa'i gnas su
NK064(ngu),002:4691: tshogs kyi khang pa steng 'og dang 'khor khang gnyis
NK064(ngu),002:4692: ka rim pa gsum ldan brtsig /
NK064(ngu),002:4693: bar khang du chu tshon sogs kyis tshom bu gang
NK064(ngu),002:4694: bsgom gyi dkyil 'khor bris pa rgyan dang ldan pa'o
NK064(ngu),002:4695: // gnyis pa gang gi tshe sgrub pa'i dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4696: de yang sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i dus ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4698: tshes grangs yar gyi brgyad nas brtsam //
NK064(ngu),002:4699: shin tu skar ma rgyal rnams la //
NK064(ngu),002:4700: byang chub spyod pa cher spyod pa //
NK064(ngu),002:4701: gsang mchog dngos grub myur ba'i phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:4702: gza' skar shis par blang bar bya //
NK064(ngu),002:4705: rigs byed dag gi yan lag las //
NK064(ngu),002:4706: dus rnams shes par bya ba ni //
NK064(ngu),002:4707: bkra shis lha yi nyi ma dang //
NK064(ngu),002:4708: 'byor dang dus tshod bzang ba ni //
NK064(ngu),002:4709: mtshan ma'i rtog pa yin mod kyang //
NK064(ngu),002:4710: brtags na dngos grub mtshan ma 'byung //
NK064(ngu),002:4712: gsum pa gang la brten nas bsgrub pa'i yo byad phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4716: mchod pa rdzas kyi yo byad rnams tshang bar gsog pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4718: gos rgyan bza' btung gsang ba dang //
NK064(ngu),002:4719: sgrub pa'i yo byad lnga rnams dang //
NK064(ngu),002:4720: dkyil 'khor yo byad mchod pa'i rdzas //
NK064(ngu),002:4721: dngos grub rten dang bar chad bzlog /
NK064(ngu),002:4722: yo byad dag pa bsdu bya ste //
NK064(ngu),002:4724: de yang dang po tsho gsum du bcad de /
NK064(ngu),002:4725: cha gcig gi sngon du mchod sbyin bya ba /
NK064(ngu),002:4726: cha gcig mjug tu dga' ston gyi phyir bzhag /
NK064(ngu),002:4727: cha gcig ram yam kham gis sbyangs la tram las
NK064(ngu),002:4728: 'dod yon du byin gyi brlabs nas sgrub pa'i cha
NK064(ngu),002:4731: tsho gsum bcad la byin gyis brlab //
NK064(ngu),002:4733: bzhi pa gang gis sgrub pa'i sgrub pa po phun sum tshogs pa la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu),002:4734: gang gis sgrub pa'i ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4736: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK064(ngu),002:4737: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK064(ngu),002:4739: rnal 'byor mthar ldan shin tu bsten //
NK064(ngu),002:4741: gnyis pa gang dang lhan cig tshogs pa'i 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4742: spyir yon tan drug ldan gyi 'khor te /
NK064(ngu),002:4744: ston pa mchod brtson rtogs pa gsal //
NK064(ngu),002:4745: dam tshig sngags dang phyag rgya rnams //
NK064(ngu),002:4746: ma nyams shes shing yo byad ldan //
NK064(ngu),002:4748: khyad par slob dpon dang dgongs pa mnyam pa'i rdo rje rgyal tshab /
NK064(ngu),002:4749: skad gdangs che zhing las 'grigs la mkhas pa'i karma gdangs can /
NK064(ngu),002:4750: sbyor ba'i sgyu rtsal shes pa'i las bzhi'i gzungs ma /
NK064(ngu),002:4751: mig rnon gyi mi ma yin mthong ldog nus pa'i rdo rje spyan pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4752: drod 'dzin pa'i rdo rje bya rog /
NK064(ngu),002:4753: sgrol ba'i las la mkhas pa'i king ka ra /
NK064(ngu),002:4754: g.yos la mkhas pa'i rdo rje byan po /
NK064(ngu),002:4755: phyi nang gi brda sbyor mkhas pa'i rdul phyag skyes
NK064(ngu),002:4756: bu sogs tshom bur 'brel ba'i 'khor phun sum tshogs
NK064(ngu),002:4758: rgyal tshab rgyal por mtshungs pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:4759: karma gdangs can phrin las ldan //
NK064(ngu),002:4760: ljon lcug sdong reg mtshan rdzogs dang //
NK064(ngu),002:4761: rnal 'byor ming sring brtse gdung ldan //
NK064(ngu),002:4762: tshom bu lnga'am zung gis sgrub //
NK064(ngu),002:4764: lnga pa sgrub pa'i thabs phun su ma tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4766: gnas dang longs spyod ci bde dang //
NK064(ngu),002:4767: ma nyams blo ni rab ldan pas //
NK064(ngu),002:4768: dang por dam nos bzhin du bya //
NK064(ngu),002:4769: le lo sgyid snyoms med pa yis //
NK064(ngu),002:4770: the tshom med par bsgrub byas na //
NK064(ngu),002:4773: gnyis pa bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhis gzhung bsrang ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4774: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK064(ngu),002:4775: bsgrub pa dang ni sgrub chen po //
NK064(ngu),002:4776: zhes pas 'dir bskyed rim gyi skabs yin pas /
NK064(ngu),002:4778: dkyil 'khor gyi lha gnas so sor rnal 'byor pa
NK064(ngu),002:4779: pho mo dang lha yab yum brang sprad de 'dug
NK064(ngu),002:4780: nas so so'i nga rgyal brtan po la sems rtse
NK064(ngu),002:4781: gcig tu gnas nas rim par bshoms dang 'brel bar
NK064(ngu),002:4782: / nub dang po 'go 'dzin gyi tshul du bya ba bsnyen pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4783: ji tsam sgrub pa'i zhag grangs phyed tshun chad nyi bsnyen te /
NK064(ngu),002:4784: de gnyis las 'od zer dkar po'i 'phro 'du bsnol mas snod dag par byed pa bsnyen pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4786: nub tha ma ma gtogs pa'i phyed phan chad 'od
NK064(ngu),002:4787: zer dmar po'i 'phro 'dus dngos grub bskul zhing bsdu
NK064(ngu),002:4788: bas bcud dag par byed pa sgrub pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4789: nub tha mar 'od zer mthing ga tshur bsdus te rgyud dag par byed pa'i sgo nas /
NK064(ngu),002:4790: srod kyi cha lha las dngos grub blangs /
NK064(ngu),002:4791: nam gung gi tshe ta na sgrol ba'i mdzad spyod kyis dgra las dngos grub blangs /
NK064(ngu),002:4792: tho rengs yum dang gnyis med du sbyor ba'i sgo
NK064(ngu),002:4793: nas a li'i mdzad spyod kyis yum gyi mkha' las
NK064(ngu),002:4794: dngos grub len pa sgrub pa chen po ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4795: zla ba gcig la dper mtshon na /
NK064(ngu),002:4797: zla phyed phyed zhal nye bsnyen pa //
NK064(ngu),002:4799: bco lnga mar phyed sgrub pa ste //
NK064(ngu),002:4801: zhag grangs tshang nas rtags byung na //
NK064(ngu),002:4802: dngos grub bzlas blang sgrub chen po //
NK064(ngu),002:4804: gsum pa 'bras bu rig 'dzin 'grub pa'i dus bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4805: de ltar zla ba drug spog chog dang bcas pas rig 'dzin gyi 'bras bu 'grub ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4806: 'di bskyed rim yin pas thun mong gi dngos grub
NK064(ngu),002:4807: las rgya dang ye rgya'i khyad par gyis 'dod pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:4809: gzugs kyi rig 'dzin gang rigs la sbyor ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4810: lam 'dis 'khor ba'i bag chags gang dag na /
NK064(ngu),002:4811: skyes pa'i rim pa gsum pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4812: de nas byis pa de rgan po rnams dang blo
NK064(ngu),002:4813: gros mnyam pas spyad ris dang khe grags la sogs
NK064(ngu),002:4814: pa'i bag chags dag par byed /
NK064(ngu),002:4815: yar sangs rgyas rnams mchod sprin mtha' yas pa'i rol
NK064(ngu),002:4816: mo la dgyes dgur spyod pa'i rigs kyi nus pa
NK064(ngu),002:4817: gsos 'debs pa'i 'bras bu rdzogs par byed /
NK064(ngu),002:4818: bar du tshogs sgrub kyi lam du bsgom pas /
NK064(ngu),002:4819: bde stong gi lha skur 'grub par byed pa'i phyir
NK064(ngu),002:4820: mchog gi dngos grub la myur du sbyor ba'i gzhi
NK064(ngu),002:4821: 'ding bas lam gong ma'i smin byed du 'gro gsungs
NK064(ngu),002:4822: / gnyis pa lam gyi gzhung shing rdzogs rim ltar bshad na /
NK064(ngu),002:4823: stong pa chen po la sogs pa'i lam gyi rnal 'byor lnga las /
NK064(ngu),002:4824: dang po stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4825: de yang lus can rnams 'chi ba'i tshe /
NK064(ngu),002:4826: 'byung ba lnga dang dkar dmar nag gsum rim par
NK064(ngu),002:4827: thim nas rnam par mi rtog pa'i 'od gsal 'char
NK064(ngu),002:4829: 'gro ba ma lus thams cad dag /
NK064(ngu),002:4830: gnas pa'i stobs ni zad pa na //
NK064(ngu),002:4831: 'dus pa lnga yi rim pa yis //
NK064(ngu),002:4832: bag chags snyigs ma rang zad nas //
NK064(ngu),002:4833: 'od gsal stong par snang bas na //
NK064(ngu),002:4834: re dogs med pa nam mkha' bzhin //
NK064(ngu),002:4836: de lam du khyer te de dang rjes su mthun pa'i lam bsgom tshul yang /
NK064(ngu),002:4837: lta ba gtan la 'bebs pa gzhir bzhag ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4838: bsam gtan la tsher ma mi 'byung ba'i gnas su
NK064(ngu),002:4839: lus gnad rnam par snang mdzad kyi chos bdun dang
NK064(ngu),002:4840: ldan pas / rig pa ma bcos pa'i ngang du so mar 'jog pa rig pa spyi blugs dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4841: sngar gyi thos bsam gyi lta ba dran par byas
NK064(ngu),002:4842: nas de'i ngang du 'jog pa mthong ba'i rjes la
NK064(ngu),002:4843: 'jog pa ste / 'jog thabs gnyis po gang rung
NK064(ngu),002:4844: gi rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK064(ngu),002:4845: mnyam par 'jog pa nyin mo'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4846: mtshan mo gnyid 'thug gi 'od gsal 'dzin pa'i man
NK064(ngu),002:4847: ngag gnyis sbrel te nyin mtshan kha sbyor du nyams
NK064(ngu),002:4848: su len pa'i sgo nas nyams lnga mthar phyin par
NK064(ngu),002:4849: bslab pa'o // gnyis pa snying rje sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK064(ngu),002:4850: sngar gyi 'chi kha'i 'od gsal ngos ma zin pa
NK064(ngu),002:4851: las snang gsum 'byung lnga'i bgrod pa go bzlog gi
NK064(ngu),002:4852: tshul du langs te bar do'i yid lus sgyu ma
NK064(ngu),002:4855: bar ma sgyu ma'i lus thob pas //
NK064(ngu),002:4856: ma spangs longs spyod rdzogs par bshad //
NK064(ngu),002:4858: de lam du khyer nas de dang rjes su mthun pa'i lam sgom tshul yang /
NK064(ngu),002:4859: sngar gyi stong chen 'od gsal gyi ngang du sems 'gags pas /
NK064(ngu),002:4864: dkar dmar nag gsum la sogs pa'i stong gzugs kyi
NK064(ngu),002:4865: snang ba shar ba na nyin gyi rnal 'byor sad
NK064(ngu),002:4867: mtshan mo rmi lam gyi snang ba thams cad sgyu
NK064(ngu),002:4868: ma chu zla lta bur mthong ba la dmigs med
NK064(ngu),002:4869: kyi snying rje ma 'gags par rang shar ba la
NK064(ngu),002:4870: goms shing bslab par byed pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4871: gsum pa phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4872: bskyed pa'i rim pa dang po'i bag chags sbyong ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:4873: de dang rjes su mthun pa'i lam ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4874: snang ba ris med la snying rje chen po'i 'phen pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4875: ting nge 'dzin gyis chu dwangs pa la gzugs brnyan
NK064(ngu),002:4876: shar ba ltar zhu bde dang mtshungs ldan du gyur
NK064(ngu),002:4877: pa'i lha sku phyag rgya gcig pa rang shar gyis
NK064(ngu),002:4878: snang ba thams cad la rgyas thebs pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4879: bzhi pa phyag rgya spros bcas kyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4880: skye ba'i rim pa bar ma'i bag chags sbyong ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:4881: de dang mthun pa'i lam ste sngar gyi lha snang
NK064(ngu),002:4882: de las ches cher 'phel ba'i snang ba thams cad
NK064(ngu),002:4883: zung 'jug gi lha gtso 'khor dang tshom bu'i rnam
NK064(ngu),002:4884: par mngon sum du spros te ma 'dres yongs rdzogs
NK064(ngu),002:4885: su 'char ba la goms par byed pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4886: lnga pa tshom bu tshogs sgrub ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4887: skye ba'i rim pa gsum pa'i bag chags sbyong ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:4888: de dang rjes su mthun pa'i lam ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4889: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa gang rung gi sgo
NK064(ngu),002:4890: nas spros bcas bskyed rim dang phyogs mthun du sgrub
NK064(ngu),002:4891: pa'am / spros med rnal 'byor pho mo gtso bo yab yum tshogs pa la brten pa'am /
NK064(ngu),002:4892: shin tu spros med yab mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po dang /
NK064(ngu),002:4893: yum rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong pa nyid kha sbyor du sgrub pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4894: gang ltar yang dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum gyi dbye bas zla ba drug gam /
NK064(ngu),002:4895: lo gcig dang zla ba gnyis /
NK064(ngu),002:4896: lo gcig dang zla ba bzhi rnams kyis nang gi
NK064(ngu),002:4897: mngon byang lnga la brten nas zag med mthong lam
NK064(ngu),002:4898: rnam gnyis gang rung la sbyor ba byed pa ste
NK064(ngu),002:4900: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK064(ngu),002:4901: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK064(ngu),002:4902: dbang bsgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK064(ngu),002:4904: zhar la zag ldog yod med kyi mu bzhi brjod par bya ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4905: de la zag ldog gnyis ka yod pa'i mu ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4906: stong chen snying rje sgyu ma phyag rgya gcig spros te tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor bzhi ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4908: de phyir lam bzhir zag ldog yod //
NK064(ngu),002:4910: zag pa yod la ldog pa med pa'i mu ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4911: sbyor lam tshom bu tshogs sgrub ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4912: spyod pa'i dus grangs nges pa zag med la dngos
NK064(ngu),002:4913: su sbyor ba'i bar chad med lam yin pa'i phyir
NK064(ngu),002:4914: ro // zag pa med la ldog pa yod pa'i mu ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4915: dman lam sngon du song ba'i 'phags pa dgra bcom
NK064(ngu),002:4916: pa sngags kyi tshogs lam la gnas pa lta bu
NK064(ngu),002:4917: ste / de ni rang don yid byed kyi bsam pas ldog par srid pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:4919: ji srid sa brgyad ma thob bar //
NK064(ngu),002:4920: de srid theg pa dman pas 'jig /
NK064(ngu),002:4922: 'o na zag pa zhes pa de gang zhe na /
NK064(ngu),002:4923: spyir mngon pa sogs nas zag pa'i sgo drug sogs bshad kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:4926: gtso bo ni kun nas nyon mongs pa dang bcas
NK064(ngu),002:4927: pa'i las kyis khams gsum du zag cing 'pho ba
NK064(ngu),002:4929: de dag 'jig rten pa la yod pa ni 'dzin pa'i phyir zag par 'gyur la /
NK064(ngu),002:4932: lus rang dbang med par len pa skye gnas kyi zag pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4933: khams bde mi bde rang dbang med par myong ba khams kyi zag pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4934: rang dbang med par lus 'dor ba lus kyi zag pa dang gsum mo //
NK064(ngu),002:4935: gsum pa lam gyur gyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4936: zag ldog gnyis ka med pa'i lam mthong sgom mthar lam gsum gyis bsdus pa rig 'dzin bzhi ste /
NK064(ngu),002:4937: de yang mthong lam pa la blo'i nus stobs che
NK064(ngu),002:4938: chung gis 'byung ba snyigs ma'i lus ye shes kyi
NK064(ngu),002:4939: mes sbyong bar ma nus pa rnam smin rig 'dzin
NK064(ngu),002:4940: dang / sbyong bar nus pas skye 'jig med pa
NK064(ngu),002:4941: dwangs ma'i lus su gyur pa lam mchog yongs su
NK064(ngu),002:4942: rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang gnyis te /
NK064(ngu),002:4944: nus pa thob dang ma thob pa'i //
NK064(ngu),002:4945: mthong lam gnyis su gyur pa yin //
NK064(ngu),002:4947: de la rnam smin rig 'dzin ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4948: lus rnam smin sha khrag gi phung po dang ma bral ba /
NK064(ngu),002:4949: yid 'od gsal gyi lha skur smin pa /
NK064(ngu),002:4950: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du lus rgya dang bral
NK064(ngu),002:4951: ma thag phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la sbyor
NK064(ngu),002:4952: nges pa ste / chos gsum dang ldan pa yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:4954: yid kyis lha yi gzugs bzung bzhin //
NK064(ngu),002:4955: lus kyi rgya mdud grol gyur na //
NK064(ngu),002:4956: phyag rgya'i sku nyid gsal gyur pas //
NK064(ngu),002:4957: rnam par smin zhes de la brjod //
NK064(ngu),002:4960: bdag don du bkod pa dkyil 'khor gyi bya ba la sogs pas tshogs gnyis rdzogs par byed cing /
NK064(ngu),002:4961: phrin las bzhi'i sgo nas gzhan don rdzogs par byed /
NK064(ngu),002:4962: zag med lha'i spyan rnam par dag pa la sogs pa'i yon tan dang ldan la /
NK064(ngu),002:4963: gling bzhi pa'i 'jig rten tsam du sku dngos kyi 'gro don cing /
NK064(ngu),002:4964: sprul gzugs ston tshul tshe dbang dang cha 'dra ba tsam mo //
NK064(ngu),002:4966: rnam smin gyi lus dwangs ma'i lus su bsgyur ma
NK064(ngu),002:4967: nus pas mthong lam du ci'i phyir 'gyur zhe na
NK064(ngu),002:4968: / skyon med de byang chub sems dpa' dbang rtul
NK064(ngu),002:4969: gyi zag bcas kyi lus sa bdun pa'i bar du
NK064(ngu),002:4970: 'gro ba mdo las bshad pa dang gnad gcig go
NK064(ngu),002:4971: / gsungs / mthong lam tshe dbang rig 'dzin ni
NK064(ngu),002:4972: lus sems gnyis ka 'od gsal gyi lha skur smin
NK064(ngu),002:4973: cing phra yang la sogs pa'i 'ja' lus kyi yon
NK064(ngu),002:4974: tan khyad par can dang ldan pa'i rdo rje'i lus
NK064(ngu),002:4976: don mthong 'jug pa mthar phyin pa'i //
NK064(ngu),002:4977: tshogs spyod sgrub pa'i dngos grub kyis //
NK064(ngu),002:4978: lus khams skye gnas zag pa zad //
NK064(ngu),002:4979: rdo rje'i lus 'gyur tshe yi rigs //
NK064(ngu),002:4981: de yang spyir tshe dbang la /
NK064(ngu),002:4982: smin gyi bcud len la brten pa'i /
NK064(ngu),002:4983: thig le dbab bzung la brten pa'i /
NK064(ngu),002:4984: sgrol ma rlung gi 'khor lo la brten pa'i /
NK064(ngu),002:4985: lam mchog yongs su rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang dang bzhi las /
NK064(ngu),002:4987: sa dang po'i rtogs pa khyad par can mthar phyin pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4989: bdag don du kun 'gro'i dri ma sbyong zhing /
NK064(ngu),002:4990: gzhan don du cho 'phrul bzhi dang phrin las bzhi sogs kyis 'gro don mdzad cing cha lugs kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:4991: mi dang lha dang tshangs pa yi //
NK064(ngu),002:4992: skye ba rnam dag 'dzin mod kyang //
NK064(ngu),002:4993: khyad par sa la gnas gyur yin //
NK064(ngu),002:4995: mngon shes kyi yul don kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:4996: dbang shes nyi shu rtsa lngas gling bzhi bye ba phrag brgyar dus gcig tu 'gro don mdzad pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:4997: sgom lam phyag chen rig 'dzin ni /
NK064(ngu),002:4998: ye shes sgyu ma'i sku can ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5000: rang sems phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK064(ngu),002:5001: bsgom pas mngon du gyur pa'i lha //
NK064(ngu),002:5002: thun mong mchog gi mtshan dper ldan //
NK064(ngu),002:5003: longs spyod gnyis pa phyag rgya'i rigs //
NK064(ngu),002:5005: ye shes sku yi cha lugs can //
NK064(ngu),002:5006: 'byung ba rdo rje'i lus las grol //
NK064(ngu),002:5008: de la yang snga ma las /
NK064(ngu),002:5009: rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NK064(ngu),002:5013: sa gnyis pa nas lnga pa'i bar bzhi la rdo rje'i rig pa 'dzin pa zhes bya ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5014: rtogs pa ye shes rdo rjes rang sa'i sgrib pa 'joms pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:5015: sa drug par sher phyin la gtso bor spyod cing chos 'khor bskor ba'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5016: sa bdun pa'ang thabs la mkhas pas 'khor lo ltar gyur pas /
NK064(ngu),002:5017: de gnyis la 'khor lo'i rig 'dzin zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5018: sa brgyad par mi rtog pa'i ye shes la dbang bsgyur bas rin po che'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5019: dgu par chags pa med pas sbyong zhing 'gro don mdzad pas pad+ma'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5020: bcu par phrin las phun sum tshogs pas sems can
NK064(ngu),002:5021: gyi don dpag med mdzad pa'i phyir ral gri'i rig
NK064(ngu),002:5022: 'dzin zhes bya'o // cha byad kyang zung 'jug gi
NK064(ngu),002:5023: lha'i sku mtshan dpe rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid can bdag
NK064(ngu),002:5024: don du lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma sbyong zhing
NK064(ngu),002:5025: 'dzin zhes bya'o // / gzhan don du rngon pa
NK064(ngu),002:5026: dang smad 'tshong ma la sogs pa gang 'dul gyi
NK064(ngu),002:5027: sprul gzugs su ston par byed pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5029: mnyam bzhag ngang las ma g.yos bzhin //
NK064(ngu),002:5031: rngon dang smad 'tshong la sogs pa //
NK064(ngu),002:5032: sprul pa'i lus kyis 'dul bar byed //
NK064(ngu),002:5034: mngon shes kyi yul don kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:5035: dbang shes nyi shu rtsa lnga'i yon tan dang ldan pa tshe dbang dang 'dra na'ang /
NK064(ngu),002:5036: 'dir gsal brtan gyis khyad par du byas shing /
NK064(ngu),002:5037: longs sku'i zhing dang mnyam pa'i 'gro don mdzad do //
NK064(ngu),002:5038: de ltar sa bcu pa'i rnam grol lam tshun chad
NK064(ngu),002:5039: sgom lam phyag chen du bsdus nas sa bcu pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:5040: khyad par gyi lam mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin
NK064(ngu),002:5041: ni / sku lnga lhun grub rdo rje 'chang gi
NK064(ngu),002:5042: cha lugs 'dzin pa drug pa'i rgyal tshab mdzad pa
NK064(ngu),002:5043: po gsang ba'i bdag po bzhin no //
NK064(ngu),002:5045: bdag don du rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin
NK064(ngu),002:5046: te nang gi mngon byang gis shes sgrib phra ba
NK064(ngu),002:5047: snang gsum gyi dri ma sbyong zhing /
NK064(ngu),002:5048: gzhan don rjes thob la sangs rgyas dang cha 'dra ba'i 'gro don mdzad /
NK064(ngu),002:5049: sprul gzugs kyang mdzad pa bcu gnyis sogs mchog gi sprul sku dang phyogs mthun du ston /
NK064(ngu),002:5050: mngon shes kyang yul don la ji snyed mkhyen pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:5051: yul rgyal ba nyid dang cha 'dra ste nam mkhas
NK064(ngu),002:5052: khyab tshad kyi don yang ci rigs pa mdzad pa
NK064(ngu),002:5054: de ltar dag pa'i ye shes nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:5055: sku lnga lhun grub rdo rje 'dzin //
NK064(ngu),002:5056: lhun mnyam ngang las mi g.yo zhing //
NK064(ngu),002:5057: mi rtog nyid du bzhugs pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5058: bag la nyal ba 'joms byed cing //
NK064(ngu),002:5059: skad cig nyid las rig 'dzin thob //
NK064(ngu),002:5061: zhar byung rgyu'i theg pa'i 'phags pa rnams dang dgongs
NK064(ngu),002:5062: pa mnyam tshul dang sa'i mu tshod mthun tshul bshad
NK064(ngu),002:5063: de / rnam smin rig 'dzin dang rgyu'i theg pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:5064: mthong lam rab dga' la gnas pa'i sems dpa' gnyis
NK064(ngu),002:5066: de las gzhan pa tshe dbang sogs ni rgyu'i theg pa'i sa dang po dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5068: bcu pa tsam du skal ba mnyam pa ste lam gyi mu tshod mtshungs mod /
NK064(ngu),002:5069: 'on kyang dgongs pa ni rgyu'i theg pa'i sgom lam sa brgyad pa dang tshe dbang /
NK064(ngu),002:5071: mi slob pa kun tu 'od dang lhun grub rig 'dzin rnams mnyam par bzhed pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:5072: de ltar yang lam chung las /
NK064(ngu),002:5073: de yang dang po dang po dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5074: skal mnyam gnyis pa'i rigs mchog ste //
NK064(ngu),002:5075: brgyad pa'i sems dpar skal ba mnyam //
NK064(ngu),002:5076: gsum pa bcu dang skal mnyam mod //
NK064(ngu),002:5077: dgongs spyod rgya mtshos khyad par 'phags //
NK064(ngu),002:5079: bsam gtan mig sgron gyi rang 'grel las /
NK064(ngu),002:5080: kun tu 'od bsti gnas kyi sa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5081: de ni 'dir lhun grub rig 'dzin dngos so //
NK064(ngu),002:5083: da ni thod rgal 'byung mi 'byung gi sa mtshams 'chad de /
NK064(ngu),002:5084: rnam smin nas thod rgal du bgrod pa mi srid de /
NK064(ngu),002:5085: thod rgal 'byung ba'i chos gsum ma tshang ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:5086: gang ma tshang na lam gzhan bar nas bor du med pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:5087: rang gi dngos 'bras rgya chen du nges pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:5089: rgya mig rgya sa ji bzhin du //
NK064(ngu),002:5090: phyag rgya thob la ma rig pa //
NK064(ngu),002:5091: gzugs rdzogs stobs chen de kho na //
NK064(ngu),002:5093: gzhan du cig car ba'i rigs ma yin pa'i lam
NK064(ngu),002:5094: pa blo che ba 'ga' zhig phyag rgya gcig spros
NK064(ngu),002:5096: tshe dbang ni lhun grub rig 'dzin /
NK064(ngu),002:5097: tshe dbang dang rgya chen gnyis nas rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK064(ngu),002:5098: rgyas kyi sar lam gzhan bar nas bor la thod
NK064(ngu),002:5099: rgal du sbyor ba srid pa yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:5100: de dag la ngang gis blo che ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5101: zung 'jug gi lam bsgom pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5102: lam gzhan bar nas bor du yod pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5103: thod rgal 'byung ba'i chos gsum tshang ba'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu),002:5104: de ltar na tshogs sgrub nas thod rgal 'byung ngam snyam na mi 'byung ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5106: lam mchog dbye sa gcig yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:5107: zhes pa zag med kyi lam gyi dbye sa dang
NK064(ngu),002:5108: 'du sa mthong lam yin par gsungs pas lam gzhan
NK064(ngu),002:5109: bar nas bor du med pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu),002:5111: gsum pa gang du mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i rgyud ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5112: sgyu 'phrul bye brag bstan pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:5114: lhun grub ji bzhin mngon byas pa'ang //
NK064(ngu),002:5115: btags pa tsam ste gnyis pa med //
NK064(ngu),002:5116: de phyir de la de brjod do //
NK064(ngu),002:5118: de la sbyang gzhi rgyu rgyud bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:5119: snying po gdod ma nas rang la rang chas su
NK064(ngu),002:5120: bzhugs pa ste / 'dam gyi dbus na bzhugs pa'i nor bu rin po che bzhin no //
NK064(ngu),002:5122: med snang glo bur gyi dri ma phra zhing phra ba dang bcas pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5123: nor bu de sgrib par byed pa'i 'dam rdzab bzhin no //
NK064(ngu),002:5125: rim pa gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i lam ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5126: 'khrud byed kyi chu dang 'dag rdzas bzhin no //
NK064(ngu),002:5128: de ltar lam gyi dri ma sbyangs pa las gzhi
NK064(ngu),002:5129: la ji ltar yod pa'i yon tan mngon du gyur
NK064(ngu),002:5131: 'dam rdzab las grol ba'i yid bzhin gyi nor bu
NK064(ngu),002:5132: rin po che las 'dod rgu'i char 'bebs pa bzhin
NK064(ngu),002:5134: ci'i phyir 'bras bu'i rgyud du 'gyur zhe na //
NK064(ngu),002:5136: grub pa mthar phyin 'bras bur brjod /
NK064(ngu),002:5137: ces pas bla na med pa mchog gi 'bras bu
NK064(ngu),002:5138: mthar thug pa don du gnyer ba rnams bsam pa
NK064(ngu),002:5139: yongs su rdzogs pas na 'bras bu dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5140: nam yang rgyun mi chad pas na rgyud do //
NK064(ngu),002:5142: 'bras bu'i ngo bo sku gsung thugs //
NK064(ngu),002:5143: yon tan phrin las rnam pa lnga //
NK064(ngu),002:5144: de yang skabs kyi lnga lnga ste //
NK064(ngu),002:5145: zhes pas sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las re
NK064(ngu),002:5146: re la'ang lnga lngar dbye bas 'bras chos nyi shu
NK064(ngu),002:5155: chos sku skye med don gyi gsung /
NK064(ngu),002:5156: longs sku dgongs pa brda yi gsung //
NK064(ngu),002:5157: sprul sku tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyi gsung //
NK064(ngu),002:5158: mngon byang rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung /
NK064(ngu),002:5159: dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung dang lnga'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5161: chos sku'i thugs chos dbyings ye shes /
NK064(ngu),002:5162: longs sku'i thugs mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK064(ngu),002:5163: sprul sku'i thugs bya grub ye shes /
NK064(ngu),002:5164: mngon byang gi thugs me long ye shes /
NK064(ngu),002:5165: rdo rje sku'i thugs sor rtog ye shes so //
NK064(ngu),002:5167: rnam par dag pa'i zhing khams /
NK064(ngu),002:5168: rgya tshad dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK064(ngu),002:5171: dgyes rgur spyod pa'i longs spyod dang lnga'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5177: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las dang lnga'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5181: mdzad pa phrin las gsum du 'du ba yin pas sku ni gsum mam lnga ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5183: dbyings spros bral nam mkha' lta bu'i klong na /
NK064(ngu),002:5184: thugs rje dang ye shes rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag nyid can no //
NK064(ngu),002:5186: de las shar ba'i thugs rje ye shes kyi sku'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5188: so so'i mos pa dang 'tshams par gong gi sku
NK064(ngu),002:5189: de gnyis kyi gzugs brnyan 'gro ba'i sems gtsang ma'i
NK064(ngu),002:5190: me long la shar ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5192: ji ltar bee d+aur sa gzhi gtsang ma la //
NK064(ngu),002:5193: lha dbang lus kyi gzugs brnyan snang ba ltar //
NK064(ngu),002:5194: de bzhin 'gro sems sa gzhi gtsang ma las //
NK064(ngu),002:5195: thub pa'i dbang po'i sku yi gzugs brnyan 'char //
NK064(ngu),002:5196: zhes sogs sku gsum snang cha ma 'dres pa'i cha nas mngon byang dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5197: ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa'i cha nas rdo rje'i sku ste gnyis po bsnan pas sku lnga'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5198: skabs 'dir zur pa rnams chos longs sprul gsum sku mtshan nyid pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5199: gzhan gnyis rnam pa'i ldog cha dang ngo bo dbyer
NK064(ngu),002:5200: mi phyed pa'i cha nas bzhag pa'i sku btags pa
NK064(ngu),002:5201: yin gsungs / kun mkhyen klong chen pas ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5202: chos sku mngon byang rdo rje'i sku gsum po sangs
NK064(ngu),002:5203: rgyas rang snang gi sku yin pas mtshan nyid pa
NK064(ngu),002:5204: yin la / longs sprul gnyis gdul bya'i snang bas
NK064(ngu),002:5205: bsdus pa'i sku btags pa ba'o gsungs pa 'thad par
NK064(ngu),002:5206: yin la / mngon gsungs / gnyis pa ye shes ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5207: de ltar sku lnga mngon du byas pa'i tshe /
NK064(ngu),002:5208: tshogs brgyad gnas su dag pa'i ye shes lnga ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5209: kun gzhi 'byed pa med pa'i cha nas de nyid
NK064(ngu),002:5210: gnas su dag pa cir yang mi dmigs pa spros
NK064(ngu),002:5211: pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba chos dbyings ye
NK064(ngu),002:5212: shes dang / kun gzhi'i rnam shes gsal la mi
NK064(ngu),002:5213: rtog pa'i cha nas de nyid gnas su dag pa
NK064(ngu),002:5214: me long ngos gnyis pa ltar rang bzhin gyis chos
NK064(ngu),002:5215: thams cad gsal la spu ris mi 'byed pa me
NK064(ngu),002:5216: long lta bu'i ye shes dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5217: nyon yid kyis phyi nang gi chos rnams la blang
NK064(ngu),002:5218: dor 'byed pa'i cha nas de nyid gnas su dag
NK064(ngu),002:5219: pa 'khor 'das bzang ngan med pa mnyam pa nyid
NK064(ngu),002:5220: du gzigs pas srid zhi'i mtha' la mi gnas pas
NK064(ngu),002:5222: rnam shes tshogs drug 'gags ma thag par yid kyi
NK064(ngu),002:5223: dpyod pa med par rtog pa'i cha nas de nyid
NK064(ngu),002:5224: gnas su dag pa chos can ma lus mngon sum
NK064(ngu),002:5225: du ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su sa ler gzigs pa
NK064(ngu),002:5226: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5227: sgo lnga'i rnam shes kyi bya ba thams cad sgrub
NK064(ngu),002:5228: pa'i cha nas de nyid gnas su dag pa 'gro
NK064(ngu),002:5229: don mdzad pa la thogs pa med pa'i phrin las
NK064(ngu),002:5230: 'jug pa bya grub ye shes te lnga'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5231: de dag gnyis su bsdu tshul ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5232: zur pa rnams chos dbyings ye shes ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5233: phyi ma bzhi po rten brten pa'i cha nas ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes su bzhed /
NK064(ngu),002:5235: chos dbyings ye shes dang mnyam nyid ye shes gnyis
NK064(ngu),002:5236: gnas lugs gzigs pa'i cha nas ji lta ba dang
NK064(ngu),002:5239: des 'gro don mdzad pa'i cha nas ji snyed pa'i ye shes so //
NK064(ngu),002:5240: zhes gsungs te ji skad bshad kyang khyad par ma mchis 'dra gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:5241: gsum pa mdzad pa phrin las ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5242: de ltar na nyon sgrib dang shes sgrib gnyis kyis
NK064(ngu),002:5243: bsdus pa'i med snang glo bur gyi sgrib gnyis bag
NK064(ngu),002:5244: chags snang gsum gyi dri ma dang bcas pa mtha'
NK064(ngu),002:5245: dag spangs shing / ji lta ba dang ji snyed
NK064(ngu),002:5246: mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis shes bya thams cad mngon
NK064(ngu),002:5247: sum du gzigs pa'i sgo nas spang rtogs kyi yon
NK064(ngu),002:5249: de'i mthu las gdul bya so so'i skal pa dang 'tshams par zhi ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5252: drag po la sogs te gang la gang gis ji
NK064(ngu),002:5253: ltar 'dul ba'i phrin las kyi sgo mtha' yas pa
NK064(ngu),002:5254: dus las yol ba med cing 'bad rtsol med par
NK064(ngu),002:5256: nam mkha' ji srid pa de srid du rgya che rgyun mi chad par 'byung ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5258: de bzhin 'khor ba ji srid du //
NK064(ngu),002:5259: las ni rgyun mi chad par 'dod //
NK064(ngu),002:5261: gnyis la lam gyi cha rkyen rgyud kyi dngos po bcu bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5262: lta spyod dkyil 'khor dbang dam tshig /
NK064(ngu),002:5263: mchod sngags ting 'dzin phrin sgrub kyi //
NK064(ngu),002:5264: gsang sngags rgyud kyi dbye ba bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5266: de kho na nyid lta ba /
NK064(ngu),002:5272: don du gnyer ba sgrub pa /
NK064(ngu),002:5274: gnas su stob pa mchod pa /
NK064(ngu),002:5276: dang po lta ba la'ang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5279: thabs kyi lta spyod chen por ni //
NK064(ngu),002:5280: bla med theg pa las 'phags pa //
NK064(ngu),002:5281: don dam du ni dkor bdun la //
NK064(ngu),002:5282: kun rdzob tu ni mnyam rdzogs so //
NK064(ngu),002:5283: yang dag skyes mchog dam pa yis //
NK064(ngu),002:5284: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med par //
NK064(ngu),002:5285: yang dag nyid du rab tu rtogs //
NK064(ngu),002:5286: zhes pas spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba
NK064(ngu),002:5287: gang du yang ma rig pa'i cha nas dbu ma
NK064(ngu),002:5288: pa dang / chos thams cad sems kyi rol rtsal
NK064(ngu),002:5289: tsam du 'du ba'i cha nas sems tsam pa dang
NK064(ngu),002:5290: pa dang / phyogs mtshungs kyang / sngags kyi lta ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5291: de dag las kyang khyad par du 'phags pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5292: gdod ma nas dbyings ye shes sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las te /
NK064(ngu),002:5293: dkor bdun ngo bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub pa lhag pa don dam bden pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5294: de nyid kyi rtsal snang snod bcud sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang bas /
NK064(ngu),002:5295: 'khor 'das bzang ngan med par mnyam pa nyid du
NK064(ngu),002:5296: rdzogs pa ni lhag pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa
NK064(ngu),002:5297: ste / de gnyis kyang phyogs su lhung ba ma
NK064(ngu),002:5298: yin par lhag pa bden gnyis zung 'jug ngo bo
NK064(ngu),002:5299: dbyer mi phyed par mnyam pa nyid du gnas shing
NK064(ngu),002:5300: ste / / der 'dzin gyi bsam brjod las kyang
NK064(ngu),002:5301: yang dag par 'das pas na tha snyad tsam du
NK064(ngu),002:5302: lhag pa bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral
NK064(ngu),002:5303: ba zhes ming du btags te /
NK064(ngu),002:5305: rgyal 'gros ma mdzad ma bcos par //
NK064(ngu),002:5306: rang bzhin ngang gis dbyer med par //
NK064(ngu),002:5307: de ming zhen pa dgrol phyir las //
NK064(ngu),002:5308: tha snyad gnyis pa bsam brjod 'das //
NK064(ngu),002:5310: lhag pa zhes pa'i sgra yang /
NK064(ngu),002:5311: khyad par du 'phags pa'i don lhag par ston pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5312: phar phyin theg pa nas don dam bden ngor 'khor
NK064(ngu),002:5313: 'das mnyam pa nyid du bzhed pa tsam phyogs mthun
NK064(ngu),002:5315: kun rdzob tu'ang chos thams cad la mi gnyis pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:5316: bsam brjod dang bral bas na rgyu'i theg pa las
NK064(ngu),002:5317: khyad par 'phags pa'i phyir de skad du brjod pa
NK064(ngu),002:5319: bla med theg pa'i nang nas ni //
NK064(ngu),002:5320: don dam du ni dbyer med la //
NK064(ngu),002:5321: kun rdzob tu ni thams cad la //
NK064(ngu),002:5322: dag dang ma dag gnyis kar 'dzin //
NK064(ngu),002:5323: thabs kyi theg pa chen por ni //
NK064(ngu),002:5324: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK064(ngu),002:5325: kun rdzoob tu'ang dbyer med de //
NK064(ngu),002:5326: lta ba mtho dman de tsam mo //
NK064(ngu),002:5329: drish+ta'i sgra las dri shi lta ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5330: zhes pas byings don gyis bsgrubs pas lta ba zhes
NK064(ngu),002:5331: bya ba la 'jug ste gnas lugs kyi don la
NK064(ngu),002:5332: de dang rjes su mthun pa'i shes rab kyi mig
NK064(ngu),002:5335: dbang po yang rab la gtan tshigs kyis rtogs par bya ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5336: rgyal po dzahs lam rnam bkod du /
NK064(ngu),002:5337: de ltar tshul gsum brjod pa yis //
NK064(ngu),002:5338: mthong ba gang yin shes rab spyan //
NK064(ngu),002:5339: de yang mngon sum gzhan spangs te //
NK064(ngu),002:5340: sgra tshig rten 'brel zhen tsam min //
NK064(ngu),002:5341: yul min rang rig bden dbyer med //
NK064(ngu),002:5342: blo'i gting go ba mngon sum yul //
NK064(ngu),002:5344: dbang po 'bring la rang bzhin dang 'bras bu'i rtags la brten nas rtog par bya ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5346: dang po rang gi rig pa yis //
NK064(ngu),002:5348: phyogs dang kha dog la sogs kyis //
NK064(ngu),002:5349: mtshon nas ji bzhin nyid rtogs byed //
NK064(ngu),002:5351: 'di ltar ma dag pa'i 'jig rten 'di yang rang
NK064(ngu),002:5352: gi rig pa ye shes lnga'i cho 'phrul yin te
NK064(ngu),002:5353: / de'i rtags su sus kyang ma byas par yul lnga dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5355: kha dog lnga la sogs pa rang bzhin gyis yod pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5356: bshags rgyud kyi rigs lnga'i dam tshig gi le'u las /
NK064(ngu),002:5357: kha dog lnga dang yul lnga la sogs pa //
NK064(ngu),002:5358: ye nas rigs lnga'i rang bzhin yin pa la //
NK064(ngu),002:5361: sems nyid la 'bras bu sku dang ye shes rang
NK064(ngu),002:5362: chas su bzhugs pa'i mtshon don chu tshon sogs kyis
NK064(ngu),002:5364: gcig shos mthar phyin ye shes kyi //
NK064(ngu),002:5365: dkyil 'khor rten dang brten can ltar //
NK064(ngu),002:5367: dbang rtul la brgyud de rtogs pa nye ring gnyis las nye ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5369: bsgoms pa'i lam du bstan par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5370: rim par skye ba the tshom med //
NK064(ngu),002:5372: de ltar thos pa'i shes rab kyis mi go ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:5373: rigs la rtsa mdud grol ba'i dmigs pa phra mo
NK064(ngu),002:5374: zhig bstan pas / nang gi rtsa mdud grol nas
NK064(ngu),002:5375: gnas lugs rtogs pa zhig yod de dper na sngon
NK064(ngu),002:5376: klu sgrub kyi slob ma grub thob sh+ri g+ai pa
NK064(ngu),002:5377: zhig bstan pas / lta bu ste / klu sgrub kyis slob ma rnams la chos bshad pa'i dus /
NK064(ngu),002:5378: sh+ri g+ai pa zhes pa des tshig gcig kyang nyin
NK064(ngu),002:5379: mang po'i bar mi zin cing don ma go bas
NK064(ngu),002:5380: / klu sgrub kyis mgo la rwa skyes pa zhig sgom zhes gsungs pas /
NK064(ngu),002:5381: slob dpon gyis dud 'gro yin 'dug gsungs pa yin
NK064(ngu),002:5382: kyang kho rang gi sems la de sgom sla bar
NK064(ngu),002:5383: go ste sgom pas ji zhig na rwa skyes pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:5384: snang bas brag phug tu rwa thogs te lang ma
NK064(ngu),002:5385: shes pa slob dpon gyis mkhyen te dmigs pa zab
NK064(ngu),002:5386: pa zhig go dgongs te rtsa mdud dgrol ba'i dmigs
NK064(ngu),002:5387: pa zhig bstan pas grol ba thob pa sogs ni
NK064(ngu),002:5389: ring ba ni rnam bkod las /
NK064(ngu),002:5390: de min rgyu tsam gsog byed pa //
NK064(ngu),002:5391: rgyud las 'di skad gsungs pa ste //
NK064(ngu),002:5392: chos nyid rten cing 'brel bris na //
NK064(ngu),002:5393: chos nyid don dam rtogs 'gyur te //
NK064(ngu),002:5395: re zhig rtogs pa'i skal pa med pa dag la
NK064(ngu),002:5396: sgrib sbyong gi phyir bde bar gshegs pa'i mchod rten
NK064(ngu),002:5397: la bskor ba byed pa dang mnyam du rten 'brel
NK064(ngu),002:5398: snying po bzlas shing bsags sbyangs la 'bad pas rtogs
NK064(ngu),002:5400: dper na rgyal ba tsong kha pa'i bla ma don grub rin chen lta bu ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5401: de ni thugs rab shin tu bul bas nyin mtshan
NK064(ngu),002:5402: ngal med kyis ring bsrel can gyi mchod rten la
NK064(ngu),002:5403: rten 'brel snying po bzlas shing bskor ba mdzad pas
NK064(ngu),002:5404: ji zhig na zhabs thams cad rmar song /
NK064(ngu),002:5405: da dung 'bad pas zhabs kyi rma yang rang shugs
NK064(ngu),002:5406: kyi dwangs shing shes rab dang go don la thogs
NK064(ngu),002:5407: pa med par byung bar grags pa lta bu'o gsungs
NK064(ngu),002:5408: / gnyis pa spyod pa la'ang gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:5412: rjes mthun spyod pa gzhung bzhin spyod //
NK064(ngu),002:5413: ces thabs shes khyad par can gyis zin pa'i sgo nas sogs te /
NK064(ngu),002:5414: de la spyir spyod pa la mnyam bzhag dang rjes thob kyi spyod pa gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:5415: mnyam bzhag gi spyod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5416: sngar bshad pa'i lam lnga dang rig 'dzin bzhi'i gnas
NK064(ngu),002:5417: skabs kyi so so'i ting nge 'dzin la rtse gcig
NK064(ngu),002:5418: tu spyod par byed pa de yin cing /
NK064(ngu),002:5419: 'dir rjes thob gtso che ba'i dbang du byas pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5420: rjes mthun spyod pa gzhung bzhin spyad //
NK064(ngu),002:5423: lta ba bdag med pas zin pa'i shes rab dang
NK064(ngu),002:5424: thabs snying rje chen po zung du 'jug pa'i sgo
NK064(ngu),002:5425: nas spyod pas lus ngag yid gsum yongs su dag
NK064(ngu),002:5430: ta na dang ga na la sogs te /
NK064(ngu),002:5431: de yang dus tshod dang 'brel bar tshul bzhin spyod pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5433: las dang po pa'i dus su bag dang ldan pa
NK064(ngu),002:5434: gzab pa lhur len pa dge sbyong gzhon nu'i spyod
NK064(ngu),002:5437: brtan pa ma thob bar du ni //
NK064(ngu),002:5438: kha na ma tho rdul med cing //
NK064(ngu),002:5439: sdom pa gsum la gnas par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5441: de nas cung zad goms te mnyam rjes bsre bar nus pa na /
NK064(ngu),002:5442: rtogs pa rkyen thub tu byed pa smyon pa brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5443: brtan pa cher thob nas rtogs pa la bri gang
NK064(ngu),002:5444: med pas na gzhan phan kho na la bslab pa
NK064(ngu),002:5445: rgyal po sa 'dzin gyi spyod pa lta bu ste
NK064(ngu),002:5447: bye brag tu thabs lam brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5448: grol lam bag yod kyi spyod pa gnyis su bshad cing /
NK064(ngu),002:5450: dang po lta ba gtan la 'bebs pa'i dus su dad brtson gyi spyod pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5451: spyir dad pa la dang ba'i dad pa /
NK064(ngu),002:5453: yid ches kyi dad pa dang gsum mo //
NK064(ngu),002:5454: de lta bu'i dad pas thos bsam la zhugs nas
NK064(ngu),002:5455: thang lhod med pa'i brtson 'grus kyis mthar phyin par
NK064(ngu),002:5456: spyod pa'o // shes rab dang mthun pa'i spyod pa
NK064(ngu),002:5457: stong pa chen po ste mnyam bzhag tu stong pa
NK064(ngu),002:5458: chen po bsgom zhing rjes thob tu'ang de'i ngang bskyangs
NK064(ngu),002:5459: spyod pa'o // te spyod pa'o // thabs dang mthun
NK064(ngu),002:5460: pa snying rje sgyu ma ste mnyam bzhag tu snying
NK064(ngu),002:5461: rje sgyu ma sgom zhing rjes thob tu'ang spyod yul
NK064(ngu),002:5462: thams cad sgyu mar blta ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5463: phyogs gcig pa ni phyag rgya gcig pa ste mnyam
NK064(ngu),002:5464: bzhag tu zung 'jug phyag rgya gcig pa bsgom zhing
NK064(ngu),002:5465: rjes thob tu'ang de'i rgyun bsring ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5466: spros pa dang bcas pa ni phyag rgya spros bcas kyi spyod pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5467: mnyam rjes gnyis kar spyod yul thams cad lha'i rol mor 'char ba la bslab pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5470: mnyam rjes gnyis ka yo byad lnga la ma chags par spyod pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5472: rig 'dzin bzhi'i gnas skabs kyi spyod pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5473: rdzu 'phrul gyi bkod pas sprul pa ma 'gags par ston cing don mdzad pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5474: de ltar grol lam rim gyis pa'i spyod pa bdun
NK064(ngu),002:5475: bshad nas cig car ba'i spyod pa ni chos thams
NK064(ngu),002:5476: cad la blang dor med pa spyod pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5478: mi dmigs pa las rnam par spyod //
NK064(ngu),002:5479: de ltar spyod pa kun spyod kyang //
NK064(ngu),002:5480: dam pa'i don te spyod mchog nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:5482: gsum pa bkod pa dkyil 'khor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5484: dkyil 'khor dbang dang dam tshig gsum //
NK064(ngu),002:5485: gsang sngags kun gyi gzhung shing yin //
NK064(ngu),002:5486: ces gtso bor ston te bshad dgos pas /
NK064(ngu),002:5488: bkod pa lha'i 'khor lo rdzogs par snang ba la 'jog cing /
NK064(ngu),002:5490: man+da la zhes pa'i sgra las len pa'am 'dzin pa ste yon tan gyi gzhi 'dzin pa'am /
NK064(ngu),002:5491: de len cing thob pa byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu),002:5492: dbye na sangs rgyas gsang bas chos don du /
NK064(ngu),002:5493: dbye ba rang bzhin ting 'dzin dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5494: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum //
NK064(ngu),002:5497: sku gsung thugs kyi dbye ba las //
NK064(ngu),002:5499: zhes gsum du dbye ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5501: dkyil 'khor rnam pa bcu gnyis te //
NK064(ngu),002:5502: de bzhin nyid dang rang bzhin dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5504: ting nge 'dzin dang gzugs brnyan dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5505: lhag pa ting 'dzin gzugs brnyan dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5506: byang chub sems dang lhag byang sems //
NK064(ngu),002:5507: tshogs dang lhun grub dkyil 'khor ro //
NK064(ngu),002:5508: zhes bcu gnyis su dbye ba sogs yod pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:5511: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5513: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan //
NK064(ngu),002:5514: zhes gsungs pa ltar bdun du phye nas 'chad de /
NK064(ngu),002:5515: dang po rang bzhin dkyil 'khor la /
NK064(ngu),002:5516: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5517: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:5518: dang po ni chos thams cad ye nas rang bzhin
NK064(ngu),002:5519: gyi rnam par dag pa gnas lugs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu),002:5521: chos nyid rang bzhin spros bral te //
NK064(ngu),002:5522: dngos po kun kyang de bzhin pas //
NK064(ngu),002:5523: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK064(ngu),002:5525: 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5526: rang rig ye shes mngon du gyur pas 'og min
NK064(ngu),002:5527: gyi gnas su sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral med
NK064(ngu),002:5528: pa'i dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5531: bzhugs pa dkyil dang 'khor gyi tshul //
NK064(ngu),002:5533: gnyis pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5534: don dam pa'i gzugs brnyan kun rdzob lha'i dkyil 'khor du rang shar ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5536: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor yang dag ni //
NK064(ngu),002:5537: chen po rags pa thabs su rtogs //
NK064(ngu),002:5538: so so'i mtshan nyid shes rab rtogs //
NK064(ngu),002:5539: gnyis med 'brel pa thabs chen yin //
NK064(ngu),002:5541: gsum pa lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5543: sa gzhi mnyam dang tshad thig dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5544: tshon dang bri dang rnam pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5545: rab gnas sbyin sreg dkyil 'khor du //
NK064(ngu),002:5546: 'jug dang zhugs pa'i yon tan no //
NK064(ngu),002:5548: dang po sa gzhi mnyam pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5550: gzhi dang rang mtshan bslang dbang dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5551: sbyang byin bsrung dang bzung ba ni //
NK064(ngu),002:5552: dang po'i nying lag nyid du bshad //
NK064(ngu),002:5554: dang po sa gzhi la brtag pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5556: gnam dang sa dang bar snang rnams //
NK064(ngu),002:5557: legs par brtags te las rnams bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5558: zhes gsungs pa ltar gnam sa bar gsum gyi dpyad la brtag pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5559: dang po nam mkha' la brtag pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5561: zur brgyad la sogs rtse mang dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5562: chu bo bzhin du ma bo zhing //
NK064(ngu),002:5563: mnyam zhing 'o kha chu ltar dwangs //
NK064(ngu),002:5564: nyi ma shin tu gnas pa ni //
NK064(ngu),002:5565: nam mkha'i mtshan nyid shes par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5567: bar gyi sgros la brtag pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5568: phyogs kyi ri la brtag pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5569: mtshams kyi dgra la brtag pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5572: shar lho gzhol zhing 'jam pa la //
NK064(ngu),002:5573: mtho dang 'dud pa nub byang yin //
NK064(ngu),002:5575: gnyis pa mtshams kyi dgra la brtag pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5578: gshin rje gdug pa'i mdung rtse dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5579: srin mo ngus pa'i mchi rjes dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5580: gnod sbyin khros pa'i sbar rjes dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5582: zhes pa lta bu shar lho nas rim pa bzhin g.yas bskor gyis mtshams bzhir med pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5583: gsum pa 'og gi sa gzhi la brtag pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5585: lhun sdug ri bo nags tshal ldan //
NK064(ngu),002:5586: rab tu mnyam zhing snum bag can //
NK064(ngu),002:5587: chu bo'i dbang gi phyogs yin te //
NK064(ngu),002:5588: cung zad kyis ni rlung nyung zhing //
NK064(ngu),002:5589: me tog shing tshal bya skad brtag /
NK064(ngu),002:5590: lo rgyus shis pa mchog tu gsungs //
NK064(ngu),002:5592: chu bo dbang gi phyogs la 'dod tshul gnyis te /
NK064(ngu),002:5593: rgyal blon snga dar gyi dus su ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5594: shar phyogs dbang po'i phyogs nas 'bab pa de yin gsungs te lha sa lta bu dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5595: khri srong gi dus su ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5596: nub phyogs klu dbang gi phyogs yin gsungs te bsam yas bzhin no //
NK064(ngu),002:5597: de gnyis ka'ang 'gal skyon med 'dra gsungs /
NK064(ngu),002:5598: gnyis pas rang gi mtshan nyid la brtag pa la bzang ngan gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:5601: bkra shis rtsa dang me tog shing //
NK064(ngu),002:5602: gnag dang kha dog ldan pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5606: thang ka sogs le lta bu dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5607: dma' dang bo ba'i mtshan nyid dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5610: gram pa thal ba shing sol dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5611: gyo mo rus pa gseg ma sogs //
NK064(ngu),002:5613: de ltar ngan pa'i skyon med pa rung ba'i mtshan nyid dang ldan na /
NK064(ngu),002:5616: rtsod pa nye bar zhi ba'i phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:5617: mngon dang mi mngon bdag po la //
NK064(ngu),002:5618: ser sna spangs pa'i yid kyis ni //
NK064(ngu),002:5619: rim bcal bden pas bsgos la bslang //
NK064(ngu),002:5621: snang ba mi las bslang ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5622: mi snang ba lha las bslang ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5624: sa de'i bdag po'i gyur pa'i rgyal po sogs la rin gzhal te bslang ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5627: sa'i lha mo 'khor bcas la bslang ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5628: bzhi pa dbang du bya ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5630: dngos grub dbang du bya ba'i phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:5631: zang sogs phur bu zla gam la //
NK064(ngu),002:5632: h'u las byung ba'i dbang mchog khro //
NK064(ngu),002:5634: pad+ma k+ai la yar bskyed pa'i dbang mchog gi phur bu gdab pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5637: sbyang ba las me sngags phyag rgya //
NK064(ngu),002:5638: ting nge 'dzin gyis dag par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5640: dang po las dang bya bas sbyong ba ni //
NK064(ngu),002:5642: lto ba nas sa brkos la /
NK064(ngu),002:5643: dong tshad sked pa'am pus nub kyi tshad gang rigs brkos la sa'i ro rnams bsal te /
NK064(ngu),002:5645: chus bkang gom pa brgyar blta bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5647: gom pa lnga bcur phyin nas tshur 'ongs te bltas pas /
NK064(ngu),002:5648: chu ma brin legs pa'i rtags te de nyid du gter gzhug cing stegs bu brtsigs la /
NK064(ngu),002:5650: zhes pas phung lnga sku lngar dag byed dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5651: gur gum gla rtsi dza ti dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5652: tsan dan dkar dmar spos lnga ste //
NK064(ngu),002:5654: dbang po lnga phrin las lngar dag byed dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5655: byu ru mu tig mu men dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5656: gser dngul rnams ni rin po che //
NK064(ngu),002:5658: yul lnga yon tan lngar dag byed dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5659: lan tsh+wa sbrang rtsi bu ram dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5660: a 'bras mar te snying po lnga //
NK064(ngu),002:5661: zhes pas rnam shes lnga ye shes lngar dag byed dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5662: ha sa de ba bri ha ti //
NK064(ngu),002:5663: swa ra kan+da ka ri dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5666: 'dod yon lnga gsung lngar dag byed dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5667: byang sems dkar dmar dri che chung //
NK064(ngu),002:5668: sha chen bdud rtsi rnam lnga ste //
NK064(ngu),002:5669: zhes pas khams lnga rigs lngar dag byed de lnga
NK064(ngu),002:5670: tshan drug gi lde gu'i rdzas sum cus skyang nul
NK064(ngu),002:5671: bya'o // gnyis pa mes sbyang ba ni sbyin sreg ste 'og tu 'chad do //
NK064(ngu),002:5672: gsum pa sngags dang phyag rgyas sbyang ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5673: lag g.yas par nyi dkyil la 'bru lnga bkod de /
NK064(ngu),002:5674: badz+ra ha na ha na kro d+ha h'u phata /
NK064(ngu),002:5675: ces pa'i sngags brjod pa dang bstun nas sa la lan gsum brdabs pa'i 'od kyis sbyang ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5676: bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyang ba la gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:5677: mtshan med stong pa nyid kyis sbyang ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5678: shu nya ta'i sngags kyis so //
NK064(ngu),002:5679: mtshan bcas kyis sbyang ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5680: zhi khro gang byed kyi dkyil 'khor 'byung ba rim brtsegs nas bzung ste gsal gdab pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5681: drug pa byin gyis brlab pa ni //
NK064(ngu),002:5682: slob dpon rgyas pa'i chas su zhugs nas rdo rje'i
NK064(ngu),002:5683: 'gros kyis dkyil 'khor la bskor zhing shar sgo nas
NK064(ngu),002:5684: zhugs te dbus su 'dug pa la /
NK064(ngu),002:5685: yum bzhi'i nga rgyal 'dzin pa'i phyogs kyi slob ma bzhis phyogs so so nas /
NK064(ngu),002:5686: zhi ba'i ye shes rang snang ba'i //
NK064(ngu),002:5687: zhes sogs kyis gsol ba btab pas /
NK064(ngu),002:5688: slob dpon gyis nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs
NK064(ngu),002:5689: pa rnams kyi byin rlabs bskul zhing bsdus nas zhe
NK064(ngu),002:5690: sdang rdo rje'i nga rgyal gyis 'bar ba'i sdang mig
NK064(ngu),002:5691: dang bcas te / rdo rje 'dzin pa nyi ma dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5692: chos dang rta mchog snang mdzad kyang //
NK064(ngu),002:5693: bdag nyid chen po nga nyid yin //
NK064(ngu),002:5694: thams cad bka' las deng ma 'da' //
NK064(ngu),002:5696: sum+b+ha'i sngags brjod cing rdo rje'i 'gros kyis bskor bas
NK064(ngu),002:5697: sa gzhi rdo rje'i rang bzhin du byin gyis brlabs
NK064(ngu),002:5698: pa'o // bdun pa bsrung ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5699: mtshon cha lngas mtshams bcad pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5701: mtshon cha lnga yi rim pa ste //
NK064(ngu),002:5702: bsrung ba'i mchog tu de gsungs so //
NK064(ngu),002:5705: de ltar lha tshogs yab yum rol pa'i 'od sa
NK064(ngu),002:5706: gzhi la thim pas dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin du
NK064(ngu),002:5707: gsal bar bsam pa ni sa bzung ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5709: nges brjod rol pa'i gzi byin gyis //
NK064(ngu),002:5710: thams cad dkyil 'khor rang bzhin du //
NK064(ngu),002:5711: gsal byas yongs su bzung ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5713: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor gyi tshad ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5715: dkyil 'khor gru gang tshad du bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5719: phur bu srad bu tshon phye dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5721: de yang spyir thig ces pa mi 'gyur ba'i don te /
NK064(ngu),002:5722: de'i rgyu 'gying phur dang bskor phur te phur bu gnyis dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5725: zhi ba la pad+ma'i rgyus pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5726: khro bo la rgyus chen te /
NK064(ngu),002:5727: gnyis ka'i dam thig gi rgyu ras bal gtsang ma dpa' bo'i rin gyis nyos pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5728: de yang ye shes kyi skud pa nyi shu rtsa lnga'am lnga bsgril dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5729: dam tshig gi skud pa dgu bsgril lam gsum bsgril du bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5731: dam thig sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin du sa la btab nas /
NK064(ngu),002:5732: sku gsung thugs re re'ang ye shes lnga dang ldan par bya ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:5733: ye thig dkyil 'khor gyi gazhi'ii steng gi nam mkha' la gdab bo //
NK064(ngu),002:5736: mkhas ldan chen pos bsgrims te bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5737: zhes pas bskor phyogs ma 'khrul bar gdab ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5738: gal te ma bsgrims pa'i nyes pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5740: skud pa chad na slob dpon 'chi //
NK064(ngu),002:5741: thig sna shor na slob ma 'chi //
NK064(ngu),002:5742: phyogs 'khrul bas ni gnyis ka nyams //
NK064(ngu),002:5743: rgyun chad lam la gnod par 'gyur //
NK064(ngu),002:5744: de phyir mkhas pas bsgrims te bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5748: ma mthong rmongs la bstan phyir tshon //
NK064(ngu),002:5749: kha dog nyi shu rtsa lnga'am //
NK064(ngu),002:5750: lnga yi tshon gyis bri bar bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5751: 'dul ba'i cho ga bzhin du dgye //
NK064(ngu),002:5755: lte ba rtsibs dang ldan pa yi //
NK064(ngu),002:5756: rtsibs bzhir 'khor lo mu khyud bcas //
NK064(ngu),002:5757: gru chad bzhi dang gru bzhi pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5758: bar khyams sgo khyud ldan par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5760: dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum gang gis 'dul ba'i cho ga bzhin du bri ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5761: drug pa rnam pa 'god pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5762: sku gsung thugs ldan gzugs kyang 'god //
NK064(ngu),002:5764: yang na gtso 'khor gyi 'gros sbyar te /
NK064(ngu),002:5766: gtso bo gzugs su rdzogs par bri //
NK064(ngu),002:5767: 'khor rnams phyag rgya dag tu bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5768: phal pa la ni yig 'brus so //
NK064(ngu),002:5771: nub gnyis pa'i las rim spyir bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5772: skabs thob kyi las rim dkyil 'khor rab gnas gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:5773: dang po yan lag gi rab gnas ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5777: thig tshon rab gnas rnams dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5778: yan lag can gyi rab gnas ni //
NK064(ngu),002:5781: lha sta gon gyis bstan no //
NK064(ngu),002:5783: las 'grigs rnam pa dgu la sogs pa'i sgo nas so //
NK064(ngu),002:5785: skabs thob kyi las bzhi ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5787: dbyibs dang kha dog mtshan ldan par //
NK064(ngu),002:5788: zhal du gyur pa'i me bos la //
NK064(ngu),002:5789: bza' btung bro ba'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK064(ngu),002:5790: las bzhi'i mchod pa rab tu sbyin //
NK064(ngu),002:5792: dgu pa dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5793: sgrub mchod la sogs pa sngon du 'gro ba'i sgo
NK064(ngu),002:5794: nas dang por slob dpon rang nyid zhugs rjes slob
NK064(ngu),002:5795: ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug par bya ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5797: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK064(ngu),002:5798: de nas slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5801: dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod gsol dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5802: khrus dgab dri dang lus dbul dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5803: bgegs bskrad lhar rlob dam tshig sbyin //
NK064(ngu),002:5804: de nyid dbab dang chu nan dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5805: bsgrags dang rin chen dor ba dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5806: lha dbab pa dang nan tan dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5807: mig dbye dkyil 'khor legs bstan dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5808: tshogs mchog yon dang rnam bco brgyad //
NK064(ngu),002:5811: bcu pa zhugs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5813: byas te dad ldan rab zhugs nas //
NK064(ngu),002:5817: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i //
NK064(ngu),002:5818: 'khor lo mngon du mthong ba yi //
NK064(ngu),002:5819: bsod nams brtags pa gang yin pa //
NK064(ngu),002:5820: phyis byas pa yang de bzhin no //
NK064(ngu),002:5822: bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5823: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor nyid ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK064(ngu),002:5824: yul du byas te rang rig ma bcos pa'i don
NK064(ngu),002:5825: la mnyam par bzhag pas rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:5826: rang rtsal ye shes 'gags med du 'char ba ste
NK064(ngu),002:5828: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus brtags te //
NK064(ngu),002:5829: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun grub ni //
NK064(ngu),002:5830: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK064(ngu),002:5833: lnga pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5835: lhag pa ting 'dzin rnam pa gnyis //
NK064(ngu),002:5836: 'dul ba'i don phyir zhi khro gnyis //
NK064(ngu),002:5838: thugs rje zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5839: bdud 'dul khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:5840: zhi khro gnyis ka la mtshungs par /
NK064(ngu),002:5841: sngon 'gro las bdun nas go bgo lus bsrung gi
NK064(ngu),002:5842: bar ting nge 'dzin gyi dmigs pa'i 'phro 'du mang
NK064(ngu),002:5843: pos lhag par sgrub dgos pas na lhag pa ting
NK064(ngu),002:5845: drug pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5847: byang sems phyi nang gsang ba dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5848: gnas gzhi khams gsum ye shes che //
NK064(ngu),002:5850: phyi byang chub kyi sems rtsa dang rlung /
NK064(ngu),002:5851: nang byang chub kyi sems thig le /
NK064(ngu),002:5852: gsang ba byang chub kyi sems bde ba'i ye shes dang gsum mo //
NK064(ngu),002:5854: sgyu 'phrul snying po bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK064(ngu),002:5855: srid gsum sems can thams cad la //
NK064(ngu),002:5856: srog shing gsum dang 'khor lo bzhi //
NK064(ngu),002:5857: zhes rtsa dang rlung la sbyang gzhi ye shes kyi rlung dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5858: sbyang bya las kyi rlung gnyis /
NK064(ngu),002:5859: las rlung la rtsa ba dang yan lag gis bsdus pa'i rlung bcu /
NK064(ngu),002:5860: snar rgyu ba'i rlung dang bcas pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5862: snying ga na srog mi shigs pa'i thig le sogs ye shes kyi thig le dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5863: rnam shes kyi thig le snyigs ma dang bcas pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5865: steng 'og gi sgo la brten nas bde chen gyi ye shes bskyed pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5867: dkyil ni snying po zhes brjod de //
NK064(ngu),002:5868: byang chub sems ni bde chen po //
NK064(ngu),002:5869: len par byed pa dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:5871: bdun pa tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5872: zhi khro gnyis ka la tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5874: tshogs ni 'byor ba rnam pa gsum //
NK064(ngu),002:5875: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5877: bzhi pa dbang la'ang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5880: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhis yan lag bsnyad //
NK064(ngu),002:5881: drug la gnas pa'i thob bya ni //
NK064(ngu),002:5882: ngo bo nyid bcas rnam par bshad //
NK064(ngu),002:5883: ces spyir dbang la rgyu gnyis dang rkyen bzhi'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5885: mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu gdod ma nas rang la dang chas su bzhugs pa'i chos nyid de /
NK064(ngu),002:5887: dbang rdzas rab gnas kyi byin gyis brlabs pa can no //
NK064(ngu),002:5889: phan nus zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur du rung ba'i snod ldan gyi slob ma rgyu'i rkyen /
NK064(ngu),002:5890: dbang gsum bskur nus pa'i slob dpon tshad ldan bdag po'i rkyen /
NK064(ngu),002:5891: rdzas sngags ting nge 'dzin gsum 'dzom pa'i nus pa khyad par can dmigs pa'i rkyen /
NK064(ngu),002:5892: dbang snga ma snga mas go phye nas phyi ma
NK064(ngu),002:5893: phyi ma 'byung ba de ma thag pa'i rkyen no
NK064(ngu),002:5894: // de ltar rgyu gnyis dang rkyen bzhi ste drug
NK064(ngu),002:5895: po tshogs pa la brten nas go 'phang gi chos
NK064(ngu),002:5896: dbang gi ye shes rgyud la 'jog pa'i las kyis
NK064(ngu),002:5897: thar pa'i myu gu mngon du bskyed pa'am skye ngos
NK064(ngu),002:5898: kyi nus rung du smin par byed pa ni dbang
NK064(ngu),002:5899: // gi ngo bo'o // nges tshig ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5902: shiny+tsa ni gtor ba'am blugs pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5903: dbang gis sgo gsum gyi dri ma 'khrud pa'i cha nas mngon par gtor ba dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5904: 'bras bu ye shes kyi nus pa khyad par can
NK064(ngu),002:5905: rgyud la 'jog pa'i cha nas mngon par blugs pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:5908: gtor dang blugs pa zhes bya ba //
NK064(ngu),002:5909: des na dbang zhes brjod par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5912: slob dpon gsang ba shes rab dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5913: de ma thag pa bzhi pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5915: yang snod kyi dbang du byas te dbye na phan nus zab mo'i dbang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5917: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK064(ngu),002:5918: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK064(ngu),002:5919: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5921: gang zag dad pa can la phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5922: de yang bsdoms su byas nas /
NK064(ngu),002:5923: snying po lnga dang dbu rgyan dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5924: bum pa cod pan phreng ba ste //
NK064(ngu),002:5925: go cha rgyal mtshan gdugs phyag rgya //
NK064(ngu),002:5926: bza' btung dbang rnams rim bzhin bskur //
NK064(ngu),002:5928: gnyis pa nang nus pa'i dbang la lnga yod de /
NK064(ngu),002:5929: bdag don nus pa la nyan dbang dang lha bsgom pa'i dbang /
NK064(ngu),002:5930: gzhan don nus pa la 'chad phrin gyi dbang /
NK064(ngu),002:5931: gnyis ka'i don nus pa la rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5933: spyod rig mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs can la bskur bas
NK064(ngu),002:5934: rim gyis phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub la sbyor
NK064(ngu),002:5935: ba ste / rdo rje las rim sas /
NK064(ngu),002:5936: dang pos sa bon 'jog pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5937: gnyis pas nus pa bskyed pa yin //
NK064(ngu),002:5938: gsum pas nyams myong bskyed pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5939: bzhi pas de nyid brtan par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:5940: lnga pas brtan pa nyams len pas //
NK064(ngu),002:5944: nus dbang gis sa bon nus ldan du smin /
NK064(ngu),002:5945: gsang dbang gis dbang don gyi ye shes rgyud la myong /
NK064(ngu),002:5946: sher dbang gis de kho na nyid rgyud la brtan par byed /
NK064(ngu),002:5947: bde ba chen po'i dbang gis mchog gi dngos grub thob par byed pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5949: gdan dang lha dbang phyag mtshan dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5950: chas bcu sgrub rdzas bco lnga'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5952: phan dbang la nyer brgyad du phye bas nang gses kyis dbye na grangs so drug ste /
NK064(ngu),002:5955: bsnams pa phyag mtshan gyi dbang /
NK064(ngu),002:5956: dregs pa gdan gyi dbang gsum ni re re dang /
NK064(ngu),002:5957: de las gzhan rnams kyi bye brag bgrang ba'i sdom tshig ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5958: rgyan chas rtags la bcu yin te //
NK064(ngu),002:5959: dbu rgyan bum pa snying po lnga //
NK064(ngu),002:5960: cod pan go cha phreng ba rgyan //
NK064(ngu),002:5961: thod phreng rtags gsum me dpung ngo //
NK064(ngu),002:5962: nus pa'i dbang ni lngar nges te //
NK064(ngu),002:5964: sgrub pa'i dbang la bco lnga ste //
NK064(ngu),002:5965: bdud rtsi lnga dang sha lnga dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5966: rak+ta kha t+wam gdugs rgyal mtshan //
NK064(ngu),002:5967: phur pa rdor dril rnge'u chung dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5968: yungs kar gzungs ma phreng ba dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5969: tshe dang bza' btung ming dbang ngo //
NK064(ngu),002:5970: zab dbang gsum ste gsang ba dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5971: shes rab ye shes bde chen no //
NK064(ngu),002:5973: de ltar dbang bskur tshul ni /
NK064(ngu),002:5975: bzhag pa'i gnas dang bstim pa'i gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:5976: de bzhin khong du chud pa gces //
NK064(ngu),002:5980: phyi dbang lus la bskur ba ste //
NK064(ngu),002:5981: khyad par snying po dbu rgyan bum //
NK064(ngu),002:5982: gdugs dang cod pan phreng ba mgo //
NK064(ngu),002:5983: go cha lus te rgyal mtshan lag /
NK064(ngu),002:5984: bza' btung ngag gi lam du'o //
NK064(ngu),002:5985: phyag rgya spyi bo'am snying ga ste //
NK064(ngu),002:5989: rdzas ni glegs bam rgya gram dang //
NK064(ngu),002:5990: 'khor lo phreng ba rdo rje dril //
NK064(ngu),002:5991: 'byung ldan don yod snang mtha' yas //
NK064(ngu),002:5992: yi dam rigs lnga'i rab gnas ldan //
NK064(ngu),002:5996: rdzas ni skabs kyi phyag rgya mo //
NK064(ngu),002:6001: sems kyi dkyil nas drangs pa'i chu //
NK064(ngu),002:6002: khyod kyi lce la bzhag pa ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6003: snying gi dkyil du bzung bar byos //
NK064(ngu),002:6005: de ltar dbang thob pa'i tshad ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6007: rno la ngar btags nus pa bzhin //
NK064(ngu),002:6008: nus pa skyes pa thob pa'i tshad //
NK064(ngu),002:6010: dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6012: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK064(ngu),002:6013: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK064(ngu),002:6014: nyan pa la sogs brtson pa ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6017: de ltar dbang thob pa'i yon tan ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6018: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK064(ngu),002:6019: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6020: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK064(ngu),002:6021: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK064(ngu),002:6023: he ru ka mngon byung las /
NK064(ngu),002:6024: dkyil 'khor bdag po mthong nas ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6025: cung zad de ni mi 'grub med //
NK064(ngu),002:6026: sdig pa kun las rnam par grol //
NK064(ngu),002:6027: dngos grub myur du thob par 'gyur //
NK064(ngu),002:6029: lnga pa dam tshig la'ang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6032: gang zhig nan tan las mi 'gong //
NK064(ngu),002:6033: rmi lam du'ang dam tshig brjod //
NK064(ngu),002:6034: dam bca' ba ni sdom par 'dod //
NK064(ngu),002:6035: ces pas gang bsrung ba'i don khyad par can ni
NK064(ngu),002:6036: 'og nas 'byung ba'i rtsa ba dang yan lag gi
NK064(ngu),002:6038: de dag las nam yang mi 'da' bar sdom byed kyi sems pa rgyun chags dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6039: gnyid dang sems yengs pa la sogs pa'i gnas skabs su yang sdom pa'i sa bon dang bcas pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6041: sa ma ya'i sgra las sa ma ya ni rnam
NK064(ngu),002:6042: pa gcig tu na dngos su yal gam bcas pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:6044: sngon rang gis ji ltar dam bcas pa las 'da'
NK064(ngu),002:6045: bar bya ba ma yin pa'i phyir dam tshig ste
NK064(ngu),002:6047: rdo rje 'da' dka' dam tshig gtan gyi gnyer //
NK064(ngu),002:6048: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK064(ngu),002:6049: snga phyi mnos shing gnyer du smras so 'tshal //
NK064(ngu),002:6050: yun du mi gtong 'da' bar mi bgyid do //
NK064(ngu),002:6053: ngan song gi gnas su rgyud tshig par 'gyur ba'i nyes dmigs kyis dam tshig tu bzhag ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6055: dam pa sku gsung thugs yin te //
NK064(ngu),002:6063: mi 'da' dam pa mchog gyur pa //
NK064(ngu),002:6064: 'das par gyur na tshig par bshad //
NK064(ngu),002:6066: dbye na rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6067: yan lag gi dam tshig lnga tshan gnyis /
NK064(ngu),002:6068: de las kyang spro na sum brgya drug cur dbye ba dang gsum mo //
NK064(ngu),002:6071: bla med mi spang bla ma bkur //
NK064(ngu),002:6072: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad //
NK064(ngu),002:6073: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams //
NK064(ngu),002:6074: gsang ba'i don phyir smra mi bya //
NK064(ngu),002:6075: 'di ni rtsa ba lnga rnams te //
NK064(ngu),002:6076: bsgrub dang bsrung ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:6078: dang po bla med mi spang ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6079: yul bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi sems lhag
NK064(ngu),002:6080: pa bden pa dbyer med rtogs go mas kyis sgo
NK064(ngu),002:6081: gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya las mi
NK064(ngu),002:6084: rang lus rgyal ba'i phyag rgya che //
NK064(ngu),002:6085: sems can khams kyang der shes shing //
NK064(ngu),002:6086: snang stong dbyer med rdo rje'i sku //
NK064(ngu),002:6087: dus gsum rgyun du ma dran na //
NK064(ngu),002:6088: theg chen sngags par ci yis tshud //
NK064(ngu),002:6090: gnyis pa bla ma bkur ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6092: spyi dang 'dren dang dam tshig dbang //
NK064(ngu),002:6093: nyams chags skong dang shes rgyud dgrol //
NK064(ngu),002:6094: man ngag lung gi slob dpon drug /
NK064(ngu),002:6095: ces pa ltar drug po bkur thabs drug gi sgo nas bkur te /
NK064(ngu),002:6097: yul la dbang ba'i rgyal po dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6098: khu bo pha dang ma dang mig /
NK064(ngu),002:6099: snying bas lhag pa'i tshul gyis te //
NK064(ngu),002:6103: man ngag nod pa gsum bka' drin sum ldan gyi
NK064(ngu),002:6104: bla ma yin pas lhag par yang bkur dgos te
NK064(ngu),002:6106: rgyud grol dbang bskur de nyid bstan //
NK064(ngu),002:6108: gsum pa sngags gsum dang phyag rgya bzhi rgyun mi bcad pa'i dam tshig ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6110: rab kyis chu bo'i gzhung bzhin nam //
NK064(ngu),002:6111: nyin gsum mtshan gsum gnyis gcig tu //
NK064(ngu),002:6112: ma yengs tsam du ngang gis bzla //
NK064(ngu),002:6113: 'bring gis zla gcig dus drug gam //
NK064(ngu),002:6114: dus bzhi'i bar du mi bcad cing //
NK064(ngu),002:6115: tha ma bya ba'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK064(ngu),002:6116: zla re'am ra ba'i dus dag tu //
NK064(ngu),002:6117: brtson pas 'bad de mi byed na //
NK064(ngu),002:6118: byang chub sa bon brlag pa yin //
NK064(ngu),002:6119: tshogs dang gtor ma'ang de bzhin du //
NK064(ngu),002:6122: bzhi pa mched la byams pa'i dam tshig ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6124: mtha' yas sems can rang rig phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:6125: gang yang bdag las gzhan min dang //
