NK064(ngu),002:6126: bde gshegs snying po'i spun yin phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:6127: ma 'ongs sangs rgyas rang bzhin ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6128: spyi yi mched de pha tshan bzhin //
NK064(ngu),002:6129: sangs rgyas chos zhugs ring ba dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6130: lta spyod mthun pa nye bar bshad //
NK064(ngu),002:6131: pha gcig dam tshig nang 'dres pa //
NK064(ngu),002:6133: des mtshon pa'i rdo rje'i mched lcam dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6134: byang chub bar du mi 'bral ba'i brtse gdung rgyun mi 'chad par byed pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6135: lnga pa gsang ba mi smra ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6137: dam nyams dam las log pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6138: dam med dkyil 'khor ma mthong dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6140: zhes gang la gsang bya'i yul bstan nas /
NK064(ngu),002:6143: spyi dang bar gsang bzhi bzhi dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6144: 'os dang gnyer gtad rnam pa bcu //
NK064(ngu),002:6149: gsang ba gnyer gtad pa rnams so //
NK064(ngu),002:6152: lta zab spyod pa barlang po dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6153: lha ming gzungs dang grub rtags rnams //
NK064(ngu),002:6155: de ni gnas skabs thams cad du'ang gsang dgos pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6158: sgrub pa'i gnas dus grogs dang rdzas //
NK064(ngu),002:6159: bar du gsang la sgrub par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:6160: zhes pas de ni sgrub pa ji tsam bya ba'i bar du gsang dgos pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6161: gsang bar 'os pa ni gzhan ma dad pa skye ba'i rdzas dang yo byad sogs so //
NK064(ngu),002:6162: gsang ba gnyer gtad pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6164: mched kyis gdams pa rnams so //
NK064(ngu),002:6165: gnyis pa yan lag gi dam tshig la /
NK064(ngu),002:6166: mi spang ba lnga dang mi dor ba lnga las /
NK064(ngu),002:6169: gti mug chags dang zhe sdang dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6170: nga rgyal phrag dog mi spang ngo //
NK064(ngu),002:6173: yang dag dug lnga log dug lnga //
NK064(ngu),002:6175: yang dag pa'i dug lnga ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6176: chos thams cad la blang dor gyis 'byed pa med pa'i gti mug /
NK064(ngu),002:6177: sems can la snying rjes chags pa'i 'dod chags /
NK064(ngu),002:6178: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis log rtog 'joms pa'i zhe sdang /
NK064(ngu),002:6179: mnyam nyid lta ba'i rgyal po gshongs su mi 'bebs pa'i nga rgyal /
NK064(ngu),002:6180: mnyam nyid kyi klong du gnyis 'dzin mi shong ba'i phrag dog go //
NK064(ngu),002:6181: log pa'i dug lnga yang mi spong ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6182: spang bya'i rdzas ma grub pas smig sgyu la chu rag mi dgos pa bzhin no //
NK064(ngu),002:6183: gnyis pa mi dor ba lnga ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6185: dkar rtsi dmar rtsi dri sha chen //
NK064(ngu),002:6186: dag pa'i snod chu mi 'dor ro //
NK064(ngu),002:6188: gsum pa sum brgya drug cur dbye ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6190: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga la ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6191: gcig la'ang gnyis dang bcu phrag gsum //
NK064(ngu),002:6192: yan lag dam tshig lnga nyid la //
NK064(ngu),002:6193: gcig la'ang bcu phrag gnyis su dbye //
NK064(ngu),002:6194: zhes pas rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po re rer thabs shes gnyis gnyis su phye bas bcu dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6195: yang rtsa ba lnga po re re la sum cur phye bas chig brgya lnga bcu ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6196: sngar gyi bcu dang bsdoms pas brgya drug cu'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6198: dper na bla med mi spang ba la sum cur dbye ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6200: byang chub sems ni bla med lha //
NK064(ngu),002:6201: zhi khro'i dgu gnyis dang ni bcu //
NK064(ngu),002:6202: bcu gnyis bsam yas mi 'da' zhing //
NK064(ngu),002:6203: thun mong mchog gi tshad med brgyad //
NK064(ngu),002:6204: bden gnyis byang chub rnam pa bcu //
NK064(ngu),002:6205: bla med gsal bas nyams mi bya //
NK064(ngu),002:6207: des mtshon nas lhag ma bzhi la'ang rgyas par bshad do //
NK064(ngu),002:6208: yan lag gi dam tshig bcu po re rer nyi shur dbye ba'ang /
NK064(ngu),002:6209: zhe sdang la thabs shes kyis mi spang ba'i bcu bcu ste nyi shu /
NK064(ngu),002:6211: de ltar yan lag gi dam tshig bcu po re rer nyi shur phye bas nyis brgya ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6212: sngar gyi brgya drug cu dang bsdoms pas sum brgya drug cu'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6213: de dag gi rnam bzhag rgyas par phra rgyas las bshad pas de blta bar bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6214: drug pa rol pa phrin las la'ang gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:6217: phyi rol tshad med nyid las bzhi //
NK064(ngu),002:6218: zhes pas sems can thams cad rang gi pha mar shes pa'i byams pa /
NK064(ngu),002:6219: de dag rigs drug gi gnas na sdug bsngal gyi
NK064(ngu),002:6220: yo langs la spyod pa rnams la snying rje sems
NK064(ngu),002:6221: can 'ga' zhig lha mi'i dpal 'byor gyi bde ba
NK064(ngu),002:6222: dga' ba / nye ring chags sdang dang bral ba'i btang snyoms te /
NK064(ngu),002:6223: de lta bu'i tshad med bzhi'i rgyu las byung ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:6224: byang chub kyi sems dang 'khor gsum mi rtog pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:6225: shes rab kyis zin pa'i sgo nas gzhan don sgrub
NK064(ngu),002:6226: pa la dmigs pa'i thabs mkhas kyi mdzad spyod do
NK064(ngu),002:6229: sgo gsum gyi bsdus pa'i bya ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi las te /
NK064(ngu),002:6231: de la dbye na phyi ma 'gos 'gyur las /
NK064(ngu),002:6232: zhi ba la sogs rab dbye bas /
NK064(ngu),002:6233: las ni rnam pa bzhir bsdus so //
NK064(ngu),002:6235: de dag kyang gang gis bya ba'i thabs kyi rim pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6240: phyag rgya'i sgo nas bya ba rnams te /
NK064(ngu),002:6242: bdag gzhan don 'grub phrin las ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6243: mchod rten phyag rgya'i sgo dang ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6244: hom bro glu dang rdzas kyis bya //
NK064(ngu),002:6246: de la me'i sgo nas bya ba sbyin sreg yin te /
NK064(ngu),002:6248: gnas rdzas thab kyi rnam pa dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6249: gzungs dang gtso sems bsgrub bya dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6250: phur bu lha dus las rim bzhin //
NK064(ngu),002:6251: lhag ma bcu gcig shes par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:6252: zhes bshad pa ltar shes par bya ba yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:6253: gnyis pa rdzas kyi sgo nas bya ba ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6257: mchod sbyin bya ba yon tan dang bcas pa rnams te /
NK064(ngu),002:6259: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la //
NK064(ngu),002:6260: mtshan ma ming du bcas pa bya //
NK064(ngu),002:6261: bkug ste rdo rje phur bus gdab //
NK064(ngu),002:6262: rdul du byas nas tshogs la dbul //
NK064(ngu),002:6264: gsum pa lu gu rgyud kyi sgo nas bya ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6265: bro'i sgo nas phrin las bzhi sgrub pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6267: e yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK064(ngu),002:6268: lu gu rgyud du sbrel bsdams nas //
NK064(ngu),002:6269: bcing bsgyur bskyod nas phyogs bcur g.yo //
NK064(ngu),002:6271: zhes pa la sogs pa rnams so //
NK064(ngu),002:6272: bzhi pa mchod rten gyi sgo nas bya ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6276: drag por badz+ra he ru kar bskyed nas rigs so
NK064(ngu),002:6277: so'i sngags kyis mchod rten dbyibs mdog sogs las mthun
NK064(ngu),002:6278: du btab pa'i bum nang du rigs mthun gyi lha
NK064(ngu),002:6279: bskyed / de yi 'od kyis bsgrub bya gang yin
NK064(ngu),002:6280: bkug nas mchod rten gyi 'og tu gnas pa la
NK064(ngu),002:6281: bskyed / / 'od des reg pas zhi rgyas dbang
NK064(ngu),002:6282: drag gi las gang yin 'grub par bsam pa ste
NK064(ngu),002:6284: drag po gtum po 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:6285: bdag nyid drag por bsgoms nas ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6287: bgegs kyi ling ga mnan par bya //
NK064(ngu),002:6289: de ltar sa la dngos su 'debs pa'am /
NK064(ngu),002:6290: yang na ting nge 'dzin gyi 'byung ba gzhan la 'debs pa'ang bshad de /
NK064(ngu),002:6292: mchod rten 'byung ba gang la 'debs kyang zhes sogs so //
NK064(ngu),002:6293: lnga pa phyag rgya'i sgo nas bya ba ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6294: phyag rgya bca' ba'i sgo nas dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6295: de bsgyur ba'i sgo nas bya ba'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6297: dpal he ru ka'i las bzhi'i phyag rgya bca' ba ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6299: yan lag snying po rtse gcig dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6300: rtse lnga rtse dgu bcu gcig tu //
NK064(ngu),002:6301: las rnams so sor rab tu bsgom //
NK064(ngu),002:6305: rdo rje lan gsum gsor nas ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6306: lha mo klu mo rigs ngan mo //
NK064(ngu),002:6308: zhes rang kun bzang yab yum khros par bskyed la /
NK064(ngu),002:6309: gzungs ma dam can dbang du bya ba dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6310: de bzhin du rigs kyi he ru ka bzhir bskyed
NK064(ngu),002:6311: nas so so'i phyag rgya bsgyur bas las bzhi 'grub
NK064(ngu),002:6312: pa'o // bdun pa sgrub pa la'ang gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:6314: rgyud phyi ma kha che'i gyur las /
NK064(ngu),002:6315: 'jig rten pa yi dngos grub ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6316: bskyed pa'i rim pas sbyor bas 'thob //
NK064(ngu),002:6318: rdzogs pa'i rim pas sbyor bas so //
NK064(ngu),002:6319: zhes pas mchog thun mong gi dngos grub rnam pa gnyis gang 'dod don du gnyer ba zhig go //
NK064(ngu),002:6321: sid+d+hi'i sgra las dngos grub ste bsgrub bya dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6322: s+aa d+ha na'i sgra las kun tu len pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6323: 'dod pa'i don len cing thob par byas pas na sgrub pa zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6324: dbye na thun mchog gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:6325: dang po thun mong gi sgrub pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6327: ro lang tshe dang pra sgrub dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6328: lha chen po dang rgyal po bzhi //
NK064(ngu),002:6329: gdug pa klu 'dul rgyal blon gyi //
NK064(ngu),002:6330: chung ma dbang du bya ba gnyis //
NK064(ngu),002:6331: yul khams lce spyang rkang mgyogs bskrad //
NK064(ngu),002:6332: mi snang gzugs sgrub lha klu mo //
NK064(ngu),002:6333: rgyal blon dmag dpon zhang blon sgrub //
NK064(ngu),002:6336: 'di dag sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i le'u re res ston te /
NK064(ngu),002:6337: ro langs rdo rje zhing chen sgrub pa le'u bcu bdun pa nas /
NK064(ngu),002:6338: tshe sgrub pa drug cu re bzhi pa nas /
NK064(ngu),002:6339: pra se na dbab pa drug cu re lnga pa nas /
NK064(ngu),002:6340: lha chen po ma h+aa de wa sgrub pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6341: rgyal po chen po sde bzhi sgrub pa re drug pa nas /
NK064(ngu),002:6342: gdug pa'i klu gdon 'dul ba zhe drug pa nas /
NK064(ngu),002:6343: rgyal blon gyi chung ma dbang du bya ba gnyis zhe lnga pa nas /
NK064(ngu),002:6344: yul khams dbang du bya ba so brgyad pa nas /
NK064(ngu),002:6345: lce spyang zhes pa rdo rje rigs kyi rkang mgyogs bye brag pa ste zhe gcig pa nas /
NK064(ngu),002:6347: dgra bgegs gzhan du bskrad pa /
NK064(ngu),002:6348: mi snang ba'i gzugs sgrub pa /
NK064(ngu),002:6349: lha mo dang klu mo phyag rgyar 'gugs pa rnams so brgyad pa nas /
NK064(ngu),002:6351: dmag mang mthu chen sgrub pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6352: zhang blon sgrub pa rnams zhe gcig pa nas bstan to //
NK064(ngu),002:6353: der ma zad thun mong gi dngos grub 'di nyid rang nas kyang bstan te /
NK064(ngu),002:6354: yon tan 'byung ba'i dngos grub drug /
NK064(ngu),002:6356: las phran tshegs brgyad dang bcas pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6359: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad sel zhing //
NK064(ngu),002:6360: longs spyod 'byung zhing ngan song sbyong //
NK064(ngu),002:6364: nam mkha' rdo rje sra 'byung zhing //
NK064(ngu),002:6368: thams cad stong zhing ltung bar 'gyur //
NK064(ngu),002:6371: dgug dang btang dang bcing dang grol //
NK064(ngu),002:6372: gso dang bsad dang pham dang rgyal //
NK064(ngu),002:6375: gnyis pa mchog gi dngos grub ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6377: yi ge sgyu 'phrul tshogs sgrub dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6378: rdo rje sems dang sman sgrub dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6379: rigs lnga sgrub dang yum lnga sems //
NK064(ngu),002:6380: byin dbab sgrub pa rnam gnyis so //
NK064(ngu),002:6382: ji ltar sgrub pa'i tshul ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6383: zhi khro so so'i chog gzhung rnams dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6384: bye brag so so'i sgrub thabs gud du phyungs pa rnams so //
NK064(ngu),002:6385: gtso bor sgrub pa ni tshom bu tshogs kyi sgrub pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6386: brgyad pa mi g.yo ba ting nge 'dzin la'ang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6389: gang dang gang du gsal ba'i yid //
NK064(ngu),002:6390: ma yengs pa ni ting 'dzin te //
NK064(ngu),002:6392: bsgom bya'i don khyad par can bskyed rdzogs kyi ting
NK064(ngu),002:6393: nge 'dzin las mi g.yo bar gnas pa'i sems rtse
NK064(ngu),002:6395: sa ma d+hi'i sgra las mnyam pa'i blo ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6397: d+hi ni blo la 'jug pa las gang bsgom bya'i
NK064(ngu),002:6398: don la sems rtse gcig tu zin pa'i don gyi
NK064(ngu),002:6402: lha yi rnam par sbyor ba yis //
NK064(ngu),002:6403: zla ba rdo rje la sogs rim //
NK064(ngu),002:6404: bskyed pa'i rim pa zhes su grags //
NK064(ngu),002:6405: rang bzhin grub pa'i rnal 'byor che //
NK064(ngu),002:6406: rdzogs pa'i rim pa zhes byar brjod //
NK064(ngu),002:6408: kun brtags bskyed rim gyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6409: yongs grub rdzogs rim gyi rnal 'byor gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:6412: bskyed rim la brten skye gnas te //
NK064(ngu),002:6413: mngal skyes la sogs dbye ba yis //
NK064(ngu),002:6414: de yang rnam pa bzhi ru 'dod //
NK064(ngu),002:6415: ces pas skye gnas bzhi'i bag chags sbyong ba dang bstun te sgom tshul bzhi ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6417: skye gnas bzhi po dag bya'i phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:6418: bskyed pa'ang de bzhin rnam pa bzhi //
NK064(ngu),002:6419: spros bcas spros dang spros pa med //
NK064(ngu),002:6420: shin tu spros pa med bzhi'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6425: shin tu bsdus pa bardzusa skyes te //
NK064(ngu),002:6426: de ltar skye gnas bzhi'i bag chags sbyong ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:6427: spros pa rgyas pa dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bdag
NK064(ngu),002:6428: sras dang gzhan sras gnyis kyi sgo nas bsgom pa
NK064(ngu),002:6429: dang / gzhan yang mngon byang lnga bskyed dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6430: rdo rje'i cho ga bzhi bskyed la sogs pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6433: thugs phyag mtshan te cho ga gsum bskyed kyi sgo nas bskyed pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6434: bsdus pa a nu yo ga'i sgom tshul ltar sa bon tsam las bskyed pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6435: bskyed sngags brjod pa'i rkyen gyis bskyed pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6436: shin tu bsdus pa a ti yo ga'i sgom tshul
NK064(ngu),002:6437: ltar chu las nya ldang ba'i tshul du skad cig
NK064(ngu),002:6438: dran rdzogs kyis lha'i skur bskyed pa sgom tshul bzhi'o
NK064(ngu),002:6439: // rdzogs rim la steng sgo 'dzu 'dul dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6440: 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i man ngag la brten pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6441: grol lam zung 'jug gi rnal 'byor rim cig car
NK064(ngu),002:6442: gnyis kyis bsdus pa rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting
NK064(ngu),002:6443: nge 'dzin no // 'o na thabs lam steng 'og la /
NK064(ngu),002:6445: yab yum lhar bskyed pa sogs kun brtags bskyed rim
NK064(ngu),002:6446: gyi cha 'dres pas rdzogs rim du ci'i phyir 'gyur
NK064(ngu),002:6447: zhe na / bskyed rdzogs gnyis lam phan tshun gcig la gcig ltos can yin pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu),002:6448: thog mar kun brtags bskyed rim gyi nyams myong gtan la 'bebs pa la bkri ba tsam las /
NK064(ngu),002:6449: rang gi ngo bo rang bzhin lhan skyes kyi ye
NK064(ngu),002:6450: shes ngo sprod par byed pa'i thabs rnam par mi
NK064(ngu),002:6451: rtog pas bsdus pa yongs grub rdzogs rim du 'gyur
NK064(ngu),002:6452: ba yin pas skyon med do gsungs so //
NK064(ngu),002:6453: dgu pa mchod pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6456: bya byed bya ba byed 'dus pas //
NK064(ngu),002:6457: dgyes tshim gyur pa'i dngos po nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:6459: mchod pa'i yul du gyur pa rnams bkur zhing mchod
NK064(ngu),002:6460: pa'i bsam pas sgo gsum gyi mnyes pa sgrub pa
NK064(ngu),002:6461: dang / da lta yongs grags ltar spyi ming bye
NK064(ngu),002:6462: brag la btags pa yo byad stob pa'i sgo nas
NK064(ngu),002:6466: p+aurba ni sngon dang dza ta bskyed pa la 'jug pas /
NK064(ngu),002:6467: bya ba gang bsgrub pa rnams kyi sngon du 'gro
NK064(ngu),002:6468: ba'i rgyu mtshan gyis sngon du dgyes pa bskyed pa
NK064(ngu),002:6469: dang / p+aur+na p+aur+na ni yang dang yang /
NK064(ngu),002:6471: de'i sgra bsdus pas p+au dza zhes pa yang dang yang du dgyes pa bskyed pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6472: p+au dza'i sgra gzugs so so'i dbang du byas na
NK064(ngu),002:6473: bkur ba'i don gyi gnas su stob pa'i phyir mchod
NK064(ngu),002:6474: pa'o // dbye na spyir 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i mchod pa gnyis /
NK064(ngu),002:6475: de gnyis ka la mtshungs par dmigs yul zhing gi khyad par /
NK064(ngu),002:6476: 'bras bu la dmigs pa'i khyad par /
NK064(ngu),002:6477: yongs su bsngo ba'i khyad par /
NK064(ngu),002:6478: mchod rdzas dngos po'i khyad par dang bzhi las /
NK064(ngu),002:6480: bla ma dang dkon mchog sogs 'jig rten las 'das pa'i mchod yul /
NK064(ngu),002:6481: tshangs pa dang brgya byin sogs 'jig rten pa'i mchod yul lo //
NK064(ngu),002:6483: myang 'das kyi rgyur 'gyur ba thar pa cha mthun te 'das pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6484: 'di phyi'i bde 'bras kyi rgyur 'gyur ba bsod nams cha mthun te 'jig rten pa'i mchod pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6486: mchod pa de nyid myang 'das thob phyir bsngo ba 'das pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6487: 'di phyi'i bde 'bras kyi phyir bsngo ba 'jig rten pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6489: thos bsam sgom gsum la sogs pa 'das pa /
NK064(ngu),002:6490: zang zing gi dngos po la sogs pa 'jig rten pa'i 'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6491: 'on kyang spyi tsam du 'das ma 'das kyi khyad par de ltar dbye ba yin mod kyang /
NK064(ngu),002:6492: zhib tu phye na der ma nges te /
NK064(ngu),002:6493: dper na yul bla ma dang sangs rgyas lta bu zhig la /
NK064(ngu),002:6494: dngos po khyad par can thos bsam sgom gsum gyis mnyes pa sgrub pa lta bu zhig /
NK064(ngu),002:6497: yang na ngan song gi 'jigs pa las thar pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:6498: ched du bsngosa na bsod nams cha mthun yin pas
NK064(ngu),002:6500: yul dman pa srang mdor rgyu ba'i khyi lta bu zhig la /
NK064(ngu),002:6501: dngos po dman pa zan kham gcig tsam zhig sbyin
NK064(ngu),002:6502: pa de nyid 'khor gsum mi rtog pa'i shes rab
NK064(ngu),002:6503: kyis zin pa'i sgo nas sangs rgyas thob phyir du
NK064(ngu),002:6504: bsngosa na thar pa cha mthun te 'jig rten las
NK064(ngu),002:6509: gsang ba sbyor sgrol zab mo ste gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:6510: de la phyi nyer spyod ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6511: me tog bdug spos la sogs pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6512: de dang phyi mchod ces pa mdo sngags gnyis kar yod pa ma zad /
NK064(ngu),002:6513: 'jig rten du'ang rgyal po nas sprang po'i bar thams
NK064(ngu),002:6514: cad kyis nye bar spyad bya yin pas de ltar
NK064(ngu),002:6515: grags so // nang dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i mchod pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6516: bdud rtsi rak+ta la sogs pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6517: de ni mdo yi theg par ma zad sngags phyi
NK064(ngu),002:6518: pa la'ang med pa'i nang pa bla med kho na'i
NK064(ngu),002:6519: khyad chos so // gsang ba sbyor sgrol zab mo yang des mtshon no //
NK064(ngu),002:6520: skabs don nye bar 'brel ba zhi khro'i cho ga gzhung gi dbang du byas na /
NK064(ngu),002:6521: zhi ba la lhag ting dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6522: khro bo la de tshab rak+ta tshar gsum gyis byas
NK064(ngu),002:6523: pa'i gus pa phyag gi mchod pa la sogs bcu
NK064(ngu),002:6524: bzhi ste / sdoms su ston na /
NK064(ngu),002:6525: gus pa phyag dang phyag rgya gar //
NK064(ngu),002:6526: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol te //
NK064(ngu),002:6527: bdud rtsi gtor ma gsang bsnan dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6528: lhag pa ting 'dzin sgrol dang sbyor //
NK064(ngu),002:6529: 'dod yon rol mo glu ye shes //
NK064(ngu),002:6531: de la sogs te mchod pa'i rnam grangs ji snyed pa rnams so //
NK064(ngu),002:6532: bcu pa sngags dang phyag rgya la'ang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6535: yi ge 'dus pa grub pa bzhi //
NK064(ngu),002:6536: mthu can red pa gang yin pa //
NK064(ngu),002:6537: bzhi rdzogs nyid las mi 'da' ba //
NK064(ngu),002:6538: gang ba snang ba de ngo bo //
NK064(ngu),002:6539: zhes pas thabs shes kyi yi ge a li ka
NK064(ngu),002:6540: lir 'dus shing grub pa bzhis byin gyis brlabs pas
NK064(ngu),002:6541: nus pa mthu can du gyur pa ni sngags kyi
NK064(ngu),002:6542: ngo bo'o // grub pa bzhi ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6543: chos nyid ngo bo nyid kyis grub pa /
NK064(ngu),002:6544: chos can rang bzhin gyis grub pa /
NK064(ngu),002:6545: byin gyis brlabs kyis grub pa /
NK064(ngu),002:6547: rig pa phyag rgya bzhi rdzogs kyi lha yi skur
NK064(ngu),002:6548: gsal ba las mi 'da' ba ni phyag rgya'i ngo
NK064(ngu),002:6550: man+t+ra'i sgra las yid shes bde myur du skyob pa'i don gyis sngags te /
NK064(ngu),002:6551: de la bde ba'i sgo nas skyob pa'i don ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6553: 'dod pa'i longs spyod lnga po la //
NK064(ngu),002:6554: ci bde bar ni spyod pas 'grub //
NK064(ngu),002:6557: grangs med gsum la sogs pa'i tshogs gsog mi dgos par /
NK064(ngu),002:6558: thabs la mkhas pa'i stobs kyis tshe gcig gis sa lam rdzogs pa yod de /
NK064(ngu),002:6560: thabs chen rnams dang ldan pa la //
NK064(ngu),002:6561: nyon mongs byang chub yan lag 'gyur //
NK064(ngu),002:6564: bla med theg pa rab nges na //
NK064(ngu),002:6565: nyon mongs 'dod lnga kun spyad kyang //
NK064(ngu),002:6566: byas la mi gsog tshogs 'gyur te //
NK064(ngu),002:6567: tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum tshogs //
NK064(ngu),002:6570: mu dra'i sgra las 'debs shing mtshon par byed pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6571: phyag rgya bzhis rgyas btab pa las 'da' bar dka' ba'i phyir mtshan ma'i don gyis na phyag rgya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6573: sngags la gsang sngags rig sngags gzugs sngags dang gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:6575: thabs dang shes rab kyi bdag nyid de'i sgo yig
NK064(ngu),002:6576: 'brur snang ba gsang sngags te ngag tu rjod par
NK064(ngu),002:6577: byed pa'i las kyis log rtog gi gnyen por gyur
NK064(ngu),002:6579: shes rab dang ye shes kyi bdag nyid dngos po'i
NK064(ngu),002:6580: don rigs par byed pa'i las kyis ma rig pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:6583: dran pa dang shes rab kyi bdag nyid tshig don
NK064(ngu),002:6584: mi brjed par 'dzin pa'i las kyi dran nyams kyi
NK064(ngu),002:6586: de gsum mtshon pa'i rtags lhar snang tshul yang /
NK064(ngu),002:6587: gsang sngags rnams lha pho'i dbyibs dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6588: phyi ma gnyis lha mo'i gzugs su 'byung zhes 'byung ngo //
NK064(ngu),002:6589: bye brag tu gsal bkra las /
NK064(ngu),002:6590: rtsa ba bskyed dang las sngags dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6592: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i /
NK064(ngu),002:6594: bzlas pa las kyi sngags dang gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:6596: de dag rdzogs rim dang sbyar te bshad na /
NK064(ngu),002:6597: chos sku bde chen gyi thig le rang la rang
NK064(ngu),002:6598: chas su bzhugs pa rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:6599: sngags / de la gnad du bsnun pa'i thabs kyi byed rtsol ni bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags /
NK064(ngu),002:6600: de bzla zhing bsgoms pa bzlas pa las kyi sngags so //
NK064(ngu),002:6601: phyag rgya la'ang rtog tshogs thams cad gdod ma nas
NK064(ngu),002:6602: lha'i dkyil 'khor du gnas pa rang bzhin gyi phyag
NK064(ngu),002:6603: rgya / de'i don la shes rab kyi mig gis
NK064(ngu),002:6604: blta zhing sgro 'dogs gcod pa lta ba'i phyag rgya
NK064(ngu),002:6605: rgya / / rang 'bras ji lta ba bzhin mngon du gyur pa 'bras bu'i phyag rgya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6606: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6608: dam tshig las dang chos dang ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6609: sku ni phyag rgya chen po bzhi //
NK064(ngu),002:6610: zhes pas phyag rgya bzhi ldan te //
NK064(ngu),002:6611: nang gses su phye na bdun ldan du'ang 'gyur ba yin no //
NK064(ngu),002:6612: de la dbye na zhi khro gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:6615: de las 'byung ba'i rigs lnga'i dam rgya /
NK064(ngu),002:6616: de las 'phros pa lha so so'i phyag rgya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6619: dbu ni bde gshegs rnam snang nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:6620: lag g.yas rdo rje mi bskyod pa //
NK064(ngu),002:6621: lag g.yon rin chen sems dpa'i rigs //
NK064(ngu),002:6622: rkang g.yon chos kyi sems dpa' ste //
NK064(ngu),002:6623: rkang g.yas las kyi sems dapa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6625: yan lag lnga rigs lngar gsal ba'i nying lag gi
NK064(ngu),002:6626: g.yas kyi sor mo lnga la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu),002:6627: re re la rigs lnga yab lnga'i sa bon bkod
NK064(ngu),002:6628: / lag g.yon gyi sor mo lnga la zla ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:6629: dkyil 'khor lngar yum lnga'i sa bon bkod nas thal
NK064(ngu),002:6630: mo sbyar ba ni phyag rgya'i rgyu rdo rje'i thal
NK064(ngu),002:6633: mi bskyod rdo rje rtse lnga la //
NK064(ngu),002:6634: nyi ma'i thig le yi ge lnga //
NK064(ngu),002:6635: rat+na par bu'i nying lag la //
NK064(ngu),002:6636: zla ba'i thig le yi ge lnga //
NK064(ngu),002:6637: thig le thabs shes lnga nyid rnams //
NK064(ngu),002:6638: 'phrad pa'i dus na rang snang ba //
NK064(ngu),002:6639: phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub 'byung //
NK064(ngu),002:6642: +amo dang m+aum gnyis rtse sbyar te //
NK064(ngu),002:6643: 'bru brgyad bsnol nas rtse sprad pa //
NK064(ngu),002:6645: gsum pa de las 'phros pa lha so so'i phyag rgya ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6647: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK064(ngu),002:6648: h+aum sgreng rtse mor rdo rje 'bar //
NK064(ngu),002:6649: zhes pa la sogs pa rnams kyis bstan no //
NK064(ngu),002:6650: gnyis pa khro bo'i phyag rgya ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6651: rnam par grol ba mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK064(ngu),002:6652: dbus kyi khro bo'i phyag rgya ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6653: zhes sogs kyis khrag 'thung rigs lnga dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6656: dbang phyug rnams kyi phyag rgya rim bzhin /
NK064(ngu),002:6657: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6658: rgyud gzhan dag dang mthun par bshad //
NK064(ngu),002:6659: ma mo rnams kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6662: de dag kyang phyag rgya bzhi ldan te /
NK064(ngu),002:6663: lha yi skur gsal ba phyag chen /
NK064(ngu),002:6664: thugs kar rang rang gi sa bon bsam zhing ngag nas sngags tshig brjod pa chos rgya /
NK064(ngu),002:6665: phyag mtshan 'dzin pa'i phyag rgya bca' zhing bsam pa dam rgya /
NK064(ngu),002:6666: phyag rgya bcas nas mdun du bsgyur te dgrol ba las rgya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6667: de ltar yang he ru ka 'dus pa las /
NK064(ngu),002:6668: sku ni phyag rgya chen po dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6669: gsung ni chos kyi phyag rgya dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6670: thugs ni dam tshig phyag rgya dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6671: phrin las las kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6673: bzhi pa rgyud kyi dgos 'brel la'ang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6676: brjod 'brel dgos pa yang dgos dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6677: rgyu rkyen yan lag bzhi ru 'gyur //
NK064(ngu),002:6678: zhes pas dgos sogs chos bzhi las /
NK064(ngu),002:6679: mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud gnas lugs de bzhin nyid ni brjod bya ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6681: mtshon bya rang bzhin gzhi yi rgyud //
NK064(ngu),002:6683: de khong du chud par bya ba'i phyir mtshon byed
NK064(ngu),002:6684: lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud sgrar snang zhing sgrar grags
NK064(ngu),002:6685: pa sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud ni rjod byed de
NK064(ngu),002:6687: sgro skur med pa bstan pa ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6688: mtshon byed sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste //
NK064(ngu),002:6690: rjod byed la brten nas brjod bya'i don go ba ni dgos pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6692: mdzub mos ri bong can bzhin no //
NK064(ngu),002:6694: de ltar shes nas bskyed rdzogs kyi don nyams su
NK064(ngu),002:6695: blangs pas nying dgos phra mo thun mong gi dngos
NK064(ngu),002:6696: grub dang / nying dgos mchog slob pa dang mi
NK064(ngu),002:6697: slob pa'i zung 'jug rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go
NK064(ngu),002:6700: dgos pa'i dgos pa 'bras bu nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:6703: shugs la bstan pas go sla'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6705: ci'i phyir rgyud kyi dgos 'brel zhes bya zhe na /
NK064(ngu),002:6706: de ltar dgos sogs chos bzhi po de ni phan tshun 'brel ba can du grub pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu),002:6707: thob bya mthar thug gi 'bras bu sgrub pa la
NK064(ngu),002:6708: med na mi 'byung gi 'brel bar grub pa'i phyir
NK064(ngu),002:6710: grol lam dbang btsan du byas pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6711: thabs lam dbang btsan du byas pa gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:6713: sngar ngo bo'i skabs su bshad pa ltar yin la /
NK064(ngu),002:6715: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes gdod ma nas rang
NK064(ngu),002:6716: la rang chas su bzhugs pa ni mtshon bya rang
NK064(ngu),002:6718: de nyid rtogs byed kyi man ngag thig le chen
NK064(ngu),002:6719: po thabs dang bcas pa ni mtshon byed lam rkyen
NK064(ngu),002:6721: de'i don nyams su blangs pas bde chen gyi ye
NK064(ngu),002:6722: shes khyad par can rgyud la skyes pa ni dgos
NK064(ngu),002:6723: pa'o // de la goms par byas pas mchog tu
NK064(ngu),002:6724: mi 'gyur ba'i ye shes chen po mngon du byas
NK064(ngu),002:6726: lnga pa 'khor la gdams shing bstan pa gtad pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6728: bstan pa'i snying po rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po
NK064(ngu),002:6729: mtshon byed lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud dang bcas pa
NK064(ngu),002:6730: 'di nyid mi nyams shing bsrung ba'i ched du 'khor
NK064(ngu),002:6731: rnams la gdams shing gtad pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6733: rang bzhin gzhi'i rgyud kyi don las mi 'gyur bar gdams pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6734: lam gyi rgyud de gzhi rtogs byed kyi thabs su
NK064(ngu),002:6735: mi nub par zungs shig ces gtad pa'ang yin pa'i
NK064(ngu),002:6736: phyir na gdams gtad ces bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6739: gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba rtogs byar gdams pa /
NK064(ngu),002:6740: log rtog 'khrul pa'i snang ba dag byar gdams pa /
NK064(ngu),002:6741: gdul bya lam gyi snang ba bsgrod byar gdams pa /
NK064(ngu),002:6742: 'bras bu bde gshegs kyi snang ba thob byar gdams pa rnams rim bzhin ston pa ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6744: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin 'di //
NK064(ngu),002:6745: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK064(ngu),002:6748: rnam rtog zhags pas so sor 'dzin //
NK064(ngu),002:6750: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK064(ngu),002:6751: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK064(ngu),002:6753: ye shes ngo mtshar rab 'byams kyis //
NK064(ngu),002:6754: don du mi 'gyur yongs ma gsungs //
NK064(ngu),002:6755: zhes pa rnams kyis bstan to //
NK064(ngu),002:6758: sdud pa po dang bud med dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6761: dang po sdud pa po la gtad pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6762: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bka' yi bsdu
NK064(ngu),002:6763: ba po gsang ba'i bdag po lag na rdo rje
NK064(ngu),002:6766: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK064(ngu),002:6767: gsang ba 'di las gzhan mi mnga' //
NK064(ngu),002:6768: sgro dang skur ba zhi ba yi //
NK064(ngu),002:6769: gsang ba snying po de kho na //
NK064(ngu),002:6770: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas phyung //
NK064(ngu),002:6772: gnyis pa phyi rabs kyi gang zag la gtad pa la gnyis las /
NK064(ngu),002:6773: gang zag chos mig can la gtad pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6774: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK064(ngu),002:6775: phyag rgya gsang chen nges pa 'di //
NK064(ngu),002:6776: rtogs nas smra bar gang byed pa //
NK064(ngu),002:6777: de nyid nga yin dbang yang rdzogs //
NK064(ngu),002:6779: gnyis pa nges par lung bstan pa'i sgo nas gtad pa ni 'thad pa dang bcas pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6781: de ni nges par lung bstan te //
NK064(ngu),002:6782: sras ni thugs las skyes pa yin //
NK064(ngu),002:6783: sa rab rig pa 'dzin la gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:6785: gsum pa ma mo dang mkha' 'gro ma rnams la gtad pa ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6787: nga yi thugs kyi snying po 'di //
NK064(ngu),002:6788: phyogs bcu kun tu spel ba dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6789: de yi gzungs la gtad pa ni //
NK064(ngu),002:6790: yid bzhin mdzod 'byor bka' yi gnas //
NK064(ngu),002:6791: bstan pa 'dzin par nus pa la //
NK064(ngu),002:6792: gsang ba'i snying po mchog tu gtad //
NK064(ngu),002:6793: ces ma mo dang mkha' 'gro rnams la bstan pa skyong zhing phyogs bcur spel bar gnyer gtad pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6794: gnyis pa tshig gi rnam grangs rnam par dbye ba la gsum las /
NK064(ngu),002:6797: gang gi brjod bya 'chad byed pa //
NK064(ngu),002:6798: de nas rjod byed du bshad do //
NK064(ngu),002:6800: brjod bya 'chad par byed pa ni rjod byed kyi rgyud de /
NK064(ngu),002:6801: sgrar snang zhing sgrar grags pa'i mtshan nyid can sgra
NK064(ngu),002:6802: yi rgyud dam glegs bam du snang ba yi ge'i
NK064(ngu),002:6803: rgyud du grags pa gang yin pa'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6804: de yang ngo bo tshogs pa gsum ldan te /
NK064(ngu),002:6805: gdung 'degs kyi shing la ka ba zhes 'dogs pa
NK064(ngu),002:6806: lta bu chos gang la sgra gang zhig de nyid
NK064(ngu),002:6807: yin pa lta bur btags nas brjod pa ni ming
NK064(ngu),002:6808: yin la / ming de mang po 'dus pa ni ming gi tshogs te /
NK064(ngu),002:6809: mngon brjod kyi bstan bcos lta bu'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6810: ming de nyid yan du ma bcug par dang po ngo bo tsam ston pa /
NK064(ngu),002:6811: gnyis pa las dang bya ba la sogs pa rnam
NK064(ngu),002:6812: dbye rnams kyi bye brag so sor phye nas chos
NK064(ngu),002:6813: dang de'i don gyi khyad par ston pa ni tshig
NK064(ngu),002:6814: yin te / rta babs kyi steng na chos 'khor
NK064(ngu),002:6815: gdugs dang bcas pa'i g.yas g.yon na ri dwags pho
NK064(ngu),002:6816: mos brten pa zhes pa lta bu'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6817: ming tshig de gsal bar byed pa'i 'bru la ni yi ge zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu),002:6818: de ltar yi ge 'dus pa las ming /
NK064(ngu),002:6820: de 'dus pa las tshigs su bcad pa dang spel
NK064(ngu),002:6821: ma la sogs te gzhung tshogs yi ge'i rgyud grub
NK064(ngu),002:6823: yi ge sgra btags ming tshogs las //
NK064(ngu),002:6824: brten pa'i tshig gi rab mtshon te //
NK064(ngu),002:6827: ci'i phyir sgra'i rgyud ces bya zhe na /
NK064(ngu),002:6828: brjod bya'i don de nyid rtogs byed kyi thabs rjod
NK064(ngu),002:6829: byed kyi sgrar snang zhing sgrar grags pa'i don gyis
NK064(ngu),002:6830: na sgra dang tshigs su bcad pa sogs gzhung gi
NK064(ngu),002:6832: gleng gzhi la sogs pa lnga rgyu rkyen 'bras bu'i tshul du 'brel bas na rgyud do //
NK064(ngu),002:6833: gzhan du na brjod bya la rgyud kyi ming thob pas rjod byed la'ang rgyud ces btags so //
NK064(ngu),002:6835: rtsa ba'i rgyud 'chad gzhir gyur pa dang /
NK064(ngu),002:6836: 'chad byed du gyur pa bshad pa'i rgyud gnyis so //
NK064(ngu),002:6837: rtsa ba'i rgyud nyid la'ang tshig gi tshogs pa le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis su bcad de gnas la /
NK064(ngu),002:6838: de yang le'u dang pos longs sku'i gleng gzhi /
NK064(ngu),002:6839: gsum pas stod kyis sprul sku 'gro 'dul gyi gleng gzhi /
NK064(ngu),002:6840: bco lnga pas khro bo'i gleng gzhi ste /
NK064(ngu),002:6841: de rnams kyis rgyu gleng gzhi'i rnam bzhag bstan /
NK064(ngu),002:6842: le'u gnyis pas rkyen gleng bslang ba /
NK064(ngu),002:6843: le'u gsum pa'i smad nas nyer gcig pa yan chad
NK064(ngu),002:6844: kyis 'bras bu yongs shes rgyud don de dag la
NK064(ngu),002:6846: le'u tha mas gdams gtad rnams ston cing /
NK064(ngu),002:6847: yongs su shes par bya ba rgyud don la'ang rgyud kyi dngos po bcu'i ston tshul ni /
NK064(ngu),002:6848: le'u gsum pa'i smad dang bcu gcig pa'i dbur lta
NK064(ngu),002:6849: ba gtan la 'bebs tshul bstan pa sogs le'u du
NK064(ngu),002:6850: ma nas dum cha dum chas dang po lta ba'i
NK064(ngu),002:6851: rnam bzhag ston pa la sogs te le'u gang dang
NK064(ngu),002:6852: gang gis rgyud kyi dngos po bcu ji ltar ston
NK064(ngu),002:6853: tshul gtso che chung gi sgo nas gzhung nyid la
NK064(ngu),002:6854: zhib mor dpyad pas shes par 'gyur zhing /
NK064(ngu),002:6855: zhi khro spyi bye brag gi chos rnams le'u gang dang gang gis ston tshul yang /
NK064(ngu),002:6856: zhi ba ston pa'i le'u dgu /
NK064(ngu),002:6857: khro bo ston pa'i le'u lnga /
NK064(ngu),002:6858: zhi khro thun mong du bstan pa'i le'u brgyad de /
NK064(ngu),002:6859: de dag gi tshul blo gros dang ldan pas spro na zhib tu bsnyad pas chog go //
NK064(ngu),002:6861: dpal ldan gsang ba snying po'i rgyud don gnad //
NK064(ngu),002:6862: bla ma'i zhal gsung bdud rtsi'i nying khu 'di //
NK064(ngu),002:6863: bdag blo'i snying gi yol gor cha shas tsam //
NK064(ngu),002:6864: 'khyil ba brjed par phangs nas yi ger bkod //
NK064(ngu),002:6865: deng sang 'di la su zhig dga' ba skye //
NK064(ngu),002:6866: de bas zang zing bre gang tsam gyis mgu //
NK064(ngu),002:6867: 'on kyang ma 'ongs chos mig can rnams dang //
NK064(ngu),002:6868: rigs sad lam 'dir 'jug 'dod skyes bu la //
NK064(ngu),002:6869: phan pa'i phyir dang gter chen bla ma yi //
NK064(ngu),002:6870: lung rtogs bstan la bya ba byas sam snyam //
NK064(ngu),002:6871: de ltar bkod pa'i dge bas 'gro ba kun //
NK064(ngu),002:6872: kun kyang rgyud don bdud rtsi'i nying khu la //
NK064(ngu),002:6873: kun tu spyod pa'i skal bzang dga' ston gyis //
NK064(ngu),002:6874: kun mkhyen go 'phang myur du thob par shog /
NK064(ngu),002:6875: ces pa 'di yang gnam sa'i dbang phyug chos kyi
NK064(ngu),002:6876: rgyal po chen po mi dbang 'gyur med bsod nams
NK064(ngu),002:6877: stobs rgyal gyi dbu yi bla mchod du bzhugs pa
NK064(ngu),002:6878: lugs gnyis la mnga' dbang 'byor ba'i grub pa'i dbang
NK064(ngu),002:6879: phyug mnga' bdag rig 'dzin rgya mtsho'i gsung gis yang
NK064(ngu),002:6880: yang bskul zhing bri gzhi'i rkyen sbyar ba dang bcas
NK064(ngu),002:6881: pas / lugs 'di la don gyi slad du mtshan
NK064(ngu),002:6882: nas smos na bdag gi mkhan po ngag dbang chos
NK064(ngu),002:6883: dpal rgya mtsho'i drung du rgyud kyi bshad pa lo
NK064(ngu),002:6884: bcu gnyis kyi bar du lo rer tshar gnyis re
NK064(ngu),002:6885: pas / dang / de rjes nas kyang lo shas
NK064(ngu),002:6886: nod pa cung zad blo yul du bcag pa smin
NK064(ngu),002:6887: gling grwa ba'i tha shal ba sh+aakya'i dge slong o
NK064(ngu),002:6888: rgyan chos grags kyis rang lo nga lnga pa lcags
NK064(ngu),002:6889: khyi hor zla bzhi pa bdag cag gi ston pa
NK064(ngu),002:6890: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i dus chen sa
NK064(ngu),002:6891: ga zla ba'i tshes bco lnga la rang gi grwa
NK064(ngu),002:6892: khang du rdzogs par bgyis pa dge legs su gyur
NK064(ngu),002:6893: pas / dang / cig / 'dis kyang bstan pa
NK064(ngu),002:6894: rin po che phyogs dus kun tu dar zhing rgyas
NK064(ngu),002:6895: la yun ring du gnas pa'i rgyur gyur cig //
